(1, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '1~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(2, 'Key Lime Pie Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you pop a piece of key lime pie candy into your mouth, your taste buds will burst with citrus sweetness. It\'s like taking a trip to the beautiful, balmy Florida Keys without even leaving your home or office. These delicious green and white hard candies are perfect for any occasion, whether you want a refreshing tropical taste on a hot summer day or you want to remind yourself of the beach in the middle of winter.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', '2~key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', 'key-lime-pie-hard-candy'),
(3, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '3~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(4, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '4~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(5, 'chocolate starlight mints thumbnail', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Chocolate starlight mints are a new and amazing take on a classic candy. Everyone loves the refreshing flavor of the traditional hard mint, now add chocolate.Starlight mints, which are also sometimes called pinwheel mints, feature a lovely white background with bold red stripes. Our chocolate starlight mints take that same elegant pattern and use it on a dark background with brilliant green stripes instead.Now you can enjoy that delicious minty taste with a touch of savory chocolate. Each round mint is crafted using solid hard candy. This allows them to provide the flavor candy lovers adore in a long lasting treat. Each mint is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can admire their dark beauty before you open the first one up!Pour them into glass jars or candy dishes and serve to guests, use them in the office candy jar or make your gingerbread houses more unique with these tasty decorations!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', '5~chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', 'chocolate-starlight-mints'),
(6, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Don\'t bite down on one of these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers! These hard candies are great for savoring a ton of sweetness for a long time.Buy a bulk bag of Jaw Busters hard candies for the little ghouls and goblins coming around the neighborhood on Halloween, or keep them around when you\'re craving something sweet for yourself. You can keep a bag of Jawbreakers in a wide assortment of colors and flavors all year long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', '6~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-wrapped'),
(7, 'Bulk Assorted Fruit Lollipops', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Lollipop, lollipop, oh lolli , lolli, lolli  Sorry, we\'re getting carried away with ourselves. It happens a lot here. It\'s just that we\'re so passionate about these scrumptious suckers that it makes us break out in song. They don\'t require a trip to the doctor and they come in bulk, so these pops are the perfect choice for any occasion. Stock up for your child\'s next party or put them in a jar on your desk for lucky coworkers to snack on. You\'ll quickly become a favorite in the office! With a light, sweet, fruity flavor, in a rainbow of colors, everyone can enjoy a mouthful of deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', '7~lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'lollipops-bulk-fruit'),
(8, 'Sour Fruit Balls Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Sour. Check. Colorful. Check. Fruity and delicious. Check, check! We\'ve got everything you need here for the makings of a great bulk candy selection.  Individually wrapped, these candies make tasty treats for parties, as filler candy, or just to have around the house for a qick fix of sweetness.With over 80 hard candies per pound, there\'s enough sweetness to treat all of your friends and family. Every time you snack from this bag, choose from yummy red, orange, yellow, green, and purple. Everyone who hears the crinkle of their wrappers will come running for more. And because of their perfect size, one after another can be enjoyed.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', '8~sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', 'sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy'),
(9, 'Andes Mints', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Ande\'s mints make the perfect welcome snack for any home, office, or restaurant. Whether your guests want to freshen their breath after they\'ve had a meal, or you\'d just like to make them feel at home with something sweet, these are the treats for you. A perfect blend of creamy milk chocolate and mint filling make these tiny sandwiches of sweetness the perfect refreshment, and they\'re individually wrapped, so there\'s no danger of spreading anyone\'s germs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', '9~andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', 'andes-mints'),
(10, 'Butterscotch Buttons Candy', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'These candies are cute as a button! Maybe that\'s because these Butterscotch Candy Buttons come in beautiful, individually wrapped gold wrappers and are a lovely bright yellow color that candy fans love. Around since the 1800s, butterscotch has built up a tasty reputation throughout the decades and continues to please candy lovers near and far. Try these little, rich sweets out for your next candy buffet bar, crush them and sprinkle them on top of cookies and baked goods for a sweet surprise, or even fill your candy dishes for an olde timey feel every snacker can enjoy. These hard candies are sure to \'\'butter you up\'\' with their irresistible flavor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', '10~butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'butterscotch-buttons'),
(11, 'Sunkist Fruit Gems', 69.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a big, sugary smooch with these Sunkist Fruit Gems! Their delicious, gummy chew and bright, fruity flavor will make you want to pucker up for more every time you take a bite. Individually wrapped, these little gummies pack the power of the sun into every chew and show off the beautiful colors of the rainbow.Stock yourself up with some rainy day sunshine with a bag of these. They\'re a great goodie bag stuffer for birthday parties, look lovely at a summertime picnic on the dessert table, and even can be kept to cheer up your little ones on a rainy day. With 42 pieces per pound, there are enough to please every gummy fan!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', '11~sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk'),
(12, 'Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get your candy fix with our Tootsie Rolls midgees candy! Tootsie Roll is one of the oldest treats in the United States. This confection was invented in 1986 when Leo Hirshfield decided to open up a shop in New York City.Today, kids and adults love the chewy texture and chocolaty taste that makes these popular confections so irresistible. They\'re not quite taffy and not quite caramel but very smooth, making snack time even sweeter! Bulk Tootsie Rolls give you more pieces for snacking, parties and sharing.Every roll is individually wrapped in that familiar brown, red and white paper. That allows the candy to remain fresh and ready to enjoy. Take a handful with you as a quick treat on a busy day or use them as an easy after school snack for the kids. Tootsie Rolls also make great treat bag filler for birthday parties, picnics, holiday events and other gatherings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', '12~tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-midgees'),
(13, 'Peppermint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '6', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peppermint Starlight mints make the perfect complimentary candy for almost any occasion, event, or environment. Are you considering putting a candy dish by the door at home? Do you run a restaurant where customers pay at a counter near the front? These Starlight mint hard candies are recognized all over the world as a true classic. They\'ll satisfy your sweet tooth and freshen your breath, too. Put some of these individually wrapped treats out in your home, office, or restaurant today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', '13~peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', 'starlight-mints-peppermint'),
(14, 'Jumbo Mint Balls Hard Candy', 11.49, '120', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'Make way for a big dose of peppermint flavor! These Jumbo Mint Balls are a sphere full of refreshing minty flavor that your mouth will love. Their beautiful red and white swirls make them the perfect sweet addition to a Christmas candy display, gingerbread house making with your family, a beach party (since these little balls resemble beach balls!), and even a Fourth of July event. With 12 of these flavorful candy balls in every order, there\'s enough to do it all. Use your imagination to decide how you and your close family and friends can enjoy these tasty mints.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', '14~jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', 'jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls'),
(15, 'Peanut Butter Bars', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peanut butter bars candy brings you all the best parts of peanuts without all the bad stuff. Each bar includes high quality peanuts that are slow roasted until they become gold brown to bring out the natural nutty flavor. Each bite is truly an experience, with the crispy, flaky crunch that everyone loves. If you are a peanut butter fanatic, then this bar candy is your dream come true!Every peanut butter bar is individually wrapped so it\'s easy to store and share. Each includes a simple white wrapper with black stripes, gold star and a classic logo that gives each piece a nostalgic look. Keep a handful in your purse or pocket or use the in favor bags for parties and holiday events. Each tasty tidbit is packed with all the rich peanut flavor you can handle in a convenient package that you can take anywhere! Our bulk candy packs are great for school events, businesses and carnivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', '15~peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', 'peanut-butter-bars'),
(16, 'Bit O Honey Candy', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Buzzzzzz. These Bit-O-Honey Candies are brimming with the sweet, creamy sugar of an entire hive! That\'s because each delightful candy is made with sweet, honey flavored taffy and complete with soft almond pieces inside. Individually wrapped, these delectable morsels can be enjoyed one, two, or three at a time! They make a perfect addition to a classic candy display, set out on a coffee table for sweet snacking, or packed into a pinata for birthday parties. Treat your busy bees to a sweet treat with a bag of these. Try these out for yourself and see what all the \'\'buzz\'\' is about with an order of these tasty treats!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/i/bit-o-honey-candy-candystore-470x470.jpg', '16~bit-o-honey-candy-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'bit-o-honey-pieces'),
(17, 'Tootsie Fruit Rolls Fruit Chews', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Let us get this straight. The classic Tootsie Roll chew that we love comes in a delicious fruity taste, too? We\'ll take it! Try these Fruit Tootsie Rolls and enjoy a whole new taste with this classic candy. Yellow is lemon, blue is vanilla, red is cherry, green is lime, and orange is...orange. Discover a whole new way to love this classic brand.Since 1896, Tootsie has been producing delectable candies that the world has grown to love. With 65 pieces per pound and a bulk bag of these, there\'s nothing tiny about the amount of delectable Tootsie Fruit Chews Rolls you\'ll get to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruit-chews-tootsie-rolls-470x470_2.jpg', '17~fruit-chews-tootsie-rolls-470x470_2.jpg', 'fruit-tootsie-rolls'),
(18, 'Peppermint Twists Mints', 19.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peppermint twists pack all of the flavor of a candy cane into a single bite-sized candy. Just seeing and tasting them will put you in the holiday spirit, no matter what time of year it is. Don\'t miss out on delicious peppermint candies all year round. Get a bag of these individually wrapped peppermint twists and liven up your home or your office. No special occasion is necessary to bring out these delicious peppermint candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', '18~peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'peppermint-twists'),
(19, 'Spearmint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'A classic concept with a colorful twist. Try our Spearmint Starlight Mints as a complementary addition to your traditional red and white peppermints. Their cool, sharp spearmint flavor in addition to their lovely green and white coloring contrasts to make them a lovely and refreshing selection for any candy bowl. Make your holiday gingerbread house extra special with these green and white mints. Or stash some in your purse for a sweet, minty treat. We can\'t deny the holiday cheer these mints give us and we hope that they will inspire the same, bright happiness in everyone you share them with.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', '19~spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', 'spearmint-starlight-mints'),
(20, 'Mary Jane Candy', 20.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you\'re in the mood for something extra chewy, try our sweet Mary Jane candies! These delectable delights are small bars of smooth taffy treats. Each is flavored with rich molasses and peanut butter to give it that memorable taste that kids of all ages have been asking for since 1914. The candy is a historic favorite that was named after its creator\'s beloved aunt â€“ a worthy choice for such a nostalgic confection!Each taffy candy is covered in a bright yellow wrapper with a bold red stripe and classic logo printed around both sides. You\'ll love Mary Janes even more when you buy our bulk candy package! Order larger quantities so you have plenty to share at family gatherings and other events. Use them to fill the office candy jar or use them to fill treat bags for birthdays and more! Our bulk Mary Janes are also convenient to hand out on trick or treat night around Halloween!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', '20~mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'mary-janes-candy'),
(21, 'Bulk Candy Mix', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Having a candy buffet and need the perfect mix to kick off the table.  You have found the perfect product with our bulk candy mix in a five pound bag.  We have included some of our all time favorites in this mix.  Assorted Salt Water taffy is always the perfect start.  Individually wrapped Starbursts are a fan favorite in our office.  Tootsie roll fruit help make the mix really stand out and to top it all off it includes assorted Jolly Rancher Hard CandyWhether for a party or your candy jar in the office or home this mix will be a hit with everyone!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulk_candy_mix_candystore.jpg', '21~bulk_candy_mix_candystore.jpg', 'bulk-candy-mix'),
(22, 'Assorted Fruit Starlight Mints', 18.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Our starlight mints are now available with amazing fruit flavors! If you love the smooth texture and fun pinwheel pattern of the classic starlight candy, then you\'ll love these vibrant treats! Each piece features the same look with a color that matches its unique fruity taste. Our bulk fruit starlight mints include an assortment of orange, lime, lemon and cherry. Pour some into a glass candy bowl for guests or share with family at home. Everyone will find a flavor they love!Pinwheel mints are also a fun part of the holidays. If you want to change things up, combine the traditional starlight mint with our fruit candies. These also make great favor bag treats for weddings, birthday parties and other events. With our enormous bulk mint pack, it\'s easy to get all the pieces you need for any occasion. Grab a handful of our assorted fruit starlight mints and share the sweetness!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/starlights-mints-assorted-fruit-5lb_1.jpg', '22~starlights-mints-assorted-fruit-5lb_1.jpg', 'starlights-mints-assorted-fruit'),
(23, 'Tootsie Rolls Fruit Chews', 96.99, '30', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Our little Tootsie Rolls fruit chews candies may be small in size, but they offer enormous amounts of flavor in every smooth piece. If you love chewy candy, then this is a must-have treat. Each package contains an assortment of Tootsie Roll\'s finest flavors in an array of brilliant colors. Sample a bright yellow lemon candy or a green lime piece. Our assortment also includes blue vanilla rolls, red cherry rolls and orange rolls - which come in orange, of course! Children and adults will love carefully untwisting each wrapper and trying the delectable tube shaped treat hidden inside! Our bulk candy assortment is perfect for parties, picnics, school events and any gathering that you want to sweeten. You can also purchase bulk Tootsie Fruit Rolls Chews candy to keep at home so you always have an easy go-to snack or dessert to put in school lunches for the kids. Sink your teeth into the soft, chewy confection that comes in your favorite flavors! Order today and find out why our Tootsie Rolls Fruit Chews fruit candy are so irresistible!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruit-tootsie-rolls-bulk-30lb_2.jpg', '23~fruit-tootsie-rolls-bulk-30lb_2.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-fruit-bulk-case'),
(24, 'Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candy', 96.99, '30', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'What\'s tiny, delicious, and chocolatey all over? Our Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candies! These bite-size treats are the perfect snack for any day of the week. They also make a delicious addition to any candy buffet bar, trick-or-treating candy bucket, or even as wedding or pinata candy. Individually wrapped, you can enjoy these classic candies in miniature form at your own leisure. Since 1896, Tootsie has been producing delectable candies that the world has grown to love. With 65 pieces per pound, there\'s nothing tiny about the amount of delectable morsels you\'ll get to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-rolls-midgees-470x470_1.jpg', '24~tootsie-rolls-midgees-470x470_1.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-midgees-bulk'),
(25, 'Chick O Stick Box', 11.99, '36', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'This big Chick-O-Stick Box is calling your name if you love crunchy, flakey, savory peanut butter. A classic candy,, this inventive and different confection is full of flavor and texture your mouth and mind will enjoy.With individually wrapped sticks, you\'ll be able to devour one at a time, pack some into a lunch box for a delightful surprise, add some to gift baskets or Christmas stockings or unwrap them and use them as utensils for eating ice cream! Use your imagination and go with your gut to come up with ways of how you can eat these Chick-O-Stick Box candies. No matter what you choose, we know you\'ll love munching and crunching on them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chick-o-stickbox36ct.jpg', '25~chick-o-stickbox36ct.jpg', 'chick-o-stick-box'),
(26, 'Chick O Stick Nuggets Candy', 21.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Remember Chick-O-Sticks? Those delicious peanut butter candies with the coconut twist are back and better than ever. Now, instead of buying a full-sized Chick-O-Stick, you can get a bag of Chick-O-Sticks nuggets that will satisfy your sweet and savory cravings. Each nugget is about an inch long, the perfect size to just pop in your mouth and enjoy the sweet tastes while you go about your day. Pick up a big bulk bag today and start nibbling on one of your favorite candies again.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chick-o-stick-nuggets-candystore-470x470.jpg', '26~chick-o-stick-nuggets-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'chick-o-sticks-nuggets'),
(27, 'Blue Foil Grape Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'These little candies contain a whole lot of flavor. They are blue in color and the wrappers that are used for them are blue as well. However, the flavor that you get from these candies is a pleasant grape flavor. This is a flavor that can be enjoyed by people of all ages and that makes it great for nearly any occasion. Since they are blue you could consider using them for a baby shower if you wanted to as well. These candies are sure to be a hit. They are hard candies and you can either suck on them or crunch on them when eating them which is great for those who like the way that hard candies feel in their mouths when they bit them. They come in a bulk bag which means that there will be plenty to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '27~blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy'),
(28, 'Laffy Taffy Candy', 37.99, '8.5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Laffy Taffy is such a well-recognized candy that hip-hop artist D4L has immortalized its name in song. You don\'t have to be a fan of rap to enjoy these chewy soft candies, though. Each individually wrapped Laffy Taffy candy comes with a joke written on the wrapper for you to share with your friends. You\'ll laugh with your friends as you satisfy your sweet tooth for this delicious taffy candy. They\'re so good, though, that you might want to share the jokes, but you won\'t ever want to share the candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', '28~laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-pieces-bulk'),
(29, 'Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'All kids are looking for sunshine, happiness and rainbows in their lives and when they are given Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy the sunshine is just a shiny wrapper away. It is the wrapper that first draws your attention. Who doesn\'t like a shiny present? It will be exactly like Christmas morning as you hold one of these lemony treats in your hand and start to unwrap it. As the wrapper is opened it will reveal a bright yellow hard candy treat like you dream about right in your hand. You might have wondered what sunshine tastes like, but once you try one of the Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candies you will be pretty sure that it tastes a lot like lemon. With a convenient bulk bag of treats there will be enough sunshine to share with a whole office or classroom or people. People can\'t help but smile and be in a good mood when they eat this delicious treat. This makes it a natural for wedding receptions as all people want to start their new lives with a whole lot of smiles and sunshine.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', '29~silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', 'silver-foil-lemon-hard-candy'),
(30, 'Chocolate Bulk Candy Mix', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get all the chocolaty goodness you can handle in this bulk candy mix! Our chocolate assortment includes a generous quantity of confections. Thereâ€™s Reeceâ€™s Pieces, mini Hershey bars, Starburst, Jolly Ranchers and assorted taffy. Each piece is individually wrapped so it stays fresh and delicious. Grab a handful and get the perfect mix of chewy and sweet for snack time or special occasions!This practical chocolate bulk candy mix is perfect for events and special occasions. Use them to get a variety of candy for treat bags or party favors. Just toss a handful in a favor box or bag and you have a gift your guests will enjoy! Keep a package in your pantry so your candy dish never goes empty or use to fill up the candy jar at work. Chocolate and taffy makes a tasty snack thatâ€™s easy to pack in lunches or in your purse or pocket!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', '30~candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', 'bulk-chocolate-candy-mix'),
(31, 'Jumbo Spearmint Balls Candy', 11.49, '120', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'Green, white, and minty. These Jumbo Spearmint Balls Candy are a delicious mint that your whole family will love. Take your gingerbread house building to the next level with a handful of these minty wonders, make a Christmas candy display even prettier and more delicious, or even stick a few in your purse to enjoy a breath freshening treat whenever you wish. The bright green and white swirls are beautiful to look at and offer a refreshing burst of spearmint flavor that your mouth will crave. With 120 pieces per order, you\'ll have enough tasty mints to satisfy a crowd.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/jumbo-spearmint-balls-candy-120ct_1.jpg', '31~jumbo-spearmint-balls-candy-120ct_1.jpg', 'jumbo-spearmint-balls'),
(32, 'Fun Size M&Ms Milk Chocolate', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get the party started with these Fun Size Packs of M&Ms;! Great for Halloween trick-or-treating, birthday parties, or just to enjoy as a perfectly portioned snack, this bulk bag is ready to add some delicious flavor to your life and those you share them with.Get your bag today to add some extra deliciousness and magic into your every day snacking. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsize_m_ms.jpg', '32~funsize_m_ms.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-milk-chocolate'),
(33, 'Atomic Fireballs', 74.99, '25', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Five, four, three, two, one. Prepare for total taste bud annihilation! These atomic fireballs may be small, but don\'t let their unassuming size fool you. Their explosive shell and spicy interior bring the heat of a five alarm fire.With about 50 blazing pieces per pound, there\'s enough candy here to nuke your mouth into oblivion and back again. But if you can summon the courage to put out the blaze, you\'ll be treated to a mild, sweet cinnamon finish that will be well worth the challenge. Just beware. Only the strong mouthed will survive to beat this atomic heat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/t/atomic-fireballs-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', '33~atomic-fireballs-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', 'atomic-fireballs-wrapped-bulk'),
(34, 'Blue Wrapped Mini Mints', 6.99, '2.2', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'They may be small, but these Mini Mints are big on refreshing flavor! With a big bag of tiny morsels wrapped individually in blue and white foil, they\'re ready to freshen your mouth with every bite.Stock up on some Mini Mints for dinner parties, weddings and any occasion that calls for a palate cleanser that is both minty and delicious. You can stock your candy dishes around the house, serve some of these alongside coffee and tea after dessert or stuff some into your purse or office desk for when you need a breath freshener and something sweet to indulge in. Mini Mints can do it all and more in this bulk supply!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mini_mints_-_2.2lb.jpg', '34~mini_mints_-_2.2lb.jpg', 'blue-wrapped-mini-mints'),
(35, 'Skittles Fun Size Bulk', 99.99, '22', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'A color and flavor for every taste bud. Pack these fun size Skittles into a pinata, add them to a stocking, or slip one into your kid\'s lunchbox for a delicious afternoon surprise. Whatever you choose, everyone will love to \'\'Taste the Rainbow.\'\' Skittles have been in the US since 1979 and have evolved into a quirky brand and a household name. Their original flavors of orange, lemon, lime, grape and strawberry got a revamp in 1989 with the introduction of tropical fruit flavors. Since then, 1 new Skittles lines have been created and amazed the mouths of people all over the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-fun-size.jpg', '35~skittles-fun-size.jpg', 'skittles-fun-size-bulk'),
(36, 'Assorted Rods Hard Candy', 63.99, '14.5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a mouthful of classic deliciousness! In sour cherry, butterscotch, apple, licorice, tangerine, strawberry, peppermint, pineapple, wild cherry, and lemon, these amazing Assorted Rods Hard Candies will satisfy any sweet tooth. Covered in a crinkly, pretty cellophane wrapper, these little hard candies make a great addition to any gift basket or present. Wrap some up in goodie bags for a little one\'s birthday, set an assortment out in a candy dish, even bring some to a friend\'s house the next time you visit. The fruity rainbow of these hard candies is sure to please candy lovers of all ages.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/s/assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', '36~assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', 'rods-hard-candy-assorted'),
(37, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '37~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(38, 'Key Lime Pie Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you pop a piece of key lime pie candy into your mouth, your taste buds will burst with citrus sweetness. It\'s like taking a trip to the beautiful, balmy Florida Keys without even leaving your home or office. These delicious green and white hard candies are perfect for any occasion, whether you want a refreshing tropical taste on a hot summer day or you want to remind yourself of the beach in the middle of winter.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', '38~key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', 'key-lime-pie-hard-candy'),
(39, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '39~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(40, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '40~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(41, 'chocolate starlight mints thumbnail', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Chocolate starlight mints are a new and amazing take on a classic candy. Everyone loves the refreshing flavor of the traditional hard mint, now add chocolate.Starlight mints, which are also sometimes called pinwheel mints, feature a lovely white background with bold red stripes. Our chocolate starlight mints take that same elegant pattern and use it on a dark background with brilliant green stripes instead.Now you can enjoy that delicious minty taste with a touch of savory chocolate. Each round mint is crafted using solid hard candy. This allows them to provide the flavor candy lovers adore in a long lasting treat. Each mint is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can admire their dark beauty before you open the first one up!Pour them into glass jars or candy dishes and serve to guests, use them in the office candy jar or make your gingerbread houses more unique with these tasty decorations!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', '41~chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', 'chocolate-starlight-mints'),
(42, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Don\'t bite down on one of these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers! These hard candies are great for savoring a ton of sweetness for a long time.Buy a bulk bag of Jaw Busters hard candies for the little ghouls and goblins coming around the neighborhood on Halloween, or keep them around when you\'re craving something sweet for yourself. You can keep a bag of Jawbreakers in a wide assortment of colors and flavors all year long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', '42~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-wrapped'),
(43, 'Bulk Assorted Fruit Lollipops', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Lollipop, lollipop, oh lolli , lolli, lolli  Sorry, we\'re getting carried away with ourselves. It happens a lot here. It\'s just that we\'re so passionate about these scrumptious suckers that it makes us break out in song. They don\'t require a trip to the doctor and they come in bulk, so these pops are the perfect choice for any occasion. Stock up for your child\'s next party or put them in a jar on your desk for lucky coworkers to snack on. You\'ll quickly become a favorite in the office! With a light, sweet, fruity flavor, in a rainbow of colors, everyone can enjoy a mouthful of deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', '43~lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'lollipops-bulk-fruit'),
(44, 'Sour Fruit Balls Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Sour. Check. Colorful. Check. Fruity and delicious. Check, check! We\'ve got everything you need here for the makings of a great bulk candy selection.  Individually wrapped, these candies make tasty treats for parties, as filler candy, or just to have around the house for a qick fix of sweetness.With over 80 hard candies per pound, there\'s enough sweetness to treat all of your friends and family. Every time you snack from this bag, choose from yummy red, orange, yellow, green, and purple. Everyone who hears the crinkle of their wrappers will come running for more. And because of their perfect size, one after another can be enjoyed.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', '44~sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', 'sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy'),
(45, 'Andes Mints', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Ande\'s mints make the perfect welcome snack for any home, office, or restaurant. Whether your guests want to freshen their breath after they\'ve had a meal, or you\'d just like to make them feel at home with something sweet, these are the treats for you. A perfect blend of creamy milk chocolate and mint filling make these tiny sandwiches of sweetness the perfect refreshment, and they\'re individually wrapped, so there\'s no danger of spreading anyone\'s germs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', '45~andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', 'andes-mints'),
(46, 'Butterscotch Buttons Candy', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'These candies are cute as a button! Maybe that\'s because these Butterscotch Candy Buttons come in beautiful, individually wrapped gold wrappers and are a lovely bright yellow color that candy fans love. Around since the 1800s, butterscotch has built up a tasty reputation throughout the decades and continues to please candy lovers near and far. Try these little, rich sweets out for your next candy buffet bar, crush them and sprinkle them on top of cookies and baked goods for a sweet surprise, or even fill your candy dishes for an olde timey feel every snacker can enjoy. These hard candies are sure to \'\'butter you up\'\' with their irresistible flavor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', '46~butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'butterscotch-buttons'),
(47, 'Sunkist Fruit Gems', 69.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a big, sugary smooch with these Sunkist Fruit Gems! Their delicious, gummy chew and bright, fruity flavor will make you want to pucker up for more every time you take a bite. Individually wrapped, these little gummies pack the power of the sun into every chew and show off the beautiful colors of the rainbow.Stock yourself up with some rainy day sunshine with a bag of these. They\'re a great goodie bag stuffer for birthday parties, look lovely at a summertime picnic on the dessert table, and even can be kept to cheer up your little ones on a rainy day. With 42 pieces per pound, there are enough to please every gummy fan!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', '47~sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk'),
(48, 'Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get your candy fix with our Tootsie Rolls midgees candy! Tootsie Roll is one of the oldest treats in the United States. This confection was invented in 1986 when Leo Hirshfield decided to open up a shop in New York City.Today, kids and adults love the chewy texture and chocolaty taste that makes these popular confections so irresistible. They\'re not quite taffy and not quite caramel but very smooth, making snack time even sweeter! Bulk Tootsie Rolls give you more pieces for snacking, parties and sharing.Every roll is individually wrapped in that familiar brown, red and white paper. That allows the candy to remain fresh and ready to enjoy. Take a handful with you as a quick treat on a busy day or use them as an easy after school snack for the kids. Tootsie Rolls also make great treat bag filler for birthday parties, picnics, holiday events and other gatherings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', '48~tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-midgees'),
(49, 'Peppermint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '6', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peppermint Starlight mints make the perfect complimentary candy for almost any occasion, event, or environment. Are you considering putting a candy dish by the door at home? Do you run a restaurant where customers pay at a counter near the front? These Starlight mint hard candies are recognized all over the world as a true classic. They\'ll satisfy your sweet tooth and freshen your breath, too. Put some of these individually wrapped treats out in your home, office, or restaurant today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', '49~peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', 'starlight-mints-peppermint'),
(50, 'Jumbo Mint Balls Hard Candy', 11.49, '120', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'Make way for a big dose of peppermint flavor! These Jumbo Mint Balls are a sphere full of refreshing minty flavor that your mouth will love. Their beautiful red and white swirls make them the perfect sweet addition to a Christmas candy display, gingerbread house making with your family, a beach party (since these little balls resemble beach balls!), and even a Fourth of July event. With 12 of these flavorful candy balls in every order, there\'s enough to do it all. Use your imagination to decide how you and your close family and friends can enjoy these tasty mints.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', '50~jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', 'jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls'),
(51, 'Peanut Butter Bars', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peanut butter bars candy brings you all the best parts of peanuts without all the bad stuff. Each bar includes high quality peanuts that are slow roasted until they become gold brown to bring out the natural nutty flavor. Each bite is truly an experience, with the crispy, flaky crunch that everyone loves. If you are a peanut butter fanatic, then this bar candy is your dream come true!Every peanut butter bar is individually wrapped so it\'s easy to store and share. Each includes a simple white wrapper with black stripes, gold star and a classic logo that gives each piece a nostalgic look. Keep a handful in your purse or pocket or use the in favor bags for parties and holiday events. Each tasty tidbit is packed with all the rich peanut flavor you can handle in a convenient package that you can take anywhere! Our bulk candy packs are great for school events, businesses and carnivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', '51~peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', 'peanut-butter-bars');
