(522, 'Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars 3pc', 94.99, '12', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Whether you are celebrating a job promotion, engagement, or the birth of a baby, Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are the perfect addition to your event. Crafted from premium milk chocolate and molded to look just like real cigars, these impressive masterpieces will have folks taking a closer look when they see you bite the end of one.The Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are all individually wrapped in exquisite Italian foil that replicates a genuine tobacco leaf. They are available in three options: Original, It\'s a Girl, and It\'s a Boy.These divine treats are kosher certified and made in the USA by Thompson Candy Company. They are perfect for baby showers, delivery celebrations at the hospital, Father\'s Day, anniversaries, birthdays, and thank you gifts, just to name a few. Order these Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars for you to handout, or give the entire box to someone as a gift. They are sure to make everyone smile, and they are a lot better for you and the environment than the real thing.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', '522~royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', 'royale-premium-chocolate-cigars'),
