(535, 'Chocolate Soccer Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in foil that looks like a classic black and white soccer ball and with amazing chocolate balls beneath, these Chocolate Soccer Balls are winners for sure! Do you have a friend or family member who plays soccer? Why not make their next game extra special by bringing an order of these Chocolate Soccer Balls by at half time? There are plenty to share with the whole team and can cheer up a losing team or help celebrate an incredible win!Chocolate Soccer Balls also are a great candy for sports-themed birthday parties or soccer training camps. Score big with your friends and family and order some today. Oleee, ole, ole, ole. Get ready to chant the most famous soccer game song of all time with these Chocolate Soccer Balls!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', '535~chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', 'chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped'),
