(556, 'Bit O Honey Candy', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Buzzzzzz. These Bit-O-Honey Candies are brimming with the sweet, creamy sugar of an entire hive! That\'s because each delightful candy is made with sweet, honey flavored taffy and complete with soft almond pieces inside. Individually wrapped, these delectable morsels can be enjoyed one, two, or three at a time! They make a perfect addition to a classic candy display, set out on a coffee table for sweet snacking, or packed into a pinata for birthday parties. Treat your busy bees to a sweet treat with a bag of these. Try these out for yourself and see what all the \'\'buzz\'\' is about with an order of these tasty treats!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/i/bit-o-honey-candy-candystore-470x470.jpg', '556~bit-o-honey-candy-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'bit-o-honey-pieces'),
(557, 'Tootsie Fruit Rolls Fruit Chews', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Let us get this straight. The classic Tootsie Roll chew that we love comes in a delicious fruity taste, too? We\'ll take it! Try these Fruit Tootsie Rolls and enjoy a whole new taste with this classic candy. Yellow is lemon, blue is vanilla, red is cherry, green is lime, and orange is...orange. Discover a whole new way to love this classic brand.Since 1896, Tootsie has been producing delectable candies that the world has grown to love. With 65 pieces per pound and a bulk bag of these, there\'s nothing tiny about the amount of delectable Tootsie Fruit Chews Rolls you\'ll get to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruit-chews-tootsie-rolls-470x470_2.jpg', '557~fruit-chews-tootsie-rolls-470x470_2.jpg', 'fruit-tootsie-rolls'),
(558, 'Peppermint Twists Mints', 19.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peppermint twists pack all of the flavor of a candy cane into a single bite-sized candy. Just seeing and tasting them will put you in the holiday spirit, no matter what time of year it is. Don\'t miss out on delicious peppermint candies all year round. Get a bag of these individually wrapped peppermint twists and liven up your home or your office. No special occasion is necessary to bring out these delicious peppermint candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', '558~peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'peppermint-twists'),
(559, 'Spearmint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'A classic concept with a colorful twist. Try our Spearmint Starlight Mints as a complementary addition to your traditional red and white peppermints. Their cool, sharp spearmint flavor in addition to their lovely green and white coloring contrasts to make them a lovely and refreshing selection for any candy bowl. Make your holiday gingerbread house extra special with these green and white mints. Or stash some in your purse for a sweet, minty treat. We can\'t deny the holiday cheer these mints give us and we hope that they will inspire the same, bright happiness in everyone you share them with.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', '559~spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', 'spearmint-starlight-mints'),
(560, 'Mary Jane Candy', 20.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you\'re in the mood for something extra chewy, try our sweet Mary Jane candies! These delectable delights are small bars of smooth taffy treats. Each is flavored with rich molasses and peanut butter to give it that memorable taste that kids of all ages have been asking for since 1914. The candy is a historic favorite that was named after its creator\'s beloved aunt â€“ a worthy choice for such a nostalgic confection!Each taffy candy is covered in a bright yellow wrapper with a bold red stripe and classic logo printed around both sides. You\'ll love Mary Janes even more when you buy our bulk candy package! Order larger quantities so you have plenty to share at family gatherings and other events. Use them to fill the office candy jar or use them to fill treat bags for birthdays and more! Our bulk Mary Janes are also convenient to hand out on trick or treat night around Halloween!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', '560~mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'mary-janes-candy'),
(561, 'Bulk Candy Mix', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Having a candy buffet and need the perfect mix to kick off the table.  You have found the perfect product with our bulk candy mix in a five pound bag.  We have included some of our all time favorites in this mix.  Assorted Salt Water taffy is always the perfect start.  Individually wrapped Starbursts are a fan favorite in our office.  Tootsie roll fruit help make the mix really stand out and to top it all off it includes assorted Jolly Rancher Hard CandyWhether for a party or your candy jar in the office or home this mix will be a hit with everyone!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulk_candy_mix_candystore.jpg', '561~bulk_candy_mix_candystore.jpg', 'bulk-candy-mix'),
(562, 'Assorted Fruit Starlight Mints', 18.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Our starlight mints are now available with amazing fruit flavors! If you love the smooth texture and fun pinwheel pattern of the classic starlight candy, then you\'ll love these vibrant treats! Each piece features the same look with a color that matches its unique fruity taste. Our bulk fruit starlight mints include an assortment of orange, lime, lemon and cherry. Pour some into a glass candy bowl for guests or share with family at home. Everyone will find a flavor they love!Pinwheel mints are also a fun part of the holidays. If you want to change things up, combine the traditional starlight mint with our fruit candies. These also make great favor bag treats for weddings, birthday parties and other events. With our enormous bulk mint pack, it\'s easy to get all the pieces you need for any occasion. Grab a handful of our assorted fruit starlight mints and share the sweetness!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/starlights-mints-assorted-fruit-5lb_1.jpg', '562~starlights-mints-assorted-fruit-5lb_1.jpg', 'starlights-mints-assorted-fruit'),
(563, 'Tootsie Rolls Fruit Chews', 96.99, '30', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Our little Tootsie Rolls fruit chews candies may be small in size, but they offer enormous amounts of flavor in every smooth piece. If you love chewy candy, then this is a must-have treat. Each package contains an assortment of Tootsie Roll\'s finest flavors in an array of brilliant colors. Sample a bright yellow lemon candy or a green lime piece. Our assortment also includes blue vanilla rolls, red cherry rolls and orange rolls - which come in orange, of course! Children and adults will love carefully untwisting each wrapper and trying the delectable tube shaped treat hidden inside! Our bulk candy assortment is perfect for parties, picnics, school events and any gathering that you want to sweeten. You can also purchase bulk Tootsie Fruit Rolls Chews candy to keep at home so you always have an easy go-to snack or dessert to put in school lunches for the kids. Sink your teeth into the soft, chewy confection that comes in your favorite flavors! Order today and find out why our Tootsie Rolls Fruit Chews fruit candy are so irresistible!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruit-tootsie-rolls-bulk-30lb_2.jpg', '563~fruit-tootsie-rolls-bulk-30lb_2.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-fruit-bulk-case'),
(564, 'Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candy', 96.99, '30', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'What\'s tiny, delicious, and chocolatey all over? Our Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candies! These bite-size treats are the perfect snack for any day of the week. They also make a delicious addition to any candy buffet bar, trick-or-treating candy bucket, or even as wedding or pinata candy. Individually wrapped, you can enjoy these classic candies in miniature form at your own leisure. Since 1896, Tootsie has been producing delectable candies that the world has grown to love. With 65 pieces per pound, there\'s nothing tiny about the amount of delectable morsels you\'ll get to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-rolls-midgees-470x470_1.jpg', '564~tootsie-rolls-midgees-470x470_1.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-midgees-bulk'),
(565, 'Chick O Stick Box', 11.99, '36', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'This big Chick-O-Stick Box is calling your name if you love crunchy, flakey, savory peanut butter. A classic candy,, this inventive and different confection is full of flavor and texture your mouth and mind will enjoy.With individually wrapped sticks, you\'ll be able to devour one at a time, pack some into a lunch box for a delightful surprise, add some to gift baskets or Christmas stockings or unwrap them and use them as utensils for eating ice cream! Use your imagination and go with your gut to come up with ways of how you can eat these Chick-O-Stick Box candies. No matter what you choose, we know you\'ll love munching and crunching on them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chick-o-stickbox36ct.jpg', '565~chick-o-stickbox36ct.jpg', 'chick-o-stick-box'),
(566, 'Chick O Stick Nuggets Candy', 21.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Remember Chick-O-Sticks? Those delicious peanut butter candies with the coconut twist are back and better than ever. Now, instead of buying a full-sized Chick-O-Stick, you can get a bag of Chick-O-Sticks nuggets that will satisfy your sweet and savory cravings. Each nugget is about an inch long, the perfect size to just pop in your mouth and enjoy the sweet tastes while you go about your day. Pick up a big bulk bag today and start nibbling on one of your favorite candies again.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chick-o-stick-nuggets-candystore-470x470.jpg', '566~chick-o-stick-nuggets-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'chick-o-sticks-nuggets'),
(567, 'Blue Foil Grape Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'These little candies contain a whole lot of flavor. They are blue in color and the wrappers that are used for them are blue as well. However, the flavor that you get from these candies is a pleasant grape flavor. This is a flavor that can be enjoyed by people of all ages and that makes it great for nearly any occasion. Since they are blue you could consider using them for a baby shower if you wanted to as well. These candies are sure to be a hit. They are hard candies and you can either suck on them or crunch on them when eating them which is great for those who like the way that hard candies feel in their mouths when they bit them. They come in a bulk bag which means that there will be plenty to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '567~blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy'),
(568, 'Laffy Taffy Candy', 37.99, '8.5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Laffy Taffy is such a well-recognized candy that hip-hop artist D4L has immortalized its name in song. You don\'t have to be a fan of rap to enjoy these chewy soft candies, though. Each individually wrapped Laffy Taffy candy comes with a joke written on the wrapper for you to share with your friends. You\'ll laugh with your friends as you satisfy your sweet tooth for this delicious taffy candy. They\'re so good, though, that you might want to share the jokes, but you won\'t ever want to share the candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', '568~laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-pieces-bulk'),
(569, 'Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'All kids are looking for sunshine, happiness and rainbows in their lives and when they are given Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy the sunshine is just a shiny wrapper away. It is the wrapper that first draws your attention. Who doesn\'t like a shiny present? It will be exactly like Christmas morning as you hold one of these lemony treats in your hand and start to unwrap it. As the wrapper is opened it will reveal a bright yellow hard candy treat like you dream about right in your hand. You might have wondered what sunshine tastes like, but once you try one of the Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candies you will be pretty sure that it tastes a lot like lemon. With a convenient bulk bag of treats there will be enough sunshine to share with a whole office or classroom or people. People can\'t help but smile and be in a good mood when they eat this delicious treat. This makes it a natural for wedding receptions as all people want to start their new lives with a whole lot of smiles and sunshine.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', '569~silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', 'silver-foil-lemon-hard-candy'),
