(571, 'Jumbo Spearmint Balls Candy', 11.49, '120', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'Green, white, and minty. These Jumbo Spearmint Balls Candy are a delicious mint that your whole family will love. Take your gingerbread house building to the next level with a handful of these minty wonders, make a Christmas candy display even prettier and more delicious, or even stick a few in your purse to enjoy a breath freshening treat whenever you wish. The bright green and white swirls are beautiful to look at and offer a refreshing burst of spearmint flavor that your mouth will crave. With 120 pieces per order, you\'ll have enough tasty mints to satisfy a crowd.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/jumbo-spearmint-balls-candy-120ct_1.jpg', '571~jumbo-spearmint-balls-candy-120ct_1.jpg', 'jumbo-spearmint-balls'),
(572, 'Fun Size M&Ms Milk Chocolate', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get the party started with these Fun Size Packs of M&Ms;! Great for Halloween trick-or-treating, birthday parties, or just to enjoy as a perfectly portioned snack, this bulk bag is ready to add some delicious flavor to your life and those you share them with.Get your bag today to add some extra deliciousness and magic into your every day snacking. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsize_m_ms.jpg', '572~funsize_m_ms.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-milk-chocolate'),
(573, 'Atomic Fireballs', 74.99, '25', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Five, four, three, two, one. Prepare for total taste bud annihilation! These atomic fireballs may be small, but don\'t let their unassuming size fool you. Their explosive shell and spicy interior bring the heat of a five alarm fire.With about 50 blazing pieces per pound, there\'s enough candy here to nuke your mouth into oblivion and back again. But if you can summon the courage to put out the blaze, you\'ll be treated to a mild, sweet cinnamon finish that will be well worth the challenge. Just beware. Only the strong mouthed will survive to beat this atomic heat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/t/atomic-fireballs-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', '573~atomic-fireballs-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', 'atomic-fireballs-wrapped-bulk'),
(574, 'Blue Wrapped Mini Mints', 6.99, '2.2', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'They may be small, but these Mini Mints are big on refreshing flavor! With a big bag of tiny morsels wrapped individually in blue and white foil, they\'re ready to freshen your mouth with every bite.Stock up on some Mini Mints for dinner parties, weddings and any occasion that calls for a palate cleanser that is both minty and delicious. You can stock your candy dishes around the house, serve some of these alongside coffee and tea after dessert or stuff some into your purse or office desk for when you need a breath freshener and something sweet to indulge in. Mini Mints can do it all and more in this bulk supply!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mini_mints_-_2.2lb.jpg', '574~mini_mints_-_2.2lb.jpg', 'blue-wrapped-mini-mints'),
(575, 'Skittles Fun Size Bulk', 99.99, '22', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'A color and flavor for every taste bud. Pack these fun size Skittles into a pinata, add them to a stocking, or slip one into your kid\'s lunchbox for a delicious afternoon surprise. Whatever you choose, everyone will love to \'\'Taste the Rainbow.\'\' Skittles have been in the US since 1979 and have evolved into a quirky brand and a household name. Their original flavors of orange, lemon, lime, grape and strawberry got a revamp in 1989 with the introduction of tropical fruit flavors. Since then, 1 new Skittles lines have been created and amazed the mouths of people all over the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-fun-size.jpg', '575~skittles-fun-size.jpg', 'skittles-fun-size-bulk'),
(576, 'Assorted Rods Hard Candy', 63.99, '14.5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a mouthful of classic deliciousness! In sour cherry, butterscotch, apple, licorice, tangerine, strawberry, peppermint, pineapple, wild cherry, and lemon, these amazing Assorted Rods Hard Candies will satisfy any sweet tooth. Covered in a crinkly, pretty cellophane wrapper, these little hard candies make a great addition to any gift basket or present. Wrap some up in goodie bags for a little one\'s birthday, set an assortment out in a candy dish, even bring some to a friend\'s house the next time you visit. The fruity rainbow of these hard candies is sure to please candy lovers of all ages.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/s/assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', '576~assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', 'rods-hard-candy-assorted'),
(577, 'White Wedding Mints', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Here comes the bride! Make your special day all the more memorable with these delicate mints. With their delicious, smooth texture and refreshing taste, it\'ll be easy to say \'\'I do.\'\' Set them out at the reception as a beautiful centerpiece or use them in party favors. You can even pop one in your mouth before you walk down the aisle to make your first kiss as man and wife as sweet as the day you met. Their pristine, pearly coloring will match the white of any wedding and set your ceremony apart from any and all of the rest.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/y/dynamite-white-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', '577~dynamite-white-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', 'white-wedding-mints-mighty'),
(578, 'Gourmet 12 Flavor Gummy Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Get ready for the fanciest gummy in the forest with these Gourmet Gummy Bears! In an array of colors and flavors, these colorful cubs come bursting with classic fruity, gummy flavor amd a luxurious chew. Enjoy a rainbow of bears from red to blue to white. Let your little ones laugh and play as these bears march into their mouths. In this bulk selection, these bears are the perfect choice to make a candy buffet bar even fancier. They\'re also great wrapped in individual bags and given out as party favors, put in a bowl of punch for a fruity, chewy surprise, or even to reward your little ones whenever you choose. Discover why these gourmet gummies are \'\'bear-resistible!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gourmet-gummy-bears-12-flavors-5lb_1.jpg', '578~gourmet-gummy-bears-12-flavors-5lb_1.jpg', 'gummy-bears-12-flavors'),
(579, 'Blue Raspberry Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'This is one time when everybody should be allowed to play with their food. And who could resist with these delightful blue raspberry Gummi Bears? Perfectly poppable. Charmingly chewy. Crafted with the care of a tried and true recipe. Everyone will go back for handful after handful of these fruity cuties.WIth each bag brimming with over 145 Gummi Bears per pound, you\'ll have enough furry friends to keep you company through numerous snack times. Their light fruity flavor has made this variety a hit among customers and will keep everyone coming back for more. They\'re what we like to call, \'\'bear-resistible.\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-raspberry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '579~blue-raspberry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'blue-raspberry-gummi-bears'),
(580, 'Gummi Killer Sharks', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Don\'t worry. These killer shark gummies are real softies. As a matter of fact, they are way more afraid of your chompers than of their own! (Cue \'\'Jaws\'\' music). With blue and white coloring, they\'re a bright and tasty candy for a number of events. Delight your kids and throw them a pirate birthday party complete with these toothed treats or pack some into their lunchboxes on a special day. Everyone will have fun playing with these big fish until it\'s time for them to swim into your mouth. They might even be the yummiest fish in under the sea.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummy-killer-sharks-470x470.jpg', '580~gummy-killer-sharks-470x470.jpg', 'gummi-killer-sharks-blue-white'),
(581, 'Haribo Gummi Dinosaurs', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Travel back in time for some prehistoric fun with our gummy dinosaurs! These tasty treats give children an excuse to play with their food before they eat it. Each chewy gummy candy features one of many popular dinos. Overpower taste buds with a realistic T-rex or charge through snack time with a triceratops. From stegosauruses to brontosauruses, everyone\'s favorite species are covered in our bulk candy pack!As if dinosaur shaped gummies weren\'t enough, our terrible lizards are colored half and half so you get two brilliant hues in every piece! These tempting treats are perfect for themed birthday parties, picnics or trips to the natural history museum. Our bulk candy package also makes it easy to get more of the dino gummies you love for gatherings, school events and other occasions. These confectionary treats don\'t roar, but they pack a powerful taste that is sure to satisfy any rampaging sweet tooth!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dinosaurs-gummy-haribo.jpg', '581~dinosaurs-gummy-haribo.jpg', 'gummi-dinosaurs-5lb'),
(582, 'main image', 11.99, '', '', 'unwrapped-loose', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drop and gum drops, then we wouldn\'t have room to try these amazing Spice Drops Candies! Coated in sweet, crystalized sugar with a spicy, gummy center, these candies will make your \'\'jaw drop!\'\' In a variety of colors and flavors, these gummies can be used for virtually any occasion. Use some to decorate a gingerbread house in a delicious, traditional way, bring some to a party for kids to munch on while they play, or even add them to a make your own ice cream sundae bar for a surprising topping. You\'ll love chewing on these gum drops as much as watching their sugar sparkle.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spice-drops-gumdrops-alt-470x470.jpg', '582~spice-drops-gumdrops-alt-470x470.jpg', 'spice-drops'),
(583, 'Haribo Gummi Gold Bears', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Silly old bear. These classic Haribo Gold Gummi Bears are here in a bulk bag to bring you even more of the tasty flavors you love. In a selection of red, orange, yellow, green, and white, everyone in your family will find a cub to love. Sprinkle a few in Jell-O for a \'\'beary\'\' good surprise, add some to a make your own sundae bar, or wrap some up for a loved one to make their day extra special. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so n the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gold-bears-gummi-icon.jpg', '583~haribo-gold-bears-gummi-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gold-gummi-bears'),
(584, 'Red Cherry Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Red cherry fruit sours candy is a great addition to any holiday spread. Let\'s face it; red goes with almost any occasion. It\'s the perfect color addition to Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, the Fourth of July, and it even works for a  bloody  element to Halloween. Red cherry fruit sours explode in your mouth with tartness and sweetness. These delicious candies are sure to be a hit with all your sour-loving friends at your next party.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-cherry-fruit-sours-candy-balls-75lb_2.jpg', '584~red-cherry-fruit-sours-candy-balls-75lb_2.jpg', 'red-cherry-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(585, 'Spearmint Leaves Candy', 10.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Old fashioned spearmint leaves gummies are a chewy treat that will invigorate your taste buds! This elegant candy features a tapered leaf shape, with a narrow tip and wider base.The sides include subtle scalloping Ã must like real foliage! A short stem extends from the base, adding even more detail to these eye-catching candies. Every piece is covered in a gentle green hue that looks even more enticing covered in sugar crystals!Every bite is packed with amazing spearmint flavor. Give your mouth something cool and refreshing to chew on with these all-purpose leaf gummies. Spearmint leaves are also a unique way to decorate cakes, cupcakes and cookies.Add realistic elements to your gingerbread houses or use them to enhance edible dÅ½cor. Our bulk spearmint leaves candy gives you many pounds so you have plenty of individual pieces to experiment with. Or you can keep things simple by pouring spearmint gummies into a bowl to serve any guests who stop by!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/brachs-spearmint-leaves-small-img.jpg', '585~brachs-spearmint-leaves-small-img.jpg', 'spearmint-leaves-candy'),
(586, 'Green Apple Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Our bulk gummi bears are the perfect choice for anyone who loves the chewy taste of this classic candy. Whether you are buying for a special event or want to perform flavor-specific experiments at home. We can help! Our green apple gummi bears offer the tangy bite of sour with a bit of apple sweetness. They also make great treats to go with school lunches or as a quick snack at home!Each adorable little edible bear includes the famous round years, chubby paws and endearing smile that kids have come to love. You\'ll savor the green apple taste and love the smooth, chewy texture. Gummi bears have been tempting children since the 1920s. Their fun shapes were inspired by trained bears that performed in street festivals throughout Europe. Today we can enjoy that save festive experience in each delicious gummy piece! Whether you eat the one at a time or by the handful, our green apple sour gummy bears will satisfy any sweet tooth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/granny-smith-apple-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '586~granny-smith-apple-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'green-apple-gummi-bears'),
(587, 'Cinnamon Imperial Hearts', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Our hearts are beating out of our chests for these Cinnamon Imperial Hearts! With a spicy, hot cinnamon flavor and chewy candy texture, your heart is sure to start pitter pattering for these loveable treats with your first bite. Bring them to a Valentine\'s Day party to share some spice that\'s extra nice with loved ones, stock up to keep your candy dishes full throughout February, or get some of these to add into a Cupid-themed candy buffet bar. The bright, red color of these vibrant hearts and delicious cinnamony flavor is something your eyes will love just as much as your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-hearts.jpg', '587~cinnamon-hearts.jpg', 'cinnamon-imperial-hearts'),
(588, 'Gummy Butterflies', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Hearts are a-flutter for these beautiful butterfly gummies! With 3 lovely gummies in every pound, you can let your taste buds take flight with every sensational bite. Hatched from their cocoon, these little gummies will make you swoon with their vibrant rainbow of colors and fruity flavors. Bring them to a little girl\'s birthday party, sprinkle some into a refreshing punch at a springtime picnic, or give your kids a lesson about the beauty of nature. Known to us as the nectar of the candy gods, see for yourself why these dainty flutterers make sweet lovers feel like they can fly.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '588~gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy'),
(589, 'Red Cherry Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Cherry gummy bears are great for any occasion. They are soft and chewy as well as a great red color that even adults love to take part in. These would make a great purchase for Valentine \'s Day or Christmas due to the fabulous red shade that they have.When you bite into one of these gummy bears you are sure to find that the ripe flavor of cherry is more than enough to please your mouth. Since they come in a bulk bag it is sure to be enough to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for. If you are looking for a way to delight almost everyone then this is certainly one of the great candies that is able to do this. After all who doesn\'t like the way that these candies are so cute and fun? It is hard to beat the greatness of this wonderful product.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '589~cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-gummi-bears'),
(590, 'Haribo Gummi Raspberries', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Haribo gummi raspberries look like real raspberries! Put them in a candy dish at your next gathering and watch your guests get surprised with a gummi taste explosion when they pick one up. These delicious fruity snacks come as a mix of red and black in a big bulk bag. Be careful opening them up, though. Once you start, you won\'t want to stop eating these sweet raspberry gummies. Get them for your candy dish at home or the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', '590~haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-raspberries'),
(591, 'Sour Gummi Poppers', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Try not to drool. These Sour Gummi Poppers have a tart flavor that will make your mouth water! With a bright pastel selection of red, blue, yellow, green, and orange candies, there\'s an entire rainbow of sour for you to choose from. Every candy is coated in a tangy sugar that leads to a sweet, fruity center. Use a handful of these colorful pucker-makers for a candy dish on your coffee table, put some in a glass jar and enjoy looking at them as much as eating them, or even add some to a candy buffet bar for guests to enjoy at their own leisure. We\'re sure you\'ll love puckering with these poppable candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', '591~sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sour-gummi-poppers'),
(592, 'Green Watermelon Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'We think these candies are \'\'de-vine.\'\' A real knee-slapper we know, but in all seriousness, these Pink Watermelon Fruit Sours Candies taste like they\'re fresh off the vine. Covered in a beautiful, glossy pink shell and complete with a soft, fruity chew, these candies are cultivated by using some of the sweetest techniques in the candy biz. Use some for a light sweet at a backyard picnic, bring some to a gathering of friends, even use them for a lovely addition to an outdoor wedding. For watermelon and candy enthusiasts, alike, this bag will provide you with hours and hours of happy snacking.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/0/8/08017-_watermelon_sours.png', '592~08017-_watermelon_sours.png', 'pink-watermelon-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(593, 'Fruit Slices Candy', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Fruit slices gummies are a fabulous treat that comes in many exciting flavors! If you love chewy gummy candy but want more options when it comes to taste, this is a must-try.Our delicious fruit slices candy include a flat wedge shape slab of confection with a flat end and curved side. A white line runs along the curved edge, creating the look of a fruit rind.Every fruit slice is different based on its flavor. Grape is all purple while black cherry includes a red middle with blue â€œrindâ€. We carry a huge variety of juicy flavors that also include lemon lime, cherry, strawberry banana, orange, pink grapefruit, peach, watermelon, sour apple, red raspberry and blue raspberry.If you can\'t decide on just one, you can instead choose our amazing assorted bulk fruit slices pack! This mouthwatering blend contains a little bit of everything so you can sample all your chewy favorites!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', '593~albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', 'fruit-slices-candy'),
(594, 'Gumdrops', 11.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drops and gumdrops, then we\'d be out of business! However, you can still feel like it\'s raining gumdrops with this bulk bag of gummy candies. A classic addition for holiday baked goods, stockings, and fancy gingerbread houses, you will be stocked up for the season with this bag. In a variety of colors and fruity flavors, savor the sweetness as the sugary coating melts in your mouth. Then get ready to chew \'til you drop with a yummy gummy center. The holidays just aren\'t complete without a few mouthfuls of these sugary sweets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gumdrops-5lbs.gif', '594~gumdrops-5lbs.gif', 'gumdrops'),
(595, 'Haribo Gummi Peaches', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'You\'re a peach! Well, actually these Haribo Gummi Peaches are. In a sugary coating and delicious light peach flavor, bite into these chewy gummies for a taste of the summertime. Bring some to a warm weather BBQ, add some as a pretty drink garnish to lemonade and adult drinks, or even use them to decorate the top of a strawberry shortcake! Haribo bears first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany. To this day, they\'re one of the biggest manufacturers of gummies and supply happy snackers all around the world. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so _ the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', '595~haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-peaches'),
(596, 'Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 25.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Wooooweee! These tart purple candies deliver an unrelenting pucker with delicious, fruity flavor. If you like a sour shot to the mouth, try our Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy. The sourest candy on the vine, these little pucker-packed candies will please every sour lover. Bring some to a purple themed party, add some to a lemonade for a sour grape flavor addition and pretty garnish, or keep them around the house when you\'re in the mood for a feisty snack. Their deep, purple coloring may look unsuspecting, but get ready for a dose of tartness that will thrill your taste buds!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '596~purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'purple-grape-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(597, 'Jelly Belly Jelly Beans', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Oh, behold the possibilities! With 50 original flavors plus even more limited-edition beans, concoct combination after combination of inventive candy recipes with this bulk bag of Jelly Belly jelly beans. Maybe you have a hankering for chocolate covered banana, vanilla espresso or coconut orange. Whatever your signature recipe, you can be the chef with the pick of the littler of hundreds of beans brimming with unique flavor. The Jelly Belly company has been around since 1976 and has honed their talent in producing tantilizing flavors that have pleased customers for years. See why for yourself why they are an American favorite with this bulk bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', '597~jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', 'jelly-belly-jelly-beans'),
(598, 'Hot Tamales Candy', 15.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'If you are looking for chewy candy with a spicy cinnamon flavor, that is sure to please, then this is the treat for you. They have a wonderful and exciting red color to them. This is great for those who have a candy buffet and are looking to add a little bit of red to it.When you bite into this great candy you are sure to find that your taste buds will be pleased with the pleasant but strong kick that you great from the awesome flavor that this candy is able to deliver. These come in a bulk bag that is sure to get plenty of them for whatever reason you need them. Whether you are throwing a birthday party, just looking to keep candy around the house, or using them for a buffet you are sure to find that you will be more than pleased with amazing Hot Tamales!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-candy-bulk-4lb_2.jpg', '598~hot-tamales-candy-bulk-4lb_2.jpg', 'hot-tamales-candy-bulk'),
(599, 'Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Pucker up, buttercup! These Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy have a mighty mix of sour and sweet to delight the mouths of many. Soft, chewy, tangy, and gorgeous, the bright mix of candy balls is a cheerful dose of sugar and citrus. Use them for an autumn inspired gift basket, on the Thanksgiving dessert table, or even as sour additions to a trick-or-treat stash. They can even make a summertime festival even more special by adding the beautiful color of the hot sun. There is no wrong way for your friends and family to enjoy these fruity, delicious and sour candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '599~orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'orange-tangerine-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(600, 'Cinnamon Imperials Candy', 20.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'These red hot little cinnamon mouth explosions are great for any candy dish! Cinnamon Imperials candies have a classic taste that everyone remembers from childhood, and they\'re great for all kinds of occasions.Include them as a sweet treat for your Valentine. Add them to an assortment of fruity and spicy candies at a party, or just keep them in the candy dish at home for guests who happen to drop by.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', '600~cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', 'cinnamon-imperials'),
(601, 'Candy Corn', 64.99, '10', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Nothing says autumn like a big bowl of sugary candy corn! At least we don\'t think so. Their bright colors of orange, yellow, and white match the changing leaves, pumpkins, gourds, and glorious sunsets of the season. With this bulk bag of autumnal joy, you will have enough to savor long after the harvest is through. Display some in mason jars for a rustic, fall-themed feel Let your kids be silly by putting them on their teeth and smiling for the camera. Even use them in individual baggies for Halloween treats. We just think these candy corns are \'\'a-maize-ing!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-corn-bulk-5lb.jpg', '601~candy-corn-bulk-5lb.jpg', 'candy-corn'),
(602, 'Sour Power Belts from Dorval', 41.99, '6.6', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Dorval Sour Power belt gummies are a delicious treat for kids and the young at heart! Each piece consist of a long, wide ribbon of flat gummy candy in bright colors. Our flavor list includes all your favorites, like strawberry, watermelon, apple, berry and much more!Sour Power belt candy is a fun choice for birthday parties and holiday events. Our flavor options also make it easy to create your own custom candy assortment! Just order 2 or more packages to combine colors for any celebration. Add to kids treat bags or use as a unique accent on edible displays like gingerbread houses. Sour Power belts also give you more ways to decorate cakes, cupcakes and other baked goods. Our bulk Sour Power gummy belts give you many long pieces so you have enough to share with guests or enjoy at home! This classic candy has been satisfying sweet cravings since 1985.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/dorval-belts-rainbow-bulk.jpg', '602~dorval-belts-rainbow-bulk.jpg', 'sour-power-belts-dorval-bulk'),
(603, 'Gummi Penguins', 11.99, '2.2', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'It\'s the \'\'march of the penguin\'\' gummies! These curious little penguins are full of funny antics and will make your next snack even more charming and delicious! In every bag of these Penguin Gummies, these white and black treats will waddle, splash, and swim into your mouths. They\'re a great snack for kids to play with and an even more adorable treat to look at! These fancy tuxedo clad birds make a cute addition to any black tie, formal affair, wedding reception, or even as a gift to a penguin-loving friend or family lover. Get a taste of the arctic with this gummy, fruity snack today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', '603~gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', 'gummi-penguins'),
(604, 'Assorted Bon Bons', 24.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'There\'s no resisting the sweet taste of Holland bon bons! These delicious treats come in a handful of popular flavors, including orange, strawberry, raspberry, lemon, pineapple and cherry. Take your pick or try them all and savor the fresh picked taste of ripe fruit in a sweet confection. Our bulk candy assortment gives you a large quantity that\'s perfect for parties, picnics, events or any situation that may call for many candy jar refills!Our bon bons come in simple yet elegant wrappers so each is individually packaged and ready for sharing. It\'s easy to identify the flavor of each piece thanks to the colorful fruit image printed right on the surface. Untwist the wrapper and experience the mouthwatering sweetness that makes our fruit bon bons so appetizing. Whether you want a complementary treat to impress clients, a delicious candy to serve guests or a quick snack to enjoy at home, our bulk Holland bon bons will give you the finest fruit flavor in a convenient package!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/columbina_fruit_filled.jpg', '604~columbina_fruit_filled.jpg', 'holland-bon-bons-assorted'),
(605, 'Haribo Happy Cola Bottles', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'There\'s nothing like a cold glass of bubbling, refreshing cola on a hot summer\'s day. Well, unless you count these amazing little Haribo Gummi Cola Bottles! With a sharp, cola flavor and the delicious chew Haribo is famous for, all your sweet snackers will love you for bringing these home. Bring some to your next picnic, add a festive element to a backyard BBQ, or even keep some around the house for snacking. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so the happy world of Haribo!\'\'These are the regular sized Haribo cola bottles. They do not have any writing on them. The Super Cola Bottles are larger and have Haribo written on them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-happy-cola-bottles-icon.jpg', '605~haribo-happy-cola-bottles-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-cola-bottles'),
(606, 'Baby Gummi Bears', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'What do you call a bear with no teeth? A \'\'gummy bear!\'\' We love that one and we\'re sure you\'ll love these Baby Gummi Bears. Shrunken down from their gummi grizzly relatives, these mini munchables are even more adorable and just as delicious! Use these cute cubs to dress up an ice cream sundae, give away in a baby shower gift basket, treat your little ones to a candy their size, or just keep them around for a petite snack. With an assortment of colors and flavors, we\'re sure you\'ll find a favorite among these amazing minis. Use your fangs to chow down on these today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/baby-gummi-bears-10lbs_1.jpg', '606~baby-gummi-bears-10lbs_1.jpg', 'baby-gummi-bears'),
(607, 'Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lite', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Summertime and the living\'s easy. And now, sugar free! Try these Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lites for a healthier fix of the boardwalk classic and all the scrumptious taste of the original recipe. In blue-raspberry, strawberry, lemon, chocolate, orange, and vanilla, let these little morsels melt away as you remember digging your toes into the sand and letting the sun shine in your hair. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', '607~sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite');
