(608, 'Candy Necklaces Unwrapped', 25.99, '100', 'ct', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Show me a kid and I will show you someone that loves candy necklaces. There is just something about colorful jewelry that you can eat that puts a smile on everyone\'s face. First there is the color of the candy necklace the entire rainbow of the spectrum in represented and each color has a unique and delicious taste. One bite can be grape the next can be orange. All kids love variety and this is one of the best kind. Candy necklaces also provide a whole lot of convenience because it is worn around the neck and it is a very short tug to pull a necklace to your mouth and crunch a little bit of candy goodness. It is a lot like carrying a snack to power you through the day. When you need a burst of sugar just take a bite, until it is gone. These treats are great for parties of any kind and all kids just simply love to wear and eat candy necklaces!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-necklaces-100-ct_2.jpg', '608~candy-necklaces-100-ct_2.jpg', 'candy-necklaces-unwrapped'),
(609, 'Runts Candy', 94.99, '30', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Runts candy made its first appearance in the 1980s. While its fruity lineup has changed since then, its popularity has not. Every kid can recognize the fun shapes and bright colors that make Runts so unique. Our extensive collection of bulk candy includes this childhood favorite so you can get your fill of sweet fruity goodness anytime you want! Serve at kid\'s parties, take as a non-perishable snack on camping trips or set some aside to hide away at home for moments when you need a sweet fix!Our Runts candy package include all the current flavors and shapes. You\'ll love biting down on a yellow banana or savoring a tart cherry piece. Each order also includes blue raspberry, watermelon and lime. Try the smooth, sweet taste of your favorite fruits followed by the tantalizing tanginess that makes Runts candies so delectable. You don\'t have to go to a vending machine to find your favorite treat because we have Runts in bulk and ready to ship right to you!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts30lbs.jpg', '609~runts30lbs.jpg', 'runts-bulk'),
(610, 'Hot Pink Sixlets', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'These glamorous Pink Sixlets chocolates are almost too pretty to eat! Almost... But eat them we shall with their pleasant crunch followed by a creamy milk chocolate center. Tinier than M&Ms; at about a third of the size, these little wonders can still satisfy every sweet tooth  big and small. Set them out in a bowl in your office, use them as a wedding candy buffet item, or add some extra girliness to a baby or bridal shower. Whatever you decide to do with these lovely, little gems, we are sure that you and your friends will love looking at them as much as eating them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', '610~sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-pink'),
(611, 'Anise Bears', 10.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Anise is a classic flavor that is very popular among many. If you love the rich, licorice-like flavor of anise but don\'t want to spend time baking to enjoy it, our gummy bears are a great alternative. This charming treat includes jell candy that\'s shaped into handsome standing bears!Each ursine figure includes round years and a human-like pose. The confection is dark brown and covered in delightful texture. Our bulk anise bear candies are ideal for any purpose. Use them to fil candy bowls at birthday parties or put them in treat bags so guests can enjoy them after the festivities.They also make unique decorations for gingerbread houses and other edible displays. Put them on cakes, cupcakes, cookies and more to create an original look that tastes amazing! Enjoy anise in a whole new way with our one-of-a-kind anise gummy bears! Our bulk candy packs will make sure you always have enough for any occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/anise-bears-5lbs.gif', '611~anise-bears-5lbs.gif', 'anise-bears'),
(612, 'Haribo Gummi Strawberries', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Feel like you\'re at the strawberry patch with these Haribo Gummi Strawberries! Modeled after the delicious fruit, these adorable berries are packed with fresh strawberry flavor that will make your snackers smile. Use them on top of strawberry shortcake to add a level of cuteness that can\'t be beat. Or bring them to a picnic and let people snack as their own leisure. These strawberries can do it all. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-strawberries.jpg', '612~haribo-strawberries.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-strawberries'),
(613, 'German Raspberries', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Haribo German raspberries recreate the sweet taste of this popular fruit in an irresistible confection! Each bag contains a combination of red and black berry candies. Instead of sticking with plain gummies, Haribo creates a smooth, chewy center that\'s covered in dainty orbs of sugary goodness. Every bite presents two distinct textures in one tasty tidbit! Order our bulk raspberry candies for special events or snacking at home. Whether you\'re hosting a party, picnic, school event or wedding, our German raspberries are a great choice! Haribo has been serving up some of the most delectable gummy candies for nearly a century. Today their catalog includes many unique confections that offer mouthwatering flavor in little bite sized pieces. Our bulk German raspberries are easy to store so you can hide a bag in your favorite snacking spots so you\'re ready the next time your sweet tooth strikes! Haribo gummy candy will tempt taste buds and satisfy cravings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/e/germanraspberries.jpeg', '613~germanraspberries.jpeg', 'german-raspberries-12ct'),
(614, 'Gourmet 12 Flavor Gummy Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Get ready for the fanciest gummy in the forest with these Gourmet Gummy Bears! In an array of colors and flavors, these colorful cubs come bursting with classic fruity, gummy flavor amd a luxurious chew. Enjoy a rainbow of bears from red to blue to white. Let your little ones laugh and play as these bears march into their mouths. In this bulk selection, these bears are the perfect choice to make a candy buffet bar even fancier. They\'re also great wrapped in individual bags and given out as party favors, put in a bowl of punch for a fruity, chewy surprise, or even to reward your little ones whenever you choose. Discover why these gourmet gummies are \'\'bear-resistible!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gourmet-gummy-bears-12-flavors-5lb_1.jpg', '614~gourmet-gummy-bears-12-flavors-5lb_1.jpg', 'gummy-bears-12-flavors'),
(615, 'Blue Raspberry Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'This is one time when everybody should be allowed to play with their food. And who could resist with these delightful blue raspberry Gummi Bears? Perfectly poppable. Charmingly chewy. Crafted with the care of a tried and true recipe. Everyone will go back for handful after handful of these fruity cuties.WIth each bag brimming with over 145 Gummi Bears per pound, you\'ll have enough furry friends to keep you company through numerous snack times. Their light fruity flavor has made this variety a hit among customers and will keep everyone coming back for more. They\'re what we like to call, \'\'bear-resistible.\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-raspberry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '615~blue-raspberry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'blue-raspberry-gummi-bears'),
(616, 'Gummi Killer Sharks', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Don\'t worry. These killer shark gummies are real softies. As a matter of fact, they are way more afraid of your chompers than of their own! (Cue \'\'Jaws\'\' music). With blue and white coloring, they\'re a bright and tasty candy for a number of events. Delight your kids and throw them a pirate birthday party complete with these toothed treats or pack some into their lunchboxes on a special day. Everyone will have fun playing with these big fish until it\'s time for them to swim into your mouth. They might even be the yummiest fish in under the sea.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummy-killer-sharks-470x470.jpg', '616~gummy-killer-sharks-470x470.jpg', 'gummi-killer-sharks-blue-white'),
(617, 'Haribo Gummi Dinosaurs', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Travel back in time for some prehistoric fun with our gummy dinosaurs! These tasty treats give children an excuse to play with their food before they eat it. Each chewy gummy candy features one of many popular dinos. Overpower taste buds with a realistic T-rex or charge through snack time with a triceratops. From stegosauruses to brontosauruses, everyone\'s favorite species are covered in our bulk candy pack!As if dinosaur shaped gummies weren\'t enough, our terrible lizards are colored half and half so you get two brilliant hues in every piece! These tempting treats are perfect for themed birthday parties, picnics or trips to the natural history museum. Our bulk candy package also makes it easy to get more of the dino gummies you love for gatherings, school events and other occasions. These confectionary treats don\'t roar, but they pack a powerful taste that is sure to satisfy any rampaging sweet tooth!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dinosaurs-gummy-haribo.jpg', '617~dinosaurs-gummy-haribo.jpg', 'gummi-dinosaurs-5lb'),
(618, 'Sunkist Fruit Gems', 69.99, '', '', 'gummy', 'Get ready for a big, sugary smooch with these Sunkist Fruit Gems! Their delicious, gummy chew and bright, fruity flavor will make you want to pucker up for more every time you take a bite. Individually wrapped, these little gummies pack the power of the sun into every chew and show off the beautiful colors of the rainbow.Stock yourself up with some rainy day sunshine with a bag of these. They\'re a great goodie bag stuffer for birthday parties, look lovely at a summertime picnic on the dessert table, and even can be kept to cheer up your little ones on a rainy day. With 42 pieces per pound, there are enough to please every gummy fan!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', '618~sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk'),
(619, 'Grape Purple Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Grape gummi bears are packed with fabulous flavor! Our chewy confections offer excellent quality in a timeless snack that children have loved for decades. There\'s something endearing about the dainty bear faces and chubby little teddy bodies that makes this fruity candy unique. We bring you single-color bulk gummy bears so you can get your favorite flavors without picking through an assortment!Our gummies are also ideal for special occasions. Decorate tables at parties and weddings by putting out glass bowls filled with purple bears! You can hide a few in favor bags to give guests as a delicious thank you! These charming little treats are also great for baby showers and other child-related celebrations. Each gummy bear offers irresistible grape flavor with a soft, chewy texture. It\'s nearly impossible to eat just one! Also check out our other bulk gummy bear packs to find the exact combination of colors you need for any event or occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-grape-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '619~purple-grape-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'purple-grape-gummi-bears'),
(620, 'Haribo Gummi Gold Bears Mini Bags Tub', 13.99, '54', 'ct', 'gummy', 'We sure think that these gummies are \'\'tastier than the average bear!\'\' That\'s because these classic Haribo Gold Gummi Bears are here in a bulk bag to bring you even more of the delicious flavors you love. In a selection of red, orange, yellow, green, and white, everyone in your family will find a cub to love. Sprinkle a few in Jell-O for a \'\'beary\'\' good surprise, add some to a make your own sundae bar, or wrap some up for a loved one to make their day extra special. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', '620~haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-gold-bears-mini-bags-tub'),
(621, 'main image', 11.99, '', '', 'gummy', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drop and gum drops, then we wouldn\'t have room to try these amazing Spice Drops Candies! Coated in sweet, crystalized sugar with a spicy, gummy center, these candies will make your \'\'jaw drop!\'\' In a variety of colors and flavors, these gummies can be used for virtually any occasion. Use some to decorate a gingerbread house in a delicious, traditional way, bring some to a party for kids to munch on while they play, or even add them to a make your own ice cream sundae bar for a surprising topping. You\'ll love chewing on these gum drops as much as watching their sugar sparkle.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spice-drops-gumdrops-alt-470x470.jpg', '621~spice-drops-gumdrops-alt-470x470.jpg', 'spice-drops'),
(622, 'Haribo Gummi Gold Bears', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Silly old bear. These classic Haribo Gold Gummi Bears are here in a bulk bag to bring you even more of the tasty flavors you love. In a selection of red, orange, yellow, green, and white, everyone in your family will find a cub to love. Sprinkle a few in Jell-O for a \'\'beary\'\' good surprise, add some to a make your own sundae bar, or wrap some up for a loved one to make their day extra special. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so n the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gold-bears-gummi-icon.jpg', '622~haribo-gold-bears-gummi-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gold-gummi-bears'),
(623, 'Swedish Fish Red', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'It\'s not polite to fish for compliments. But these gilled little gummies just can\'t help themselves! With their bright, cherry flavor and craveable chewiness, Swedish fish have swam their way out of the sea into the hearts of millions. The original flavor and shape of their brand, these little swimmers have inspired the Swedish Fish AquaLife variety as well as Assorted colors and flavors. They\'ve quickly become the biggest fish in the pond and are a beloved candy staple for people around the world. Dive into this bulk bag and \'\'sea\'\' for yourself what all the fuss is about.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/swedish-fish-red-5lbs_2.jpg', '623~swedish-fish-red-5lbs_2.jpg', 'swedish-fish-red'),
(624, 'Gold Bears Theater Box', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Snack like a king with the Haribo Gold Bears theater box! Whether you love action, comedy, drama or a good animated flick, this handy box of candy will be ready to keep your taste buds busy while you enjoy the show! Our bulk candy pack includes a number of individual boxes so you can share them with a group or keep a few around for easy munching. You know when you\'re reaching for the gold box you\'re getting Haribo\'s finest gummy bears!Each package includes a generous helping of soft, chewy gummy pieces. The fun bear shape is great for children while movie goers of all ages will love the sweet fruit flavor packed into every morsel. Order multiple cases and host a neighborhood movie night at home or keep for special occasions like sleep overs, picnics, parties and more! Any time is a good time to sink your teeth into Haribo gummy bears!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo_gold_bears_theater.jpg', '624~haribo_gold_bears_theater.jpg', 'gold-bears-theater-box-12ct'),
(625, 'Green Apple Gummy Rings Candy', 15.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'We\'re green with envy just thinking about the lucky munchers of these yummy gummies! Sugary, sweet, and packed with a green apple punch, these green and white candies really hit the spot. Put them on your fingers and pop them in your mouth one at a time. Spruce up a St. Patrick\'s day candy display. Even set some out for wedding or birthday party guests to munch on. Whatever you do, these green apple gummy rings are coated with enough sugar and taste to make everyone smile, chew after chew. So what are you waiting for? Make us wish we had a bag of our own.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/p/apple-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', '625~apple-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', 'apple-rings-gummy-candy'),
(626, 'White Pineapple Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'If you\'re putting together a formal dessert table or buffet, don\'t forget the White Pineapple Gummi Bears. They\'re a perfect kid-friendly treat that won\'t clash with the decor for weddings and other formal events. Everyone wins! With these off-white to yellow-colored gummy candies, the kids get the desserts they like, and the adults get the beautiful settings they want. There is some color variation in manufacturing, but it won\'t be nearly as much as if your kids got to choose what went on the dessert tray!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/white-pineapple-gummi-bears-5lbs.jpg', '626~white-pineapple-gummi-bears-5lbs.jpg', 'white-pineapple-gummi-bears'),
(627, 'Green Apple Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Our bulk gummi bears are the perfect choice for anyone who loves the chewy taste of this classic candy. Whether you are buying for a special event or want to perform flavor-specific experiments at home. We can help! Our green apple gummi bears offer the tangy bite of sour with a bit of apple sweetness. They also make great treats to go with school lunches or as a quick snack at home!Each adorable little edible bear includes the famous round years, chubby paws and endearing smile that kids have come to love. You\'ll savor the green apple taste and love the smooth, chewy texture. Gummi bears have been tempting children since the 1920s. Their fun shapes were inspired by trained bears that performed in street festivals throughout Europe. Today we can enjoy that save festive experience in each delicious gummy piece! Whether you eat the one at a time or by the handful, our green apple sour gummy bears will satisfy any sweet tooth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/granny-smith-apple-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '627~granny-smith-apple-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'green-apple-gummi-bears'),
(628, 'Freedom Rings Gummies', 17.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Let freedom ring with these patriotic gummy candies! Gummies have been enjoyed for generations and across many countries. Each variation offers a delicious taste and chewy texture that makes it irresistible.Our Freedom Rings gummies are no different, however they offer a patriotic look that is perfect for special occasions celebrated in America!Each package contains many round rings of smooth, gummy goodness! Each ring includes a two toned pattern, with one half in snow white and the other in either brilliant blue or firecracker red. All are sprinkled in sweet sugar granules for even more delicious taste and texture.Freedom Rings gummies are a must-have at summer picnics, family reunions and baseball games. Create gorgeous baked goods by decorating cakes, cupcakes and more with these fun gummy rings! Our bulk Freedom Rings gummy pack gives you larger quantities that are convenient for holidays, wedding favors and community events.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/freedom-gummi-rings-red-white-blue-candystore.jpg', '628~freedom-gummi-rings-red-white-blue-candystore.jpg', 'freedom-rings-gummies'),
(629, 'Gummy Butterflies', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Hearts are a-flutter for these beautiful butterfly gummies! With 3 lovely gummies in every pound, you can let your taste buds take flight with every sensational bite. Hatched from their cocoon, these little gummies will make you swoon with their vibrant rainbow of colors and fruity flavors. Bring them to a little girl\'s birthday party, sprinkle some into a refreshing punch at a springtime picnic, or give your kids a lesson about the beauty of nature. Known to us as the nectar of the candy gods, see for yourself why these dainty flutterers make sweet lovers feel like they can fly.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '629~gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy'),
(630, 'Sour Patch Watermelon Slices', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Sour Patch Watermelon Slices look like tiny, sugar-dusted pieces of watermelon. Their pink and green coloring makes them perfect to put out at any pink-themed party. They\'ll make a great addition to a bachelorette party or baby shower. They\'re also a perfect pick for Valentine\'s, as their sour taste is sure to make your guests pucker up! You can get these deliciously tart chewy watermelon candies in a big bulk bag, but don\'t let the size fool you. They\'ll be gone before you know it.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-slices-5lbs_2.jpg', '630~watermelon-slices-5lbs_2.jpg', 'watermelon-slices'),
(631, 'Red Cherry Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Cherry gummy bears are great for any occasion. They are soft and chewy as well as a great red color that even adults love to take part in. These would make a great purchase for Valentine \'s Day or Christmas due to the fabulous red shade that they have.When you bite into one of these gummy bears you are sure to find that the ripe flavor of cherry is more than enough to please your mouth. Since they come in a bulk bag it is sure to be enough to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for. If you are looking for a way to delight almost everyone then this is certainly one of the great candies that is able to do this. After all who doesn\'t like the way that these candies are so cute and fun? It is hard to beat the greatness of this wonderful product.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '631~cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-gummi-bears'),
(632, 'White Gummi Bears Strawberry Banana', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Don\'t let their pristine, white color fool you. Or their dainty size. These petite Gummi Bears have the powerful strawberry banana flavor of a giant grizzly. Roar! Pretty enough for a wedding candy display, they also are right at home in a five star candy buffet or as a neutral filler candy in gift bags. With an average of 145 bears per pound, you will have an entire forest-full of flavorful friends to share with friends and family. Chewy and fruity, these Gummies are crowd pleasers. And we would like to think of them as way tastier than the average bear.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears_1.jpg', '632~white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears_1.jpg', 'white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears'),
(633, 'Haribo Gummi Raspberries', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Haribo gummi raspberries look like real raspberries! Put them in a candy dish at your next gathering and watch your guests get surprised with a gummi taste explosion when they pick one up. These delicious fruity snacks come as a mix of red and black in a big bulk bag. Be careful opening them up, though. Once you start, you won\'t want to stop eating these sweet raspberry gummies. Get them for your candy dish at home or the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', '633~haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-raspberries'),
(634, 'Sour Gummi Poppers', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Try not to drool. These Sour Gummi Poppers have a tart flavor that will make your mouth water! With a bright pastel selection of red, blue, yellow, green, and orange candies, there\'s an entire rainbow of sour for you to choose from. Every candy is coated in a tangy sugar that leads to a sweet, fruity center. Use a handful of these colorful pucker-makers for a candy dish on your coffee table, put some in a glass jar and enjoy looking at them as much as eating them, or even add some to a candy buffet bar for guests to enjoy at their own leisure. We\'re sure you\'ll love puckering with these poppable candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', '634~sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sour-gummi-poppers'),
(635, 'Gummi Frogs', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Everyone will jump for joy when they get a taste of Haribo gummy frogs! These little green candies aren\'t slippery and slimy, but they offer a smooth, soft texture that\'s pleasant on the tongue. Each piece includes fun details that recreate this popular amphibian â€“ right down to its folded legs, round head and raised back. Our gummy frogs are solid green and arrive fresh in sealed bags that are ready to enjoy! Hide gummi frogs around the house or save them to put in school lunches for the kids. These charming croakers are also great for serving at birthday parties, picnics and school events. Put them in a bowl or use them to dress up cakes, cupcakes, cookies and more! No matter how you display them, our Haribo gummy candies will entice children of all ages. Order our bulk candy pack so you have plenty of chewy frogs for any occasion!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', '635~haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', 'gummi-frogs-12ct'),
(636, 'Gummi Bears', 15.49, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Why didn\'t the teddy bear eat his lunch? Because he was stuffed! You\'ll be stuffed after eating mouthful after mouthful of these assorted gummi bears. In a big bulk bag of rainbow fruity cuties, you\'ll have a lot to chew about. Bring these little cubs to a birthday party. Put them in a sparkling punch at a backyard barbeque. Spoil your little ones by tucking some of these away in their lunch boxes. Or even fill goodie bags with a handful of these yummy gummies. Whatever you do, you\'ll love sampling the rainbow of colors and flavors. They\'re \'\'bear-resistable!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummi-bears-5lbs_2.jpg', '636~gummi-bears-5lbs_2.jpg', 'gummi-bears'),
(637, 'Fruit Slices Candy', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Fruit slices gummies are a fabulous treat that comes in many exciting flavors! If you love chewy gummy candy but want more options when it comes to taste, this is a must-try.Our delicious fruit slices candy include a flat wedge shape slab of confection with a flat end and curved side. A white line runs along the curved edge, creating the look of a fruit rind.Every fruit slice is different based on its flavor. Grape is all purple while black cherry includes a red middle with blue â€œrindâ€. We carry a huge variety of juicy flavors that also include lemon lime, cherry, strawberry banana, orange, pink grapefruit, peach, watermelon, sour apple, red raspberry and blue raspberry.If you can\'t decide on just one, you can instead choose our amazing assorted bulk fruit slices pack! This mouthwatering blend contains a little bit of everything so you can sample all your chewy favorites!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', '637~albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', 'fruit-slices-candy'),
(638, 'Orange Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Orange you excited about these? Because we are! A real knee-slapper, we know. But in all seriousness, these pint sized, orange Gummi Bears are packed with crisp citrus flavor that will have you smacking your lips with every chew. Use them to make a thematic Halloween display or drop them into a refreshing summer punch. They make delightful gift bag stuffers and even cake toppers, too. A popular and well-known chew among candy lovers, these make a great choice in satisfying all of your friends and family. Whatever occasion you can dream up, let these adorable bears brighten your day.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '638~orange-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'orange-gummi-bears'),
(639, 'Gumdrops', 11.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drops and gumdrops, then we\'d be out of business! However, you can still feel like it\'s raining gumdrops with this bulk bag of gummy candies. A classic addition for holiday baked goods, stockings, and fancy gingerbread houses, you will be stocked up for the season with this bag. In a variety of colors and fruity flavors, savor the sweetness as the sugary coating melts in your mouth. Then get ready to chew \'til you drop with a yummy gummy center. The holidays just aren\'t complete without a few mouthfuls of these sugary sweets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gumdrops-5lbs.gif', '639~gumdrops-5lbs.gif', 'gumdrops'),
(640, 'Haribo Gummi Peaches', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'You\'re a peach! Well, actually these Haribo Gummi Peaches are. In a sugary coating and delicious light peach flavor, bite into these chewy gummies for a taste of the summertime. Bring some to a warm weather BBQ, add some as a pretty drink garnish to lemonade and adult drinks, or even use them to decorate the top of a strawberry shortcake! Haribo bears first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany. To this day, they\'re one of the biggest manufacturers of gummies and supply happy snackers all around the world. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so _ the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', '640~haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-peaches'),
(641, 'Mini Neon Sour Gummy Worms', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'They\'re creepy. They\'re crawly. And they\'re also delicious? Yeah, we know. An unexpected turn to what you thought these Mini Neon Sour Gummy Worms might be. But rest assured, these little wrigglers are so yummy!In a rainbow of colors, these colorful mini gummy worms are packed with fruity flavor and a burst of sour sugar flavor that will make you pucker. Make your next Halloween bash even creepier with these night crawlers. You can set them out in a dish, add them to the top of a special Halloween cake, or just munch on them to gross out your little ones.Or if you\'re planning on a birthday party for boys and girls who love bugs and all things crawly, then order yourself a bulk bag of these Mini Neon Sour Gummy Worms for that!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mini-neon-sour-gummy-worms-470x470_3.jpg', '641~mini-neon-sour-gummy-worms-470x470_3.jpg', 'mini-neon-sour-gummy-worms'),
(642, 'Red Cherry Gummy Rings Candy', 15.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'We\'re seeing red. Red Cherry Gummy Rings, to be exact! These glistening gummies are coated with sweet specks of sugar for you to enjoy as they melt away in your mouth. Their bright red and white coloring is pleasing to the eye as well to the taste buds. Bite into these mini rings for a healthy dose of sweet cherry flavor that will make your mouth water. Put them on your fingers and pop them in your mouth one at a time. Add them to a holiday display. Even set some out for wedding or birthday party guests to munch on. Whatever you do, these red cherry gummy rings are coated with enough sugar and taste to make everyone smile, chew after chew.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', '642~cherry-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', 'cherry-rings-gummy-candy'),
(643, 'Swedish Fish Assorted', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Swedish Fish are one of the world\'s most classic and recognizable gummy candies. The red candy fish are instantly recognizable, and they\'re guaranteed to get your mouth watering. As if that wasn\'t good enough, you can get a big bulk bag of assorted flavors and colors of the classic gummy candy fish. That\'s right; you can get them in red, yellow, green, and orange, too. It\'s a simple and delicious twist on an old favorite.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/swedish-fish-assorted-5lbs_2.jpg', '643~swedish-fish-assorted-5lbs_2.jpg', 'swedish-fish-assorted'),
(644, 'Swedish Fish Red Mini', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'They may be the size of sardines, but these Swedish Fish Red Minis have a punch of cherry burst that rivals some of the biggest fish in the sea. The original flavor and shape of their brand, these little swimmers have swam their way into the hearts and stomachs of thousands of candy lovers. With a soft, chewy bite and gummy center, they\'ve quickly become the biggest fish in the pond and a beloved candy staple for people around the world. Dive into this bulk bag of Swedish Fish Red Minis and \'\'sea\'\' for yourself what all the fuss is about.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/swedish-fish-red-mini-5lbs_2.jpg', '644~swedish-fish-red-mini-5lbs_2.jpg', 'swedish-fish-red-mini'),
(645, 'Watermelon Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Who doesn\'t love the flavor of watermelon? This gummies have the great flavor that you love as well as the fun and exciting color of pink. The texture is fun and chewy. This is a great item for children and even adults. It will be fun to add to a candy buffet for your next birthday party.If you are looking for the fun and exciting flavor of watermelon without the mess, pain of cutting the watermelon, and the seeds that come with real fresh watermelon then this is what you need. These great gummy bears are approximately one inch each in size. This is sure to make your mouth water and keep you coming back for more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-pink-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '645~watermelon-pink-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'watermelon-pink-gummi-bears'),
(646, 'Gummi Fruit Salad', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Haribo gummi fruit salad combines all your favorite flavors in one convenient package! Since 1920, Haribo has been producing new confections for the world to enjoy. Their current selection features a number of the most popular sugary snacks, including our irresistible gummy fruit salad! Every bag contains a selection of brightly colored chewy pieces that feature recognizable shapes that make mouths water.Reach into a bag of gummy fruit salad and enjoy the sweet sensation of orange, lime, cherry and more! Every piece is brightly colored in red, green, orange and other hues that match their fruity counterparts. This fat free candy is covered in a generous dusting of sugar for added texture and taste. Enjoy it as a guilt-free snack at home or buy our bulk candy pack and get plenty of Haribo fruit pieces to serve at any event. This nature-inspired confection is a big hit at picnics, parties, summer events and school activities!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/0/108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', '646~108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', 'gummi-fruit-salad-12ct'),
(647, 'Gummi Penguins', 11.99, '2.2', 'lb', 'gummy', 'It\'s the \'\'march of the penguin\'\' gummies! These curious little penguins are full of funny antics and will make your next snack even more charming and delicious! In every bag of these Penguin Gummies, these white and black treats will waddle, splash, and swim into your mouths. They\'re a great snack for kids to play with and an even more adorable treat to look at! These fancy tuxedo clad birds make a cute addition to any black tie, formal affair, wedding reception, or even as a gift to a penguin-loving friend or family lover. Get a taste of the arctic with this gummy, fruity snack today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', '647~gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', 'gummi-penguins'),
(648, 'Fruit Slices Lemon', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Want a candy that is able to look just like a lemon slice? If so, then you have found it. These lemon candies look almost like really lemon slices. They have a nice yellow color to them and then have a white curve through them to make it appear like the skin is still on the lemon. They texture is smooth and this great candy is able to combine sweetness with the taste of citrus. You can tell just by looking at them that they are going to please your mouth as you get to take part in eating them. These candies would make a great garnishment and they would be great all on their own as well. You could use them at some special event or party that you were having or just buy them to keep around the house. Children and adults are both sure to enjoy the great taste of these.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruit-slices-lemon-5lb_2.jpg', '648~fruit-slices-lemon-5lb_2.jpg', 'fruit-slices-lemon'),
(649, 'Blueberry Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Get ready for your tongues to turn blue! These Blueberry Old Fashioned Candy Sticks have enough blueberry power to dye your mouth and satisfy your sweet tooth. Having a blue themed birthday party for a family member or friend? Celebrating the birth of a baby boy? Want to add some pop of flavor to typical punches and lemonades? These classic candy sticks can do that all and more with a delicious, long lasting flavor. With 80 individually wrapped candy sticks in each box, you\'ll have enough to go around. Get a taste of summertime\'s favorite berry with your order of these tasty sticks today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blueberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', '649~blueberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', 'blueberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(650, 'Gilliam Hard Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned hard candy sticks are the ultimate go-to treat for anyone with a sweet tooth. Stick candy has been a favorite of young and old since the mid-1800s, and it\'s no wonder why. Each piece features a unique flavor and fun colors that make every lick a memorable experience! Simply peel away the hard candy wrapper and you are ready to snack. Each piece is individually wrapped so they are easy to store and can be given as party favors or a special treat for the kids!We carry a huge list of exciting flavors so you never get bored. Try exotic pina colada, orange pineapple or rum and butter! If you prefer something simpler, classic bubblegum, peppermint, sassafras or strawberry are just as enticing. You\'ll love watching the striped candy melt away with each bite! Grab the old family photo album and your favorite flavors and relive your childhood memories with Gilliam hard candy sticks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', '650~stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', 'old-fashioned-stick-candy-box-flavors'),
(651, 'Spearmint Leaves Candy', 10.99, '5', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned spearmint leaves gummies are a chewy treat that will invigorate your taste buds! This elegant candy features a tapered leaf shape, with a narrow tip and wider base.The sides include subtle scalloping Ã must like real foliage! A short stem extends from the base, adding even more detail to these eye-catching candies. Every piece is covered in a gentle green hue that looks even more enticing covered in sugar crystals!Every bite is packed with amazing spearmint flavor. Give your mouth something cool and refreshing to chew on with these all-purpose leaf gummies. Spearmint leaves are also a unique way to decorate cakes, cupcakes and cookies.Add realistic elements to your gingerbread houses or use them to enhance edible dÅ½cor. Our bulk spearmint leaves candy gives you many pounds so you have plenty of individual pieces to experiment with. Or you can keep things simple by pouring spearmint gummies into a bowl to serve any guests who stop by!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/brachs-spearmint-leaves-small-img.jpg', '651~brachs-spearmint-leaves-small-img.jpg', 'spearmint-leaves-candy'),
(652, 'Grape Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Grape candy sticks are the best way to enjoy this popular flavor any time you want it! Hard candy sticks are tasty and convenient. Each arrives individually wrapped so you can hide them anywhere â€“ in your purse, in a drawer or in the candy jar! Each piece includes a length of tube shaped hard candy in dark plumb with a distinctive white stripe that spirals from end to end.Our hard candy sticks offer a great taste that lasts a long time. Savor every lick of grapey-goodness when you enjoy one of these irresistible sweets! Break one in half for a quick snack or sit down and relax with an entire stick. Every piece offers the nostalgic appeal of old fashioned candy in a product that\'s just as sweet and tempting as any modern confection. Place your grape sticks in a glass jar and take them to the office, a party or leave them at home so you\'re always ready to satisfy sugary cravings!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', '652~grape-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', 'grape-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(653, 'Mary Jane Candy', 20.99, '', '', 'old-fashioned', 'When you\'re in the mood for something extra chewy, try our sweet Mary Jane candies! These delectable delights are small bars of smooth taffy treats. Each is flavored with rich molasses and peanut butter to give it that memorable taste that kids of all ages have been asking for since 1914. The candy is a historic favorite that was named after its creator\'s beloved aunt â€“ a worthy choice for such a nostalgic confection!Each taffy candy is covered in a bright yellow wrapper with a bold red stripe and classic logo printed around both sides. You\'ll love Mary Janes even more when you buy our bulk candy package! Order larger quantities so you have plenty to share at family gatherings and other events. Use them to fill the office candy jar or use them to fill treat bags for birthdays and more! Our bulk Mary Janes are also convenient to hand out on trick or treat night around Halloween!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', '653~mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'mary-janes-candy'),
(654, 'Pina Colada Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned hard candy is a timeless treat that you can take anywhere â€“ even the beach! Imagine sitting back on a lounge chair while sun bathing along the seashore with a pina colada candy stick in hand. Our famous Gilliam candy sticks are easy to pack because they come individually wrapped. Just grab a few and tuck away in your beach tote! Each piece includes a sunny yellow color with a thick white stripe that can be displayed in a glass jar to brighten the kitchen.Our bulk hard candy package includes enough sticks to go around - even when hosting a large event like a wedding or birthday celebration! Bring a little slice of paradise to the occasion with these delectable confections. You can also include them in party or wedding favors so guests can take the tropical fun with them after the festivities have concluded. Enjoy the flavors of an exotic paradise everywhere you go with our pina colada hard candy sticks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pina-colada-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '654~pina-colada-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'pina-colada-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(655, 'Blue Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Feeling blue never felt so sweet! Stock up with these pint-sized, blue raspberry sticks for a color-themed party, birth of a baby boy, or to place around your home. They\'re even great for a winter-themed party or Hanukkah event. At half the size of regular candy sticks, they\'re the perfect fruity affair for a midday treat or any occasion you can think up. Candy sticks look lovely displayed in a glass jar and can give any candy bar buffet a retro feel. Suck on one of these for an explosion of fruity flavor that your friends and family are sure to love.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '655~blue-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'blue-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(656, 'Blackberry Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Enjoy an all-time, American favorite berry without having to combat any of the prickers or seeds in your teeth! These Old Fashioned Blackberry Candy Sticks have a lovely and girly swirl of pink between the dark black candy, making them an ideal addition to any baby shower, wedding reception, dessert display, or even little or teen girl birthday parties. The delicious blackberry flavor will remind you of warm summer days picking berries and can make a great addition to a lemonade or daiquiri! Use your imagination and decide how you\'d like to use these delectable sticks to make your life yummier.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blackberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '656~blackberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'blackberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(657, 'Licorice Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'When it comes to class and dignity there is nothing like a black tie affair. Now there is a candy that is tailor made for these fancy occasions.  Old Fashioned Licorice Candy Sticks add class and sophistication to any occasion. They have elegant black color with delicate white stripes running through them. Each licorice stick comes individually wrapped and will look formal in a display or in a person\'s pocket just waiting to be eaten. Put a glass jar of these delicious treats on your coffee table and people will start to wear a tie when they come for a visit. These hard candy sticks will provide the elegance and grace to any formal gathering that all event planners are looking for.  This is five inches of traditional candy goodness that will put the smile back on a person\'s face and make all people realize the class and dignity that you possess!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '657~licorice-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'licorice-old-fashioned-stick-candy');
INSERT INTO `candy` (`id`, `title`, `price`, `amount`, `units`, `category`, `description`, `original_image_url`, `local_image`, `page`) VALUES
(658, 'Tangerine Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Tangerine candy sticks will make your taste buds tingle with citrusy goodness! Gilliam old fashioned candy sticks are a must-have treat for all candy lovers. This popular confection is reminiscent of classic candy shops and fond childhood memories.Our tangerine hard candy includes a deep orange hue that\'s accentuated by a pure white stripe that twists from end to end like a barbershop pole. Gilliam hard candy sticks aren\'t just beautiful to look at, they amazing to taste! Each is individually wrapped so they stay fresh and ready to enjoy.Tear one end and experience the exciting taste of tangerine along with the smoothness of quality hard candy. Use alone or combine with our other bulk candy stick packages to display in jars, vases and more. Candy sticks are also a great choice for wedding favors, shower favors, after school snacks and can be given as a special reward for students.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/a/tangerine_stick_candy.jpg', '658~tangerine_stick_candy.jpg', 'tangerine-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(659, 'IBC Root Beer Barrels Candy', 34.99, '8', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'Ladies and gentlemen, boys and girls, we present you with the 8th wonder of the world, IBC rootbeer barrel candies! At least we think it\'s a wonder that IBC found a way to mimic their frothy, refreshing, world-famous root beer in a tiny hard candy. You\'ll feel like you\'re sipping a bubbly fountain soda on a hot summer day every time you pop one of these into your mouth. The adorable barrels make an exceptional and thematic display at beer festivals and are a timeless choice for your candy dishes. See for yourself why people can\'t get enough of this groundbreaking treat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rootbeerbarrels.jpg', '659~rootbeerbarrels.jpg', 'ibc-root-beer-barrels-candy'),
(660, 'Lemon Lime Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Lemon and lime. Undoubtedly, one of the most famous duos to ever hit our taste buds. Now combined with a classic candy shoppe treat, these Lemon Lime Old Fashioned Candy Sticks are here to continue a tradition of fabulous citrusy flavor. Their green and yellow colored swirls are a perfect complement to their bright, fruity taste. Stock up on these for a fantastic lemonade stirrer or summertime punch garnish, use them as a bright addition to any candy buffet bar, or just have some around the house for any of your classic candy fans to enjoy. With 8 individually wrapped candy sticks in each box, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/e/lemon-lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '660~lemon-lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'lemon-lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(661, 'Bubblegum Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Bubblegum, bubblegum in a dish. How many pieces do you wish? Apparently, you\'re wishing for a whole 80 count bag of Bubblegum Old Fashioned Candy Sticks! With a rainbow of red, yellow, blue, green, and white, these sticks are tasty as they are beautiful. Their hard candy crunch and colorful style make them the perfect candy for amongst any event you can dream up. Stick one in a cool fruity drink as an adorable and unique stirrer. Display these in a glass vase on your kitchen counter for a lovely look. Even bring these to a party and set them out on the dessert table as a different and delicious treat! You\'ll love these bubblegum sticks no matter what you do.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bubblegum_stick_candy.jpg', '661~bubblegum_stick_candy.jpg', 'bubblegum-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(662, 'Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates Tub', 22.99, '240', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'When you think of classy candy then immediately Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates jump to mind. These delicious treats have been sold in a delightful and recognizable green wrapping. When a person sees that wrapping they know that wherever they are, it is a place filled with class. It could be a restaurant that provides a free snack with the bill. It could be left on the pillow in a hotel. Even if it is in your own home the person who sees the shiny green wrapper will know that they are dealing with a person and a place that knows class. The chocolate treat is the reason for this as it provides a delicious chocolate treat with the blast of creamy goodness that shakes your taste buds and zaps them awake. There is just the right minty freshness to allow you to feel refreshed. There will always be enough class around with a tub of Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub-240ct_1.jpg', '662~andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub-240ct_1.jpg', 'andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub'),
(663, 'Wintergreen Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Wintergreen Candy Sticks are an excellent addition to any holiday, Christmas, or Birthday party. These Candy Sticks are made using natural and artificial flavorings, they are gluten free and certified kosher. Wintergreen Candy Sticks are a perfect on the go treat, and a great way to tell your customers thank you. Place these Candy Sticks in an old fashioned jar for a nostalgic feel, in a decorative mug for easy access, or treat bags for that extra special addition. Wintergreen Sticks are flavorful and provide a long lasting peppermint flavor. Grab a Wintergreen Candy Stick for an afternoon pick me up, the delicious peppermint will awaken your senses and heighten alertness. Wintergreen Candy Sticks are 5  long making them just the right size for decorative swag on Christmas presents, or in any hot beverage for stirring, and flavor. No matter the use these Wintergreen Candy Sticks are sure to please.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/i/wintergreen_sticks.jpg', '663~wintergreen_sticks.jpg', 'wintergreen-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(664, 'Tutti Frutti Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'This candy has a name that\'s almost as fun to say as the candy is to eat! However, we still think it\'s fruity, sweet flavor is the best part. Try these Tutti Fruiti Old Fashioned Candy Sticks for a delicious burst of bright, fruity flavor. Their beautiful yellow, pink, and green swirls make them a perfect addition to a Mardi Gras party or even for New Years Eve! Try these crunchy, hard candy sticks in cold lemonade or punch for a dose of extra sweetness and fresh, fruity flavor. Even bring some to a party with friends as a delicious dessert or pack them up in a present for a flavor flashback everyone can enjoy. With 8 sticks per order, you\'ll have enough to do it all.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/u/tutti-fruitti-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct.jpg', '664~tutti-fruitti-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct.jpg', 'tutti-fruitti-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(665, 'Nut Goodie Bars', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Nostalgic. Classic. Vintage. You\'re a special kind of candy fan who appreciates where every sweet got its roots. With these Nut Goodie\'s, you can enjoy a taste of yesteryear in every milk chocolatey, nutty bite! Introduced in 1912, Nut Goodie hit candy store shelves for a whopping 5 cents! To this day, not much has changed about the delicious, salty, sweet nut clusters including their vintage wrapper. Add these to a 2\'s themed party for a tasty treat, share a bit of history with loved ones, or surprise your grandmother or grandfather with a taste of their youth. Whatever you do, you\'ll love these tried and true confections.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/u/nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', '665~nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', 'nut-goodie-bars'),
(666, 'Claey\'s Wild Cherry Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'What\'s red, sweet, and delicious all over? These Wild Cherry Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops! Dusted in crystalized, sweet sugar, these bright red candies pack a serious punch of wild cherry flavor that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Bring some to a holiday gathering that needs a dose of festive red, use some to decorate a gingerbread house with a delicious treat, add them to a Fourth of July dessert table, or add a yummy, fruity treat to a Valentine\'s Day gift. With this 1 pound order of wild cherry candies, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys-cherry-candy-drops-small.jpg', '666~claeys-cherry-candy-drops-small.jpg', 'wild-cherry-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(667, 'Orange Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Candy sticks are a favorite of many. These great candy sticks are hard candy that is in the shape of a stick. They are orange in flavor. They also have a great orange color to them that would blend well when use for almost any occasion. You will find that these might really work great around Halloween as each one is individually wrapped, so if you are giving them out to children that you don\'t know then the parents are not as likely to be concerned with it. You can either suck on the sticks until they are gone, or if you are one that likes to crunch then you will be able to do this as well. However, you should know that it is not good for your teeth so do this at your own risks. However, you decide to enjoy your sticks you are sure to find that they will hit the spot.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange_stick_candy.jpg', '667~orange_stick_candy.jpg', 'orange-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(668, 'Long Boys Coconut', 8.99, '48', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Long Boys coconut candy sticks are a classic favorite that\'s full of rich flavor! This traditional candy originated in New Orleans, making it a staple for local children.Today, people all over the country rave about the amazing taste of these long, chewy confections. Every piece includes a stick of candy that\'s individually wrapped in a nostalgic red and yellow wrapper.Coconut Long Boys offer a unique blend of caramel and exotic coconut for a snacking experience that\'s memorable and satisfying! Untwist the wrapper and take small bites to fully enjoy the taste of this one-of-a-kind flavor combination! Kids can try stretching their Long Boy candy to see who can make the longest rope!Our bulk Long Boy coconut candy is a great choice for parties, picnics and family reunions. Use them to fill treat bags for birthdays or set out a bowl or box so adults can munch while reminiscing about their favorite childhood sweets!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', '668~long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', 'long-boys-coconut'),
(669, 'Chocolate Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Chocolate candy sticks are the long lasting treat that\'s delicious and nostalgic! For generations, kids have hurried to their local candy shop to enjoy the sweet taste of flavorful hard candy.Now you can relive those fond memories with your favorite flavor! Gilliam\'s old fashioned candy sticks are simple, elegant and absolutely irresistible.Each lengthy piece includes a solid tube of delectable hard candy with a rich chocolate flavor. This version comes in a dark, deep brown with a brilliant white stripe that runs from end to end. The clear wrapper, emblazoned with the famous Gilliam\'s logo, allows the beautiful pattern to show through. Match our classic candy sticks up with a special event or theme.They are gorgeous when placed upright in jars or vases at showers. Send guests off with something sweet by adding these chocolaty sticks to your wedding favors! Keep them at home as a quick sugar fix or take them to the office and share the Gilliam\'s hard candy stick love with your colleagues and clients.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '669~chocolate-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'chocolate-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(670, 'Butterscotch Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Butterscotch and candy sticks: two classics that have finally united to bring you a nostalgic taste of yesteryear! Bring back the happy, memory-filled days of yore with a lick of one of these Butterscotch Old Fashioned Candy Sticks. Their golden yellow and honey colored swirls are a perfect complement to their rich, buttery taste. Stock up on these for a festive Thanksgiving dessert addition, use them as a delicious hot chocolate stirrer, or just have some around the house for any of your classic candy fans to enjoy. With 8 individually wrapped candy sticks in each box, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/butterscotch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', '670~butterscotch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', 'butterscotch-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(671, 'Rum & Butter Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'We\'re positive that these candies will \'\'butter you up!\'\' That\'s because these Rum Butter Old Fashioned Candy Sticks pack a supremely rich and delicious taste that you won\'t be able to resist. In bright yellow, these little rays of sunshine look like a beautiful pat of butter on a slice of toast. Bring some to your next outdoor party, or even use some in the colder months to stir into a cup of hot cocoa for a warm, rich flavor in a cheerful color. With 8 sticks per order, you\'ll be able to snack happily and decadently for a long, long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/rum-butter-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct-inset.jpg', '671~rum-butter-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct-inset.jpg', 'rum-butter-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(672, 'Green Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Have a lick of one of these Green and White Mini Candy Sticklettes and you\'ll be hooked! Its bright, lime flavor and citrusy burst is an addictive combination that our customers love. Individually wrapped and at half the size of regular candy sticks, these little wonders will make a delightful snack, time after time. Try them for a St. Patrick\'s Day party, a spring backyard barbeque, or even on a gingerbread house as cute little columns! Their bright green and white swirls are a lovely combination and stand out on candy shelves. They make a great candy choice at any time of the year.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '672~green-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'green-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(673, 'Island Punch Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Things are going to get tropical when you try our exotic Island Punch candy sticks! This timeless treat has been enjoyed for decades.Adults and children alike savor the sweet flavor that comes with every delicious stick! Whisk your taste buds off to fruity paradise with each rainbow colored tube of solid hard candy! Gilliam\'s old fashioned candy sticks are known for their superb flavor and elegant design.Each Island Punch candy stick includes vibrant orange, yellow, red and green in lovely spirals that reach from one end to the other. The clear plastic wrapper allows the beautiful pattern to show through, making these hard candies an excellent choice for wedding favors, showers and other special events.Place a handful in a glass vase or jar or add them to an edible gift and impress guests! Our Island Punch candy sticks will conjure images of seaside vacations spent lazing along the sun-kissed sands.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/i/s/island-punch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '673~island-punch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'island-punch-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(674, 'Pineapple Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'A pretty yellow candy stick gets swirled with a green stripe to create the fun visual display of this Pineapple Old-Fashioned Stick Candy. Dress up your Pina Colada with one or put them in glasses of punch or lemonade for kids. They are great for Easter and St. Patrick\'s Day, and if you know someone trying to kick the nicotine habit, these long-lasting candies might be exactly what they need.They are sweet, easy to eat, and as long as you resist the urge to bite, they last a really long time. Each Pineapple Old-fashioned Stick Candy is individually wrapped. This makes them perfect to hand out at parties, share with friends at the campground, or use at Halloween for trick-or-treaters. Their tropical look and taste makes them ideal for beach-themed parties for folks of all ages. They are kosher certified, too.Finding pineapple-flavored candy is not easy. If you have ever specifically looked for it then you know this is a tall order to fill. This is unfortunate, considering it is one of the sweetest and most delicious island fruits. Well, your search is over! This Pineapple Old-Fashioned Stick Candy is exactly what you are looking for and appropriate for any occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pineapple-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '674~pineapple-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'pineapple-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(675, 'Peaches & Cream Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned candy sticks by Gilliam are a must-have treat for any confectionary connoisseur. These delightful sticks of flavor conjure images of simpler times when children rushed to the candy shop to buy their favorite sweets for a few coins.Today you can enjoy that same great taste with Gilliam peaches and cream candy sticks! Each length is packed with enormous fruit flavor and the smooth texture you know and love. Our Gilliam hard candy sticks arrive individually packaged in clear wrappers. This allows you to admire the brilliant hues that decorate each piece.Our Peaches and cream hard candy features a rich blend of bright orange and sunshine yellow that twists from top to bottom. These creamy-sweet candy sticks look fabulous whether you prop them up in a glass vase, candy bowl or use them to fill up party favors! Our bulk old fashioned candy stick pack gives you large quantities that are perfect for holidays, events and other special occasions.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peaches-and-cream-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '675~peaches-and-cream-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'peaches-cream-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(676, 'Orange Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Good things come in small packages. Especially in this Orange and White Mini Sticklette Candy! Feel like you\'re biting into a fresh orange with a burst of juicy flavor in every bite. And enjoy looking at the vibrant orange color every time you snack. Individually wrapped and at half the size of regular candy sticks, these little wonders will make a delightful treat time after time. Spice up a brunch display with by using these little Sticklettes as orange juice stirrers, put them in an orange-themed candy display, or keep them around the house for a cheerful treat. Whatever you do with this mini sticklettes, you\'ll love stirring, licking, and chomping them as much as looking at them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '676~orange-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'orange-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(677, 'Sesame Seed Snaps', 19.99, '24', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Sezme sesame snaps are an amazingly delicious treat that\'s also good for you! If you simply can\'t decide between sweet and salty, you can enjoy both in every bite with these bar shaped confections.Each is packed with savory sesame seed flavor that\'s complemented by a touch of sugary goodness. They come individually wrapped so they stay fresh until it\'s time to snack. Our bulk Sezme sesame snaps are an excellent alternative food to chocolaty or overly sugary treats.Eat better while satisfying your cravings. This Poland-born treat is cholesterol free and gluten free. Take a bite and experience the pleasant crunch and satisfying flavor that taste buds crave. Our bulk sesame snaps box is a must-have for daily snacking.Use them to pack healthier lunches for your family or keep them as a quick and easy after school snack. Sesame seed candy also makes a great Christmas stocking stuffer!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/e/sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', '677~sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', 'sesame-seed-snaps'),
(678, 'Claey\'s Root Beer Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'We\'re rooting for these classic candies. That\'s because Claey\'s Root beer Old-Fashioned Candy Drops are completely coated in crystally, crunchy sugar granules that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Beyond the saccharine coating, lies a delicious hard candy. They\'ll take you back to a warm, summer\'s day of sipping a refreshing root beer float. Stock up on some to add to root beer treats, add to a gift basket, or put out on the Thanksgiving table. Among root beer, Claey\'s favorite flavors include green apple, licorice, natural horehound, watermelon, lemon, and wild cherry. They\'ll look lovely in your coffee table candy dish or set out in a jar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', '678~root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', 'root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(679, 'Spearmint Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'The green that swirls through the sweet, suckable Spearmint Old Fashioned Stick Candy is refreshing to the eye, just as the burst of spearmint flavor it provides is refreshing to the mouth! Finish a meal by providing after-dinner mints in a nostalgic form that will send your guests into raptures of reminiscing delight.Candy sticks remind everyone of childhood trips to the county fair or the farm market, and their stripes are always a dose of high contrast in a display. Sharp spearmint was once much more common in candies than it is today, but a few manufacturers keep the flavor tradition alive!Old-fashioned yet gluten-free and nut-free, these candy sticks are an instant dose of nostalgia when you include them in a selection of elegant emerald-green candy. The possibilities for styling an inventive dessert with the classic sweets are as endless as the rush of freshness in these minty candy sticks.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spearmint_sticks.jpg', '679~spearmint_sticks.jpg', 'spearmint-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(680, 'C. Howard\'s Mints', 22.99, '24', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Get a taste of the olden days with this bulk selection of C. Howard\'s Mints! In vintage flavors of lemon, peppermint, spearmint, and unique violet, you\'ll have the pleasure of tasting a bit of history. Their cute, retro wrappers add a vintage feel to their deliciousness and make them perfect for a nostalgic candy selection. These little candies have been around since the 1930s and have graced both old and new candy store shelves. Give your friends and family a sample of a tried and true candy that has stood the test of time with a box of these today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-howards-mints-24ct_2.gif', '680~c-howards-mints-24ct_2.gif', 'c-howards-mints'),
(681, 'Yellow Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Mirror, mirror on the wall. Who\'s the fairest of them all? These Yellow and White Mini Candy Sticklettes are to us! Their pristine white swirled around bright, cheerful yellow is a show-stopper. Individually wrapped and at half the size of regular candy sticks, these little wonders will make a delightful snack, time after time. Set them out in summertime punches and lemonade for a lovely garnish, put them in a yellow-themed candy display, or keep them around the house for a cheerful reminder of warmer days to come. Whatever you do with this mini sticklettes, you\'ll love stirring, licking, and chomping them as much as looking at them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/e/yellow-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '681~yellow-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'yellow-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(682, 'Lime Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Let\'s start with the obvious, shall we? If the mere sight of these Lime Candy Sticks doesn\'t inspire you to throw a party, nothing will!Leprechauns will be coming out of the woodwork to get their hands on these tasty treats on St. Patrick\'s Day, and of course, they will be the perfect complement to other holiday candy at Christmas.Throwing a celebration for Earth or Arbor Day? The light green and yellow stripes swirled around these rich green Lime Candy Sticks can represent the forest for these environmental celebrations.Now, let\'s talk about flavor! The bold, tangy fruit taste of these Lime Candy Sticks will have guests of all ages grinning ear-to-ear. They can be eaten as is, or you can add them to water, soda, or even margaritas and daiquiris by the pool. They are certified kosher and manufactured in a facility that uses no gluten or nuts.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lime_old_fashioned_1.jpg', '682~lime_old_fashioned_1.jpg', 'lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(683, 'Life Savers Candy', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Laver Savers candies have been around for many years. They are enjoyed by everyone from children to adults. These great candies are available in many different colors such as red, purple, green, orange, white, and even yellow. You can get many different flavors such as wild cherry, grape, lime, pineapple, orange, and even butter rum. You are sure to find a flavor that you are able to enjoy. You are also sure to find that these small hard, crunchy candies are able to provide a great deal of taste that you are sure to be pleased with. These candies are great for birthday parties, Halloween, weddings, and more. They come in rolls and you can choose from multi-flavored rolls, or the ones that one has a single flavor depending on your preference. There is nothing that can take you back to your childhood more than the great taste of Life Savers.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', '683~life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', 'life-savers-rolls'),
(684, 'Charms Sour Balls Tins', 42.99, '12', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'When it comes to making friends, candy is a great ice breaker. Choosing the right candy will determine how successful you are at this endeavor. Charms Sour Balls are definitely the right candy. These delicious hard candy treats make the young happy and the old nostalgic. There is a power in the sour ball that will win friends because it is the perfect combination of both sweet and sour that appeal to everyone. They come in cherry, grape, lemon, lime and of course orange. When you see a tin of these delicious treats, you can\'t help think of Christmas and other celebrations. Once a can is open it is nearly impossible to stop the smiles and good times. With a whole tin of this candy on your side, you will be able to win a whole lot of new friends and in the end, would you want to be friends with someone who didn\'t like Charms Sour Balls?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', '684~charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', 'charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz'),
(685, 'Hershey\'s Kisses', 36.99, '4', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Show some love with our bulk Hershey kisses! Few candies are as recognizable as the familiar cone shape that is the trademark of these chocolate treats. They are simply yet extremely versatile. Hand them out at parties, use them to fill your candy dish at home or add them to party or wedding favors. No matter where you are or what the occasion may be, guests will savor the sweet taste and unique shape that has earned these charming confections enormous popularity. Every Hershey kiss candy is covered in a silver foil wrapper. Simply peel back the top and enjoy the full, rich flavor that comes with every dainty bite! Our bulk candy packages are the most convenient way to order your Hershey kisses in large quantities for gatherings and events. You can also purchase a pack or two for baking around the holidays so you always have enough to make your favorite Hershey cookies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hershey-kisses-bulk-470x470.jpg', '685~hershey-kisses-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'hersheys-kisses-original'),
(686, 'Chocolate Bulk Candy Mix', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Get all the chocolaty goodness you can handle in this bulk candy mix! Our chocolate assortment includes a generous quantity of confections. Thereâ€™s Reeceâ€™s Pieces, mini Hershey bars, Starburst, Jolly Ranchers and assorted taffy. Each piece is individually wrapped so it stays fresh and delicious. Grab a handful and get the perfect mix of chewy and sweet for snack time or special occasions!This practical chocolate bulk candy mix is perfect for events and special occasions. Use them to get a variety of candy for treat bags or party favors. Just toss a handful in a favor box or bag and you have a gift your guests will enjoy! Keep a package in your pantry so your candy dish never goes empty or use to fill up the candy jar at work. Chocolate and taffy makes a tasty snack thatâ€™s easy to pack in lunches or in your purse or pocket!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', '686~candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', 'bulk-chocolate-candy-mix'),
(687, 'Red Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'The mere sight of these will have you longing for Valentine\'s Day. Although these Red Milk Chocolate Hearts are the perfect candy or the year\'s most romantic day, you certainly don\'t have to wait until February to enjoy them.They are popular for weddings, engagement parties, bridal showers, and New Year\'s Eve parties, too. A lot of love goes into making these mouthwatering Red Chocolate Hearts. The delectable chocolate sauce is poured into molds and left to harden.Then, they are carefully wrapped with shiny red foil.Since they are all individually wrapped they\'re appropriate for any candy dish. You can even pour some in small jars, add a pretty ribbon, and hand them out to all your friends who don\'t have sweetheart to spend Valentine\'s Day with. Your mom, sister, aunt, and cousin will surely love them, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', '687~red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', 'red-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(688, 'Gold Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Gold milk chocolate hearts are a rich, beautiful treat that\'s versatile and delicious. Every piece is made using high quality milk chocolate that\'s molded to form a solid heart shape.Heart candy is a great choice for events that celebrate love and friendship. Give them away during Valentine\'s Day or use them in shower and wedding favors. Our gold milk chocolate hearts are especially attractive thanks to their elegant presentation.Each solid milk chocolate heart is protected by a thin layer of shimmering foil. The surface is covered in a breathtaking metallic gold hue that produces the same shine as the metal. Unwrap and enjoy the amazingly sweet taste of traditional milk chocolate!These irresistible heart candies look sophisticated whether you pour them into a jar or bowl or display them on a tray with other treats. Impress coworkers and clients by keeping our bulk milk chocolate hearts at work or save them for home snacking!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', '688~gold-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', 'gold-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(689, 'Lindt Chocolate Lindor Truffles', 49.99, '120', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Savor every rich bite of our Lindt chocolate Lindor truffles! Exquisitely smooth and irresistibly chocolaty, these delectable round candies are simply irresistible. Pamper your taste buds by biting into the classic chocolate shell to sample the creamy confection hidden deep inside. We carry the finest Lindt truffles flavors, including luxurious dark chocolate, sweet hazelnut, traditional milk chocolate, refreshing mint, delightful peanut butter, sensational raspberry and dark chocolate and scrumptious white chocolate. We make it easy to get all the Lindt chocolate truffles you need for any occasion. Our bulk candy packs are wonderful for serving at parties or as part of beautiful wedding favors. Treat your beloved guests to the heavenly taste that makes Lindor truffles so desirable! Every piece is individually packaged in a colorful wrapper with the elegant Lindt brand clearly displayed. Simply untwist the ends and you have a chocolate truffle treat that is unlike any other!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lindor-truffles-main.jpg', '689~lindor-truffles-main.jpg', 'lindt-chocolate-lindor-truffles'),
(690, 'Blue Milk Chocolate Stars', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'The stars have aligned in this delicious milk chocolate candy to bring you the best of the cosmos chocolate-y and adorable! These Blue Milk Chocolate Stars come in a bulk bag and possess all the beauty and majesty of space plus, even better taste! Wrapped in a shiny, blue foil and stuffed with star-shaped chocolate, every sweet lover will want and entire galaxy full of these treats. Use them for a super hero themed party, add them to a candy bar buffet at a Fourth of July event, or even put some on your Christmas tree as beautiful ornaments that will sparkle and taste delicious.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-milk-chocolate-stars-5lb_1.jpg', '690~blue-milk-chocolate-stars-5lb_1.jpg', 'blue-milk-chocolate-stars'),
(691, 'Chocolate Ladybugs', 39.99, '60', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Chocolate ladybugs will brighten anyone\'s day! Each piece consists of high quality chocolate that forms a solid bug shape. This delicious foil wrapped chocolate candy is the perfect addition to any gathering or event.The top creates a dome with a flat bottom and narrower head.Each piece is wrapped in shiny foil to create a red body with black spots and a cute gold face with smile and nostalgic eyes! Bulk chocolate ladybugs are a great way to get more candy for any celebration! Their bright red color makes them a great choice for Valentine\'s Day favors or wedding favors.They also present an adorable look that is so sweet for baby showers. Any spring or summer event is a great time to serve these edible bugs! Businesses can give them to customers as a sweet thank you for doing business while schools and communities can include these economical treats in their annual festivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-ladybugs-60ct_1.jpg', '691~chocolate-ladybugs-60ct_1.jpg', 'chocolate-ladybugs-foil-wrapped'),
(692, 'Kimmie Gemstones Chocolate Rocks', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'These rocks may look real, but they are actually quite edible! Kimmie gemstones chocolate rocks are a gorgeous assortment of earthy candies that are designed to look and feel like real stones.Each piece features a uniquely organic shape with straight edges and uneven sides that produce an original, naturally made look. Take a bite of a gemstone chocolate rock and you\'ll discover a center that\'s filled with sweet, rich chocolate! The outside is covered in a shimmering candy coating that carefully lines each crease and dent in the chocolate rock\'s surface.This gives each piece a realistic appearance. Serve them up and make guests think you just chiseled this delectable confection out of a secret cave of confections! Chocolate rocks are a tasty snack that also makes great party favors. Use them to decorate cakes, cupcakes and cookies or add to candy dishes to serve at wedding receptions, birthdays and more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/e/gemstones.jpg', '692~gemstones.jpg', 'kimmie-gemstones-chocolate-rocks-5lb'),
(693, 'Red Milk Chocolate Stars', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'If making a wish on a star is a good thing, imagine what is going to happen when you make a wish on a special Red Milk Chocolate Star! These chocolate treats are star shaped extravagance that is packaged up in a beautiful red foiled wrapper. Many people eat these special treats at Independence Day and not only help celebrate the birthday of a nation. They can help to mark the celebration of anyone\'s birthday in the most delicious way. The five points of the stars are going to bring a remarkable feeling of joy as each point of the star leads to a treasure of chocolaty goodness. Valentine\'s Day and Christmas are holidays that naturally lead to using these Red Milk Chocolate Stars to add some extra zip to each holiday.  Hand these chocolate treats to your friends and everyone will want to be your valentine. This bulk bag of chocolates will be enough to make a small party of people feel the happiness this candy treat can bring.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-foil-chocolate-stars.jpg', '693~red-foil-chocolate-stars.jpg', 'red-milk-chocolate-stars'),
(694, 'Chocolate Covered Pretzels', 69.99, '6', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Everyone knows that it\'s what\'s on the inside that counts. But what if on the outside is ooey-gooey chocolate? In the interest of deliciousness, we\'ll bend the rules for these titillating twists just this once! With a yummy selection of dark, milk, and white chocolate, it\'ll be hard to choose. But with a salty, crunchy pretzel interior and a melty chocolate coating, any of these dipped wonders will provide you will hours upon hours of happy snacking. Surprise a chocolate lover with a bag of these or keep them around for a rainy day snack. Whatever you do, everyone can satisfy their sweet and salty tooth with one of these tasty triplets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-pretzels-6lbs_2.gif', '694~chocolate-covered-pretzels-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-pretzels'),
(695, 'Fort Knox Gold Coins Chocolate', 28.99, '30', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Fort Knox may hold all of the country\'s gold. But here at CandyStore.com, we hold a good portion of the world\'s sweets! We\'re not sure which one you find more valuable, but whatever it may be, these Fort Knox Gold Chocolate Coins will make you feel like you\'ve struck it rich every time you take a bite.With a gleaming gold aluminum wrapper and tasty chocolate coin center, unwrap each coin one at a time or by the dozen. If you\'re hosting a casino game night, want to reward your kids with a tasty and valuable treat, are planning to make a opt of gold for a St. Patrick\'s Day celebration, or anything else, these are the candies for you.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins-48ct_1.jpg', '695~fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins-48ct_1.jpg', 'fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins'),
(696, 'Riverstones Kimmie Mix', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Riverstones Kimmie mix is the best way to get a wide variety of Choco Rocks for events, parties or baking. These tasty little morsels are unique from any other candy you have ever eaten.Each piece contains a solid piece of rich chocolate candy. The outside is blanketed in a solid candy shell. The exterior features realistic texture and earthy colors.Our Riverstone Choco Rocks mix contains a number of delightful hues. You\'ll see marble white stones along with vibrant green and burnt orange. Many other natural tones are included to produce an assortment with variety. Even though many colors are used, each piece blends well, adhering to an organic palette.Use these to decorate construction birthday cakes or ad to bags to give out as a fun party favor. They are even elegant enough to use in your wedding favors! Order our bulk chocolate river stones and enjoy the irresistible taste of candy rocks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/i/riverstones.jpg', '696~riverstones.jpg', 'riverstones-kimmie-mix-5lb'),
(697, 'Life Savers Pep O Mint', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Is your mouth screaming \'\'SOS\'\' for a breath freshening treat? Well, these Life Savers Pep-O-Mint and Wint-O-Green are here to save the day! Let them toss you a life preserver for your taste buds with their fresh minty flavor and classic \'\'O\'\' shaped form. This hero of the candy world has been around since 1912 and has saved mouths all over the world. Pep-O-Mint was the first flavor and quickly made an impression in the mouths of many. Since then, a variety of fruity and other mint flavors have been invented. Try these minty rolls on for size and see for yourself if you think they\'re worthy of their heroic name!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', '697~mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', 'mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct'),
(698, 'Silver Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Silver milk chocolate hearts aren\'t made of sterling silver metal, but they sure look like they are! These eye-catching heart candies are a superb choice for Valentine\'s Day and major events.Every piece is made of a solid serving of sweet milk chocolate. The smooth surface is protected by a thin layer of shimmering foil. This creates that gorgeous shiny finish that makes these heart candies so stunning!Silver milk chocolate hearts are a convenient choice for wedding favors, shower favors and more. Our bulk candy pack gives you many pieces that are economical for bigger crowds.Arrange them on a cookie tray or pour into a glass candy dish and you have an elegant presentation for guests. This package contains all silver wrappers. Also check out our other milk chocolate heart candy to find additional wrapper colors. Order just one or try 2, 3 or more to create a custom chocolate mix for your event!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', '698~silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', 'silver-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(699, 'Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars', 38.99, '14', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Behold, a 200 year old chocolate. Well, not this one specifically. That would be gross. However, Cadbury has been around since the 1800s and has been making work famous chocolates ever since. Bring these Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars home to spoil your family and friends with a taste of the past. With their breakable sections, they\'re great to enjoy in small nibbles or big bites! Get a loved one a bar for Valentine\'s Day, melt a few of these bars into fondue, or just keep them around for delicious baking. Get your chocolate bar today and try out the famous recipe that has been honed over two centuries.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', '699~cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', 'cadbury-chocolate-bars'),
(700, 'red chocolate hearts foil wrapped', 109.99, '', '', 'chocolate', 'We\'ve met our soul mate. That\'s because these adorable Red Chocolate Foil Hearts are so delicious and cute that we want our taste buds to spend the rest of their lives together! Add these loveable little chocolates to a Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of heart shaped chocolates is here to make a romantic day even more memorable.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-foil-hearts.jpg', '700~red-chocolate-foil-hearts.jpg', 'red-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(701, 'Lavender Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'It might be hard to believe, but what\'s underneath the gorgeous pastel foil of these lavender foil chocolate balls awaits something equally as amazing: chocolate. Did we blow your mind? Because these lavender chocolate balls are going to as soon as you unwrap one and rest it on your tongue.If you love a candy that\'s as beautiful as it is delicious, then look no further. These lavender foil-wrapped chocolate balls will add a glamorous and girly look to any candy dish, candy jar or candy buffet bar you set out. Use them as decor and a delicious snack for guests to munch on while they await a meal. Or keep them around to tuck into lunchboxes or on top of baked goods that need a touch of something special.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lavendar_chocolate_balls.jpg', '701~lavendar_chocolate_balls.jpg', 'lavender-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(702, 'Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars 3pc', 94.99, '12', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Whether you are celebrating a job promotion, engagement, or the birth of a baby, Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are the perfect addition to your event. Crafted from premium milk chocolate and molded to look just like real cigars, these impressive masterpieces will have folks taking a closer look when they see you bite the end of one.The Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are all individually wrapped in exquisite Italian foil that replicates a genuine tobacco leaf. They are available in three options: Original, It\'s a Girl, and It\'s a Boy.These divine treats are kosher certified and made in the USA by Thompson Candy Company. They are perfect for baby showers, delivery celebrations at the hospital, Father\'s Day, anniversaries, birthdays, and thank you gifts, just to name a few. Order these Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars for you to handout, or give the entire box to someone as a gift. They are sure to make everyone smile, and they are a lot better for you and the environment than the real thing.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', '702~royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', 'royale-premium-chocolate-cigars'),
(703, 'Royal Blue Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Royal blue foil chocolate balls offer the perfect combination of visual appeal and taste. Everyone loves the smooth, rich flavor of high quality chocolate. Our individually wrapped candy balls make it easy to share this classic treat at any event or right at home! Each piece includes a solid ball of savory milk chocolate that\'s wrapped in a thin layer of foil. Our royal blue chocolate balls add elegance to any presentation. Pour them into glass bowls or jars to set out on guest tables. You can also add a few to sachets or bags to give away as wedding favors. The dark blue color goes with almost any celebration! Add an icy blue chill to a winter feast or celebrate a birthday with the irresistible taste of pure chocolate. You can even share them with coworkers or give complimentary candies to clients as a thank you for their business!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '703~royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped');
