(704, 'Ghirardelli Twilight Delight 72% Dark Chocolate Squares Caddy', 26.99, '50', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Ghirardelli Twilight Delight 72% Dark Chocolate Squares Caddy - 50ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/h/ghirardelli_twilight_delight_72_dark_chocolate_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', '704~ghirardelli_twilight_delight_72_dark_chocolate_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', 'ghirardelli-twilight-delight-72percent-dark-chocolate-squares-caddy'),
(705, 'Chocolate Basketballs', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Getting together to watch the game is a momentous occasion worthy of marking with specialty candy â€“ at least, if your team is doing well! Celebrate victories and mourn losses with these foil-wrapped Chocolate Basketballs, solid balls of chocolate that melt in your mouth once you remove the realistically-printed orange foil wrapper.These bulk chocolate basketballs are great for sports parties, birthday parties, and candy buffets tailored to the interests of the guest of honor! When the NCAA tournament rolls around, you will be glad to have these chocolate balls on hand for dropping into lunch boxes or topping off the office candy jar!These chocolate candies are also sure to enthuse a youth basketball team if offered by the handful at their end-of-season bash. The foil wrappers are not just clever and thematic, but also easy to remove, making chocolate basketballs a perfect candy-dish sweet.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolatebasketballs.jpg', '705~chocolatebasketballs.jpg', 'chocolate-basketballs-foil-wrapped'),
(706, 'Gold Nugget Choco Rocks Bulk', 39.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Gold nugget choco rocks are one of the most fascinating and unique candies available! This treat is unlike any other chocolate snack. Every piece features an original shape that looks much like natural rocks.The surface is covered in a luxurious gold shell that produces an alluring shimmer that looks very realistic, right down to the fine gravelly texture that runs along all sides. While these chocolate nuggets look like rocks, they taste amazing! Don\'t worry, you won\'t break any teeth when you bite down on each rich piece. The candy coating on the outside provides a crunch while smooth, irresistible chocolate hides within Ã just waiting to take your taste buds on a sweet adventure!Our bulk gold nugget choco rocks are perfect for many occasions. Use them to fill a pot of gold at your next St. Patrick\'s Day party. Choco rocks are also great for decorating baked goods and edible decor!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks-bulk_1.jpg', '706~gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks-bulk_1.jpg', 'gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks'),
(707, 'Chocolate Golf Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Now golfers can enjoy their favorite confection and their favorite sport at the same time! Our chocolate golf balls are packed with rich flavor that comes in a fun themed package.Each bite-sized morsel consists of a solid orb of delectable chocolate. The smooth, dark surface is covered in a thin foil wrapper with a uniquely printed exterior. The pure white background is covered in realistic pock marks to recreate the look of an actual golf ball!You can take these delicious chocolate with you anywhere, from the green to the clubhouse! Our bulk chocolate balls are also a great treat for special occasions like golf themed birthday parties, picnics and holidays.Impress a fellow golfer with the smooth taste of fine chocolate that comes in a package they can appreciate! Our bulk chocolate golf balls makes it easy to order enough for wedding favors, treat bags and edible gifts.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', '707~chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', 'chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(708, 'Silver Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This candy will steal your heart! And how could they not with their shimmery, shiny silver wrapper and even more amazing chocolate heart that lays within. Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Silver Foil Hearts is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '708~silver-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'silver-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(709, 'Ghirardelli Dark and Sea Salt Caramel Squares Caddy', 26.99, '50', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Ghirardelli Dark and Sea Salt Caramel Squares Caddy - 50ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/h/ghirardelli_dark_and_sea_salt_caramel_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', '709~ghirardelli_dark_and_sea_salt_caramel_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', 'ghirardelli-dark-and-sea-salt-caramel-squares-caddy'),
(710, 'Purple Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wear your heart on your sleeve with these heavenly chocolates. The indulgent mouthfuls of joy are the perfect message to send the special someone who has your whole heart. Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Purple Foil Hearts is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '710~purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'purple-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(711, 'Sour Power Belts Wrapped', 24.99, '150', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'With 150 Sour Power Belts in this big bulk supply you will have plenty of opportunity for flavorful fun. These candies were introduced in 1985, and folks of all ages have not been able to get enough of them.If you love pucker-inducing treats, these Sour Power Belts should definitely be on your shopping list. This box of delicious treats is available in Green Apple, Blue Raspberry, Strawberry, and Watermelon. We recommend getting all four before you drive yourself crazy trying to pick only one.The belts are about 9-inches long and just under 1-inch wide, so they are pretty much the perfect size. Big enough to satisfy, but not so big you get a tummy ache. Since these Sour Power Belts are individually wrapped you can surprise your kids with them in their lunch box and hand them out at Halloween.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', '711~sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', 'sour-power-belts-dorval-wrapped'),
(712, 'Tiffany Blue Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Do you have expensive taste but a budget to stick to? Well, these Tiffany Blue Foil Chocolate Balls might be the perfect candy for you! With the famous, powder blue of the high end jewelry store, Tiffany, and decadent chocolate underneath, you\'ll add a sophistication to every sweet snack break. Bring these to a bridal shower, bachelorette party, or the baby shower for a boy! They even make a great addition to a blue themed candy buffet bar or a wedding reception. These glamorous chocolates come in a bulk bag and will impress your taste buds and guests whenever you serve them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/i/tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '712~tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(713, 'Chocolate Covered Oreo Cookies', 64.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This may be the one time when we encourage people to judge a confection by its cover. Because this cookie\'s cover is a thick layer of creamy, melty chocolate! Chocolate Covered Oreos have become a sensation in recent years, and with this bulk bulk bag, there are over 70 cookies to enjoy. Whether you\'re an Oreo fan who insists on eating the cream first and then the cookie or vice versa, we think you\'ll all agree that savoring the chocolate cookie coating before it all is the best way to go about this particular batch. It\'s a problem we don\'t think you\'ll take issue with while you make your way through mouthwatering layer upon layer of chocolatey, creamy goodness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-oreo-cookie5lbs_2.gif', '713~chocolate-covered-oreo-cookie5lbs_2.gif', 'oreo-cookies-chocolate-covered'),
(714, 'White Yogurt Mini Twist Pretzels', 50.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Our white yogurt mini twist pretzels give you a new way to enjoy your favorite baked treat! Pretzels are delicious on their own, with their crunchy texture and salty taste. This version takes miniature knots and smothers them in cool, smooth white yogurt. Itâ€™s an irresistible combination that will please taste buds and calm cravings! Bulk white yogurt pretzels give you more pieces for snacking, sharing, and parties.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/o/yogurt-tiny-pretzels_2.jpg', '714~yogurt-tiny-pretzels_2.jpg', 'white-yogurt-mini-twist-pretzels-candy'),
(715, 'Chocolate Soccer Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in foil that looks like a classic black and white soccer ball and with amazing chocolate balls beneath, these Chocolate Soccer Balls are winners for sure! Do you have a friend or family member who plays soccer? Why not make their next game extra special by bringing an order of these Chocolate Soccer Balls by at half time? There are plenty to share with the whole team and can cheer up a losing team or help celebrate an incredible win!Chocolate Soccer Balls also are a great candy for sports-themed birthday parties or soccer training camps. Score big with your friends and family and order some today. Oleee, ole, ole, ole. Get ready to chant the most famous soccer game song of all time with these Chocolate Soccer Balls!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', '715~chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', 'chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(716, 'Chocolate Rocks', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Rocks aren\'t very appetizing, unless they are chocolate rocks! These natural looking candies are absolutely gorgeous to see and so sweet to the taste buds.If you love cocoa flavor, then you will fall in love with these charming little edible pebbles. Each includes a dense chocolate candy that\'s covered in a solid candy coating in a rainbow of earthy colors!What makes chocolate rocks so delicious isn\'t just their taste, but also their appearance. Each stone looks just like the real thing! The candy coating creates lovely texture while each chocolate is uniquely shaped Ã just like real rocks. This assortment includes a variety of hues, ranging from slate blue to burnt orange and black.Grab a handful or enjoy one at a time. No matter which color you choose, each offers the same amazing chocolate taste. Our bulk chocolate rocks are a must-have for cake decorating and special occasions!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolaterocks.jpg', '716~chocolaterocks.jpg', 'chocolate-rocks-5lb'),
(717, 'Assorted Sports Chocolate Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Golf balls, tennis balls, basketballs, baseballs, soccer balls and footballs, oh my! We\'re sure everyone will want to be on your team when you bring these Assorted Sports Chocolate Balls in bulk supply to your next party or sporting event.That\'s because these sports balls aren\'t only melty milk chocolate and scrumptious, but they\'re also fun to play with! Hit a home run with one of these baseballs and throw it into your mouth. Kick a field goal through your friend\'s fingers and then indulge in chocolate. You\'re going to score big points with whoever you share these Assorted Sports Chocolate balls with, that\'s for sure!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/foil-sports-balls-chocolate.jpg', '717~foil-sports-balls-chocolate.jpg', 'chocolate-assorted-sports-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(718, 'Milk Chocolate Gold Coins Medium Size', 136.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This 5-pound supply of Milk Chocolate Gold Coins is perfect to hand out at nearly any event. Fill a treasure chest with them for a pirate-themed birthday party.Use them as a snack at your next poker party, include them in a gift bag, or hand them out at Halloween. These Milk Chocolate Gold Coins are about the size of a quarter, and the highly detailed gold foil makes them look like real currency. There are hundreds of coins in this bulk supply, which should be more than enough for any celebration.Although great for a party, you don\'t need to be planning a special event to order these Milk Chocolate Gold Coins. Stock your candy jar with them and you\'ll always have a quick bite size snack handy when you need to satisfy a little sugar craving. These medium size yummy chocolate coins are certified kosher, making them an ideal Hanukkah gift, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', '718~milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', 'milk-chocolate-gold-coins-medium'),
(719, 'Bright Pink Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Bright pink foil chocolate balls are delightful to look at and pleasing to the taste buds. These simple candies offer big visual appeal. Each piece includes a luxuriously solid orb of milk chocolate with a smooth exterior.The surface is covered in a delicate blanket of foil with a glorious pink shine. It\'s both tasty snack and elegant display that works at home, the office or at events!Pour our bright pink foil chocolate balls into any glass container and you have a beautiful chocolate display!That\'s why our colorful foil wrapped candies are such a great choice for wedding favors, showers and other high class celebrations. We make it easy to get large quantities for a big crowd with our affordable bulk chocolate balls pack. Order just one package of chocolate balls or multiple so you have plenty to go around whether you\'re hosting an event for 10, 100 or 1,000!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/bright-pink-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '719~bright-pink-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'chocolate-balls-bright-pink-foil-wrapped'),
(720, 'Red Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in shiny, metallic red wrappers, these little Red Foil Chocolate Balls are sure to make your eyes pop as your mouth waters for what\'s inside. Inside is a solid ball of melty milk chocolate. It\'s up to you whether you want to chomp, chew or let this little sphere melt away. Red Foil Chocolate Balls are the perfect color and candy for Christmas, the Fourth of July, and a birthday party for someone who adores the color. Stock up on these Red Foil Chocolate Balls and mix and match with other flavors and colors or enjoy them all by themselves. Whatever you do, you\'ll love unwrapping these chocolate balls one after the other.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '720~red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(721, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '721~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(722, 'Assorted Salt Water Taffy Mix', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Assorted salt water taffy mix. Do you remember those amazing trips to the beach with your family when you were a kid? Vacation was never complete without a trip to the candy store and a big bag of salt water taffy. Bring those great memories to life in your mouth any time you like with these assorted salt water taffy candies. Set them out in a candy dish at home or work and share the sweet experience.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', '722~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(723, 'Vanilla Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When was the last time your hard working mouth took a vacation? Treat it with a lovely retreat to the salty shores of the boardwalk-lined coast with these saltwater taffys. Complete with a soft, chewy texture and light vanilla taste, you\'ll remember why it\'s so good to get away for a while. Feel like the breeze is in your hair, the sand is between your toes and the jubilant hubub of the boardwalk is buzzing around you bite after bite. In the late 1800s, salt water taffy was discovered when a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be for generations to come.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '723~vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'vanilla-salt-water-taffy'),
(724, 'Grape Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Beach bums, get ready for a treat that will remind you of the summer heat! This grape salt water taffy has been stretched, chewed, and loved for years. Inspired by the sunny boardwalk, these individually wrapped candies can bring back summertime memories whenever you wish.Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '724~grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'grape-salt-water-taffy'),
(725, 'Raspberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Sally may sell sea shells by the seashore, but we sell savory salt water taffy that gives her a run for her money! A summertime classic, this raspberry flavored taffy is ready to take you back to the boardwalk any time of the year. Individually wrapped, they are the perfect solution to a sweet tooth or to be used as a party favor. You can almost hear the surf as you let these morsels melt away. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '725~raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'raspberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(726, 'Peppermint Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When days at the beach get hot, you can do more than jumping in the waves for a cool-down. Try our refreshing Peppermint Salt Water Taffy to beat the heat. The individually wrapped morsels make them ideal to pack in a beach bag or cooler. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '726~peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'peppermint-salt-water-taffy'),
(727, 'Strawberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'What happens when you combine creamy saltwater taffy with the juicy flavor of ripe red strawberries? You get one of the most mouthwatering confections found on land or in the sea! Saltwater taffy is a classic treat that hails from the sundrenched boardwalks of Atlantic City, NJ. This classic confection has been around for decades and has become a popular souvenir at many seaside destinations. Our strawberry saltwater taffy is easy to get because you don\'t have to go on vacation to buy it!The blend of molasses, sea salt and strawberry flavorings gives our saltwater taffy an irresistibly soft, smooth taste. Every piece is individually wrapped so you can easily separate servings for snacking or place a few in a party or wedding favor! The gentle pink taffy color includes deep red stripes around the sides that make this treat perfect for Valentine\'s Day, anniversaries or any special occasion that celebrates love!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '727~strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'strawberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(728, 'Laffy Taffy Candy', 37.99, '8.5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Laffy Taffy is such a well-recognized candy that hip-hop artist D4L has immortalized its name in song. You don\'t have to be a fan of rap to enjoy these chewy soft candies, though. Each individually wrapped Laffy Taffy candy comes with a joke written on the wrapper for you to share with your friends. You\'ll laugh with your friends as you satisfy your sweet tooth for this delicious taffy candy. They\'re so good, though, that you might want to share the jokes, but you won\'t ever want to share the candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', '728~laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-pieces-bulk'),
(729, 'Tropical Assorted Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'This seashore classic is now heading to the tropics with these Assorted Tropical Salt Water Taffies! Feel the sun on your face, the wind in your hair, and hear the crash of the ocean waves with every bite of these colorful taffies. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/r/tropical_assorted.jpg', '729~tropical_assorted.jpg', 'tropical-salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(730, 'Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Prepare to hypnotize your taste buds with these Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffies. In a stark contrast of black and white swirls, these candies are as yummy to eat as they are to look at. Use them for a thematic addition to Halloween or a formal wedding reception. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '730~licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(731, 'Key Lime Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Don\'t you just love the light, refreshing sweetness that comes with biting into a slice of key lime pie? How about the fun, chewy tastiness of salt water taffy? Well, you can have the best of both worlds with Key Lime Salt Water Taffy!These individually wrapped goodies have a classic taste that everyone loves and a great chewy texture, too. Put them in a candy dish for your guests at home or your coworkers at the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '731~key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'key-lime-salt-water-taffy'),
(732, 'Cherry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Cherry salt water taffy is sure to take you back to your childhood vacations to the beach. These red and pink chewy candies will be a huge hit anywhere you take them. Put them out in a candy dish at home, or take them to share the sweet taffy goodness at work or at a party. Cherry salt water taffy makes a great addition to a Valentine\'s Day gift bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '732~cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-salt-water-taffy'),
(733, 'Blueberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Blueberry saltwater taffy combines all the goodness of fresh picked berries with the seaside nostalgia of this timeless treat! Our soft taffy candy is just as smooth as a soft sandy beach with flavor that\'s as powerful as the ocean waves. The first saltwater taffy was born right along the seashore in Atlantic City, New Jersey. Over 100 years later we still savor the luxuriously smooth texture and mouthwatering taste that comes with each piece. Our bulk saltwater taffy pack includes all the blueberry candy you can handle, individually packaged. Each piece is protected by a clear wrapper that shows its pleasant blue color. Eating is easy: just untwist the ends and take a bite of timeless saltwater taffy! Our blue version is perfect for baby showers, wedding favors, birthday celebrations, 4th of July events and any occasion that features azure hues. Try just one bulk candy bag or order other flavors to create an attractive contrast at parties and picnics!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blueberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '733~blueberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'blueberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(734, 'Banana Taffy Taffy Town', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you love to visit the zoo then this is the perfect candy for you to enjoy. This Banana Salt Water Taffy has such a real banana flavor that each and even monkeys can be fooled about their authenticity. Salt water taffy is going to make you feel great about yourself anyway, because it provides a person with a bit of nostalgia. There is no other treat which screams about summer more than salt water taffy. This sweet banana taste is going to make eating one of these treats an impossibility but no need to worry as they come in a hefty bulk bag. That should be enough to keep you munching for hours. The real banana taste is going to make you want to visit the local zoo, because you will want to share them with all the other primates. Candy is always best when it is shared with someone who appreciates it and primates of all ages will absolutely love this!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '734~banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'banana-salt-water-taffy'),
(735, 'Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lite', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Summertime and the living\'s easy. And now, sugar free! Try these Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lites for a healthier fix of the boardwalk classic and all the scrumptious taste of the original recipe. In blue-raspberry, strawberry, lemon, chocolate, orange, and vanilla, let these little morsels melt away as you remember digging your toes into the sand and letting the sun shine in your hair. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', '735~sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite'),
(736, 'cinnamon swirl salt water taffy in a white bowl', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you have never tried cinnamon salt water taffy then you don\'t know what you are missing out on. The flavor of these is perfect. They have a cinnamon blend that is spicy and works just right with the sweet flavor that they have as well. There is nothing better than the tasty of salt water taffy and when you combine it with cinnamon the flavor really seems to explode. The candies are pink in color and are sure to look great for a many different occasions. You will also like to know that each piece is wrapped individually which is very helpful in making sure that they stay fresh as long as possible. There is just something about the chewy texture of taffy that is able to please so many people. This is a great tasting candy with a great texture that is hard to beat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '736~cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'cinnamon-salt-water-taffy'),
(737, 'Watermelon Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Two summer classics unite in this amazing, summery confection. Try our refreshing Watermelon Salt Water Taffy to beat the heat. The individually wrapped morsels make them ideal to pack in a beach bag or cooler and their bright pink and green color combination makes them a lovely addition to any pinata or candy buffet bar. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '737~watermelon-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'watermelon-salt-water-taffy'),
(738, 'Green Apple Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Which way to the beach? These delicious Green Apple Salt Water Taffies will make you want to lay on the warm sand with every chew. Their bright green color and tart green apple flavor will please every boardwalk lover and remind you of warmer days to come. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', '738~green-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', 'green-apple-salt-water-taffy'),
(739, 'Cotton Candy Taffy', 9.99, '3', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Relive your fondest childhood memories with every bite of cotton candy taffy! This irresistible snack offers a nostalgic flavor that\'s sure to please. Recall the excitements of visits to the local candy shop, where you could pick out your favorite chewy taffy treats.Or how about the soft, fluffy taste of cotton candy while spending time at the carnival! Our cotton candy taffy combines both of those wonderful experiences into one bite-sized confection. Our bulk cotton candy taffy includes large quantities that are individually wrapped to ensure freshness and flavor.They are convenient for sharing and giving. Use them to fill up the office candy jar or pour in a bowl to serve guests who stop by. Cotton candy taffy features a lovely light blue hue that looks elegant in wedding favors or can be used to complement a boys baby shower theme! Everyone will love the eye-catching look and sweet taste of our cotton candy taffy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/cotton-candy-taffy-sweets.jpg', '739~cotton-candy-taffy-sweets.jpg', 'sweets-cotton-candy-taffy'),
(740, 'Passion Fruit Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'We\'ve got the love and the passion for these Passion Fruit Salt Water Taffies! Let these individually wrapped taffies make your heart pitter patter with their beautiful, bright blue and yellow coloring and citrusy flavor experience. A boardwalk favorite amongst beach vacationers for years, this recipe upholds the high standard of the original. Discovered in the late 1800s when a shop owner\'s candy store was flooded by rising ocean tides, he made the best of it and decided to market the salt-soaked candies to the public and they loved them! Ever since, people haven\'t been able to get enough of these chewy, salty-sweet, creamy taffies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '740~passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy'),
(741, 'Orange Creme Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'You can almost feel the fresh salty breeze in your hair and hear the roaring of the waves hitting the beach with every bite of these Orange Creme Salt Water Taffies. Their beautiful orange and white swirls will remind you of summer and melt away in your mouth every time you snack. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-cr-me-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', '741~orange-cr-me-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', 'orange-creme-salt-water-taffy'),
(742, 'Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When you can invoke memories with a piece of candy then you must be doing something right. The delicious Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy treats provide a powerful punch of goodness for all to enjoy. The taste of any salt water taffy is going to bring back memories of summer time spent near the shore as you enjoyed the sweet taste of salt water taffy with your friends as you passed the hours of fun in your youth. Then there is the taste of lemon meringue that is going to be a reminder of the wonder and renewal of springtime. The fact that it comes in a bright shiny wrapper will make each piece seem like a gift, and it is a gift of delicious lemony flavor. It is yellow in color which will make you think of the happiness that sunshine can bring you. These Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy candies can make any occasion just a little more special. Who doesn\'t remember the taste of homemade pie?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/e/lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '742~lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy'),
(743, 'Chocolate Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'What\'s all the fuss about? \'\'Sea\'\' for yourself with these amazingly creamy and delectable Chocolate Salt Water Taffies. Hit the sand with every bite of these individually wrapped morsels. Surprise your chocolate-loving family with a bag of these. Even drop a few into your hot cocoa for extra chocolatey goodness. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '743~chocolate-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'chocolate-salt-water-taffy'),
(744, 'Huckleberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Well, there is a lot we could say about these delicious treats, but we want to tell you most is that they\'re \'\'berry\'\' good! These Huckleberry Sal Water Taffies are a gorgeous shade of deep purple and white and will delight your family and friends. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/u/huckleberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', '744~huckleberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', 'huckleberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(745, 'Cran Raspberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you love salt water taffy then you will certainly love the cran raspberry salt water taffy. This gives a new twist to an old favorite. The flavor of these is amazing which means they are sure to please nearly anyone. They also have a nice white and pink color to them which means they would be great for many different occasions and events that were themed with the same color. Each piece is wrapped individually as well which is certainly a benefit. Some may even find that these would be great to use if you were having a baby shower for someone who had a little girl that was on the way or recently born. So if you think that this is a candy that you would really enjoy and that would add to your occasion then you want to make sure that you get your candy as soon as possible.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/r/cran-raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '745~cran-raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cran-raspberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(746, 'Sassy Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Me. Ow. These Sassy Salt Water Taffies have enough sweet and sour spunk to knock you back to last Tuesday! In a colorful mix of blue, yellow, orange, green, red, and purple these saucy salt water taffies make a bold addition to a pinata, party favor bags, and candy stashes. Individually wrapped, enjoy them one at a time or take your chances on upping the ante by enjoying them by the mouthful! Their sweet, fruity taste combined with a sour punch will satisfy even the most daring candy lovers. But be careful because the more you eat, the sassier you may become.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/sassy-taffy-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', '746~sassy-taffy-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', 'sassy-taffy-salt-water-taffy'),
(747, 'Laffy Taffy Ropes', 10.99, '24', 'ct', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Laffy Taffy Ropes are a fun and exciting type of candy that are great for adults and children. They come in a variety of different flavors. You can choose from banana, grape, cherry, sour apple, strawberry or wild blue raspberry. If you want a variety, you can get all of them! There are 24 in this box, which means that they will go a long way! You can stretch it, twist it and bite it! You will also have a whole lot of fun, because just like the smaller Laffy Taffy candies, these ropes still have the jokes on the wrapper! This will provide for hours of enjoyment for you, and it is sure to please your taste buds as well! They even come in a display box with an open top, which makes them great for concessions too! They make great treats for the kids in your life too!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-ropes-24ct.jpg', '747~laffy-taffy-ropes-24ct.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-ropes'),
(748, 'Giant Taffy', 23.99, '24', 'ct', 'salt-water-taffy', 'McCraw\'s Giant Taffy is ready to take on your most intense sweet cravings! Who doesn\'t love the smooth, chewy texture of delicious taffy? Now you can get more of your favorite confection in one big, long sheet!Giant Taffy includes a generous portion of this classic candy rolled out into a long, thin bar. Each features layers of pastel hues including blue, yellow, green and pink. Color combinations may vary but the quality and taste never does! Our bulk giant taffy package gives you many individually wrapped pieces to enjoy or share.Give them to guests or serve them to children as a quick after school treat. McCraw\'s Giant Taffy can also be served at events like birthday parties. Use them as a colorful stocking stuffer, put them in Easter baskets or hand them out during school and community events. Any time is a great time to sink your teeth into a piece of McCraw\'s Giant Taffy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/c/mccrawtaffy.jpg', '748~mccrawtaffy.jpg', 'mccraws-giant-taffy'),
(749, 'Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy candies are a mix of chewy, red licorice and incredibly rich taffy. With a red and white swirl inside of a wax paper wrapper that\'s twisted at the ends, this Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy is also a beautiful candy that looks as good as it tastes.Do you know someone who is a classic candy lover? Want to surprise your kids with a fun, red-themed candy at your Fourth of July celebration? Have another red-themed event you need something yummy for? These Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy candies are ready to take your events to the next level with their scrumptious flavor and addicting chew.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-licorice-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '749~red-licorice-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'red-licorice-salt-water-taffy'),
(750, 'Raspberry Lemonade Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Get ready to feel nostalgic! These Raspberry Lemonade Salt Water Taffies have so many memories packed into every bite. Maybe you used to run a lemonade stand in front of your house every summer. Or maybe your family used to take trips to the boardwalk and bring home boxes of salt water taffy. Take a trip down memory lane with these bright yellow and purple colored and delicious taffies. Set them out in the summertime to make new memories with your family. Whatever you do, every time you eat one you\'ll remember a beloved memory as well as make a new one!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/raspberry-lemonade-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '750~raspberry-lemonade-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'raspberry-lemonade-salt-water-taffy'),
(751, 'Caramel Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Caramel swirl salt water taffy is a rich, chewy treat that you\'ll love to eat! Anyone who adores the sweet, savory flavor of classic caramel must experience the taste of our salt water taffy. Each piece recreates the feeling of eating a bite-sized piece of high quality caramel but with that taffy texture you know and love.Our salt water taffy is available in single-flavor packages so you get exactly what you want every time you order! Bulk caramel swirl salt water taffy can be used for events and much more. Fill treat bags or wedding favors with these elegant little pinwheels. Each includes a toasty brown hue that\'s accented by a slender spiral swirl of white.Each piece arrives individually wrapped so it stays fresh and enjoyable. Order our caramel saltwater taffy for your next event or keep a package at home or at the office to eat as a quick snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '751~caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(752, 'Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', '\'\'Mooo-ve\'\' over for these Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffies. With their beautiful white and black cow spots and creamy flavor, you won\'t ever want to put these down or put them out to pasture. This snack is a classic that has satisfied candy lovers for years.Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice_caramel.jpg', '752~licorice_caramel.jpg', 'licorice-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(753, 'Orange Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Delectable orange juice flavor, individual waxed paper wrappers, and the unforgettable texture of a boardwalk treat make Orange Salt Water Taffy an awesome choice for your next event. This salt water taffy is colored a creamy, dreamy orange to add sweet sunshine to your color scheme, and its flavor is delicately tangy without straying into the sour.A great addition to an assortment of fruit-flavored sweets, this nostalgic candy choice speaks of the seaside! Orange salt water taffy has been enjoyed for a century at seaside resorts and retreats, and it keeps that old-time association for generations of taffy fans!This single-color wholesale taffy for filling jars or treat bags has all the happy traits of that timeless sweet, like the distinctive soft texture that high-quality traditional taffy provides and the lasting flavor that suffuses every bit of the candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '753~orange-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'orange-salt-water-taffy');
