(804, 'Gummy Butterflies', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Hearts are a-flutter for these beautiful butterfly gummies! With 3 lovely gummies in every pound, you can let your taste buds take flight with every sensational bite. Hatched from their cocoon, these little gummies will make you swoon with their vibrant rainbow of colors and fruity flavors. Bring them to a little girl\'s birthday party, sprinkle some into a refreshing punch at a springtime picnic, or give your kids a lesson about the beauty of nature. Known to us as the nectar of the candy gods, see for yourself why these dainty flutterers make sweet lovers feel like they can fly.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '804~gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy'),
(805, 'Red Cherry Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Cherry gummy bears are great for any occasion. They are soft and chewy as well as a great red color that even adults love to take part in. These would make a great purchase for Valentine \'s Day or Christmas due to the fabulous red shade that they have.When you bite into one of these gummy bears you are sure to find that the ripe flavor of cherry is more than enough to please your mouth. Since they come in a bulk bag it is sure to be enough to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for. If you are looking for a way to delight almost everyone then this is certainly one of the great candies that is able to do this. After all who doesn\'t like the way that these candies are so cute and fun? It is hard to beat the greatness of this wonderful product.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '805~cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-gummi-bears'),
(806, 'Haribo Gummi Raspberries', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Haribo gummi raspberries look like real raspberries! Put them in a candy dish at your next gathering and watch your guests get surprised with a gummi taste explosion when they pick one up. These delicious fruity snacks come as a mix of red and black in a big bulk bag. Be careful opening them up, though. Once you start, you won\'t want to stop eating these sweet raspberry gummies. Get them for your candy dish at home or the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', '806~haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-raspberries'),
(807, 'Sour Gummi Poppers', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Try not to drool. These Sour Gummi Poppers have a tart flavor that will make your mouth water! With a bright pastel selection of red, blue, yellow, green, and orange candies, there\'s an entire rainbow of sour for you to choose from. Every candy is coated in a tangy sugar that leads to a sweet, fruity center. Use a handful of these colorful pucker-makers for a candy dish on your coffee table, put some in a glass jar and enjoy looking at them as much as eating them, or even add some to a candy buffet bar for guests to enjoy at their own leisure. We\'re sure you\'ll love puckering with these poppable candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', '807~sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sour-gummi-poppers'),
(808, 'Green Watermelon Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'We think these candies are \'\'de-vine.\'\' A real knee-slapper we know, but in all seriousness, these Pink Watermelon Fruit Sours Candies taste like they\'re fresh off the vine. Covered in a beautiful, glossy pink shell and complete with a soft, fruity chew, these candies are cultivated by using some of the sweetest techniques in the candy biz. Use some for a light sweet at a backyard picnic, bring some to a gathering of friends, even use them for a lovely addition to an outdoor wedding. For watermelon and candy enthusiasts, alike, this bag will provide you with hours and hours of happy snacking.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/0/8/08017-_watermelon_sours.png', '808~08017-_watermelon_sours.png', 'pink-watermelon-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(809, 'Fruit Slices Candy', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Fruit slices gummies are a fabulous treat that comes in many exciting flavors! If you love chewy gummy candy but want more options when it comes to taste, this is a must-try.Our delicious fruit slices candy include a flat wedge shape slab of confection with a flat end and curved side. A white line runs along the curved edge, creating the look of a fruit rind.Every fruit slice is different based on its flavor. Grape is all purple while black cherry includes a red middle with blue â€œrindâ€. We carry a huge variety of juicy flavors that also include lemon lime, cherry, strawberry banana, orange, pink grapefruit, peach, watermelon, sour apple, red raspberry and blue raspberry.If you can\'t decide on just one, you can instead choose our amazing assorted bulk fruit slices pack! This mouthwatering blend contains a little bit of everything so you can sample all your chewy favorites!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', '809~albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', 'fruit-slices-candy'),
(810, 'Gumdrops', 11.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drops and gumdrops, then we\'d be out of business! However, you can still feel like it\'s raining gumdrops with this bulk bag of gummy candies. A classic addition for holiday baked goods, stockings, and fancy gingerbread houses, you will be stocked up for the season with this bag. In a variety of colors and fruity flavors, savor the sweetness as the sugary coating melts in your mouth. Then get ready to chew \'til you drop with a yummy gummy center. The holidays just aren\'t complete without a few mouthfuls of these sugary sweets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gumdrops-5lbs.gif', '810~gumdrops-5lbs.gif', 'gumdrops'),
(811, 'Haribo Gummi Peaches', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'You\'re a peach! Well, actually these Haribo Gummi Peaches are. In a sugary coating and delicious light peach flavor, bite into these chewy gummies for a taste of the summertime. Bring some to a warm weather BBQ, add some as a pretty drink garnish to lemonade and adult drinks, or even use them to decorate the top of a strawberry shortcake! Haribo bears first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany. To this day, they\'re one of the biggest manufacturers of gummies and supply happy snackers all around the world. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so _ the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', '811~haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-peaches'),
(812, 'Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 25.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Wooooweee! These tart purple candies deliver an unrelenting pucker with delicious, fruity flavor. If you like a sour shot to the mouth, try our Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy. The sourest candy on the vine, these little pucker-packed candies will please every sour lover. Bring some to a purple themed party, add some to a lemonade for a sour grape flavor addition and pretty garnish, or keep them around the house when you\'re in the mood for a feisty snack. Their deep, purple coloring may look unsuspecting, but get ready for a dose of tartness that will thrill your taste buds!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '812~purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'purple-grape-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(813, 'Jelly Belly Jelly Beans', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Oh, behold the possibilities! With 50 original flavors plus even more limited-edition beans, concoct combination after combination of inventive candy recipes with this bulk bag of Jelly Belly jelly beans. Maybe you have a hankering for chocolate covered banana, vanilla espresso or coconut orange. Whatever your signature recipe, you can be the chef with the pick of the littler of hundreds of beans brimming with unique flavor. The Jelly Belly company has been around since 1976 and has honed their talent in producing tantilizing flavors that have pleased customers for years. See why for yourself why they are an American favorite with this bulk bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', '813~jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', 'jelly-belly-jelly-beans'),
(814, 'Hot Tamales Candy', 15.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'If you are looking for chewy candy with a spicy cinnamon flavor, that is sure to please, then this is the treat for you. They have a wonderful and exciting red color to them. This is great for those who have a candy buffet and are looking to add a little bit of red to it.When you bite into this great candy you are sure to find that your taste buds will be pleased with the pleasant but strong kick that you great from the awesome flavor that this candy is able to deliver. These come in a bulk bag that is sure to get plenty of them for whatever reason you need them. Whether you are throwing a birthday party, just looking to keep candy around the house, or using them for a buffet you are sure to find that you will be more than pleased with amazing Hot Tamales!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-candy-bulk-4lb_2.jpg', '814~hot-tamales-candy-bulk-4lb_2.jpg', 'hot-tamales-candy-bulk'),
(815, 'Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Pucker up, buttercup! These Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy have a mighty mix of sour and sweet to delight the mouths of many. Soft, chewy, tangy, and gorgeous, the bright mix of candy balls is a cheerful dose of sugar and citrus. Use them for an autumn inspired gift basket, on the Thanksgiving dessert table, or even as sour additions to a trick-or-treat stash. They can even make a summertime festival even more special by adding the beautiful color of the hot sun. There is no wrong way for your friends and family to enjoy these fruity, delicious and sour candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '815~orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'orange-tangerine-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(816, 'Cinnamon Imperials Candy', 20.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'These red hot little cinnamon mouth explosions are great for any candy dish! Cinnamon Imperials candies have a classic taste that everyone remembers from childhood, and they\'re great for all kinds of occasions.Include them as a sweet treat for your Valentine. Add them to an assortment of fruity and spicy candies at a party, or just keep them in the candy dish at home for guests who happen to drop by.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', '816~cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', 'cinnamon-imperials'),
(817, 'Candy Corn', 64.99, '10', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Nothing says autumn like a big bowl of sugary candy corn! At least we don\'t think so. Their bright colors of orange, yellow, and white match the changing leaves, pumpkins, gourds, and glorious sunsets of the season. With this bulk bag of autumnal joy, you will have enough to savor long after the harvest is through. Display some in mason jars for a rustic, fall-themed feel Let your kids be silly by putting them on their teeth and smiling for the camera. Even use them in individual baggies for Halloween treats. We just think these candy corns are \'\'a-maize-ing!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-corn-bulk-5lb.jpg', '817~candy-corn-bulk-5lb.jpg', 'candy-corn'),
(818, 'Sour Power Belts from Dorval', 41.99, '6.6', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Dorval Sour Power belt gummies are a delicious treat for kids and the young at heart! Each piece consist of a long, wide ribbon of flat gummy candy in bright colors. Our flavor list includes all your favorites, like strawberry, watermelon, apple, berry and much more!Sour Power belt candy is a fun choice for birthday parties and holiday events. Our flavor options also make it easy to create your own custom candy assortment! Just order 2 or more packages to combine colors for any celebration. Add to kids treat bags or use as a unique accent on edible displays like gingerbread houses. Sour Power belts also give you more ways to decorate cakes, cupcakes and other baked goods. Our bulk Sour Power gummy belts give you many long pieces so you have enough to share with guests or enjoy at home! This classic candy has been satisfying sweet cravings since 1985.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/dorval-belts-rainbow-bulk.jpg', '818~dorval-belts-rainbow-bulk.jpg', 'sour-power-belts-dorval-bulk'),
(819, 'Gummi Penguins', 11.99, '2.2', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'It\'s the \'\'march of the penguin\'\' gummies! These curious little penguins are full of funny antics and will make your next snack even more charming and delicious! In every bag of these Penguin Gummies, these white and black treats will waddle, splash, and swim into your mouths. They\'re a great snack for kids to play with and an even more adorable treat to look at! These fancy tuxedo clad birds make a cute addition to any black tie, formal affair, wedding reception, or even as a gift to a penguin-loving friend or family lover. Get a taste of the arctic with this gummy, fruity snack today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', '819~gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', 'gummi-penguins'),
(820, 'Assorted Bon Bons', 24.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'There\'s no resisting the sweet taste of Holland bon bons! These delicious treats come in a handful of popular flavors, including orange, strawberry, raspberry, lemon, pineapple and cherry. Take your pick or try them all and savor the fresh picked taste of ripe fruit in a sweet confection. Our bulk candy assortment gives you a large quantity that\'s perfect for parties, picnics, events or any situation that may call for many candy jar refills!Our bon bons come in simple yet elegant wrappers so each is individually packaged and ready for sharing. It\'s easy to identify the flavor of each piece thanks to the colorful fruit image printed right on the surface. Untwist the wrapper and experience the mouthwatering sweetness that makes our fruit bon bons so appetizing. Whether you want a complementary treat to impress clients, a delicious candy to serve guests or a quick snack to enjoy at home, our bulk Holland bon bons will give you the finest fruit flavor in a convenient package!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/columbina_fruit_filled.jpg', '820~columbina_fruit_filled.jpg', 'holland-bon-bons-assorted'),
(821, 'Haribo Happy Cola Bottles', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'There\'s nothing like a cold glass of bubbling, refreshing cola on a hot summer\'s day. Well, unless you count these amazing little Haribo Gummi Cola Bottles! With a sharp, cola flavor and the delicious chew Haribo is famous for, all your sweet snackers will love you for bringing these home. Bring some to your next picnic, add a festive element to a backyard BBQ, or even keep some around the house for snacking. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so the happy world of Haribo!\'\'These are the regular sized Haribo cola bottles. They do not have any writing on them. The Super Cola Bottles are larger and have Haribo written on them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-happy-cola-bottles-icon.jpg', '821~haribo-happy-cola-bottles-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-cola-bottles'),
(822, 'Baby Gummi Bears', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'What do you call a bear with no teeth? A \'\'gummy bear!\'\' We love that one and we\'re sure you\'ll love these Baby Gummi Bears. Shrunken down from their gummi grizzly relatives, these mini munchables are even more adorable and just as delicious! Use these cute cubs to dress up an ice cream sundae, give away in a baby shower gift basket, treat your little ones to a candy their size, or just keep them around for a petite snack. With an assortment of colors and flavors, we\'re sure you\'ll find a favorite among these amazing minis. Use your fangs to chow down on these today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/baby-gummi-bears-10lbs_1.jpg', '822~baby-gummi-bears-10lbs_1.jpg', 'baby-gummi-bears'),
(823, 'Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lite', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Summertime and the living\'s easy. And now, sugar free! Try these Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lites for a healthier fix of the boardwalk classic and all the scrumptious taste of the original recipe. In blue-raspberry, strawberry, lemon, chocolate, orange, and vanilla, let these little morsels melt away as you remember digging your toes into the sand and letting the sun shine in your hair. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', '823~sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite'),
(824, 'Candy Necklaces Unwrapped', 25.99, '100', 'ct', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Show me a kid and I will show you someone that loves candy necklaces. There is just something about colorful jewelry that you can eat that puts a smile on everyone\'s face. First there is the color of the candy necklace the entire rainbow of the spectrum in represented and each color has a unique and delicious taste. One bite can be grape the next can be orange. All kids love variety and this is one of the best kind. Candy necklaces also provide a whole lot of convenience because it is worn around the neck and it is a very short tug to pull a necklace to your mouth and crunch a little bit of candy goodness. It is a lot like carrying a snack to power you through the day. When you need a burst of sugar just take a bite, until it is gone. These treats are great for parties of any kind and all kids just simply love to wear and eat candy necklaces!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-necklaces-100-ct_2.jpg', '824~candy-necklaces-100-ct_2.jpg', 'candy-necklaces-unwrapped'),
(825, 'Runts Candy', 94.99, '30', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Runts candy made its first appearance in the 1980s. While its fruity lineup has changed since then, its popularity has not. Every kid can recognize the fun shapes and bright colors that make Runts so unique. Our extensive collection of bulk candy includes this childhood favorite so you can get your fill of sweet fruity goodness anytime you want! Serve at kid\'s parties, take as a non-perishable snack on camping trips or set some aside to hide away at home for moments when you need a sweet fix!Our Runts candy package include all the current flavors and shapes. You\'ll love biting down on a yellow banana or savoring a tart cherry piece. Each order also includes blue raspberry, watermelon and lime. Try the smooth, sweet taste of your favorite fruits followed by the tantalizing tanginess that makes Runts candies so delectable. You don\'t have to go to a vending machine to find your favorite treat because we have Runts in bulk and ready to ship right to you!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts30lbs.jpg', '825~runts30lbs.jpg', 'runts-bulk'),
(826, 'Hot Pink Sixlets', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'These glamorous Pink Sixlets chocolates are almost too pretty to eat! Almost... But eat them we shall with their pleasant crunch followed by a creamy milk chocolate center. Tinier than M&Ms; at about a third of the size, these little wonders can still satisfy every sweet tooth  big and small. Set them out in a bowl in your office, use them as a wedding candy buffet item, or add some extra girliness to a baby or bridal shower. Whatever you decide to do with these lovely, little gems, we are sure that you and your friends will love looking at them as much as eating them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', '826~sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-pink'),
(827, 'Anise Bears', 10.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Anise is a classic flavor that is very popular among many. If you love the rich, licorice-like flavor of anise but don\'t want to spend time baking to enjoy it, our gummy bears are a great alternative. This charming treat includes jell candy that\'s shaped into handsome standing bears!Each ursine figure includes round years and a human-like pose. The confection is dark brown and covered in delightful texture. Our bulk anise bear candies are ideal for any purpose. Use them to fil candy bowls at birthday parties or put them in treat bags so guests can enjoy them after the festivities.They also make unique decorations for gingerbread houses and other edible displays. Put them on cakes, cupcakes, cookies and more to create an original look that tastes amazing! Enjoy anise in a whole new way with our one-of-a-kind anise gummy bears! Our bulk candy packs will make sure you always have enough for any occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/anise-bears-5lbs.gif', '827~anise-bears-5lbs.gif', 'anise-bears'),
(828, 'Haribo Gummi Strawberries', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'unwrapped-loose', 'Feel like you\'re at the strawberry patch with these Haribo Gummi Strawberries! Modeled after the delicious fruit, these adorable berries are packed with fresh strawberry flavor that will make your snackers smile. Use them on top of strawberry shortcake to add a level of cuteness that can\'t be beat. Or bring them to a picnic and let people snack as their own leisure. These strawberries can do it all. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-strawberries.jpg', '828~haribo-strawberries.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-strawberries'),
(829, 'German Raspberries', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Haribo German raspberries recreate the sweet taste of this popular fruit in an irresistible confection! Each bag contains a combination of red and black berry candies. Instead of sticking with plain gummies, Haribo creates a smooth, chewy center that\'s covered in dainty orbs of sugary goodness. Every bite presents two distinct textures in one tasty tidbit! Order our bulk raspberry candies for special events or snacking at home. Whether you\'re hosting a party, picnic, school event or wedding, our German raspberries are a great choice! Haribo has been serving up some of the most delectable gummy candies for nearly a century. Today their catalog includes many unique confections that offer mouthwatering flavor in little bite sized pieces. Our bulk German raspberries are easy to store so you can hide a bag in your favorite snacking spots so you\'re ready the next time your sweet tooth strikes! Haribo gummy candy will tempt taste buds and satisfy cravings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/e/germanraspberries.jpeg', '829~germanraspberries.jpeg', 'german-raspberries-12ct'),
(830, 'Gourmet 12 Flavor Gummy Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Get ready for the fanciest gummy in the forest with these Gourmet Gummy Bears! In an array of colors and flavors, these colorful cubs come bursting with classic fruity, gummy flavor amd a luxurious chew. Enjoy a rainbow of bears from red to blue to white. Let your little ones laugh and play as these bears march into their mouths. In this bulk selection, these bears are the perfect choice to make a candy buffet bar even fancier. They\'re also great wrapped in individual bags and given out as party favors, put in a bowl of punch for a fruity, chewy surprise, or even to reward your little ones whenever you choose. Discover why these gourmet gummies are \'\'bear-resistible!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gourmet-gummy-bears-12-flavors-5lb_1.jpg', '830~gourmet-gummy-bears-12-flavors-5lb_1.jpg', 'gummy-bears-12-flavors'),
(831, 'Blue Raspberry Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'This is one time when everybody should be allowed to play with their food. And who could resist with these delightful blue raspberry Gummi Bears? Perfectly poppable. Charmingly chewy. Crafted with the care of a tried and true recipe. Everyone will go back for handful after handful of these fruity cuties.WIth each bag brimming with over 145 Gummi Bears per pound, you\'ll have enough furry friends to keep you company through numerous snack times. Their light fruity flavor has made this variety a hit among customers and will keep everyone coming back for more. They\'re what we like to call, \'\'bear-resistible.\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-raspberry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '831~blue-raspberry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'blue-raspberry-gummi-bears'),
(832, 'Gummi Killer Sharks', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Don\'t worry. These killer shark gummies are real softies. As a matter of fact, they are way more afraid of your chompers than of their own! (Cue \'\'Jaws\'\' music). With blue and white coloring, they\'re a bright and tasty candy for a number of events. Delight your kids and throw them a pirate birthday party complete with these toothed treats or pack some into their lunchboxes on a special day. Everyone will have fun playing with these big fish until it\'s time for them to swim into your mouth. They might even be the yummiest fish in under the sea.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummy-killer-sharks-470x470.jpg', '832~gummy-killer-sharks-470x470.jpg', 'gummi-killer-sharks-blue-white'),
(833, 'Haribo Gummi Dinosaurs', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Travel back in time for some prehistoric fun with our gummy dinosaurs! These tasty treats give children an excuse to play with their food before they eat it. Each chewy gummy candy features one of many popular dinos. Overpower taste buds with a realistic T-rex or charge through snack time with a triceratops. From stegosauruses to brontosauruses, everyone\'s favorite species are covered in our bulk candy pack!As if dinosaur shaped gummies weren\'t enough, our terrible lizards are colored half and half so you get two brilliant hues in every piece! These tempting treats are perfect for themed birthday parties, picnics or trips to the natural history museum. Our bulk candy package also makes it easy to get more of the dino gummies you love for gatherings, school events and other occasions. These confectionary treats don\'t roar, but they pack a powerful taste that is sure to satisfy any rampaging sweet tooth!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dinosaurs-gummy-haribo.jpg', '833~dinosaurs-gummy-haribo.jpg', 'gummi-dinosaurs-5lb'),
(834, 'Sunkist Fruit Gems', 69.99, '', '', 'gummy', 'Get ready for a big, sugary smooch with these Sunkist Fruit Gems! Their delicious, gummy chew and bright, fruity flavor will make you want to pucker up for more every time you take a bite. Individually wrapped, these little gummies pack the power of the sun into every chew and show off the beautiful colors of the rainbow.Stock yourself up with some rainy day sunshine with a bag of these. They\'re a great goodie bag stuffer for birthday parties, look lovely at a summertime picnic on the dessert table, and even can be kept to cheer up your little ones on a rainy day. With 42 pieces per pound, there are enough to please every gummy fan!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', '834~sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk'),
(835, 'Grape Purple Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Grape gummi bears are packed with fabulous flavor! Our chewy confections offer excellent quality in a timeless snack that children have loved for decades. There\'s something endearing about the dainty bear faces and chubby little teddy bodies that makes this fruity candy unique. We bring you single-color bulk gummy bears so you can get your favorite flavors without picking through an assortment!Our gummies are also ideal for special occasions. Decorate tables at parties and weddings by putting out glass bowls filled with purple bears! You can hide a few in favor bags to give guests as a delicious thank you! These charming little treats are also great for baby showers and other child-related celebrations. Each gummy bear offers irresistible grape flavor with a soft, chewy texture. It\'s nearly impossible to eat just one! Also check out our other bulk gummy bear packs to find the exact combination of colors you need for any event or occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-grape-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '835~purple-grape-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'purple-grape-gummi-bears'),
(836, 'Haribo Gummi Gold Bears Mini Bags Tub', 13.99, '54', 'ct', 'gummy', 'We sure think that these gummies are \'\'tastier than the average bear!\'\' That\'s because these classic Haribo Gold Gummi Bears are here in a bulk bag to bring you even more of the delicious flavors you love. In a selection of red, orange, yellow, green, and white, everyone in your family will find a cub to love. Sprinkle a few in Jell-O for a \'\'beary\'\' good surprise, add some to a make your own sundae bar, or wrap some up for a loved one to make their day extra special. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', '836~haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-gold-bears-mini-bags-tub'),
(837, 'main image', 11.99, '', '', 'gummy', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drop and gum drops, then we wouldn\'t have room to try these amazing Spice Drops Candies! Coated in sweet, crystalized sugar with a spicy, gummy center, these candies will make your \'\'jaw drop!\'\' In a variety of colors and flavors, these gummies can be used for virtually any occasion. Use some to decorate a gingerbread house in a delicious, traditional way, bring some to a party for kids to munch on while they play, or even add them to a make your own ice cream sundae bar for a surprising topping. You\'ll love chewing on these gum drops as much as watching their sugar sparkle.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spice-drops-gumdrops-alt-470x470.jpg', '837~spice-drops-gumdrops-alt-470x470.jpg', 'spice-drops'),
(838, 'Haribo Gummi Gold Bears', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Silly old bear. These classic Haribo Gold Gummi Bears are here in a bulk bag to bring you even more of the tasty flavors you love. In a selection of red, orange, yellow, green, and white, everyone in your family will find a cub to love. Sprinkle a few in Jell-O for a \'\'beary\'\' good surprise, add some to a make your own sundae bar, or wrap some up for a loved one to make their day extra special. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so n the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gold-bears-gummi-icon.jpg', '838~haribo-gold-bears-gummi-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gold-gummi-bears'),
(839, 'Swedish Fish Red', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'It\'s not polite to fish for compliments. But these gilled little gummies just can\'t help themselves! With their bright, cherry flavor and craveable chewiness, Swedish fish have swam their way out of the sea into the hearts of millions. The original flavor and shape of their brand, these little swimmers have inspired the Swedish Fish AquaLife variety as well as Assorted colors and flavors. They\'ve quickly become the biggest fish in the pond and are a beloved candy staple for people around the world. Dive into this bulk bag and \'\'sea\'\' for yourself what all the fuss is about.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/swedish-fish-red-5lbs_2.jpg', '839~swedish-fish-red-5lbs_2.jpg', 'swedish-fish-red'),
(840, 'Gold Bears Theater Box', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Snack like a king with the Haribo Gold Bears theater box! Whether you love action, comedy, drama or a good animated flick, this handy box of candy will be ready to keep your taste buds busy while you enjoy the show! Our bulk candy pack includes a number of individual boxes so you can share them with a group or keep a few around for easy munching. You know when you\'re reaching for the gold box you\'re getting Haribo\'s finest gummy bears!Each package includes a generous helping of soft, chewy gummy pieces. The fun bear shape is great for children while movie goers of all ages will love the sweet fruit flavor packed into every morsel. Order multiple cases and host a neighborhood movie night at home or keep for special occasions like sleep overs, picnics, parties and more! Any time is a good time to sink your teeth into Haribo gummy bears!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo_gold_bears_theater.jpg', '840~haribo_gold_bears_theater.jpg', 'gold-bears-theater-box-12ct'),
(841, 'Green Apple Gummy Rings Candy', 15.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'We\'re green with envy just thinking about the lucky munchers of these yummy gummies! Sugary, sweet, and packed with a green apple punch, these green and white candies really hit the spot. Put them on your fingers and pop them in your mouth one at a time. Spruce up a St. Patrick\'s day candy display. Even set some out for wedding or birthday party guests to munch on. Whatever you do, these green apple gummy rings are coated with enough sugar and taste to make everyone smile, chew after chew. So what are you waiting for? Make us wish we had a bag of our own.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/p/apple-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', '841~apple-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', 'apple-rings-gummy-candy'),
(842, 'White Pineapple Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'If you\'re putting together a formal dessert table or buffet, don\'t forget the White Pineapple Gummi Bears. They\'re a perfect kid-friendly treat that won\'t clash with the decor for weddings and other formal events. Everyone wins! With these off-white to yellow-colored gummy candies, the kids get the desserts they like, and the adults get the beautiful settings they want. There is some color variation in manufacturing, but it won\'t be nearly as much as if your kids got to choose what went on the dessert tray!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/white-pineapple-gummi-bears-5lbs.jpg', '842~white-pineapple-gummi-bears-5lbs.jpg', 'white-pineapple-gummi-bears'),
(843, 'Green Apple Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Our bulk gummi bears are the perfect choice for anyone who loves the chewy taste of this classic candy. Whether you are buying for a special event or want to perform flavor-specific experiments at home. We can help! Our green apple gummi bears offer the tangy bite of sour with a bit of apple sweetness. They also make great treats to go with school lunches or as a quick snack at home!Each adorable little edible bear includes the famous round years, chubby paws and endearing smile that kids have come to love. You\'ll savor the green apple taste and love the smooth, chewy texture. Gummi bears have been tempting children since the 1920s. Their fun shapes were inspired by trained bears that performed in street festivals throughout Europe. Today we can enjoy that save festive experience in each delicious gummy piece! Whether you eat the one at a time or by the handful, our green apple sour gummy bears will satisfy any sweet tooth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/granny-smith-apple-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '843~granny-smith-apple-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'green-apple-gummi-bears'),
(844, 'Freedom Rings Gummies', 17.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Let freedom ring with these patriotic gummy candies! Gummies have been enjoyed for generations and across many countries. Each variation offers a delicious taste and chewy texture that makes it irresistible.Our Freedom Rings gummies are no different, however they offer a patriotic look that is perfect for special occasions celebrated in America!Each package contains many round rings of smooth, gummy goodness! Each ring includes a two toned pattern, with one half in snow white and the other in either brilliant blue or firecracker red. All are sprinkled in sweet sugar granules for even more delicious taste and texture.Freedom Rings gummies are a must-have at summer picnics, family reunions and baseball games. Create gorgeous baked goods by decorating cakes, cupcakes and more with these fun gummy rings! Our bulk Freedom Rings gummy pack gives you larger quantities that are convenient for holidays, wedding favors and community events.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/freedom-gummi-rings-red-white-blue-candystore.jpg', '844~freedom-gummi-rings-red-white-blue-candystore.jpg', 'freedom-rings-gummies'),
(845, 'Gummy Butterflies', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Hearts are a-flutter for these beautiful butterfly gummies! With 3 lovely gummies in every pound, you can let your taste buds take flight with every sensational bite. Hatched from their cocoon, these little gummies will make you swoon with their vibrant rainbow of colors and fruity flavors. Bring them to a little girl\'s birthday party, sprinkle some into a refreshing punch at a springtime picnic, or give your kids a lesson about the beauty of nature. Known to us as the nectar of the candy gods, see for yourself why these dainty flutterers make sweet lovers feel like they can fly.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '845~gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'gummy-butterfly-bulk-candy'),
(846, 'Sour Patch Watermelon Slices', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Sour Patch Watermelon Slices look like tiny, sugar-dusted pieces of watermelon. Their pink and green coloring makes them perfect to put out at any pink-themed party. They\'ll make a great addition to a bachelorette party or baby shower. They\'re also a perfect pick for Valentine\'s, as their sour taste is sure to make your guests pucker up! You can get these deliciously tart chewy watermelon candies in a big bulk bag, but don\'t let the size fool you. They\'ll be gone before you know it.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-slices-5lbs_2.jpg', '846~watermelon-slices-5lbs_2.jpg', 'watermelon-slices'),
(847, 'Red Cherry Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Cherry gummy bears are great for any occasion. They are soft and chewy as well as a great red color that even adults love to take part in. These would make a great purchase for Valentine \'s Day or Christmas due to the fabulous red shade that they have.When you bite into one of these gummy bears you are sure to find that the ripe flavor of cherry is more than enough to please your mouth. Since they come in a bulk bag it is sure to be enough to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for. If you are looking for a way to delight almost everyone then this is certainly one of the great candies that is able to do this. After all who doesn\'t like the way that these candies are so cute and fun? It is hard to beat the greatness of this wonderful product.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '847~cherry-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-gummi-bears'),
(848, 'White Gummi Bears Strawberry Banana', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Don\'t let their pristine, white color fool you. Or their dainty size. These petite Gummi Bears have the powerful strawberry banana flavor of a giant grizzly. Roar! Pretty enough for a wedding candy display, they also are right at home in a five star candy buffet or as a neutral filler candy in gift bags. With an average of 145 bears per pound, you will have an entire forest-full of flavorful friends to share with friends and family. Chewy and fruity, these Gummies are crowd pleasers. And we would like to think of them as way tastier than the average bear.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears_1.jpg', '848~white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears_1.jpg', 'white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears'),
(849, 'Haribo Gummi Raspberries', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Haribo gummi raspberries look like real raspberries! Put them in a candy dish at your next gathering and watch your guests get surprised with a gummi taste explosion when they pick one up. These delicious fruity snacks come as a mix of red and black in a big bulk bag. Be careful opening them up, though. Once you start, you won\'t want to stop eating these sweet raspberry gummies. Get them for your candy dish at home or the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', '849~haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-raspberries'),
(850, 'Sour Gummi Poppers', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Try not to drool. These Sour Gummi Poppers have a tart flavor that will make your mouth water! With a bright pastel selection of red, blue, yellow, green, and orange candies, there\'s an entire rainbow of sour for you to choose from. Every candy is coated in a tangy sugar that leads to a sweet, fruity center. Use a handful of these colorful pucker-makers for a candy dish on your coffee table, put some in a glass jar and enjoy looking at them as much as eating them, or even add some to a candy buffet bar for guests to enjoy at their own leisure. We\'re sure you\'ll love puckering with these poppable candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', '850~sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sour-gummi-poppers'),
(851, 'Gummi Frogs', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Everyone will jump for joy when they get a taste of Haribo gummy frogs! These little green candies aren\'t slippery and slimy, but they offer a smooth, soft texture that\'s pleasant on the tongue. Each piece includes fun details that recreate this popular amphibian â€“ right down to its folded legs, round head and raised back. Our gummy frogs are solid green and arrive fresh in sealed bags that are ready to enjoy! Hide gummi frogs around the house or save them to put in school lunches for the kids. These charming croakers are also great for serving at birthday parties, picnics and school events. Put them in a bowl or use them to dress up cakes, cupcakes, cookies and more! No matter how you display them, our Haribo gummy candies will entice children of all ages. Order our bulk candy pack so you have plenty of chewy frogs for any occasion!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', '851~haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', 'gummi-frogs-12ct'),
(852, 'Gummi Bears', 15.49, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Why didn\'t the teddy bear eat his lunch? Because he was stuffed! You\'ll be stuffed after eating mouthful after mouthful of these assorted gummi bears. In a big bulk bag of rainbow fruity cuties, you\'ll have a lot to chew about. Bring these little cubs to a birthday party. Put them in a sparkling punch at a backyard barbeque. Spoil your little ones by tucking some of these away in their lunch boxes. Or even fill goodie bags with a handful of these yummy gummies. Whatever you do, you\'ll love sampling the rainbow of colors and flavors. They\'re \'\'bear-resistable!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummi-bears-5lbs_2.jpg', '852~gummi-bears-5lbs_2.jpg', 'gummi-bears'),
(853, 'Fruit Slices Candy', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Fruit slices gummies are a fabulous treat that comes in many exciting flavors! If you love chewy gummy candy but want more options when it comes to taste, this is a must-try.Our delicious fruit slices candy include a flat wedge shape slab of confection with a flat end and curved side. A white line runs along the curved edge, creating the look of a fruit rind.Every fruit slice is different based on its flavor. Grape is all purple while black cherry includes a red middle with blue â€œrindâ€. We carry a huge variety of juicy flavors that also include lemon lime, cherry, strawberry banana, orange, pink grapefruit, peach, watermelon, sour apple, red raspberry and blue raspberry.If you can\'t decide on just one, you can instead choose our amazing assorted bulk fruit slices pack! This mouthwatering blend contains a little bit of everything so you can sample all your chewy favorites!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', '853~albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', 'fruit-slices-candy'),
(854, 'Orange Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Orange you excited about these? Because we are! A real knee-slapper, we know. But in all seriousness, these pint sized, orange Gummi Bears are packed with crisp citrus flavor that will have you smacking your lips with every chew. Use them to make a thematic Halloween display or drop them into a refreshing summer punch. They make delightful gift bag stuffers and even cake toppers, too. A popular and well-known chew among candy lovers, these make a great choice in satisfying all of your friends and family. Whatever occasion you can dream up, let these adorable bears brighten your day.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '854~orange-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'orange-gummi-bears'),
(855, 'Gumdrops', 11.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drops and gumdrops, then we\'d be out of business! However, you can still feel like it\'s raining gumdrops with this bulk bag of gummy candies. A classic addition for holiday baked goods, stockings, and fancy gingerbread houses, you will be stocked up for the season with this bag. In a variety of colors and fruity flavors, savor the sweetness as the sugary coating melts in your mouth. Then get ready to chew \'til you drop with a yummy gummy center. The holidays just aren\'t complete without a few mouthfuls of these sugary sweets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gumdrops-5lbs.gif', '855~gumdrops-5lbs.gif', 'gumdrops');
