(1149, 'Yellow Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Mirror, mirror on the wall. Who\'s the fairest of them all? These Yellow and White Mini Candy Sticklettes are to us! Their pristine white swirled around bright, cheerful yellow is a show-stopper. Individually wrapped and at half the size of regular candy sticks, these little wonders will make a delightful snack, time after time. Set them out in summertime punches and lemonade for a lovely garnish, put them in a yellow-themed candy display, or keep them around the house for a cheerful reminder of warmer days to come. Whatever you do with this mini sticklettes, you\'ll love stirring, licking, and chomping them as much as looking at them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/e/yellow-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '1149~yellow-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'yellow-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(1150, 'Lime Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Let\'s start with the obvious, shall we? If the mere sight of these Lime Candy Sticks doesn\'t inspire you to throw a party, nothing will!Leprechauns will be coming out of the woodwork to get their hands on these tasty treats on St. Patrick\'s Day, and of course, they will be the perfect complement to other holiday candy at Christmas.Throwing a celebration for Earth or Arbor Day? The light green and yellow stripes swirled around these rich green Lime Candy Sticks can represent the forest for these environmental celebrations.Now, let\'s talk about flavor! The bold, tangy fruit taste of these Lime Candy Sticks will have guests of all ages grinning ear-to-ear. They can be eaten as is, or you can add them to water, soda, or even margaritas and daiquiris by the pool. They are certified kosher and manufactured in a facility that uses no gluten or nuts.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lime_old_fashioned_1.jpg', '1150~lime_old_fashioned_1.jpg', 'lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(1151, 'Life Savers Candy', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Laver Savers candies have been around for many years. They are enjoyed by everyone from children to adults. These great candies are available in many different colors such as red, purple, green, orange, white, and even yellow. You can get many different flavors such as wild cherry, grape, lime, pineapple, orange, and even butter rum. You are sure to find a flavor that you are able to enjoy. You are also sure to find that these small hard, crunchy candies are able to provide a great deal of taste that you are sure to be pleased with. These candies are great for birthday parties, Halloween, weddings, and more. They come in rolls and you can choose from multi-flavored rolls, or the ones that one has a single flavor depending on your preference. There is nothing that can take you back to your childhood more than the great taste of Life Savers.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', '1151~life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', 'life-savers-rolls'),
(1152, 'Charms Sour Balls Tins', 42.99, '12', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'When it comes to making friends, candy is a great ice breaker. Choosing the right candy will determine how successful you are at this endeavor. Charms Sour Balls are definitely the right candy. These delicious hard candy treats make the young happy and the old nostalgic. There is a power in the sour ball that will win friends because it is the perfect combination of both sweet and sour that appeal to everyone. They come in cherry, grape, lemon, lime and of course orange. When you see a tin of these delicious treats, you can\'t help think of Christmas and other celebrations. Once a can is open it is nearly impossible to stop the smiles and good times. With a whole tin of this candy on your side, you will be able to win a whole lot of new friends and in the end, would you want to be friends with someone who didn\'t like Charms Sour Balls?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', '1152~charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', 'charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz'),
(1153, 'Hershey\'s Kisses', 36.99, '4', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Show some love with our bulk Hershey kisses! Few candies are as recognizable as the familiar cone shape that is the trademark of these chocolate treats. They are simply yet extremely versatile. Hand them out at parties, use them to fill your candy dish at home or add them to party or wedding favors. No matter where you are or what the occasion may be, guests will savor the sweet taste and unique shape that has earned these charming confections enormous popularity. Every Hershey kiss candy is covered in a silver foil wrapper. Simply peel back the top and enjoy the full, rich flavor that comes with every dainty bite! Our bulk candy packages are the most convenient way to order your Hershey kisses in large quantities for gatherings and events. You can also purchase a pack or two for baking around the holidays so you always have enough to make your favorite Hershey cookies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hershey-kisses-bulk-470x470.jpg', '1153~hershey-kisses-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'hersheys-kisses-original'),
(1154, 'Chocolate Bulk Candy Mix', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Get all the chocolaty goodness you can handle in this bulk candy mix! Our chocolate assortment includes a generous quantity of confections. Thereâ€™s Reeceâ€™s Pieces, mini Hershey bars, Starburst, Jolly Ranchers and assorted taffy. Each piece is individually wrapped so it stays fresh and delicious. Grab a handful and get the perfect mix of chewy and sweet for snack time or special occasions!This practical chocolate bulk candy mix is perfect for events and special occasions. Use them to get a variety of candy for treat bags or party favors. Just toss a handful in a favor box or bag and you have a gift your guests will enjoy! Keep a package in your pantry so your candy dish never goes empty or use to fill up the candy jar at work. Chocolate and taffy makes a tasty snack thatâ€™s easy to pack in lunches or in your purse or pocket!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', '1154~candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', 'bulk-chocolate-candy-mix'),
(1155, 'Red Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'The mere sight of these will have you longing for Valentine\'s Day. Although these Red Milk Chocolate Hearts are the perfect candy or the year\'s most romantic day, you certainly don\'t have to wait until February to enjoy them.They are popular for weddings, engagement parties, bridal showers, and New Year\'s Eve parties, too. A lot of love goes into making these mouthwatering Red Chocolate Hearts. The delectable chocolate sauce is poured into molds and left to harden.Then, they are carefully wrapped with shiny red foil.Since they are all individually wrapped they\'re appropriate for any candy dish. You can even pour some in small jars, add a pretty ribbon, and hand them out to all your friends who don\'t have sweetheart to spend Valentine\'s Day with. Your mom, sister, aunt, and cousin will surely love them, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', '1155~red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', 'red-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(1156, 'Gold Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Gold milk chocolate hearts are a rich, beautiful treat that\'s versatile and delicious. Every piece is made using high quality milk chocolate that\'s molded to form a solid heart shape.Heart candy is a great choice for events that celebrate love and friendship. Give them away during Valentine\'s Day or use them in shower and wedding favors. Our gold milk chocolate hearts are especially attractive thanks to their elegant presentation.Each solid milk chocolate heart is protected by a thin layer of shimmering foil. The surface is covered in a breathtaking metallic gold hue that produces the same shine as the metal. Unwrap and enjoy the amazingly sweet taste of traditional milk chocolate!These irresistible heart candies look sophisticated whether you pour them into a jar or bowl or display them on a tray with other treats. Impress coworkers and clients by keeping our bulk milk chocolate hearts at work or save them for home snacking!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', '1156~gold-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', 'gold-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(1157, 'Lindt Chocolate Lindor Truffles', 49.99, '120', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Savor every rich bite of our Lindt chocolate Lindor truffles! Exquisitely smooth and irresistibly chocolaty, these delectable round candies are simply irresistible. Pamper your taste buds by biting into the classic chocolate shell to sample the creamy confection hidden deep inside. We carry the finest Lindt truffles flavors, including luxurious dark chocolate, sweet hazelnut, traditional milk chocolate, refreshing mint, delightful peanut butter, sensational raspberry and dark chocolate and scrumptious white chocolate. We make it easy to get all the Lindt chocolate truffles you need for any occasion. Our bulk candy packs are wonderful for serving at parties or as part of beautiful wedding favors. Treat your beloved guests to the heavenly taste that makes Lindor truffles so desirable! Every piece is individually packaged in a colorful wrapper with the elegant Lindt brand clearly displayed. Simply untwist the ends and you have a chocolate truffle treat that is unlike any other!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lindor-truffles-main.jpg', '1157~lindor-truffles-main.jpg', 'lindt-chocolate-lindor-truffles'),
(1158, 'Blue Milk Chocolate Stars', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'The stars have aligned in this delicious milk chocolate candy to bring you the best of the cosmos chocolate-y and adorable! These Blue Milk Chocolate Stars come in a bulk bag and possess all the beauty and majesty of space plus, even better taste! Wrapped in a shiny, blue foil and stuffed with star-shaped chocolate, every sweet lover will want and entire galaxy full of these treats. Use them for a super hero themed party, add them to a candy bar buffet at a Fourth of July event, or even put some on your Christmas tree as beautiful ornaments that will sparkle and taste delicious.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-milk-chocolate-stars-5lb_1.jpg', '1158~blue-milk-chocolate-stars-5lb_1.jpg', 'blue-milk-chocolate-stars'),
(1159, 'Chocolate Ladybugs', 39.99, '60', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Chocolate ladybugs will brighten anyone\'s day! Each piece consists of high quality chocolate that forms a solid bug shape. This delicious foil wrapped chocolate candy is the perfect addition to any gathering or event.The top creates a dome with a flat bottom and narrower head.Each piece is wrapped in shiny foil to create a red body with black spots and a cute gold face with smile and nostalgic eyes! Bulk chocolate ladybugs are a great way to get more candy for any celebration! Their bright red color makes them a great choice for Valentine\'s Day favors or wedding favors.They also present an adorable look that is so sweet for baby showers. Any spring or summer event is a great time to serve these edible bugs! Businesses can give them to customers as a sweet thank you for doing business while schools and communities can include these economical treats in their annual festivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-ladybugs-60ct_1.jpg', '1159~chocolate-ladybugs-60ct_1.jpg', 'chocolate-ladybugs-foil-wrapped'),
(1160, 'Kimmie Gemstones Chocolate Rocks', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'These rocks may look real, but they are actually quite edible! Kimmie gemstones chocolate rocks are a gorgeous assortment of earthy candies that are designed to look and feel like real stones.Each piece features a uniquely organic shape with straight edges and uneven sides that produce an original, naturally made look. Take a bite of a gemstone chocolate rock and you\'ll discover a center that\'s filled with sweet, rich chocolate! The outside is covered in a shimmering candy coating that carefully lines each crease and dent in the chocolate rock\'s surface.This gives each piece a realistic appearance. Serve them up and make guests think you just chiseled this delectable confection out of a secret cave of confections! Chocolate rocks are a tasty snack that also makes great party favors. Use them to decorate cakes, cupcakes and cookies or add to candy dishes to serve at wedding receptions, birthdays and more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/e/gemstones.jpg', '1160~gemstones.jpg', 'kimmie-gemstones-chocolate-rocks-5lb'),
(1161, 'Red Milk Chocolate Stars', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'If making a wish on a star is a good thing, imagine what is going to happen when you make a wish on a special Red Milk Chocolate Star! These chocolate treats are star shaped extravagance that is packaged up in a beautiful red foiled wrapper. Many people eat these special treats at Independence Day and not only help celebrate the birthday of a nation. They can help to mark the celebration of anyone\'s birthday in the most delicious way. The five points of the stars are going to bring a remarkable feeling of joy as each point of the star leads to a treasure of chocolaty goodness. Valentine\'s Day and Christmas are holidays that naturally lead to using these Red Milk Chocolate Stars to add some extra zip to each holiday.  Hand these chocolate treats to your friends and everyone will want to be your valentine. This bulk bag of chocolates will be enough to make a small party of people feel the happiness this candy treat can bring.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-foil-chocolate-stars.jpg', '1161~red-foil-chocolate-stars.jpg', 'red-milk-chocolate-stars'),
(1162, 'Chocolate Covered Pretzels', 69.99, '6', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Everyone knows that it\'s what\'s on the inside that counts. But what if on the outside is ooey-gooey chocolate? In the interest of deliciousness, we\'ll bend the rules for these titillating twists just this once! With a yummy selection of dark, milk, and white chocolate, it\'ll be hard to choose. But with a salty, crunchy pretzel interior and a melty chocolate coating, any of these dipped wonders will provide you will hours upon hours of happy snacking. Surprise a chocolate lover with a bag of these or keep them around for a rainy day snack. Whatever you do, everyone can satisfy their sweet and salty tooth with one of these tasty triplets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-pretzels-6lbs_2.gif', '1162~chocolate-covered-pretzels-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-pretzels'),
(1163, 'Fort Knox Gold Coins Chocolate', 28.99, '30', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Fort Knox may hold all of the country\'s gold. But here at CandyStore.com, we hold a good portion of the world\'s sweets! We\'re not sure which one you find more valuable, but whatever it may be, these Fort Knox Gold Chocolate Coins will make you feel like you\'ve struck it rich every time you take a bite.With a gleaming gold aluminum wrapper and tasty chocolate coin center, unwrap each coin one at a time or by the dozen. If you\'re hosting a casino game night, want to reward your kids with a tasty and valuable treat, are planning to make a opt of gold for a St. Patrick\'s Day celebration, or anything else, these are the candies for you.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins-48ct_1.jpg', '1163~fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins-48ct_1.jpg', 'fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins'),
(1164, 'Riverstones Kimmie Mix', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Riverstones Kimmie mix is the best way to get a wide variety of Choco Rocks for events, parties or baking. These tasty little morsels are unique from any other candy you have ever eaten.Each piece contains a solid piece of rich chocolate candy. The outside is blanketed in a solid candy shell. The exterior features realistic texture and earthy colors.Our Riverstone Choco Rocks mix contains a number of delightful hues. You\'ll see marble white stones along with vibrant green and burnt orange. Many other natural tones are included to produce an assortment with variety. Even though many colors are used, each piece blends well, adhering to an organic palette.Use these to decorate construction birthday cakes or ad to bags to give out as a fun party favor. They are even elegant enough to use in your wedding favors! Order our bulk chocolate river stones and enjoy the irresistible taste of candy rocks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/i/riverstones.jpg', '1164~riverstones.jpg', 'riverstones-kimmie-mix-5lb'),
(1165, 'Life Savers Pep O Mint', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Is your mouth screaming \'\'SOS\'\' for a breath freshening treat? Well, these Life Savers Pep-O-Mint and Wint-O-Green are here to save the day! Let them toss you a life preserver for your taste buds with their fresh minty flavor and classic \'\'O\'\' shaped form. This hero of the candy world has been around since 1912 and has saved mouths all over the world. Pep-O-Mint was the first flavor and quickly made an impression in the mouths of many. Since then, a variety of fruity and other mint flavors have been invented. Try these minty rolls on for size and see for yourself if you think they\'re worthy of their heroic name!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', '1165~mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', 'mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct'),
(1166, 'Silver Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Silver milk chocolate hearts aren\'t made of sterling silver metal, but they sure look like they are! These eye-catching heart candies are a superb choice for Valentine\'s Day and major events.Every piece is made of a solid serving of sweet milk chocolate. The smooth surface is protected by a thin layer of shimmering foil. This creates that gorgeous shiny finish that makes these heart candies so stunning!Silver milk chocolate hearts are a convenient choice for wedding favors, shower favors and more. Our bulk candy pack gives you many pieces that are economical for bigger crowds.Arrange them on a cookie tray or pour into a glass candy dish and you have an elegant presentation for guests. This package contains all silver wrappers. Also check out our other milk chocolate heart candy to find additional wrapper colors. Order just one or try 2, 3 or more to create a custom chocolate mix for your event!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', '1166~silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', 'silver-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(1167, 'Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars', 38.99, '14', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Behold, a 200 year old chocolate. Well, not this one specifically. That would be gross. However, Cadbury has been around since the 1800s and has been making work famous chocolates ever since. Bring these Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars home to spoil your family and friends with a taste of the past. With their breakable sections, they\'re great to enjoy in small nibbles or big bites! Get a loved one a bar for Valentine\'s Day, melt a few of these bars into fondue, or just keep them around for delicious baking. Get your chocolate bar today and try out the famous recipe that has been honed over two centuries.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', '1167~cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', 'cadbury-chocolate-bars'),
(1168, 'red chocolate hearts foil wrapped', 109.99, '', '', 'chocolate', 'We\'ve met our soul mate. That\'s because these adorable Red Chocolate Foil Hearts are so delicious and cute that we want our taste buds to spend the rest of their lives together! Add these loveable little chocolates to a Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of heart shaped chocolates is here to make a romantic day even more memorable.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-foil-hearts.jpg', '1168~red-chocolate-foil-hearts.jpg', 'red-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(1169, 'Lavender Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'It might be hard to believe, but what\'s underneath the gorgeous pastel foil of these lavender foil chocolate balls awaits something equally as amazing: chocolate. Did we blow your mind? Because these lavender chocolate balls are going to as soon as you unwrap one and rest it on your tongue.If you love a candy that\'s as beautiful as it is delicious, then look no further. These lavender foil-wrapped chocolate balls will add a glamorous and girly look to any candy dish, candy jar or candy buffet bar you set out. Use them as decor and a delicious snack for guests to munch on while they await a meal. Or keep them around to tuck into lunchboxes or on top of baked goods that need a touch of something special.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lavendar_chocolate_balls.jpg', '1169~lavendar_chocolate_balls.jpg', 'lavender-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1170, 'Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars 3pc', 94.99, '12', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Whether you are celebrating a job promotion, engagement, or the birth of a baby, Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are the perfect addition to your event. Crafted from premium milk chocolate and molded to look just like real cigars, these impressive masterpieces will have folks taking a closer look when they see you bite the end of one.The Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are all individually wrapped in exquisite Italian foil that replicates a genuine tobacco leaf. They are available in three options: Original, It\'s a Girl, and It\'s a Boy.These divine treats are kosher certified and made in the USA by Thompson Candy Company. They are perfect for baby showers, delivery celebrations at the hospital, Father\'s Day, anniversaries, birthdays, and thank you gifts, just to name a few. Order these Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars for you to handout, or give the entire box to someone as a gift. They are sure to make everyone smile, and they are a lot better for you and the environment than the real thing.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', '1170~royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', 'royale-premium-chocolate-cigars'),
