(1188, 'Red Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in shiny, metallic red wrappers, these little Red Foil Chocolate Balls are sure to make your eyes pop as your mouth waters for what\'s inside. Inside is a solid ball of melty milk chocolate. It\'s up to you whether you want to chomp, chew or let this little sphere melt away. Red Foil Chocolate Balls are the perfect color and candy for Christmas, the Fourth of July, and a birthday party for someone who adores the color. Stock up on these Red Foil Chocolate Balls and mix and match with other flavors and colors or enjoy them all by themselves. Whatever you do, you\'ll love unwrapping these chocolate balls one after the other.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '1188~red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1189, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '1189~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(1190, 'Assorted Salt Water Taffy Mix', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Assorted salt water taffy mix. Do you remember those amazing trips to the beach with your family when you were a kid? Vacation was never complete without a trip to the candy store and a big bag of salt water taffy. Bring those great memories to life in your mouth any time you like with these assorted salt water taffy candies. Set them out in a candy dish at home or work and share the sweet experience.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', '1190~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(1191, 'Vanilla Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When was the last time your hard working mouth took a vacation? Treat it with a lovely retreat to the salty shores of the boardwalk-lined coast with these saltwater taffys. Complete with a soft, chewy texture and light vanilla taste, you\'ll remember why it\'s so good to get away for a while. Feel like the breeze is in your hair, the sand is between your toes and the jubilant hubub of the boardwalk is buzzing around you bite after bite. In the late 1800s, salt water taffy was discovered when a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be for generations to come.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1191~vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'vanilla-salt-water-taffy'),
(1192, 'Grape Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Beach bums, get ready for a treat that will remind you of the summer heat! This grape salt water taffy has been stretched, chewed, and loved for years. Inspired by the sunny boardwalk, these individually wrapped candies can bring back summertime memories whenever you wish.Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1192~grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'grape-salt-water-taffy'),
