(1273, 'Gold Foil Orange Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Many people love the hard candies that come wrapped in foil. If you are one of these people then you will find that the orange flavored hard candy may be just what you have been looking for. These are a great color of orange and are wrapped in a foil that is gold in color which is able to make them unique and can also make you feel like you are really rolling in the money. Since the color is a festive color you will find that these will look great for any occasion that you want to use them for. This means you can use them at a party, wedding, or even a candy bar. Who would have thought that hard candies could be so full of flavor and color? These are certain to be a hit among almost everyone who has the great pleasure of being able to try them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '1273~gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy'),
(1274, 'Citrus Slices Candy Assorted', 44.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Finally! We\'ve discovered a delicious candy that does grow on trees! These Citrus Slices Candies have all the delicious flavor of some of your favorite fruits and are a beautiful treat to look at. Individually wrapped, each grapefruit, lemon, lime, orange, and tangerine candy treat in green, yellow, pink, orange will make every snacker smile. Bring some to a beach party for a summery, festive treat, add some to a punch to add a burst of bright color and sweet flavor, or even wrap some up in a gift bag for a fruity surprise. These classic citrus slice candies will please every boy and girl.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/citrus-slices-candy-bulk-10lb_1.jpg', '1274~citrus-slices-candy-bulk-10lb_1.jpg', 'citrus-slices-candy'),
(1275, 'Lifesavers Hard Candy 5 Flavors 41oz', 13.99, '', '', 'hard-candy', 'Lifesavers hard candy brings big flavor in a little package. There\'s a lot to love in every bag of Lifesavers, especially if you have hard time picking out just one flavor. You can taste all your favorites with our enormous bulk Lifesaver bag! This package offers a great value with more of the hard candy you love. Order for at home or bring a bag into the office or worksite so you can share with everyone! Teachers can reward their students with a sweet treat and parents can fill treat bags with lifesavers for parties and other events.Lifesavers are more than just a hard candy: they are an edible piece of the past. These renowned sweets were originally made in 1913. Things were different back then and it wasn\'t until 1925 that the iconic hole was added to each disc. Today you can get all the fruity flavor you want with our bulk Lifesaver package!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/f/5flavors41oz.jpg', '1275~5flavors41oz.jpg', 'lifesavers-hard-candy-41ct'),
(1276, 'Claey\'s Root Beer Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'We\'re rooting for these classic candies. That\'s because Claey\'s Root beer Old-Fashioned Candy Drops are completely coated in crystally, crunchy sugar granules that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Beyond the saccharine coating, lies a delicious hard candy. They\'ll take you back to a warm, summer\'s day of sipping a refreshing root beer float. Stock up on some to add to root beer treats, add to a gift basket, or put out on the Thanksgiving table. Among root beer, Claey\'s favorite flavors include green apple, licorice, natural horehound, watermelon, lemon, and wild cherry. They\'ll look lovely in your coffee table candy dish or set out in a jar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', '1276~root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', 'root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
