(1281, 'Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags', 39.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Leave it to Jolly Ranchers to provide a delicious, colorful and fun treat that is also good for you. While providing all of the expected value expected from Jolly Rancher, they upped the ante by making their snacks sugar free as well! The classic candy comes individually wrapped to keep in the unique freshness. Each piece of candy provides a classic blast of fruit refreshment without the worry of taking in any extra sugar that will make parents and dentists smile. This treat can be enjoyed all by yourself or with a bunch of your friends. Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags make it always seem like a party. Enjoy the explosion of fruit flavor in your mouth without any of the guilt. Get the best Jolly Rancher hard candy that has your favorite flavor, watermelon, apple, grape or raspberry. Not only are these treats sugar free but each candy contains only 1 calories, which means that you can enjoy your fruity flavored candies all day long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', '1281~jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-sugar-free-candy-bags'),
(1282, 'Claey\'s Watermelon Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'We think these candies are \'\'de-vine.\'\' That\'s because these amazing Watermelon Cherry Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops are the most delicious candy in the patch! Dusted in powdery, sweet sugar, these bright red candies pack a serious punch of watermelon flavor that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Bring some to a holiday gathering that needs a dose of festive red, drop a few into a cold lemonade or punch for a sweeter, fruity flavor, add them to a Fourth of July dessert table, or make a Valentine\'s Day gift even yummier. With this 1 pound order of watermelon candies, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.gif', '1282~watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.gif', 'watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(1283, 'Charms Squares Candy', 24.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Cherry, Grape, Lemon, Lime, Orange, and Raspberry combine to make one incredibly delicious pack of treats in this Charms Squares Candy order. You\'ll be in for a surprise every time you unwrap one of the packet\'s 10 candies and stuff it into your mouth.Charms are known for their sour sweet treats and this supply isn\'t short in any of the above. If this sounds like a match made in heaven for you, then why not order yourself some of our Charms Squares Candies today? They\'ll wow all of your guests, impress your family and keep you snacking with a smile on your face for days and days.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-squares-candy-20ct.gif', '1283~charms-squares-candy-20ct.gif', 'charms-squares'),
(1284, 'Aquarium Hard Candy Fish', 49.99, '15', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Where does the fish keep his money? In the river bank! These Aquarium Hard Candies are a lovely reminder of summertime and the beautiful ocean and will make every candy lover smile. They\'re just as intricate as the natural ocean variety, but a million times more delicious. In a variety of colors and flavors from under the sea there\'s a flavor for every beach-lover. Use them for a luau-themed party. Throw a beachside bash for all of your friends. Even enjoy one while you\'re sitting on the hot sand. Or give them to a fishing fanatic you know. Just make sure you\'re not \'\'shellfish\'\' with these delicious candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/q/aquarium-hard-candy-fish-candystore.jpg', '1284~aquarium-hard-candy-fish-candystore.jpg', 'aquarium-hard-candy-fish'),
