(1288, 'Green Apple Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Claey\'s old-fashioned green apple candy drops are a tasty treat that comes with history. The brand has been producing high quality classic treats since 1919. For three generations, Claey\'s Candy has been giving the world some of the best old time confections available.Their selection includes a number of nostalgic favorites, like fudge, Chocolate Charlie and irresistible old fashioned candy drops. Green apple candy drops are available in bulk quantities so you get more juicy flavor in every package! These round little tidbits are a great choice for family gatherings like reunions, picnics and birthday parties.Share them with loved ones when they come to visit or keep a sweet stash on hand to satisfy apple and sugar cravings. Candy has become a longstanding tradition in the Claey family, and now it can become a tradition in your family! Order your bulk green apple candy drops today and enjoy the memories packed into every piece.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_1.jpg', '1288~green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_1.jpg', 'green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(1289, 'Lifesavers Butterrum', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Butter rum Lifesavers candy is a sweet treat with classic personality. While it may not be as outrageous as wild cherry or as refreshing as wint-o-green, butter rum is packed with tasty sweetness that satisfies like no other candy can. This rich blend of flavors is even better when packed into each hard candy hoop. Lifesavers are easy to enjoy and come in a convenient tube package that you can place in a purse, pocket, desk drawer or wherever you may be when cravings hit!The history of the Lifesaver candy begins in 1912 when Clarence Crane invented the hard mint version. At the time he needed a pill manufacturer to produce the shape of each piece. It wasn\'t until 1925 that the familiar hole was added, creating the popular donut shape we all know and love today. Our bulk Lifesaver candy boxes are a great choice for offices, schools or anyone planning an event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lifesaversbutterrum.jpg', '1289~lifesaversbutterrum.jpg', 'lifesavers-butterrum-20ct'),
(1290, 'Spree Candy', 37.99, '36', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'It is a dilemma as old as Spree candies themselves: eat just one and enjoy its sweet-and-sour flavor individually, or snack your way through the whole roll?The carefree name and colorful purple-based packaging make it no surprise that Spree is one of the Willy Wonka Candy Company confections, and there are some sweet tooths among us who feel that the candy disks unique texture and bold flavor make them the best. This box of bulk Spree rolls offers the colorful sweets in a convenient form great for traveling.Each cylindrical package is a party favor or picnic dessert in itself! The bright colors of this oh-so-simple sour sweet are instantly appealing to kids â€“ and nostalgic to those who grew up in the days of rainbow confections gorgeously assorted in sweet-shop jars.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spree-candy-36ct_1.gif', '1290~spree-candy-36ct_1.gif', 'spree-candy'),
(1291, 'Altoids Cinnamon', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Altoids cinnamon candy are more than just a curiously strong mint. These refreshing treats are a confection that comes with a long, rich history. The original recipe was created by a London-based company in the 1780s, when King George III sat on the throne. The product\'s high concentration of peppermint oil is what inspired the popular slogan we all know and love today. Altoids are currently available in six different flavors, including cinnamon. The storage tin was introduced in the 1920s and still helps keep each mint fresh and clean, even while on the go. Our bulk mint package is a convenient option for anyone who never wants to go without their favorite candy! Hide a tin in your purse or pocket or keep them in the glove box. The larger quantity is also great to share at the office or while on the job. Invigorate your mouth with Altoids cinnamon mints!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoidscinnamon.jpg', '1291~altoidscinnamon.jpg', 'altoids-cinnamon-12ct'),
(1292, 'Lifesavers Wild Cherry', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Wild cherry Lifesavers is a quick and easy snack that everyone can enjoy! Each hard candy piece is filled with sweet cherry flavor. Just open the end and treat your taste buds to the irresistible taste of fresh picked cherry sweetness! Lifesavers aren\'t just delicious â€“ they are also convenient! Each box contains individual packages that you can keep anywhere. Hide them in your desk, purse, pocket or car so you always have something to satisfy your sweet tooth!Lifesavers candy is a classic confection that was created in 1912. The original hard mints were later expanded upon with wintergreen, clove, chocolate, cinnamon and violet flavors. Today we can enjoy a huge list of Lifesavers, including succulent wild cherry! Our bulk candy box makes these treats even better because you can get more hard candy to store or share. Just order a box or two and you will always have something to give guests, coworkers or clients!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/i/wildcherrylifesavers.jpg', '1292~wildcherrylifesavers.jpg', 'lifesavers-wild-cherry-20ct');
