(1442, 'Chocolate Bulk Candy Mix', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Get all the chocolaty goodness you can handle in this bulk candy mix! Our chocolate assortment includes a generous quantity of confections. Thereâ€™s Reeceâ€™s Pieces, mini Hershey bars, Starburst, Jolly Ranchers and assorted taffy. Each piece is individually wrapped so it stays fresh and delicious. Grab a handful and get the perfect mix of chewy and sweet for snack time or special occasions!This practical chocolate bulk candy mix is perfect for events and special occasions. Use them to get a variety of candy for treat bags or party favors. Just toss a handful in a favor box or bag and you have a gift your guests will enjoy! Keep a package in your pantry so your candy dish never goes empty or use to fill up the candy jar at work. Chocolate and taffy makes a tasty snack thatâ€™s easy to pack in lunches or in your purse or pocket!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', '1442~candy-mix-chocolate-starburst-candystore.jpg', 'bulk-chocolate-candy-mix'),
(1443, 'Red Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'The mere sight of these will have you longing for Valentine\'s Day. Although these Red Milk Chocolate Hearts are the perfect candy or the year\'s most romantic day, you certainly don\'t have to wait until February to enjoy them.They are popular for weddings, engagement parties, bridal showers, and New Year\'s Eve parties, too. A lot of love goes into making these mouthwatering Red Chocolate Hearts. The delectable chocolate sauce is poured into molds and left to harden.Then, they are carefully wrapped with shiny red foil.Since they are all individually wrapped they\'re appropriate for any candy dish. You can even pour some in small jars, add a pretty ribbon, and hand them out to all your friends who don\'t have sweetheart to spend Valentine\'s Day with. Your mom, sister, aunt, and cousin will surely love them, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', '1443~red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', 'red-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(1444, 'Gold Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Gold milk chocolate hearts are a rich, beautiful treat that\'s versatile and delicious. Every piece is made using high quality milk chocolate that\'s molded to form a solid heart shape.Heart candy is a great choice for events that celebrate love and friendship. Give them away during Valentine\'s Day or use them in shower and wedding favors. Our gold milk chocolate hearts are especially attractive thanks to their elegant presentation.Each solid milk chocolate heart is protected by a thin layer of shimmering foil. The surface is covered in a breathtaking metallic gold hue that produces the same shine as the metal. Unwrap and enjoy the amazingly sweet taste of traditional milk chocolate!These irresistible heart candies look sophisticated whether you pour them into a jar or bowl or display them on a tray with other treats. Impress coworkers and clients by keeping our bulk milk chocolate hearts at work or save them for home snacking!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', '1444~gold-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', 'gold-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(1445, 'Lindt Chocolate Lindor Truffles', 49.99, '120', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Savor every rich bite of our Lindt chocolate Lindor truffles! Exquisitely smooth and irresistibly chocolaty, these delectable round candies are simply irresistible. Pamper your taste buds by biting into the classic chocolate shell to sample the creamy confection hidden deep inside. We carry the finest Lindt truffles flavors, including luxurious dark chocolate, sweet hazelnut, traditional milk chocolate, refreshing mint, delightful peanut butter, sensational raspberry and dark chocolate and scrumptious white chocolate. We make it easy to get all the Lindt chocolate truffles you need for any occasion. Our bulk candy packs are wonderful for serving at parties or as part of beautiful wedding favors. Treat your beloved guests to the heavenly taste that makes Lindor truffles so desirable! Every piece is individually packaged in a colorful wrapper with the elegant Lindt brand clearly displayed. Simply untwist the ends and you have a chocolate truffle treat that is unlike any other!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lindor-truffles-main.jpg', '1445~lindor-truffles-main.jpg', 'lindt-chocolate-lindor-truffles'),
(1446, 'Blue Milk Chocolate Stars', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'The stars have aligned in this delicious milk chocolate candy to bring you the best of the cosmos chocolate-y and adorable! These Blue Milk Chocolate Stars come in a bulk bag and possess all the beauty and majesty of space plus, even better taste! Wrapped in a shiny, blue foil and stuffed with star-shaped chocolate, every sweet lover will want and entire galaxy full of these treats. Use them for a super hero themed party, add them to a candy bar buffet at a Fourth of July event, or even put some on your Christmas tree as beautiful ornaments that will sparkle and taste delicious.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-milk-chocolate-stars-5lb_1.jpg', '1446~blue-milk-chocolate-stars-5lb_1.jpg', 'blue-milk-chocolate-stars'),
(1447, 'Chocolate Ladybugs', 39.99, '60', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Chocolate ladybugs will brighten anyone\'s day! Each piece consists of high quality chocolate that forms a solid bug shape. This delicious foil wrapped chocolate candy is the perfect addition to any gathering or event.The top creates a dome with a flat bottom and narrower head.Each piece is wrapped in shiny foil to create a red body with black spots and a cute gold face with smile and nostalgic eyes! Bulk chocolate ladybugs are a great way to get more candy for any celebration! Their bright red color makes them a great choice for Valentine\'s Day favors or wedding favors.They also present an adorable look that is so sweet for baby showers. Any spring or summer event is a great time to serve these edible bugs! Businesses can give them to customers as a sweet thank you for doing business while schools and communities can include these economical treats in their annual festivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-ladybugs-60ct_1.jpg', '1447~chocolate-ladybugs-60ct_1.jpg', 'chocolate-ladybugs-foil-wrapped'),
(1448, 'Kimmie Gemstones Chocolate Rocks', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'These rocks may look real, but they are actually quite edible! Kimmie gemstones chocolate rocks are a gorgeous assortment of earthy candies that are designed to look and feel like real stones.Each piece features a uniquely organic shape with straight edges and uneven sides that produce an original, naturally made look. Take a bite of a gemstone chocolate rock and you\'ll discover a center that\'s filled with sweet, rich chocolate! The outside is covered in a shimmering candy coating that carefully lines each crease and dent in the chocolate rock\'s surface.This gives each piece a realistic appearance. Serve them up and make guests think you just chiseled this delectable confection out of a secret cave of confections! Chocolate rocks are a tasty snack that also makes great party favors. Use them to decorate cakes, cupcakes and cookies or add to candy dishes to serve at wedding receptions, birthdays and more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/e/gemstones.jpg', '1448~gemstones.jpg', 'kimmie-gemstones-chocolate-rocks-5lb'),
(1449, 'Red Milk Chocolate Stars', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'If making a wish on a star is a good thing, imagine what is going to happen when you make a wish on a special Red Milk Chocolate Star! These chocolate treats are star shaped extravagance that is packaged up in a beautiful red foiled wrapper. Many people eat these special treats at Independence Day and not only help celebrate the birthday of a nation. They can help to mark the celebration of anyone\'s birthday in the most delicious way. The five points of the stars are going to bring a remarkable feeling of joy as each point of the star leads to a treasure of chocolaty goodness. Valentine\'s Day and Christmas are holidays that naturally lead to using these Red Milk Chocolate Stars to add some extra zip to each holiday.  Hand these chocolate treats to your friends and everyone will want to be your valentine. This bulk bag of chocolates will be enough to make a small party of people feel the happiness this candy treat can bring.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-foil-chocolate-stars.jpg', '1449~red-foil-chocolate-stars.jpg', 'red-milk-chocolate-stars'),
(1450, 'Chocolate Covered Pretzels', 69.99, '6', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Everyone knows that it\'s what\'s on the inside that counts. But what if on the outside is ooey-gooey chocolate? In the interest of deliciousness, we\'ll bend the rules for these titillating twists just this once! With a yummy selection of dark, milk, and white chocolate, it\'ll be hard to choose. But with a salty, crunchy pretzel interior and a melty chocolate coating, any of these dipped wonders will provide you will hours upon hours of happy snacking. Surprise a chocolate lover with a bag of these or keep them around for a rainy day snack. Whatever you do, everyone can satisfy their sweet and salty tooth with one of these tasty triplets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-pretzels-6lbs_2.gif', '1450~chocolate-covered-pretzels-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-pretzels'),
(1451, 'Fort Knox Gold Coins Chocolate', 28.99, '30', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Fort Knox may hold all of the country\'s gold. But here at CandyStore.com, we hold a good portion of the world\'s sweets! We\'re not sure which one you find more valuable, but whatever it may be, these Fort Knox Gold Chocolate Coins will make you feel like you\'ve struck it rich every time you take a bite.With a gleaming gold aluminum wrapper and tasty chocolate coin center, unwrap each coin one at a time or by the dozen. If you\'re hosting a casino game night, want to reward your kids with a tasty and valuable treat, are planning to make a opt of gold for a St. Patrick\'s Day celebration, or anything else, these are the candies for you.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins-48ct_1.jpg', '1451~fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins-48ct_1.jpg', 'fort-knox-gold-chocolate-coins'),
(1452, 'Riverstones Kimmie Mix', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Riverstones Kimmie mix is the best way to get a wide variety of Choco Rocks for events, parties or baking. These tasty little morsels are unique from any other candy you have ever eaten.Each piece contains a solid piece of rich chocolate candy. The outside is blanketed in a solid candy shell. The exterior features realistic texture and earthy colors.Our Riverstone Choco Rocks mix contains a number of delightful hues. You\'ll see marble white stones along with vibrant green and burnt orange. Many other natural tones are included to produce an assortment with variety. Even though many colors are used, each piece blends well, adhering to an organic palette.Use these to decorate construction birthday cakes or ad to bags to give out as a fun party favor. They are even elegant enough to use in your wedding favors! Order our bulk chocolate river stones and enjoy the irresistible taste of candy rocks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/i/riverstones.jpg', '1452~riverstones.jpg', 'riverstones-kimmie-mix-5lb'),
(1453, 'Life Savers Pep O Mint', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Is your mouth screaming \'\'SOS\'\' for a breath freshening treat? Well, these Life Savers Pep-O-Mint and Wint-O-Green are here to save the day! Let them toss you a life preserver for your taste buds with their fresh minty flavor and classic \'\'O\'\' shaped form. This hero of the candy world has been around since 1912 and has saved mouths all over the world. Pep-O-Mint was the first flavor and quickly made an impression in the mouths of many. Since then, a variety of fruity and other mint flavors have been invented. Try these minty rolls on for size and see for yourself if you think they\'re worthy of their heroic name!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', '1453~mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', 'mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct'),
(1454, 'Silver Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Silver milk chocolate hearts aren\'t made of sterling silver metal, but they sure look like they are! These eye-catching heart candies are a superb choice for Valentine\'s Day and major events.Every piece is made of a solid serving of sweet milk chocolate. The smooth surface is protected by a thin layer of shimmering foil. This creates that gorgeous shiny finish that makes these heart candies so stunning!Silver milk chocolate hearts are a convenient choice for wedding favors, shower favors and more. Our bulk candy pack gives you many pieces that are economical for bigger crowds.Arrange them on a cookie tray or pour into a glass candy dish and you have an elegant presentation for guests. This package contains all silver wrappers. Also check out our other milk chocolate heart candy to find additional wrapper colors. Order just one or try 2, 3 or more to create a custom chocolate mix for your event!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', '1454~silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', 'silver-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(1455, 'Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars', 38.99, '14', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Behold, a 200 year old chocolate. Well, not this one specifically. That would be gross. However, Cadbury has been around since the 1800s and has been making work famous chocolates ever since. Bring these Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars home to spoil your family and friends with a taste of the past. With their breakable sections, they\'re great to enjoy in small nibbles or big bites! Get a loved one a bar for Valentine\'s Day, melt a few of these bars into fondue, or just keep them around for delicious baking. Get your chocolate bar today and try out the famous recipe that has been honed over two centuries.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', '1455~cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', 'cadbury-chocolate-bars'),
(1456, 'red chocolate hearts foil wrapped', 109.99, '', '', 'chocolate', 'We\'ve met our soul mate. That\'s because these adorable Red Chocolate Foil Hearts are so delicious and cute that we want our taste buds to spend the rest of their lives together! Add these loveable little chocolates to a Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of heart shaped chocolates is here to make a romantic day even more memorable.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-foil-hearts.jpg', '1456~red-chocolate-foil-hearts.jpg', 'red-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(1457, 'Lavender Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'It might be hard to believe, but what\'s underneath the gorgeous pastel foil of these lavender foil chocolate balls awaits something equally as amazing: chocolate. Did we blow your mind? Because these lavender chocolate balls are going to as soon as you unwrap one and rest it on your tongue.If you love a candy that\'s as beautiful as it is delicious, then look no further. These lavender foil-wrapped chocolate balls will add a glamorous and girly look to any candy dish, candy jar or candy buffet bar you set out. Use them as decor and a delicious snack for guests to munch on while they await a meal. Or keep them around to tuck into lunchboxes or on top of baked goods that need a touch of something special.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lavendar_chocolate_balls.jpg', '1457~lavendar_chocolate_balls.jpg', 'lavender-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1458, 'Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars 3pc', 94.99, '12', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Whether you are celebrating a job promotion, engagement, or the birth of a baby, Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are the perfect addition to your event. Crafted from premium milk chocolate and molded to look just like real cigars, these impressive masterpieces will have folks taking a closer look when they see you bite the end of one.The Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars are all individually wrapped in exquisite Italian foil that replicates a genuine tobacco leaf. They are available in three options: Original, It\'s a Girl, and It\'s a Boy.These divine treats are kosher certified and made in the USA by Thompson Candy Company. They are perfect for baby showers, delivery celebrations at the hospital, Father\'s Day, anniversaries, birthdays, and thank you gifts, just to name a few. Order these Royale Premium Chocolate Cigars for you to handout, or give the entire box to someone as a gift. They are sure to make everyone smile, and they are a lot better for you and the environment than the real thing.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', '1458~royal_cigars_3pk.jpg', 'royale-premium-chocolate-cigars'),
(1459, 'Royal Blue Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Royal blue foil chocolate balls offer the perfect combination of visual appeal and taste. Everyone loves the smooth, rich flavor of high quality chocolate. Our individually wrapped candy balls make it easy to share this classic treat at any event or right at home! Each piece includes a solid ball of savory milk chocolate that\'s wrapped in a thin layer of foil. Our royal blue chocolate balls add elegance to any presentation. Pour them into glass bowls or jars to set out on guest tables. You can also add a few to sachets or bags to give away as wedding favors. The dark blue color goes with almost any celebration! Add an icy blue chill to a winter feast or celebrate a birthday with the irresistible taste of pure chocolate. You can even share them with coworkers or give complimentary candies to clients as a thank you for their business!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '1459~royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1460, 'Ghirardelli Twilight Delight 72% Dark Chocolate Squares Caddy', 26.99, '50', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Ghirardelli Twilight Delight 72% Dark Chocolate Squares Caddy - 50ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/h/ghirardelli_twilight_delight_72_dark_chocolate_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', '1460~ghirardelli_twilight_delight_72_dark_chocolate_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', 'ghirardelli-twilight-delight-72percent-dark-chocolate-squares-caddy'),
(1461, 'Chocolate Basketballs', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Getting together to watch the game is a momentous occasion worthy of marking with specialty candy â€“ at least, if your team is doing well! Celebrate victories and mourn losses with these foil-wrapped Chocolate Basketballs, solid balls of chocolate that melt in your mouth once you remove the realistically-printed orange foil wrapper.These bulk chocolate basketballs are great for sports parties, birthday parties, and candy buffets tailored to the interests of the guest of honor! When the NCAA tournament rolls around, you will be glad to have these chocolate balls on hand for dropping into lunch boxes or topping off the office candy jar!These chocolate candies are also sure to enthuse a youth basketball team if offered by the handful at their end-of-season bash. The foil wrappers are not just clever and thematic, but also easy to remove, making chocolate basketballs a perfect candy-dish sweet.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolatebasketballs.jpg', '1461~chocolatebasketballs.jpg', 'chocolate-basketballs-foil-wrapped'),
(1462, 'Gold Nugget Choco Rocks Bulk', 39.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Gold nugget choco rocks are one of the most fascinating and unique candies available! This treat is unlike any other chocolate snack. Every piece features an original shape that looks much like natural rocks.The surface is covered in a luxurious gold shell that produces an alluring shimmer that looks very realistic, right down to the fine gravelly texture that runs along all sides. While these chocolate nuggets look like rocks, they taste amazing! Don\'t worry, you won\'t break any teeth when you bite down on each rich piece. The candy coating on the outside provides a crunch while smooth, irresistible chocolate hides within Ã just waiting to take your taste buds on a sweet adventure!Our bulk gold nugget choco rocks are perfect for many occasions. Use them to fill a pot of gold at your next St. Patrick\'s Day party. Choco rocks are also great for decorating baked goods and edible decor!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks-bulk_1.jpg', '1462~gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks-bulk_1.jpg', 'gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks'),
(1463, 'Chocolate Golf Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Now golfers can enjoy their favorite confection and their favorite sport at the same time! Our chocolate golf balls are packed with rich flavor that comes in a fun themed package.Each bite-sized morsel consists of a solid orb of delectable chocolate. The smooth, dark surface is covered in a thin foil wrapper with a uniquely printed exterior. The pure white background is covered in realistic pock marks to recreate the look of an actual golf ball!You can take these delicious chocolate with you anywhere, from the green to the clubhouse! Our bulk chocolate balls are also a great treat for special occasions like golf themed birthday parties, picnics and holidays.Impress a fellow golfer with the smooth taste of fine chocolate that comes in a package they can appreciate! Our bulk chocolate golf balls makes it easy to order enough for wedding favors, treat bags and edible gifts.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', '1463~chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', 'chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1464, 'Silver Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This candy will steal your heart! And how could they not with their shimmery, shiny silver wrapper and even more amazing chocolate heart that lays within. Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Silver Foil Hearts is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '1464~silver-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'silver-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(1465, 'Ghirardelli Dark and Sea Salt Caramel Squares Caddy', 26.99, '50', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Ghirardelli Dark and Sea Salt Caramel Squares Caddy - 50ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/h/ghirardelli_dark_and_sea_salt_caramel_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', '1465~ghirardelli_dark_and_sea_salt_caramel_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', 'ghirardelli-dark-and-sea-salt-caramel-squares-caddy'),
(1466, 'Purple Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wear your heart on your sleeve with these heavenly chocolates. The indulgent mouthfuls of joy are the perfect message to send the special someone who has your whole heart. Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Purple Foil Hearts is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '1466~purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'purple-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(1467, 'Sour Power Belts Wrapped', 24.99, '150', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'With 150 Sour Power Belts in this big bulk supply you will have plenty of opportunity for flavorful fun. These candies were introduced in 1985, and folks of all ages have not been able to get enough of them.If you love pucker-inducing treats, these Sour Power Belts should definitely be on your shopping list. This box of delicious treats is available in Green Apple, Blue Raspberry, Strawberry, and Watermelon. We recommend getting all four before you drive yourself crazy trying to pick only one.The belts are about 9-inches long and just under 1-inch wide, so they are pretty much the perfect size. Big enough to satisfy, but not so big you get a tummy ache. Since these Sour Power Belts are individually wrapped you can surprise your kids with them in their lunch box and hand them out at Halloween.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', '1467~sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', 'sour-power-belts-dorval-wrapped'),
(1468, 'Tiffany Blue Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Do you have expensive taste but a budget to stick to? Well, these Tiffany Blue Foil Chocolate Balls might be the perfect candy for you! With the famous, powder blue of the high end jewelry store, Tiffany, and decadent chocolate underneath, you\'ll add a sophistication to every sweet snack break. Bring these to a bridal shower, bachelorette party, or the baby shower for a boy! They even make a great addition to a blue themed candy buffet bar or a wedding reception. These glamorous chocolates come in a bulk bag and will impress your taste buds and guests whenever you serve them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/i/tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '1468~tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1469, 'Chocolate Covered Oreo Cookies', 64.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This may be the one time when we encourage people to judge a confection by its cover. Because this cookie\'s cover is a thick layer of creamy, melty chocolate! Chocolate Covered Oreos have become a sensation in recent years, and with this bulk bulk bag, there are over 70 cookies to enjoy. Whether you\'re an Oreo fan who insists on eating the cream first and then the cookie or vice versa, we think you\'ll all agree that savoring the chocolate cookie coating before it all is the best way to go about this particular batch. It\'s a problem we don\'t think you\'ll take issue with while you make your way through mouthwatering layer upon layer of chocolatey, creamy goodness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-oreo-cookie5lbs_2.gif', '1469~chocolate-covered-oreo-cookie5lbs_2.gif', 'oreo-cookies-chocolate-covered'),
(1470, 'White Yogurt Mini Twist Pretzels', 50.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Our white yogurt mini twist pretzels give you a new way to enjoy your favorite baked treat! Pretzels are delicious on their own, with their crunchy texture and salty taste. This version takes miniature knots and smothers them in cool, smooth white yogurt. Itâ€™s an irresistible combination that will please taste buds and calm cravings! Bulk white yogurt pretzels give you more pieces for snacking, sharing, and parties.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/o/yogurt-tiny-pretzels_2.jpg', '1470~yogurt-tiny-pretzels_2.jpg', 'white-yogurt-mini-twist-pretzels-candy'),
(1471, 'Chocolate Soccer Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in foil that looks like a classic black and white soccer ball and with amazing chocolate balls beneath, these Chocolate Soccer Balls are winners for sure! Do you have a friend or family member who plays soccer? Why not make their next game extra special by bringing an order of these Chocolate Soccer Balls by at half time? There are plenty to share with the whole team and can cheer up a losing team or help celebrate an incredible win!Chocolate Soccer Balls also are a great candy for sports-themed birthday parties or soccer training camps. Score big with your friends and family and order some today. Oleee, ole, ole, ole. Get ready to chant the most famous soccer game song of all time with these Chocolate Soccer Balls!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', '1471~chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', 'chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1472, 'Chocolate Rocks', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Rocks aren\'t very appetizing, unless they are chocolate rocks! These natural looking candies are absolutely gorgeous to see and so sweet to the taste buds.If you love cocoa flavor, then you will fall in love with these charming little edible pebbles. Each includes a dense chocolate candy that\'s covered in a solid candy coating in a rainbow of earthy colors!What makes chocolate rocks so delicious isn\'t just their taste, but also their appearance. Each stone looks just like the real thing! The candy coating creates lovely texture while each chocolate is uniquely shaped Ã just like real rocks. This assortment includes a variety of hues, ranging from slate blue to burnt orange and black.Grab a handful or enjoy one at a time. No matter which color you choose, each offers the same amazing chocolate taste. Our bulk chocolate rocks are a must-have for cake decorating and special occasions!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolaterocks.jpg', '1472~chocolaterocks.jpg', 'chocolate-rocks-5lb'),
(1473, 'Assorted Sports Chocolate Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Golf balls, tennis balls, basketballs, baseballs, soccer balls and footballs, oh my! We\'re sure everyone will want to be on your team when you bring these Assorted Sports Chocolate Balls in bulk supply to your next party or sporting event.That\'s because these sports balls aren\'t only melty milk chocolate and scrumptious, but they\'re also fun to play with! Hit a home run with one of these baseballs and throw it into your mouth. Kick a field goal through your friend\'s fingers and then indulge in chocolate. You\'re going to score big points with whoever you share these Assorted Sports Chocolate balls with, that\'s for sure!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/foil-sports-balls-chocolate.jpg', '1473~foil-sports-balls-chocolate.jpg', 'chocolate-assorted-sports-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1474, 'Milk Chocolate Gold Coins Medium Size', 136.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This 5-pound supply of Milk Chocolate Gold Coins is perfect to hand out at nearly any event. Fill a treasure chest with them for a pirate-themed birthday party.Use them as a snack at your next poker party, include them in a gift bag, or hand them out at Halloween. These Milk Chocolate Gold Coins are about the size of a quarter, and the highly detailed gold foil makes them look like real currency. There are hundreds of coins in this bulk supply, which should be more than enough for any celebration.Although great for a party, you don\'t need to be planning a special event to order these Milk Chocolate Gold Coins. Stock your candy jar with them and you\'ll always have a quick bite size snack handy when you need to satisfy a little sugar craving. These medium size yummy chocolate coins are certified kosher, making them an ideal Hanukkah gift, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', '1474~milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', 'milk-chocolate-gold-coins-medium'),
(1475, 'Bright Pink Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Bright pink foil chocolate balls are delightful to look at and pleasing to the taste buds. These simple candies offer big visual appeal. Each piece includes a luxuriously solid orb of milk chocolate with a smooth exterior.The surface is covered in a delicate blanket of foil with a glorious pink shine. It\'s both tasty snack and elegant display that works at home, the office or at events!Pour our bright pink foil chocolate balls into any glass container and you have a beautiful chocolate display!That\'s why our colorful foil wrapped candies are such a great choice for wedding favors, showers and other high class celebrations. We make it easy to get large quantities for a big crowd with our affordable bulk chocolate balls pack. Order just one package of chocolate balls or multiple so you have plenty to go around whether you\'re hosting an event for 10, 100 or 1,000!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/bright-pink-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '1475~bright-pink-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'chocolate-balls-bright-pink-foil-wrapped'),
(1476, 'Red Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in shiny, metallic red wrappers, these little Red Foil Chocolate Balls are sure to make your eyes pop as your mouth waters for what\'s inside. Inside is a solid ball of melty milk chocolate. It\'s up to you whether you want to chomp, chew or let this little sphere melt away. Red Foil Chocolate Balls are the perfect color and candy for Christmas, the Fourth of July, and a birthday party for someone who adores the color. Stock up on these Red Foil Chocolate Balls and mix and match with other flavors and colors or enjoy them all by themselves. Whatever you do, you\'ll love unwrapping these chocolate balls one after the other.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '1476~red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1477, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '1477~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(1478, 'Assorted Salt Water Taffy Mix', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Assorted salt water taffy mix. Do you remember those amazing trips to the beach with your family when you were a kid? Vacation was never complete without a trip to the candy store and a big bag of salt water taffy. Bring those great memories to life in your mouth any time you like with these assorted salt water taffy candies. Set them out in a candy dish at home or work and share the sweet experience.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', '1478~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(1479, 'Vanilla Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When was the last time your hard working mouth took a vacation? Treat it with a lovely retreat to the salty shores of the boardwalk-lined coast with these saltwater taffys. Complete with a soft, chewy texture and light vanilla taste, you\'ll remember why it\'s so good to get away for a while. Feel like the breeze is in your hair, the sand is between your toes and the jubilant hubub of the boardwalk is buzzing around you bite after bite. In the late 1800s, salt water taffy was discovered when a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be for generations to come.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1479~vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'vanilla-salt-water-taffy'),
(1480, 'Grape Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Beach bums, get ready for a treat that will remind you of the summer heat! This grape salt water taffy has been stretched, chewed, and loved for years. Inspired by the sunny boardwalk, these individually wrapped candies can bring back summertime memories whenever you wish.Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1480~grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'grape-salt-water-taffy'),
(1481, 'Raspberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Sally may sell sea shells by the seashore, but we sell savory salt water taffy that gives her a run for her money! A summertime classic, this raspberry flavored taffy is ready to take you back to the boardwalk any time of the year. Individually wrapped, they are the perfect solution to a sweet tooth or to be used as a party favor. You can almost hear the surf as you let these morsels melt away. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1481~raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'raspberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(1482, 'Peppermint Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When days at the beach get hot, you can do more than jumping in the waves for a cool-down. Try our refreshing Peppermint Salt Water Taffy to beat the heat. The individually wrapped morsels make them ideal to pack in a beach bag or cooler. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1482~peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'peppermint-salt-water-taffy'),
(1483, 'Strawberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'What happens when you combine creamy saltwater taffy with the juicy flavor of ripe red strawberries? You get one of the most mouthwatering confections found on land or in the sea! Saltwater taffy is a classic treat that hails from the sundrenched boardwalks of Atlantic City, NJ. This classic confection has been around for decades and has become a popular souvenir at many seaside destinations. Our strawberry saltwater taffy is easy to get because you don\'t have to go on vacation to buy it!The blend of molasses, sea salt and strawberry flavorings gives our saltwater taffy an irresistibly soft, smooth taste. Every piece is individually wrapped so you can easily separate servings for snacking or place a few in a party or wedding favor! The gentle pink taffy color includes deep red stripes around the sides that make this treat perfect for Valentine\'s Day, anniversaries or any special occasion that celebrates love!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1483~strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'strawberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(1484, 'Laffy Taffy Candy', 37.99, '8.5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Laffy Taffy is such a well-recognized candy that hip-hop artist D4L has immortalized its name in song. You don\'t have to be a fan of rap to enjoy these chewy soft candies, though. Each individually wrapped Laffy Taffy candy comes with a joke written on the wrapper for you to share with your friends. You\'ll laugh with your friends as you satisfy your sweet tooth for this delicious taffy candy. They\'re so good, though, that you might want to share the jokes, but you won\'t ever want to share the candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', '1484~laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-pieces-bulk'),
(1485, 'Tropical Assorted Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'This seashore classic is now heading to the tropics with these Assorted Tropical Salt Water Taffies! Feel the sun on your face, the wind in your hair, and hear the crash of the ocean waves with every bite of these colorful taffies. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/r/tropical_assorted.jpg', '1485~tropical_assorted.jpg', 'tropical-salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(1486, 'Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Prepare to hypnotize your taste buds with these Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffies. In a stark contrast of black and white swirls, these candies are as yummy to eat as they are to look at. Use them for a thematic addition to Halloween or a formal wedding reception. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1486~licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(1487, 'Key Lime Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Don\'t you just love the light, refreshing sweetness that comes with biting into a slice of key lime pie? How about the fun, chewy tastiness of salt water taffy? Well, you can have the best of both worlds with Key Lime Salt Water Taffy!These individually wrapped goodies have a classic taste that everyone loves and a great chewy texture, too. Put them in a candy dish for your guests at home or your coworkers at the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1487~key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'key-lime-salt-water-taffy'),
(1488, 'Cherry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Cherry salt water taffy is sure to take you back to your childhood vacations to the beach. These red and pink chewy candies will be a huge hit anywhere you take them. Put them out in a candy dish at home, or take them to share the sweet taffy goodness at work or at a party. Cherry salt water taffy makes a great addition to a Valentine\'s Day gift bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1488~cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-salt-water-taffy'),
(1489, 'Blueberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Blueberry saltwater taffy combines all the goodness of fresh picked berries with the seaside nostalgia of this timeless treat! Our soft taffy candy is just as smooth as a soft sandy beach with flavor that\'s as powerful as the ocean waves. The first saltwater taffy was born right along the seashore in Atlantic City, New Jersey. Over 100 years later we still savor the luxuriously smooth texture and mouthwatering taste that comes with each piece. Our bulk saltwater taffy pack includes all the blueberry candy you can handle, individually packaged. Each piece is protected by a clear wrapper that shows its pleasant blue color. Eating is easy: just untwist the ends and take a bite of timeless saltwater taffy! Our blue version is perfect for baby showers, wedding favors, birthday celebrations, 4th of July events and any occasion that features azure hues. Try just one bulk candy bag or order other flavors to create an attractive contrast at parties and picnics!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blueberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1489~blueberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'blueberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(1490, 'Banana Taffy Taffy Town', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you love to visit the zoo then this is the perfect candy for you to enjoy. This Banana Salt Water Taffy has such a real banana flavor that each and even monkeys can be fooled about their authenticity. Salt water taffy is going to make you feel great about yourself anyway, because it provides a person with a bit of nostalgia. There is no other treat which screams about summer more than salt water taffy. This sweet banana taste is going to make eating one of these treats an impossibility but no need to worry as they come in a hefty bulk bag. That should be enough to keep you munching for hours. The real banana taste is going to make you want to visit the local zoo, because you will want to share them with all the other primates. Candy is always best when it is shared with someone who appreciates it and primates of all ages will absolutely love this!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1490~banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'banana-salt-water-taffy');
