(1491, 'Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lite', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Summertime and the living\'s easy. And now, sugar free! Try these Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lites for a healthier fix of the boardwalk classic and all the scrumptious taste of the original recipe. In blue-raspberry, strawberry, lemon, chocolate, orange, and vanilla, let these little morsels melt away as you remember digging your toes into the sand and letting the sun shine in your hair. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', '1491~sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite'),
(1492, 'cinnamon swirl salt water taffy in a white bowl', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you have never tried cinnamon salt water taffy then you don\'t know what you are missing out on. The flavor of these is perfect. They have a cinnamon blend that is spicy and works just right with the sweet flavor that they have as well. There is nothing better than the tasty of salt water taffy and when you combine it with cinnamon the flavor really seems to explode. The candies are pink in color and are sure to look great for a many different occasions. You will also like to know that each piece is wrapped individually which is very helpful in making sure that they stay fresh as long as possible. There is just something about the chewy texture of taffy that is able to please so many people. This is a great tasting candy with a great texture that is hard to beat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1492~cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'cinnamon-salt-water-taffy'),
(1493, 'Watermelon Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Two summer classics unite in this amazing, summery confection. Try our refreshing Watermelon Salt Water Taffy to beat the heat. The individually wrapped morsels make them ideal to pack in a beach bag or cooler and their bright pink and green color combination makes them a lovely addition to any pinata or candy buffet bar. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1493~watermelon-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'watermelon-salt-water-taffy'),
(1494, 'Green Apple Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Which way to the beach? These delicious Green Apple Salt Water Taffies will make you want to lay on the warm sand with every chew. Their bright green color and tart green apple flavor will please every boardwalk lover and remind you of warmer days to come. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', '1494~green-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', 'green-apple-salt-water-taffy'),
(1495, 'Cotton Candy Taffy', 9.99, '3', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Relive your fondest childhood memories with every bite of cotton candy taffy! This irresistible snack offers a nostalgic flavor that\'s sure to please. Recall the excitements of visits to the local candy shop, where you could pick out your favorite chewy taffy treats.Or how about the soft, fluffy taste of cotton candy while spending time at the carnival! Our cotton candy taffy combines both of those wonderful experiences into one bite-sized confection. Our bulk cotton candy taffy includes large quantities that are individually wrapped to ensure freshness and flavor.They are convenient for sharing and giving. Use them to fill up the office candy jar or pour in a bowl to serve guests who stop by. Cotton candy taffy features a lovely light blue hue that looks elegant in wedding favors or can be used to complement a boys baby shower theme! Everyone will love the eye-catching look and sweet taste of our cotton candy taffy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/cotton-candy-taffy-sweets.jpg', '1495~cotton-candy-taffy-sweets.jpg', 'sweets-cotton-candy-taffy'),
(1496, 'Passion Fruit Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'We\'ve got the love and the passion for these Passion Fruit Salt Water Taffies! Let these individually wrapped taffies make your heart pitter patter with their beautiful, bright blue and yellow coloring and citrusy flavor experience. A boardwalk favorite amongst beach vacationers for years, this recipe upholds the high standard of the original. Discovered in the late 1800s when a shop owner\'s candy store was flooded by rising ocean tides, he made the best of it and decided to market the salt-soaked candies to the public and they loved them! Ever since, people haven\'t been able to get enough of these chewy, salty-sweet, creamy taffies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1496~passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy'),
(1497, 'Orange Creme Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'You can almost feel the fresh salty breeze in your hair and hear the roaring of the waves hitting the beach with every bite of these Orange Creme Salt Water Taffies. Their beautiful orange and white swirls will remind you of summer and melt away in your mouth every time you snack. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-cr-me-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', '1497~orange-cr-me-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', 'orange-creme-salt-water-taffy'),
(1498, 'Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When you can invoke memories with a piece of candy then you must be doing something right. The delicious Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy treats provide a powerful punch of goodness for all to enjoy. The taste of any salt water taffy is going to bring back memories of summer time spent near the shore as you enjoyed the sweet taste of salt water taffy with your friends as you passed the hours of fun in your youth. Then there is the taste of lemon meringue that is going to be a reminder of the wonder and renewal of springtime. The fact that it comes in a bright shiny wrapper will make each piece seem like a gift, and it is a gift of delicious lemony flavor. It is yellow in color which will make you think of the happiness that sunshine can bring you. These Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy candies can make any occasion just a little more special. Who doesn\'t remember the taste of homemade pie?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/e/lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1498~lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy'),
(1499, 'Chocolate Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'What\'s all the fuss about? \'\'Sea\'\' for yourself with these amazingly creamy and delectable Chocolate Salt Water Taffies. Hit the sand with every bite of these individually wrapped morsels. Surprise your chocolate-loving family with a bag of these. Even drop a few into your hot cocoa for extra chocolatey goodness. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1499~chocolate-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'chocolate-salt-water-taffy'),
(1500, 'Huckleberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Well, there is a lot we could say about these delicious treats, but we want to tell you most is that they\'re \'\'berry\'\' good! These Huckleberry Sal Water Taffies are a gorgeous shade of deep purple and white and will delight your family and friends. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/u/huckleberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', '1500~huckleberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', 'huckleberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(1501, 'Cran Raspberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you love salt water taffy then you will certainly love the cran raspberry salt water taffy. This gives a new twist to an old favorite. The flavor of these is amazing which means they are sure to please nearly anyone. They also have a nice white and pink color to them which means they would be great for many different occasions and events that were themed with the same color. Each piece is wrapped individually as well which is certainly a benefit. Some may even find that these would be great to use if you were having a baby shower for someone who had a little girl that was on the way or recently born. So if you think that this is a candy that you would really enjoy and that would add to your occasion then you want to make sure that you get your candy as soon as possible.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/r/cran-raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1501~cran-raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cran-raspberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(1502, 'Sassy Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Me. Ow. These Sassy Salt Water Taffies have enough sweet and sour spunk to knock you back to last Tuesday! In a colorful mix of blue, yellow, orange, green, red, and purple these saucy salt water taffies make a bold addition to a pinata, party favor bags, and candy stashes. Individually wrapped, enjoy them one at a time or take your chances on upping the ante by enjoying them by the mouthful! Their sweet, fruity taste combined with a sour punch will satisfy even the most daring candy lovers. But be careful because the more you eat, the sassier you may become.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/sassy-taffy-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', '1502~sassy-taffy-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', 'sassy-taffy-salt-water-taffy'),
(1503, 'Laffy Taffy Ropes', 10.99, '24', 'ct', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Laffy Taffy Ropes are a fun and exciting type of candy that are great for adults and children. They come in a variety of different flavors. You can choose from banana, grape, cherry, sour apple, strawberry or wild blue raspberry. If you want a variety, you can get all of them! There are 24 in this box, which means that they will go a long way! You can stretch it, twist it and bite it! You will also have a whole lot of fun, because just like the smaller Laffy Taffy candies, these ropes still have the jokes on the wrapper! This will provide for hours of enjoyment for you, and it is sure to please your taste buds as well! They even come in a display box with an open top, which makes them great for concessions too! They make great treats for the kids in your life too!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-ropes-24ct.jpg', '1503~laffy-taffy-ropes-24ct.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-ropes'),
(1504, 'Giant Taffy', 23.99, '24', 'ct', 'salt-water-taffy', 'McCraw\'s Giant Taffy is ready to take on your most intense sweet cravings! Who doesn\'t love the smooth, chewy texture of delicious taffy? Now you can get more of your favorite confection in one big, long sheet!Giant Taffy includes a generous portion of this classic candy rolled out into a long, thin bar. Each features layers of pastel hues including blue, yellow, green and pink. Color combinations may vary but the quality and taste never does! Our bulk giant taffy package gives you many individually wrapped pieces to enjoy or share.Give them to guests or serve them to children as a quick after school treat. McCraw\'s Giant Taffy can also be served at events like birthday parties. Use them as a colorful stocking stuffer, put them in Easter baskets or hand them out during school and community events. Any time is a great time to sink your teeth into a piece of McCraw\'s Giant Taffy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/c/mccrawtaffy.jpg', '1504~mccrawtaffy.jpg', 'mccraws-giant-taffy'),
(1505, 'Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy candies are a mix of chewy, red licorice and incredibly rich taffy. With a red and white swirl inside of a wax paper wrapper that\'s twisted at the ends, this Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy is also a beautiful candy that looks as good as it tastes.Do you know someone who is a classic candy lover? Want to surprise your kids with a fun, red-themed candy at your Fourth of July celebration? Have another red-themed event you need something yummy for? These Red Licorice Salt Water Taffy candies are ready to take your events to the next level with their scrumptious flavor and addicting chew.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-licorice-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1505~red-licorice-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'red-licorice-salt-water-taffy'),
(1506, 'Raspberry Lemonade Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Get ready to feel nostalgic! These Raspberry Lemonade Salt Water Taffies have so many memories packed into every bite. Maybe you used to run a lemonade stand in front of your house every summer. Or maybe your family used to take trips to the boardwalk and bring home boxes of salt water taffy. Take a trip down memory lane with these bright yellow and purple colored and delicious taffies. Set them out in the summertime to make new memories with your family. Whatever you do, every time you eat one you\'ll remember a beloved memory as well as make a new one!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/raspberry-lemonade-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1506~raspberry-lemonade-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'raspberry-lemonade-salt-water-taffy'),
(1507, 'Caramel Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Caramel swirl salt water taffy is a rich, chewy treat that you\'ll love to eat! Anyone who adores the sweet, savory flavor of classic caramel must experience the taste of our salt water taffy. Each piece recreates the feeling of eating a bite-sized piece of high quality caramel but with that taffy texture you know and love.Our salt water taffy is available in single-flavor packages so you get exactly what you want every time you order! Bulk caramel swirl salt water taffy can be used for events and much more. Fill treat bags or wedding favors with these elegant little pinwheels. Each includes a toasty brown hue that\'s accented by a slender spiral swirl of white.Each piece arrives individually wrapped so it stays fresh and enjoyable. Order our caramel saltwater taffy for your next event or keep a package at home or at the office to eat as a quick snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1507~caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(1508, 'Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', '\'\'Mooo-ve\'\' over for these Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffies. With their beautiful white and black cow spots and creamy flavor, you won\'t ever want to put these down or put them out to pasture. This snack is a classic that has satisfied candy lovers for years.Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice_caramel.jpg', '1508~licorice_caramel.jpg', 'licorice-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(1509, 'Orange Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Delectable orange juice flavor, individual waxed paper wrappers, and the unforgettable texture of a boardwalk treat make Orange Salt Water Taffy an awesome choice for your next event. This salt water taffy is colored a creamy, dreamy orange to add sweet sunshine to your color scheme, and its flavor is delicately tangy without straying into the sour.A great addition to an assortment of fruit-flavored sweets, this nostalgic candy choice speaks of the seaside! Orange salt water taffy has been enjoyed for a century at seaside resorts and retreats, and it keeps that old-time association for generations of taffy fans!This single-color wholesale taffy for filling jars or treat bags has all the happy traits of that timeless sweet, like the distinctive soft texture that high-quality traditional taffy provides and the lasting flavor that suffuses every bit of the candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1509~orange-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'orange-salt-water-taffy'),
(1510, 'Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'One classic confection with the flavor of another: it is a novelty with the appeal of a tradition! Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy has a bright green center that looks bright as springtime when you use it as a table scatter or to fill an heirloom dish.A symbol of playful days and sunny summers by the sea, bulk saltwater taffy is beloved by kids and adults for its soft, chewy, flavorful composition, and the individual wrappers on these green and brown taffy delicacies make them perfect for candy buffets, treat bags, and pantry stockpiles of tasty sweets.The tart green apple flavor in this wholesale caramel apple taffy combines with a creamy, sweet caramel taste that is reminiscent of the original molasses recipe from which modern taffy flavors evolved. Apple flavor, too, takes your taste buds straight to the autumn orchards, too. The combination of classic taste appeals makes caramel apple saltwater taffy an especially evocative little treat!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1510~caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy'),
(1511, 'Peach Taffy', 9.99, '3', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Enjoy the fresh picked taste of juicy peaches and the smooth, chewy texture of your favorite candy with our peach taffy! Each enticing morsel features a lovely orange-peach color that looks similar to the skin on the ripe fruit it is inspired by.The bite-sized round pieces are perfect for quick snacking while on the go or as an easy treat at home. Take a bite and enjoy the fruit flavor of succulent peaches â€“ it\'s like a trip to the orchard neatly packaged in its own wrapper!Bulk peach taffy is a convenient choice for special occasions. Use them to make unique wedding favors that match your color scheme or put together a fun treat bag for a birthday party.Our single flavor taffy packs make it easy to build a custom candy mix for your event! Enjoy alone or combine with other bulk taffy flavors. Discover another reason to love classic candy with our delectable peach taffy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peach-taffy-sweets.jpg', '1511~peach-taffy-sweets.jpg', 'peach-taffy-sweets'),
(1512, 'Strawberry Banana Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Strawberry banana salt water taffy will wash your taste buds with waves of sweet flavor! Salt water taffy has been a favorite among travelers ever since it was created in 1883.For over a century, families have been buying boxes of salt water taffy as souvenirs for loved ones back home. Now you can enjoy the chewy taste of classic salt water taffy without an expensive beach vacation! No matter how far inland you may be, our taffy is ready to ship right to your location!Many flavors are available, but our strawberry banana is definitely a must-try for fruit lovers. Enjoy the juicy sensation of fresh picked strawberries blended with the exotic taste of ripe bananas. The best part is that this fruit candy never over ripens! Keep it in your pantry or cupboard to satisfy unexpected cravings or buy our single flavor bulk salt water taffy for special events like weddings, parties and picnics!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/strawberry-banana-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '1512~strawberry-banana-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'strawberry-banana-salt-water-taffy'),
(1513, 'Bulk Assorted Fruit Lollipops', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Lollipop, lollipop, oh lolli , lolli, lolli  Sorry, we\'re getting carried away with ourselves. It happens a lot here. It\'s just that we\'re so passionate about these scrumptious suckers that it makes us break out in song. They don\'t require a trip to the doctor and they come in bulk, so these pops are the perfect choice for any occasion. Stock up for your child\'s next party or put them in a jar on your desk for lucky coworkers to snack on. You\'ll quickly become a favorite in the office! With a light, sweet, fruity flavor, in a rainbow of colors, everyone can enjoy a mouthful of deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1513~lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'lollipops-bulk-fruit'),
(1514, 'Caramel Apple Pops', 9.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Enjoy the bounty of the autumn harvest without setting foot in an orchard. A play on a classic fall favorite, these classic green apple lollies are slathered in a creamy, chewy, caramel coating that has been greedily gobbled up for years. Bring them to a fall party, use them as Halloween treats, or remind yourself of autumn any time of the year. Every snacker will feel like you\'re on a tractor ride, traversing a corn maze, and smelling fresh bales of hay every time you eat one of these. And the best part is, these tart treats are here all year \'round.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-apple-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '1514~caramel-apple-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'caramel-apple-pops'),
(1515, 'Mini Tootsie Pops', 11.99, '200', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Mini Tootsie Pops are just a miniaturized version of the original, famous Tootsie Pop. That owl\'s still trying to figure out how many licks it will take to get to the center, and we\'re pretty sure even in miniature that you\'ll want to bite on in before you get there. These mini-pops, in assorted colors and flavors, are perfect for party favors, Halloween treats, or any time you\'re feeling a hankering for something sweet with a chocolaty center.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-pops-mini-bulk-200ct_1.jpg', '1515~tootsie-pops-mini-bulk-200ct_1.jpg', 'tootsie-pops-minis-bulk'),
(1516, 'Pink & White Squiggly Pops Lollipops', 14.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'You can\'t go wrong with strawberry flavored pink and white Squiggly Pops. They\'re the perfect mix of sweet and cute, just like your little girl! Get a bunch of these pretty pink lollipops for your young daughter\'s birthday, a baby shower, or a springtime get-together. These suckers pack in a ton of delicious strawberry flavor, and any little girl would love their color and swirl. Get a 48-count bag today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-squiggly-pop-lollipops.jpg', '1516~pink-squiggly-pop-lollipops.jpg', 'pink-white-squiggly-pop-lollipops'),
(1517, 'Jolly Rancher Lollipops', 13.99, '50', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Who doesn\'t love lollipops? Well now you can get great Jolly Rancher Lollipops. These come in a box of 5 of them. You will find that these have a fun tart, fruit flavor that nearly everyone is sure to enjoy. They also come in many different colors such as green, pink, blue, and red. Some of the flavors that you can expect with these great suckers are cherry, pink lemonade, watermelon, and even apple. That means that you are sure to have plenty of options when it comes to choosing a flavor that you are sure to enjoy. These are hard candies that are each wrapped individually. It really gives a great twist to the wonderful Jolly Rancher flavors that you have already come to love by allow them to now be suckers instead of just little hard candies. This means that you are able to enjoy more of the flavor at a time with only having to unwrap one piece.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-rancher-lollipops-50pc_1.jpg', '1517~jolly-rancher-lollipops-50pc_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-lollipops'),
(1518, 'Dum Dum Pops', 10.99, '120', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'We don\'t like to call any candy a bad name, but these lollipops sure are Dum Dums! In this case, we\'re sure they won\'t mind, since that\'s the name they were given when they hit the market in 1924. These Dum Dums may be known for their silly title, but their miniature sticks and dainty candy have made a splash too. With original flavors of lemon, lime, orange, coconut-pineapple, cherry, grape, and butterscotch, Dum Dums has added even more including root beer, raspberry, chocolate and more! With this assorted bag, you can try them all. They\'re an American classic that every lollipop lover can enjoy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/u/dum-dum-pops-120ct.gif', '1518~dum-dum-pops-120ct.gif', 'dum-dum-pops'),
(1519, 'Charms Sweet & Sour Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'These lollipops sure are two-faced. But with one side of delicious, sweet fruity flavor and the other packed with a puckering sour punch, we don\'t think that\'s necessarily a bad thing at all! These classic Sweet and Sour Charms Pops will give you the best of both worlds sour and sweet. If your tongue gets tired of one flavorful sensation, simply flip this lolli around to find something new. Since WWI, Charms Pops have been delighting the world of candy lovers. Pass this bit of history along with this sweet and sour treat to all your friends and family. We\'re sure they\'ll love \'em!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/sweet_n_sour_pops.jpg', '1519~sweet_n_sour_pops.jpg', 'charms-sweet-sour-pops'),
(1520, 'Blow Pops Bulk', 38.99, '11', 'lb', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Any child of the 80s and 90s will remember the colorful commercials that aired for Charms Blow Pops. With flavors like watermelon, sour apple, cherry, strawberry and grape, these sugary treats were at the top of any kid\'s favorite candy list. Now you can relive those fun, bubblegum filled moments with our bulk Blow Pop pack! You receive an assortment of your favorite Charms lollipops that are perfect for birthday parties, picnics, holiday celebrations and other gatherings.Each Blow Pop starts with a hard fruit flavored candy shell. Chewy bubble gum is hidden inside, adding excitement to every lick! Our bulk candy pack includes individually wrapped lollipops that you can keep at home or use for events. Take them to hand out at your child\'s after school event or put a few in a jar at the office to share with coworkers. No kid ever gets too old to enjoy the sweet, sugary goodness of a classic Charms Blow Pop!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blow-pops-bulk-11lbs_2.jpg', '1520~blow-pops-bulk-11lbs_2.jpg', 'blow-pops-assorted-bulk'),
(1521, 'Blow Pops from Charms', 19.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Like two candy treats in one! Charms Blow Pops merge the flavorful functionality of suckers with the long lasting joy of gum. Blow pops are artificially flavored with a variety of flavors like; cherry, blue raspberry, green apple, and bubble gum. Blow Pops are a classic candy perfect for every event. Make a Blow Pop bouquet for a wedding candy bar, or grab bag in your classroom for games and achievements. Place Blow Pops in your companies break room for that efficient afternoon pick me up, or in your own home for a variety of Holiday displays. With so many options, the sky is the limit, but don\'t forget to get your friends and family together for a Blow Pop race to the delicious gum center! Charms Blow Pop 1 count box of assorted flavors has everyone\'s favorites and is sure to be a hit for kids and adults alike.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blow-pops-from-charms-100ct_1.jpg', '1521~blow-pops-from-charms-100ct_1.jpg', 'blow-pops-assorted'),
(1522, 'Tootsie Pops Bulk', 53.99, '13', 'lb', 'lollipops-suckers', 'A wise owl once asked, \'\'how many licks does it take to get to the center of a Tootsie Pop?\'\' We think the better question may be \'\'how many licks it will take to get to the bottom of this bulk Tootsie Pop box?\'\' We\'ll let you determine the right answer as you enjoy classic flavors or orange, chocolate, cherry, and grape lick after lick. The Tootsie Roll journey to the center of customers\' hearts began in 1896 in New York City. We think the work is well worth the wait with a signature Tootsie Roll on the inside of every pop.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-pops-bulk-13lb_2.jpg', '1522~tootsie-pops-bulk-13lb_2.jpg', 'tootsie-pops-bulk'),
(1523, 'Green & White Squiggly Pops Lollipops', 14.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Brilliant green and pure white stripes swirl through the surface of these Squiggly Pops lollipops, classic lime-flavored confections on a stick that provide a carnival feel! A top choice for candy buffets at summer weddings, Squiggly Pops are relatively small as novelty suckers go, but definitely large enough to display the visual punch of the fairground-style treat.The size and color of these lime lollipops makes them a great choice for creating the leaves of a thoughtful candy bouquet gift, but the spiral form of a Squiggly Pop has such a strong association with amusement parks and childhood candy novelties that they\'ll always add circus flair. Paired with other deep green candies, however, they take on an elegant feel that would be at home in an old-world sweet shop window.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-squiggly-pop-lollipops.jpg', '1523~green-squiggly-pop-lollipops.jpg', 'green-white-squiggly-pop-lollipops'),
(1524, 'Charms Sweet Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'The best thing about a lolly pop is that it last for a long time. Leave it to Charms to develop an old fashioned sucker that will last a long time and provide people with a individually wrapped session of fruity goodness. These sweet pops come in assorted flavors so it can satisfy cherry, grape, blue raspberry, orange and even watermelon lovers. These are a delicious candy treat that candy lovers of all ages simply love. The great appeal of this candy is that it contains a sweet taste that comes in one flavor or another that appeals to everyone. Since it takes longer than fifteen seconds to devour this piece of candy, it provides a value that other styles of candy just can\'t compete with. There are many different types of suckers out there but the Charms Sweet Pops provide all of the crunchy, sweet candy enjoyment that anyone could want.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-sweet-pops-icon.jpg', '1524~charms-sweet-pops-icon.jpg', 'charms-sweet-pop'),
(1525, 'Black Ice Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Is there anything cooler than ice? Only one thing and that is black ice! Introducing the latest Charms Blow Pop, Black Ice! This is the taking the traditional lollipop treat and turning its enjoyment to turbo. There is still a delicious bubble gum treat located in the middle as a reward for getting to the bottom. Now there is a delicious blackberry flavor that creates a whole new level of charm to the Blow Pops! Everything about this candy is cool, from the colorful packaging that draws your eye, to the fact that each pop actually looks like the candy has captured a small piece of black ice on a stick for your enjoyment. Your ideal of candy will be redefined the first moment that you start to enjoy this delicious blackberry flavor! Like all Blow Pops the gum will be your ultimate goal but you will want the candy to last as long as possible because it is just that good! Get out of your comfort zone and get out on the ice, the Black Ice Blow Pop that is.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '1525~black-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'black-ice-blow-pops'),
(1526, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops Large', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Chewy Sugar Daddy caramel pops offer the best of everything when it comes to sweet snacking. These mouthwatering delights produce big flavor that no caramel fanatic can resist! The beauty is in the taste and the design. Each piece includes a generous bar of creamy caramel candy perched atop a convenient disposable stick. Simply peel the bright yellow wrapper and enjoy golden caramel confection to your heart\'s content without the gooey mess!Anytime is a great time to buy Sugar Daddy candy! Give them away during holidays, hide them in party favors or keep them around the pantry for days when you\'re craving something smooth and sweet. Since 1925, Sugar Daddies have been the go-to candy for caramel lovers. New sizes have been introduced over the years, but none compare to the large Sugar Daddy caramel pop. Take your mouth on a saccharine vacation with a box of nostalgic Sugar Daddy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', '1526~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-large'),
(1527, 'Sour Apple Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Why the sour puss? Get used to getting asked this question a lot if you order Sour Apple Blow Pops! With a tart sour apple tang and hard candy crunch, you can look forward to a delicious bubblegum center to save the day and give your pucker a break.Order a bulk box of these Sour Apple Blow Pops if you have a family or group of friends who love lollipops that pack serious pucker power. They\'re also great set out in a candy jar, given away as good bag stuffers or kept in the pantry for when you need a sweet treat that bites back.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-apple-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '1527~sour-apple-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'sour-apple-blow-pops'),
(1528, 'Rainbow Whirly Pops 4', 119.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Rainbow Whirly Pops 4  lollipops are a true classic! Think of all the movies you\'ve seen with a happy little boy or girl licking a lollipop almost as big as their face. These sweet treats look like a rainbow vortex, and they taste like the best days of childhood. Get a 48-count bag of magical Rainbow Whirly Pops for your kids and their friends. They\'ll love the sweet taste, and you\'ll love seeing them enjoy a piece of candy that makes you nostalgic for your own childhood.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/rainbow-whirly-pops-4-48ct_2.jpg', '1528~rainbow-whirly-pops-4-48ct_2.jpg', 'rainbow-whirly-pops-4-inch'),
(1529, 'Blue Razzberry Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Bring on the old razzle dazzle because our Blue Razzberry Blow Pops are here for you to bring home! In a rocking bright blue wrapper and electric blue colored lollipop, these classic suckers will get your blood pumping with their delicious blue raspberry flavor and fun look.And since these Blue Razzberry Blow Pops come in bulk, you\'ll have enough to spread the excitement amongst your friends and family. Lick, chomp and suck on these pops and you\'ll find an even more delicious thing at the very end: bubble gum! So this means you\'ll be able to keep your mouth snacking on deliciousness for a long time whenever you enjoy these bright blue pops.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blow-pops-blue-raspberry-48ct_2.jpg', '1529~blow-pops-blue-raspberry-48ct_2.jpg', 'blow-pops-blue-raspberry'),
(1530, 'Saf T Pops Lollipops', 17.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'These flavorful lollies are often called Doctors Pops because they are the preferred choice by pediatricians who enjoy giving patients a treat. Saf-T-Pops Lollipops feature a fiber cord loop handle to prevent choking.This bulk supply includes an assortment of flavors, including apple, cherry, grape, lemon, orange, and strawberry. Each one is individually wrapped and features a number or letter on the side, so they can be used as a learning tool in the classroom. Saf-T-Pops Lollipops are not just for kids though. Adults love these bold fruity flavors, too.As a child, lollipops were likely one of your favorite treats. If you are a parent now, you probably want your kids to enjoy the same yummy flavors you loved, but you can\'t help being terrified they may end up choking. You may have heard horror stories about children choking on candy, so you are just not willing to take a chance. Well, before you say goodbye to candy for good, try our Saf-T-Pops Lollipops first.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/saf-t-pops.jpg', '1530~saf-t-pops.jpg', 'saf-t-pops-lollipops'),
(1531, 'Tootsie Pops', 19.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Tootsie Pops are even better when you buy them in bulk! This famous candy has become an icon for many. Each piece includes a disposable stick that supports a hard candy shell containing a chewy piece of Tootsie roll candy.These fun lollipops were introduced in 1931 and originally came in chocolate. Today many fruit flavors have been added including strawberry, raspberry, watermelon, grape, orange, cherry and green apple. Our bulk Tootsie Pops box contains a delightful assortment of treats that will give you many options when it\'s time to snack. Each is individually wrapped in colors that hint at its flavor.Tootsie Pops are a must-have for birthday parties and other gatherings that cater to children. While they may be a kid-friendly candy, they are also a popular choice among adults who grew up with the famous Tootsie Pop owl commercials! Try all the flavors you love with this Tootsie Pops box.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-pops-100ct.gif', '1531~tootsie-pops-100ct.gif', 'tootsie-pops-assorted-box'),
(1532, 'Double Lollies', 28.99, '200', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'If you love sweet tarts then you are sure to find that you love Double Lollies by Smarties. These great candies are able to provide you the sweet tart in a larger piece on a stick. There are two different sweet flavors in each pop to ensure that you get a little change when you are indulging. You will also be able to get 2 suckers that are already unwrapped for your convenience. This puts a new twist on an old favorite that is sure to be a big hit for people of all ages. These would be great to put out a party that you were having as a treat for those who were in attendance. Nearly everyone is sure to find that they are more than happy with the flavor that they get. You can expect the candy to be somewhat hard but certainly not too hard which makes it perfect.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/double-lollies-200ct_1.gif', '1532~double-lollies-200ct_1.gif', 'double-lollies-smarties-tub'),
(1533, 'Pink Striped Ball Petite Lollipops', 26.99, '400', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Strawberry fields forever. We know the famous Beatles song and drew inspiration from their lyrics to create an almost endless bag of Strawberry Striped Ball Lollipops. With 4 strawberry suckers in every order, you will feel like you have the sun on your back while picking wild berries with every lick. Have a daughter or friend who just loves pink or a fruity, strawberry flavor? Have a party coming up that needs the pretty punch of this white and pink swirl to dress it up? Want to stick these into the top of a strawberry shortcake dessert to make it extra special and beautiful? These pops can do it all and please every taste bud.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', '1533~pink-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', 'pink-striped-ball-lollipops-petite'),
(1534, 'Large Blue Striped Ball Lollipops', 26.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Like miniature beach balls flying through the air on a warm, summer day on the sand, these Blue Striped Ball Lollipops will add some fun to your candy repertoire. Individually wrapped in a package of 1, these blue and white striped lollipops have a bursting blueberry flavor that will make your taste buds say, \'\'wow!\'\' These bright pops look lovely in a homemade candy bouquet for a special event, set out on a table for a Fourth of July picnic, or even in goodie bags for your little ones\' birthday parties. Enjoying these suckers will be fun and delicious, time after time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', '1534~blue-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', 'blue-striped-ball-lollipops-large'),
(1535, 'Rainbow Whirly Pops 5.25', 129.99, '36', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Suckers are always fun whether you are getting them for a child or an adult. There is just something to be said about Whirly Pops however. These giant suckers are 5.25 inches which means that it could take you quite a while to finish them off. You will also find that they are swirled with many different colors such as blue, red, orange, yellow, white, and green. This would make a fun gift for someone, and would also be a great party favor. These would even look great in a homemade arrangement because they are so large. Whatever you decide to do with them you are sure to be pleased and with a count of 36 of them there is sure to be plenty for everyone. These suckers are hard in texture but are sweet and sure to be able to please anyone who is lucky enough to get to take part in eating one.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/rainbow-whirly-pops-525-36ct_2.jpg', '1535~rainbow-whirly-pops-525-36ct_2.jpg', 'rainbow-whirly-pops-5-quarter-inch'),
(1536, 'Super Blow Pops from Charms', 18.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Super-sized, two candies in one, Super Blow Pops from Charms combine the long lasting sugary goodness of suckers with the satisfying slow burn of sweet gum. These tasty twofers are perfect for weddings, birthday parties, and classrooms. Super Blow Pops are easily formed into bouquets, trees, and any other imaginable design for that super sweet decoration. Super Pops make great Trick-R-Treat giveaways, and party favors for any themed party. Super Pops can even be used for party games. These delicious treats are also great for break rooms, and grab baskets in companies. They provide a thank you to customers and a pick me up for employees. Super Blow Pops also make great fundraisers to help your company meet its\' goals. These pops are great for personal snacking when only the sweetest treat will do. 48 assorted flavors come in each classic display box, ensuring everyone gets their favorite, every time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/super_blow_pops.jpg', '1536~super_blow_pops.jpg', 'super-blow-pops-charms'),
(1537, 'Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops', 26.99, '400', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'There\'s no reason to feel blue about these Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops. In their pristine white and bright blue stripes, these are some of the happiest candies around. On a snow white stick, these little lollies are full of fruity flavor that will wake your taste buds up and put a smile on your face.Having a baby boy and want to celebrate with a thematic treat? These Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops are perfect for that sort of occasion. They also work well when paired with red candies on the Fourth of July, make Hanukah extra special, or can be bought for a special dad on Father\'s Day. Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops are delicious and good looking enough for almost any event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', '1537~blue-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', 'blue-striped-ball-lollipops-petite'),
(1538, 'What A Melon Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Charms Blow Pops are absolutely irresistible! No matter how old you get, you\'ll always love licking one of these delicious lollies! Our What A Melon Blow Pops offer that same two-candy combination you love with the fresh taste of juicy watermelon.Each includes a thick shell of hard candy that surrounds a mouthful of sweet chewing gum, all perched neatly atop a disposable lollipop stick.Our bulk What A Melon Blow Pops are individually wrapped so they stay fresh until it\'s time to snack. Each box contains many lollipops so you have plenty to enjoy and share. Bulk Blow Pops are a must-have for kids\' birthday parties. Use them as Christmas stocking stuffers or keep them as a fast after school snack on busy days.No matter what season it is, our What A Melon Blow Pops are always ripe and ready to eat! Also check out our other single-flavor Blow Pop boxes so you can mix and match your favorites.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/what-a-watermelon-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '1538~what-a-watermelon-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'what-a-watermelon-blow-pops');
INSERT INTO `candy` (`id`, `title`, `price`, `amount`, `units`, `category`, `description`, `original_image_url`, `local_image`, `page`) VALUES
(1539, 'Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops', 26.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Quite possibly the pretties treat available on CandyStore.com, these Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops are sure to invoke a lot of smiles. What\'s the first thing that comes to mind, when you look at these lollies? A beach ball, right? This makes them perfect for beach-themed parties and weddings. They will cause shrieks of excitement from little ones and they can bring out the inner child in anyone.These Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops are 1 inch in diameter, so they last a really long time. Creamy white balls get swirled in bright pink stripes for a look anyone will be charmed by. These suckers are not just pretty though. Their delicious strawberry flavor will have you reaching into the candy jar a little more often.Decorate a birthday cake with these or make bouquets of them for centerpieces by stabbing the sticks in green floral foam. They are perfect for baby showers, kids\' parties, and Valentine\'s Day.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', '1539~pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', 'pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large'),
(1540, 'Cherry Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Cherry Blow Pops are super sweet and a popular treat for candy lovers of all ages! This exciting snack is actually two confections in one. Each includes a disposable stick tipped in an orb of delightful hard candy.The center is filled with a gob of smooth chewing gum. Lick and nibble away until you reach the chewy middle! Your lollipop will go longer when there\'s bubblegum waiting inside!Blow Pops are one of the most popular types of lollipops sold in the United States. It\'s easy to see why once you taste one for yourself. Our bulk Blow Pops in cherry give you many individually wrapped pieces that are convenient for events, birthday parties and much more!Use them to fill up treat bags for kids or keep them in your pantry as an easy sweet snack. Our Charms Blow Pops are fun, delicious and packed with juicy cherry flavor!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '1540~cherry-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'cherry-blow-pops'),
(1541, 'Blow Pops from Charms', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'We have a dozen delicious Blow Pops from Charms flavors for you to choose from here in bulk! Black Cherry, Black Ice, Blue Razzberry, Cherry, Cherry Ice, Kiwi Berry Blast, Mean Green, Sour Apple, Tangerine, Watermelon, Way-2-Sour, and  Mango flavors, if you can pick just one!Whatever you choose, you\'ll have a delicious and famous hard lollipop to suck on and chewy, sweet bubblegum to enjoy once you reach the middle. These Blow Pops from Charms are a real crowd-pleaser, so pick some up and keep them around the house for when your kids\' friends come over or you need something special and sweet to savor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blow-pops-from-charms-48ct_2.jpg', '1541~blow-pops-from-charms-48ct_2.jpg', 'blow-pops-charms-flavors'),
(1542, 'Rainbow Unicorn Pops 12', 139.99, '72', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'They do exist! At least their tasty, rainbow horns do. And we love \'em. With all the colors of the rainbow, a sweet, fruity flavor and beautiful swirls, these Unicorn Pops are a delightful treat with notable heritage. The mythical tales of the unicorn date back to ancient Greece and even the Bible with stories of people glimpsing white, goat-like horses with a single, long horn. The legendary lore depicted the unicorns as a symbol of purity, hope and grace as they would heal ailments and injuries. We think these pops are just as healing as they were originally thought to be. See for yourself why they\'re so magical at your child\'s next birthday party or any special occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-72ct.jpg', '1542~rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-72ct.jpg', 'rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-inch'),
(1543, 'Green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops Lime', 14.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops are an eye-catching treat that is full of powerful sweetness. Our lollipops are made with high quality confection and offer a distinctive look that works for events, school activities and more.Instead of a basic round shape, our green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops include a length of smooth hard candy with a fabulous white and green stripe. The tube is twisted to form a tight coil that\'s long lasting and so irresistible! Bulk lollipops are the best way to get bigger quantities for special celebrations and more. Dress up tables at a birthday party or block party by putting these beautiful lollies out in a jar.Add a ribbon and tag to give as an edible stocking stuffer or Easter basket filler. Our green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops are also a great choice for shower and wedding favors! We also carry other brilliant colors so you can find the perfect twisted lollipop for your event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/e/teslas-tiny-twist-pops-green-yumjunkie.jpg', '1543~teslas-tiny-twist-pops-green-yumjunkie.jpg', 'green-tiny-tesla-twist-pops-lime'),
(1544, 'Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'These pink and blue swirled lollies are perfect for birthday parties and baby showers. You don\'t need an excuse to enjoy one though, and since they are fat-free and only 70 calories, you can indulge in them a lot more often than the real thing.Everyone knows that the best thing about going to the fair is for the sweet, sticky, and delicious cotton candy. Of course, the one bad thing about cotton candy is that it does not last very long. The moment that spun sugar touches your tongue it instantly dissolves.Not to mention, it seems to shrink before your very eyes, if it is hot or humid outside. These Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops taste just like the real thing, only they last a whole lot longer.What do Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops taste like? Well, like you pulled a handful of sticky goodness off both pink and blue rolls and popped them in your mouth together, but these are hard candy suckers, so you get to enjoy the flavor a lot longer. Not to mention, unlike the real thing, Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops are not messy to eat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/l/fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops-48ct.gif', '1544~fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops-48ct.gif', 'fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops'),
(1545, 'Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops are a new take on the classic lollipop. Blow Pops are one of the most famous treats made by Charms.This candy was first introduced during the 1970s and quickly became Charms\' bestselling confection. Each lollipop includes a generous dollop of sweet bubblegum surrounded by a thick hard candy shell perched atop a disposable stick.Lick away then enjoy a good chew with this long lasting candy! While classic Blow Pops are tasty, sometimes you want something more exotic to enjoy. Our kiwi berry lollipops offer that same unique design with a blast of flavor inspired by two sweet fruits.Each features a deep red color that\'s complemented by a matching wrapper. Simply untwist the top and prepare to take a stroll through fruit flavor paradise! Bulk Blow Pops are a must-have for children\'s birthday parties, picnics and school activities. Hand them out during holidays or keep a box at home so you always have Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops ready to eat!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/i/kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '1545~kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops'),
(1546, 'Black Cherry Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'One of the newest flavors of Blow Pops is also one of the most fabulous! Bulk, display-packaged Black Cherry Blow Pops contain a heart of bubble gum within a thick shell of dark, glossy black cherry candy. It\'s two kinds of confection on one convenient stick!Popular for classroom rewards, lunch bags, and birthday parties, Blow Pops also make a delicious and nostalgia-inducing treat whenever you need something to pick up your mood. Contained in a display box that\'s great for store counters and retro candy buffets, wholesale Black Cherry Blow Pops are the perfect candy choice when you want something familiar and fun.Not too prosaic in flavor, these pops will jazz up your event or draw people to a fair booth. Bursting with flavor at the start and filled with long-lasting chewing gum, these suckers make a great on-the-go dessert!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-cherry-blow-pops-48ct_2.jpg', '1546~black-cherry-blow-pops-48ct_2.jpg', 'black-cherry-blow-pops'),
(1547, 'Wrapped Smarties Pops Jar', 16.99, '120', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'If you ever wished Smarties were bigger, then consider it granted with these Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars! With traditional Smarties candy sized up to lollipop standards and put on a stick, you can munch and crunch on these classic candies in a whole new way.If you like to mix things up in your candy routine, try these Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars! You can keep them around the kitchen for when you want a sweet snack or to reward a bookworm for a great test grade. You can even order some Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars to sell at concessions stands for school sporting events or give out in goodie bags at parties. Just be smart and order some of these luscious lollipops today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/m/smarties-pops-lollipops-alt-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1547~smarties-pops-lollipops-alt-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'smarties-pops-wrapped-jar'),
(1548, 'Cherry Ice Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Now you can get Charms Blow Pops in bulk! Our enormous box contains many individual lollipops that are a tasty treat anytime â€“ day or night!Take a few lollies with you to enjoy throughout the work day or pack them in lunches as a sweet way to end the midday meal. Our Cherry Ice Blow Pops offer intense flavor that kids and adults will love.This version of the classic Blow Pop lollipop includes the same disposable stick and hard candy shell you love with a chewy gummy center. What makes them so unique is the cool cherry taste packed into every round pop!Hand them out during school or community events or use them as Christmas stocking stuffers or Easter basket filler. Cherry Ice Blow Pops are an easy party favor as well. Add them to a treat bag or tie on a personalized tag to customize your candy gift!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '1548~cherry-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'cherry-ice-blow-pops'),
(1549, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '1549~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(1550, 'Gilliam Hard Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Old fashioned hard candy sticks are the ultimate go-to treat for anyone with a sweet tooth. Stick candy has been a favorite of young and old since the mid-1800s, and it\'s no wonder why. Each piece features a unique flavor and fun colors that make every lick a memorable experience! Simply peel away the hard candy wrapper and you are ready to snack. Each piece is individually wrapped so they are easy to store and can be given as party favors or a special treat for the kids!We carry a huge list of exciting flavors so you never get bored. Try exotic pina colada, orange pineapple or rum and butter! If you prefer something simpler, classic bubblegum, peppermint, sassafras or strawberry are just as enticing. You\'ll love watching the striped candy melt away with each bite! Grab the old family photo album and your favorite flavors and relive your childhood memories with Gilliam hard candy sticks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', '1550~stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', 'old-fashioned-stick-candy-box-flavors'),
(1551, 'Peppermint Twists Mints', 19.99, '', '', 'hard-candy', 'Peppermint twists pack all of the flavor of a candy cane into a single bite-sized candy. Just seeing and tasting them will put you in the holiday spirit, no matter what time of year it is. Don\'t miss out on delicious peppermint candies all year round. Get a bag of these individually wrapped peppermint twists and liven up your home or your office. No special occasion is necessary to bring out these delicious peppermint candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1551~peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'peppermint-twists'),
