(1586, 'Haribo Gummi Gold Bears Mini Bags Tub', 13.99, '54', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'We sure think that these gummies are \'\'tastier than the average bear!\'\' That\'s because these classic Haribo Gold Gummi Bears are here in a bulk bag to bring you even more of the delicious flavors you love. In a selection of red, orange, yellow, green, and white, everyone in your family will find a cub to love. Sprinkle a few in Jell-O for a \'\'beary\'\' good surprise, add some to a make your own sundae bar, or wrap some up for a loved one to make their day extra special. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', '1586~haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-gold-bears-mini-bags-tub'),
(1587, 'Gummi Frogs', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Everyone will jump for joy when they get a taste of Haribo gummy frogs! These little green candies aren\'t slippery and slimy, but they offer a smooth, soft texture that\'s pleasant on the tongue. Each piece includes fun details that recreate this popular amphibian â€“ right down to its folded legs, round head and raised back. Our gummy frogs are solid green and arrive fresh in sealed bags that are ready to enjoy! Hide gummi frogs around the house or save them to put in school lunches for the kids. These charming croakers are also great for serving at birthday parties, picnics and school events. Put them in a bowl or use them to dress up cakes, cupcakes, cookies and more! No matter how you display them, our Haribo gummy candies will entice children of all ages. Order our bulk candy pack so you have plenty of chewy frogs for any occasion!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', '1587~haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', 'gummi-frogs-12ct'),
(1588, 'Gummi Fruit Salad', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo gummi fruit salad combines all your favorite flavors in one convenient package! Since 1920, Haribo has been producing new confections for the world to enjoy. Their current selection features a number of the most popular sugary snacks, including our irresistible gummy fruit salad! Every bag contains a selection of brightly colored chewy pieces that feature recognizable shapes that make mouths water.Reach into a bag of gummy fruit salad and enjoy the sweet sensation of orange, lime, cherry and more! Every piece is brightly colored in red, green, orange and other hues that match their fruity counterparts. This fat free candy is covered in a generous dusting of sugar for added texture and taste. Enjoy it as a guilt-free snack at home or buy our bulk candy pack and get plenty of Haribo fruit pieces to serve at any event. This nature-inspired confection is a big hit at picnics, parties, summer events and school activities!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/0/108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', '1588~108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', 'gummi-fruit-salad-12ct'),
(1589, 'Gummi Happy Cola Bottles', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo Happy Cola bottle candies are a fun way to enjoy the fizzy flavor of a soda without a glass. This unique confection includes classic bottle-shaped pieces that are reminiscent of antique Coke bottles. The top half is clear with detailed bands around the middle and a narrow top where the cap would normally be. The bottom half is dark amber brown, just like a refreshing drink of cola on a hot summer\'s day!Our Haribo Happy Cola gummies will put a smile on everyone\'s face as the bite down on the distinct taste of their favorite sugary beverage! Now you can get bulk cola bottle candies so you get more fizzy fun with your order. Save them for snack time and school lunches or put them out as a special treat for guests at birthday parties, picnics and family reunions. No matter what you\'re celebrating, Haribo Happy cola bottle gummies will make the event more exciting!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-happycola.jpg', '1589~haribo-happycola.jpg', 'gummi-happy-cola-bottles-12ct'),
(1590, 'Gummi Peaches', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Life\'s a peach when you have Haribo gummy candies! This company made itself famous for introducing some of the most fun and tasty chewy snacks to the world, including their irresistible peaches. This fruity candy includes round peach-shaped pieces in orange and red. Each is covered in a delicious dusting of sugar and includes sweet, succulent flavor that excites the taste buds. Take a bite and let your mind wander through sprawling orchards with plump, fresh picked peaches waiting in bushel baskets. Unlike the real thing, our Haribo gummy peaches never over ripen. Every bite is just as delectable as the last! Now you can get your fill of peachy goodness because we offer a bulk candy pack that gives you more ounces. Order for picnics, parties, school events or simply to enjoy anytime your craving something sweet and savory. Keep your candy dish full with Haribo peach gummy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-peaches.jpg', '1590~haribo-peaches.jpg', 'gummi-peaches-12ct'),
(1591, 'Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags', 39.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Leave it to Jolly Ranchers to provide a delicious, colorful and fun treat that is also good for you. While providing all of the expected value expected from Jolly Rancher, they upped the ante by making their snacks sugar free as well! The classic candy comes individually wrapped to keep in the unique freshness. Each piece of candy provides a classic blast of fruit refreshment without the worry of taking in any extra sugar that will make parents and dentists smile. This treat can be enjoyed all by yourself or with a bunch of your friends. Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags make it always seem like a party. Enjoy the explosion of fruit flavor in your mouth without any of the guilt. Get the best Jolly Rancher hard candy that has your favorite flavor, watermelon, apple, grape or raspberry. Not only are these treats sugar free but each candy contains only 1 calories, which means that you can enjoy your fruity flavored candies all day long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', '1591~jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-sugar-free-candy-bags'),
(1592, 'Haribo Gummi Alphabet Letters 5oz Bag', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo always finds a way to make everyone\'s favorite gummy candy even better! Now you can order a large package of our extra tasty Haribo gummy letters! This alphabet-inspired snack is sweet, chewy and â€“ best of all â€“ educational! Help little ones learn their consonants and vowels by turning snack time into reading time! Each package contains an assortment of edible letters in bright colors. Your child will love spelling out vocabulary words that they can eat!Our gummy alphabet treats are a must-have for school lunches and events. They are the perfect fat free candy for child care businesses and others who work with little ones. Whether you\'re a teacher, parent or simply someone who loves the fruity taste of gummies, you will love our Haribo letters! Each bulk candy pack contains a generous number of gummy pieces so you have enough to share at picnics, classroom parties or family events!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/alphabetletters.jpg', '1592~alphabetletters.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-alphabet-letters-5oz-bag-12ct'),
(1593, 'Life Savers Pep O Mint', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Is your mouth screaming \'\'SOS\'\' for a breath freshening treat? Well, these Life Savers Pep-O-Mint and Wint-O-Green are here to save the day! Let them toss you a life preserver for your taste buds with their fresh minty flavor and classic \'\'O\'\' shaped form. This hero of the candy world has been around since 1912 and has saved mouths all over the world. Pep-O-Mint was the first flavor and quickly made an impression in the mouths of many. Since then, a variety of fruity and other mint flavors have been invented. Try these minty rolls on for size and see for yourself if you think they\'re worthy of their heroic name!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', '1593~mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', 'mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct'),
(1594, 'Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars 12 Bags', 39.99, '', '', 'bagged-candy', 'You won\'t find a smidgen of guilt in this bulk supply of Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars. These mouthwatering treats have only 32 calories each, and are perfect for chocoholics with diabetes. Hershey made these divine treats as part of its Special Dietary Needs line.They are sweetened with sugar alcohols, which coincidently are not sugar or alcohol, but a natural product with a unique chemical structure that resembles both sugar and alcohol. Each one of the Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars is individually wrapped, so you can easily share, slip them in lunches, and stash them in your desk.All you have to do is see that iconic dark brown logo and taste buds start getting a little crazy. Then, you notice the words Sugar Free, and assume you must be dreaming. Is it possible to enjoy melt-in-your-mouth, creamy chocolate without all the sugar? Well, you might not think it\'s possible, but our Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars prove dreams really do come true.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-sugar-free-milk-chocolate-bars-12-bags_1.jpg', '1594~hersheys-sugar-free-milk-chocolate-bars-12-bags_1.jpg', 'hersheys-sugar-free-milk-chocolate-bars-bags'),
(1595, 'Red Vines Sugar Free Strawberry Licorice Vines', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Sugar free Vines licorice is the best way to enjoy your favorite childhood treat! Everyone loves the smooth, chewy taste of classic licorice. It\'s been around for decades and has become a fast favorite among the young and young at heart.Our Red Vines licorice makes the experience even better because you can enjoy the same sweet strawberry taste with no fat so every snacking session is guilt-free! Each piece includes a length of irresistible red licorice with a juicy strawberry flavor. The vines include flat ends with a twisted design that runs from top to bottom, adding unique texture to every bite.Our bulk red licorice pack includes individual bags that are great for travel or sharing. Simply hide a bag of licorice wherever you need it so you always have a treat within reach. Tuck one in the glove box before a long car ride or stow red licorice in luggage so you have an easy snack while away from home!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-vines-sugar-free-strawberry-licorice-vines-12ct.jpg', '1595~red-vines-sugar-free-strawberry-licorice-vines-12ct.jpg', 'red-vines-sugar-free-strawberry-licorice-vines'),
(1596, 'Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Box', 19.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Feel like you\'re sitting on a stool at your neighborhood ice cream shoppe every time you take a candy out of one these Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Boxes. If you love the original malted milk ball, these sweet strawberry coated candies will blow your mind.Since these Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Boxes are a lovely shade of light pink, it makes them perfect for gift baskets for about to be moms of little girls. They also fit right in among bachelorette candy or breast cancer awareness events. Keep these Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Boxes closed or dump the candy out into dishes to add a pretty and tasty treat to your candy jars.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/whoppers_strawberry_milkshake.jpg', '1596~whoppers_strawberry_milkshake.jpg', 'strawberry-milkshake-whoppers-theatre-box'),
(1597, 'Ginger Lemon Gummi Peg Bags', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Zesty and tangy, our ginger lemon gummies are the perfect way to wake up your taste buds! These unusual sweet treats combine two popular flavors into one original snack. Each piece is made using Haribo\'s soft and chewy recipe so you know you\'re getting a high quality candy that\'s full of irresistible flavor! Each piece is covered in a sugary coating to tempt the senses and enhance the experience found in each bite. Our ginger lemon candy is truly a one-of-a-kind Haribo creation! These round morsels come in a soft, pale yellow color and are reminiscent of soothing cough drops. Once hugely popular in Europe, now you can buy them anywhere when you order online with us! Our bulk gummy package gives you more ginger lemon drop pieces so you have enough to last. Enjoy them at home or put them out as a unique snack to share with friends and family. Haribo ginger lemon gummy candies are fat-free and delicious!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-lemon-ginger-bags-icon.jpg', '1597~haribo-lemon-ginger-bags-icon.jpg', 'ginger-lemon-gummi-peg-pags-12ct'),
(1598, 'Brite Sour Gummi Candy 12ct Bags', 23.99, 'Octop', 'us', 'bagged-candy', 'Why didn\'t the octopus go to the zoo? He had an \'\'ink-ling\'\' that it would rain! These Trolli Brite Octopus Sour Gummi Candy are as funny as they are delicious and we\'re sure you\'ll love them from first bite. With 8 legs of delicious, sour gummy chew, you\'ll have a ton of snacking to do with every candy.Bring some home if you have a family who loves everything aquatic. Add some to a pinata to make the little ones squeal. Even give them to someone as a gag gift if they get the heeby jeebies from these creepy sea crawlers. Whatever you do, you\'ll love these tentacles of delicious flavor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/brite-octopus-sour-gummi-candy-12ct-bags_1.gif', '1598~brite-octopus-sour-gummi-candy-12ct-bags_1.gif', 'brite-octopus-sour-gummi-octopi-bags'),
(1599, 'Fizzy Cola Bags', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Your taste buds will dance with delight when they feel the tingly sensation that comes with each bite of our Haribo fizzy cola gummies! These soda pop candies are guaranteed to be a big hit with any age group! Serve them up at birthday parties, holiday events, picnics or any other occasion you want to make a little sweeter. When you can\'t have a gulp of your favorite cola beverage, you can always reach for Haribo fizzy cola candy!Each piece includes a classic shape with a clear white top and rich brown bottom, just like a half full glass bottle of your favorite cola! You never have to twist off a cap or worry about recycling a bottle with these tasty tidbits. Just bite down and enjoy every mouthful of fizzy goodness! You\'ll love the unique blend of tangy, sweet and sour flavor that comes with our Haribo fizzy cola gummies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/i/fizzycola.jpg', '1599~fizzycola.jpg', 'fizzy-cola-bags-12ct'),
(1600, 'Gummi Bears 12 Flavor Peg Bag 9oz', 19.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Taste the difference high quality ingredients make when you enjoy Albanese gummy bears! This candy company knows how to bring out the best in the confections it produces.For more than 30 years, Albanese has been improving its recipes and techniques to bring candy lovers across the world a collection of the finest gummy candy available. Now you can get more of the Albanese gummy bears you love in one convenient order! Our bulk gummy bears include several peg bags that are wonderful for storage and sharing. Keep a bag in the car, your desk drawer at work or wherever you like to snack at home. Give them out as a gift to friends and family or use them to fill the office candy jar.Everyone will love the 12 exciting flavors packed into every peg bag! Our Albanese gummy bears offer chewy pieces that feature a dozen intense flavors, including green apple, blue raspberry, lime, lemon, pineapple, grape, mango, orange, pink grapefruit, wild cherry and strawberry.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/2/12-flavor-wild-fruit-bears_albanese_peg_bag_9oz.jpg', '1600~12-flavor-wild-fruit-bears_albanese_peg_bag_9oz.jpg', 'gummi-bears-12-flavor-peg-bag-9oz'),
(1601, 'Brite Crawlers Sour Gummi Worms Theater Bags', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Once upon a time, a bunch of worms crawled into a nuclear power plant site and ate radioactive dirt. From that day forward, they grew and grew until they became sour, neon and gummy! Who knows if the folklore is true, but we can tell you one thing: that these Brite Crawlers Sour Gummi Worms sure seem like a crazy science experiment!That\'s because these Brite Crawlers come in a rainbow of neon colors and are coated in a super sour sugar. If you\'re up to the task of gobbling down sour as can be gummi worms in bright as the sun hues, then order yourself a bulk supply. They\'re sure to wriggly, crawl and slither down your throat and make you smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/brite-crawlers-sour-gummi-worms-12ct-bags_1.gif', '1601~brite-crawlers-sour-gummi-worms-12ct-bags_1.gif', 'brite-crawlers-sour-gummi-worms-bags'),
(1602, 'Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy 2.5oz', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'No candy store is complete without a selection of light, fluffy, and sweet cotton candy. It has come to be trademark of the summer fun and sweetness and you do not want to miss out on it!  Available in sweet flavors, our cotton candy will bring smiles to the faces of all who enjoy it and everyone who craves that melt in your mouth sensation .Our specially packaged bulk order will give you 12 bags of 25 ounce cotton candy ready to be displayed and ready to sell. Give your customers what they are looking for and make sure to include some of our cotton candy on your next order!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/l/fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-25oz-12ct.gif', '1602~fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-25oz-12ct.gif', 'fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-bags'),
(1603, 'Sugar Free Reeses Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bag', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'These Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bags are almost too good to be true. With the savory peanut butter filling Reese\'s is famous for and the crinkle cut chocolate exterior, you\'ll feel like you\'re breaking your diet but you won\'t be!Inside every Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bag are individually wrapped mini Reese\'s Cups that are just waiting to be devoured by you. If you love sweets, but don\'t want to eat too much of them, then these are a great candy choice for you. You can sprinkle them on non fat yogurt or ice cream for added deliciousness or even pack some into lunch boxes for a low calorie dessert. Whatever you do, Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bags will keep you coming back for more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar_free_reeses_pegbag.jpg', '1603~sugar_free_reeses_pegbag.jpg', 'sugar-free-reeses-peanut-butter-cups-peg-bag'),
(1604, 'Rainbow Mini Frogs Bag', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Our Haribo rainbow mini frog gummies are ready to hop right in and make snack time even tastier! These fun fruit snacks come in a rainbow of fun colors, including yellow, red and green â€“ of course! Every piece includes a white back that\'s just as soft and chewy. Who doesn\'t love munching on tiny frog candy pieces? These delectable sweets will prove that not all amphibians are covered in slime!Enjoy our rainbow frog gummy pieces alone or use them to decorate birthday cakes, cupcakes, cookies and other baked treats. Our bulk candy package makes it so easy to get larger quantities of chewy frogs to serve at parties, picnics and school events. Pour them in a dish and let guests dive right in or include a handful in party favors. No one will be able to resist the adorable shape and sweet taste that makes Haribo gummies so delightful!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/minirainbowfrogs.jpg', '1604~minirainbowfrogs.jpg', 'rainbow-mini-frogs-bag-12ct'),
(1605, 'Jelly Belly 49 Flavors Mix Bags', 64.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'If you just can\'t decide on one Jelly Belly jelly bean flavor, you need to reach for the 49 flavors assortment! This handsome Jelly Belly bag contains a diverse collection of their finest beans. Each includes the brilliant colors, intense taste and familiar white Jelly Belly brand printed on one side.Grab a handful, come up with your own fun combinations or pick and choose individual jelly beans! Our bulk Jelly Belly 49 flavors mix bags give you more of the candy you love with every order! Stay stocked up in case guests or a demanding sweet tooth show up. Our assortment includes multiple individual bags that feature beautiful Jelly Belly branding that\'s perfect for gift giving.Use them as stocking stuffers, add to Easter basket candy for the kids or include in a gourmet gift basket. Jelly Belly candy is made with love to ensure the best quality and eating experience no matter how many beans you order!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', '1605~jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags'),
(1606, 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/r/dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '1606~dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'dr-pepper-licorice-twists-bags'),
(1607, 'Starburst Peg Bag', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Starburst fruit chews are the sweetest way to get your fruit fix. Each piece is square and includes a soft, chewy texture that feels smooth and tastes amazing!Our bulk Starburst fruit chews include multiple peg bags with individually wrapped blocks of confectionary goodness. Sink your teeth into juicy strawberry, orange, cherry or lemon or combine two flavors for a mouthful of fun!The original Starburst candies were introduced in 1959 as Opal Fruits under the Mars brand in the United Kingdom. They were later renamed Starburst and made available for sale in the United States. Needless to say, Starburst fruit chews were a big hit here in the states!Today they are one of the most popular confections available in grocery stores and candy shops all over the country. Now you can get larger quantities for parties, events, holidays or at home snacking by ordering our convenient bulk Starburst packs!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/starburstpegbag.jpg', '1607~starburstpegbag.jpg', 'starburst-peg-bag-12ct'),
