(1609, 'Vidal Ocean Gummies', 18.99, '18', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Make a big splash at snack time by giving the kids a taste of Vidal\'s Ocean Gummies! This fun candy is not only tasty, but also exciting to see. While regular gummy bears usually feature a solid color look, our gummy ocean creatures present a brilliant color with bright exciting colors.Each piece is shaped into a different sea creature. Our bulk package includes 18 4 count packs so the gummies are always fresh â€“ even if you don\'t open it right away! Vidal Ocean Gummies are convenient for gift giving, sharing and casual snacking.Keep a pack anywhere you might crave something sweet, like in the car, at your desk or in the pantry. Open up a few packs and pour into a candy dish to offer guests or use your gummy ocean creatures to decorate cakes and cookies for an ocean or beach themed birthday party!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/i/vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', '1609~vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', 'vidal-ocean-gummies-peg-bag'),
(1610, 'Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties Bags', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'You can almost hear the breath-freshening aaaaah of these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties. That\'s because they\'re both satisfying and low in calories. With melty chocolate covering a potently peppermint center, these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties are a serious breath of fresh air. If you love Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties but want to try a lower calorie option, these are a great choice for you! Bring some home to keep in your office drawer, put into lunch boxes or serve alongside dessert for guests to eat if they\'re watching their waistlines. Individually wrapped, these glimmering silver wrappers are ready to be ripped open so that you can devour the goodness that awaits inside!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', '1610~sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', 'sf-york-peppermint-patties'),
(1611, 'Claey\'s Horehound Drop Bags', 34.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Old fashioned Claeyâ€™s Horehound Drops are one of the most unique and timeless treats you can put in your mouth. This version helps sooth the throat with a confection thatâ€™s fat free. Each hard candy features the classic round shape produced using a mold and drop method. Horehound is produced using an herb tea thatâ€™s steeped in a copper kettle to bring out the unique mint and licorice taste of Claeyâ€™s Drops.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '1611~claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'claeys-horehound-drop-bags'),
(1612, 'Apple O\'s Gummi Rings Bag', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Trolli Apple O\'s gummy rings are the perfect candy when you\'re craving something sweet and chewy. Trolli is a longstanding favorite in the candy world. The brand was formed in 1948 and originally sold pasta and noodles.Throughout the next decade, Trolli would expand to offer a selection of jelly fruits and cream drops. Today it is a brand that is most commonly known for its delicious gummy candy!Apple O\'s gummy rings are similar to peach rings with a sour apple flavor. Each piece is round with an open center. One side is white and the other is vibrant green, just like the skin on a Granny Smith apple!Take a bite and enjoy sweet apple flavor with a touch of tangy sugar. Bulk gummy rings are a great treat to serve at events or to use in party favors. Kids love snacking with them and adults will enjoy the unique sweet and sour flavor that makes Trolli gummies so tasty!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/p/apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', '1612~apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', 'apple-os-gummi-rings-bag'),
(1613, 'Claey\'s Lemon Drop Bags', 34.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Claeyâ€™s Lemon Drops are a longstanding favorite that have been satisfying sweet cravings for decades. This traditional treat includes a bite-sized morsel of hard candy with refreshing lemon citrus flavor. Claeyâ€™s makes their confections the natural way, using California lemons. Each piece is poured into a mold then dropped to produce a unique fruit shape. Enjoy fat free hard candy anytime with Claeyâ€™s Lemon Drops!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys_lemon_drop_bags_-_24ct.png', '1613~claeys_lemon_drop_bags_-_24ct.png', 'claeys-lemon-drop-bags'),
(1614, 'Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings Bags', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Fruity and mild, the flavor of Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings is like no other candy, and the soft, chewy texture is one of the best of the gummy varieties!A bulk package of market-size Peachie O\'s bags makes these fun candy rings easy to pack for car trips and family picnics, and the bags are the perfect size for the movie theater, too! These gummi peach slices are an economical way to enjoy gummi candies on the go. Each Peachie O\'s gummi candy is dusted with sugar and consists of two pretty layers, one yellow and one two-toned red and orange to mimic the hues of real peach fuzz.They make a pretty addition to a warmly-hued candy buffet in summer or fall. Cover a layer cake in Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings for a playful (and edible) geometric decoration Ã or just slide a Peachie O on every finger and wave to your friends.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peachie-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bags_1.gif', '1614~peachie-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bags_1.gif', 'peachie-os-gummi-rings-bags'),
(1615, 'Jelly Belly Super Hero Bags', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly Super Hero Bags - 24ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_super_hero_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '1615~jelly_belly_super_hero_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-super-hero-bags'),
(1616, 'Hawaiian Punch Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Hawaiian Punch Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/hawaiian_punch_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '1616~hawaiian_punch_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'hawaiian-punch-licorice-twists-bags'),
(1617, 'Neon Squiggles Gummi Worms', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Neon Squiggles gummy worms are fun, colorful and always ready to eat! Everyone loves the soft, chewy taste of classic gummy worms. This popular treat was actually created to honor the 60th birthday of the gummy bear.Even though they came later, gummy worms are just as delicious and preferred by many candy lovers because of their long, bendable shape! Each gummy worm includes a narrow body with rounded ends. The back is covered in a segmented pattern that looks similar to the body of a real worm. The bottom is flat so it sits upright on flat surfaces. You get multiple colors in every worm!Taste yellow, red, white and green in every Trolli Squiggles bag! Our bulk gummy worms are convenient for birthday parties and more. Use them to fill party favors or add a fun touch by decorating cakes with these chewy worm candies. Everyone will love the sweet taste and playful look of Trolli Neon Squiggles gummy worms!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/e/neon-squiggles-gummi-worms-12ct_1.gif', '1617~neon-squiggles-gummi-worms-12ct_1.gif', 'neon-squiggles-gummi-worms'),
(1618, 'Jelly Belly Assorted Sugar Free Jelly Beans Bags', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly makes it even easier to enjoy their famous jellybeans and stick to a sugar-free diet. This colorful assortment features all sugar-free jellybeans in your favorite flavors. Each piece includes the familiar coffee bean shape and smooth texture along with the authentic brand logo printed on the side. Splenda is added to the recipe to produce a sweet tasting bean without the added sugar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_assorted_sugar_free_jelly_beans_bags_-_12ct.jpg', '1618~jelly_belly_assorted_sugar_free_jelly_beans_bags_-_12ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-assorted-sugar-free-jelly-beans-bags'),
(1619, 'Grape Crush Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Grape Crush Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape_crush_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '1619~grape_crush_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'grape-crush-licorice-twists-bags'),
(1620, 'Haribo Sour Gummi Spaghetti', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo Sour S\'ghetti is unlike any pasta you have ever eaten! Don\'t worry, you won\'t need to twirl these noodles on a fork. They are enjoyed cool and can be picked up by hand. Each bag features a generous collection of wiggly, wobbly slender lengths that are similar to classic spaghetti.Each piece comes in red, white or yellow. Our bulk sour gummy spaghetti is a great choice for after school snacks, lunches or special events. Sweeten any day by grabbing a handful of chewy spaghetti gummies when you\'re craving something sweet. Each bite features the taste of sugary gummy candy that\'s smothered in a coating of sour sugar.Your taste buds will tingle when they experience this one-of-a-kind confection! Kids won\'t be able to resist playing with the long noodle-y pieces which jiggle and bend. Add to birthday party favors or find fun ways to decorate cakes and cookies with Haribo sour gummy spaghetti!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', '1620~haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', 'haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti'),
(1621, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '1621~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(1622, 'Key Lime Pie Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you pop a piece of key lime pie candy into your mouth, your taste buds will burst with citrus sweetness. It\'s like taking a trip to the beautiful, balmy Florida Keys without even leaving your home or office. These delicious green and white hard candies are perfect for any occasion, whether you want a refreshing tropical taste on a hot summer day or you want to remind yourself of the beach in the middle of winter.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', '1622~key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', 'key-lime-pie-hard-candy'),
(1623, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '1623~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(1624, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '1624~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(1625, 'chocolate starlight mints thumbnail', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Chocolate starlight mints are a new and amazing take on a classic candy. Everyone loves the refreshing flavor of the traditional hard mint, now add chocolate.Starlight mints, which are also sometimes called pinwheel mints, feature a lovely white background with bold red stripes. Our chocolate starlight mints take that same elegant pattern and use it on a dark background with brilliant green stripes instead.Now you can enjoy that delicious minty taste with a touch of savory chocolate. Each round mint is crafted using solid hard candy. This allows them to provide the flavor candy lovers adore in a long lasting treat. Each mint is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can admire their dark beauty before you open the first one up!Pour them into glass jars or candy dishes and serve to guests, use them in the office candy jar or make your gingerbread houses more unique with these tasty decorations!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', '1625~chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', 'chocolate-starlight-mints'),
(1626, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Don\'t bite down on one of these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers! These hard candies are great for savoring a ton of sweetness for a long time.Buy a bulk bag of Jaw Busters hard candies for the little ghouls and goblins coming around the neighborhood on Halloween, or keep them around when you\'re craving something sweet for yourself. You can keep a bag of Jawbreakers in a wide assortment of colors and flavors all year long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', '1626~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-wrapped'),
(1627, 'Bulk Assorted Fruit Lollipops', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Lollipop, lollipop, oh lolli , lolli, lolli  Sorry, we\'re getting carried away with ourselves. It happens a lot here. It\'s just that we\'re so passionate about these scrumptious suckers that it makes us break out in song. They don\'t require a trip to the doctor and they come in bulk, so these pops are the perfect choice for any occasion. Stock up for your child\'s next party or put them in a jar on your desk for lucky coworkers to snack on. You\'ll quickly become a favorite in the office! With a light, sweet, fruity flavor, in a rainbow of colors, everyone can enjoy a mouthful of deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1627~lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'lollipops-bulk-fruit'),
(1628, 'Sour Fruit Balls Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Sour. Check. Colorful. Check. Fruity and delicious. Check, check! We\'ve got everything you need here for the makings of a great bulk candy selection.  Individually wrapped, these candies make tasty treats for parties, as filler candy, or just to have around the house for a qick fix of sweetness.With over 80 hard candies per pound, there\'s enough sweetness to treat all of your friends and family. Every time you snack from this bag, choose from yummy red, orange, yellow, green, and purple. Everyone who hears the crinkle of their wrappers will come running for more. And because of their perfect size, one after another can be enjoyed.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', '1628~sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', 'sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy'),
(1629, 'Andes Mints', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Ande\'s mints make the perfect welcome snack for any home, office, or restaurant. Whether your guests want to freshen their breath after they\'ve had a meal, or you\'d just like to make them feel at home with something sweet, these are the treats for you. A perfect blend of creamy milk chocolate and mint filling make these tiny sandwiches of sweetness the perfect refreshment, and they\'re individually wrapped, so there\'s no danger of spreading anyone\'s germs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', '1629~andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', 'andes-mints'),
(1630, 'Butterscotch Buttons Candy', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'These candies are cute as a button! Maybe that\'s because these Butterscotch Candy Buttons come in beautiful, individually wrapped gold wrappers and are a lovely bright yellow color that candy fans love. Around since the 1800s, butterscotch has built up a tasty reputation throughout the decades and continues to please candy lovers near and far. Try these little, rich sweets out for your next candy buffet bar, crush them and sprinkle them on top of cookies and baked goods for a sweet surprise, or even fill your candy dishes for an olde timey feel every snacker can enjoy. These hard candies are sure to \'\'butter you up\'\' with their irresistible flavor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1630~butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'butterscotch-buttons'),
(1631, 'Sunkist Fruit Gems', 69.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a big, sugary smooch with these Sunkist Fruit Gems! Their delicious, gummy chew and bright, fruity flavor will make you want to pucker up for more every time you take a bite. Individually wrapped, these little gummies pack the power of the sun into every chew and show off the beautiful colors of the rainbow.Stock yourself up with some rainy day sunshine with a bag of these. They\'re a great goodie bag stuffer for birthday parties, look lovely at a summertime picnic on the dessert table, and even can be kept to cheer up your little ones on a rainy day. With 42 pieces per pound, there are enough to please every gummy fan!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', '1631~sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk'),
(1632, 'Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get your candy fix with our Tootsie Rolls midgees candy! Tootsie Roll is one of the oldest treats in the United States. This confection was invented in 1986 when Leo Hirshfield decided to open up a shop in New York City.Today, kids and adults love the chewy texture and chocolaty taste that makes these popular confections so irresistible. They\'re not quite taffy and not quite caramel but very smooth, making snack time even sweeter! Bulk Tootsie Rolls give you more pieces for snacking, parties and sharing.Every roll is individually wrapped in that familiar brown, red and white paper. That allows the candy to remain fresh and ready to enjoy. Take a handful with you as a quick treat on a busy day or use them as an easy after school snack for the kids. Tootsie Rolls also make great treat bag filler for birthday parties, picnics, holiday events and other gatherings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', '1632~tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-midgees'),
(1633, 'Peppermint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '6', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peppermint Starlight mints make the perfect complimentary candy for almost any occasion, event, or environment. Are you considering putting a candy dish by the door at home? Do you run a restaurant where customers pay at a counter near the front? These Starlight mint hard candies are recognized all over the world as a true classic. They\'ll satisfy your sweet tooth and freshen your breath, too. Put some of these individually wrapped treats out in your home, office, or restaurant today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', '1633~peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', 'starlight-mints-peppermint'),
(1634, 'Jumbo Mint Balls Hard Candy', 11.49, '120', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'Make way for a big dose of peppermint flavor! These Jumbo Mint Balls are a sphere full of refreshing minty flavor that your mouth will love. Their beautiful red and white swirls make them the perfect sweet addition to a Christmas candy display, gingerbread house making with your family, a beach party (since these little balls resemble beach balls!), and even a Fourth of July event. With 12 of these flavorful candy balls in every order, there\'s enough to do it all. Use your imagination to decide how you and your close family and friends can enjoy these tasty mints.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', '1634~jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', 'jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls'),
(1635, 'Peanut Butter Bars', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peanut butter bars candy brings you all the best parts of peanuts without all the bad stuff. Each bar includes high quality peanuts that are slow roasted until they become gold brown to bring out the natural nutty flavor. Each bite is truly an experience, with the crispy, flaky crunch that everyone loves. If you are a peanut butter fanatic, then this bar candy is your dream come true!Every peanut butter bar is individually wrapped so it\'s easy to store and share. Each includes a simple white wrapper with black stripes, gold star and a classic logo that gives each piece a nostalgic look. Keep a handful in your purse or pocket or use the in favor bags for parties and holiday events. Each tasty tidbit is packed with all the rich peanut flavor you can handle in a convenient package that you can take anywhere! Our bulk candy packs are great for school events, businesses and carnivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', '1635~peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', 'peanut-butter-bars');
