(1783, 'Royal Blue Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Royal blue foil chocolate balls offer the perfect combination of visual appeal and taste. Everyone loves the smooth, rich flavor of high quality chocolate. Our individually wrapped candy balls make it easy to share this classic treat at any event or right at home! Each piece includes a solid ball of savory milk chocolate that\'s wrapped in a thin layer of foil. Our royal blue chocolate balls add elegance to any presentation. Pour them into glass bowls or jars to set out on guest tables. You can also add a few to sachets or bags to give away as wedding favors. The dark blue color goes with almost any celebration! Add an icy blue chill to a winter feast or celebrate a birthday with the irresistible taste of pure chocolate. You can even share them with coworkers or give complimentary candies to clients as a thank you for their business!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '1783~royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'royal-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1784, 'Ghirardelli Twilight Delight 72% Dark Chocolate Squares Caddy', 26.99, '50', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Ghirardelli Twilight Delight 72% Dark Chocolate Squares Caddy - 50ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/h/ghirardelli_twilight_delight_72_dark_chocolate_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', '1784~ghirardelli_twilight_delight_72_dark_chocolate_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', 'ghirardelli-twilight-delight-72percent-dark-chocolate-squares-caddy'),
(1785, 'Chocolate Basketballs', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Getting together to watch the game is a momentous occasion worthy of marking with specialty candy â€“ at least, if your team is doing well! Celebrate victories and mourn losses with these foil-wrapped Chocolate Basketballs, solid balls of chocolate that melt in your mouth once you remove the realistically-printed orange foil wrapper.These bulk chocolate basketballs are great for sports parties, birthday parties, and candy buffets tailored to the interests of the guest of honor! When the NCAA tournament rolls around, you will be glad to have these chocolate balls on hand for dropping into lunch boxes or topping off the office candy jar!These chocolate candies are also sure to enthuse a youth basketball team if offered by the handful at their end-of-season bash. The foil wrappers are not just clever and thematic, but also easy to remove, making chocolate basketballs a perfect candy-dish sweet.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolatebasketballs.jpg', '1785~chocolatebasketballs.jpg', 'chocolate-basketballs-foil-wrapped'),
(1786, 'Gold Nugget Choco Rocks Bulk', 39.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Gold nugget choco rocks are one of the most fascinating and unique candies available! This treat is unlike any other chocolate snack. Every piece features an original shape that looks much like natural rocks.The surface is covered in a luxurious gold shell that produces an alluring shimmer that looks very realistic, right down to the fine gravelly texture that runs along all sides. While these chocolate nuggets look like rocks, they taste amazing! Don\'t worry, you won\'t break any teeth when you bite down on each rich piece. The candy coating on the outside provides a crunch while smooth, irresistible chocolate hides within Ã just waiting to take your taste buds on a sweet adventure!Our bulk gold nugget choco rocks are perfect for many occasions. Use them to fill a pot of gold at your next St. Patrick\'s Day party. Choco rocks are also great for decorating baked goods and edible decor!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks-bulk_1.jpg', '1786~gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks-bulk_1.jpg', 'gold-nuggets-candy-choco-rocks'),
(1787, 'Chocolate Golf Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Now golfers can enjoy their favorite confection and their favorite sport at the same time! Our chocolate golf balls are packed with rich flavor that comes in a fun themed package.Each bite-sized morsel consists of a solid orb of delectable chocolate. The smooth, dark surface is covered in a thin foil wrapper with a uniquely printed exterior. The pure white background is covered in realistic pock marks to recreate the look of an actual golf ball!You can take these delicious chocolate with you anywhere, from the green to the clubhouse! Our bulk chocolate balls are also a great treat for special occasions like golf themed birthday parties, picnics and holidays.Impress a fellow golfer with the smooth taste of fine chocolate that comes in a package they can appreciate! Our bulk chocolate golf balls makes it easy to order enough for wedding favors, treat bags and edible gifts.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', '1787~chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', 'chocolate-golf-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(1788, 'Silver Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This candy will steal your heart! And how could they not with their shimmery, shiny silver wrapper and even more amazing chocolate heart that lays within. Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Silver Foil Hearts is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '1788~silver-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'silver-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(1789, 'Ghirardelli Dark and Sea Salt Caramel Squares Caddy', 26.99, '50', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Ghirardelli Dark and Sea Salt Caramel Squares Caddy - 50ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/h/ghirardelli_dark_and_sea_salt_caramel_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', '1789~ghirardelli_dark_and_sea_salt_caramel_squares_caddy_-_50ct.jpg', 'ghirardelli-dark-and-sea-salt-caramel-squares-caddy'),
(1790, 'Purple Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wear your heart on your sleeve with these heavenly chocolates. The indulgent mouthfuls of joy are the perfect message to send the special someone who has your whole heart. Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Purple Foil Hearts is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '1790~purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'purple-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(1791, 'Sour Power Belts Wrapped', 24.99, '150', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'With 150 Sour Power Belts in this big bulk supply you will have plenty of opportunity for flavorful fun. These candies were introduced in 1985, and folks of all ages have not been able to get enough of them.If you love pucker-inducing treats, these Sour Power Belts should definitely be on your shopping list. This box of delicious treats is available in Green Apple, Blue Raspberry, Strawberry, and Watermelon. We recommend getting all four before you drive yourself crazy trying to pick only one.The belts are about 9-inches long and just under 1-inch wide, so they are pretty much the perfect size. Big enough to satisfy, but not so big you get a tummy ache. Since these Sour Power Belts are individually wrapped you can surprise your kids with them in their lunch box and hand them out at Halloween.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', '1791~sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', 'sour-power-belts-dorval-wrapped'),
