(1926, 'Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy 2.5oz', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'No candy store is complete without a selection of light, fluffy, and sweet cotton candy. It has come to be trademark of the summer fun and sweetness and you do not want to miss out on it!  Available in sweet flavors, our cotton candy will bring smiles to the faces of all who enjoy it and everyone who craves that melt in your mouth sensation .Our specially packaged bulk order will give you 12 bags of 25 ounce cotton candy ready to be displayed and ready to sell. Give your customers what they are looking for and make sure to include some of our cotton candy on your next order!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/l/fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-25oz-12ct.gif', '1926~fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-25oz-12ct.gif', 'fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-bags'),
(1927, 'Sugar Free Reeses Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bag', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'These Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bags are almost too good to be true. With the savory peanut butter filling Reese\'s is famous for and the crinkle cut chocolate exterior, you\'ll feel like you\'re breaking your diet but you won\'t be!Inside every Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bag are individually wrapped mini Reese\'s Cups that are just waiting to be devoured by you. If you love sweets, but don\'t want to eat too much of them, then these are a great candy choice for you. You can sprinkle them on non fat yogurt or ice cream for added deliciousness or even pack some into lunch boxes for a low calorie dessert. Whatever you do, Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bags will keep you coming back for more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar_free_reeses_pegbag.jpg', '1927~sugar_free_reeses_pegbag.jpg', 'sugar-free-reeses-peanut-butter-cups-peg-bag'),
(1928, 'Rainbow Mini Frogs Bag', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Our Haribo rainbow mini frog gummies are ready to hop right in and make snack time even tastier! These fun fruit snacks come in a rainbow of fun colors, including yellow, red and green â€“ of course! Every piece includes a white back that\'s just as soft and chewy. Who doesn\'t love munching on tiny frog candy pieces? These delectable sweets will prove that not all amphibians are covered in slime!Enjoy our rainbow frog gummy pieces alone or use them to decorate birthday cakes, cupcakes, cookies and other baked treats. Our bulk candy package makes it so easy to get larger quantities of chewy frogs to serve at parties, picnics and school events. Pour them in a dish and let guests dive right in or include a handful in party favors. No one will be able to resist the adorable shape and sweet taste that makes Haribo gummies so delightful!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/minirainbowfrogs.jpg', '1928~minirainbowfrogs.jpg', 'rainbow-mini-frogs-bag-12ct'),
(1929, 'Jelly Belly 49 Flavors Mix Bags', 64.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'If you just can\'t decide on one Jelly Belly jelly bean flavor, you need to reach for the 49 flavors assortment! This handsome Jelly Belly bag contains a diverse collection of their finest beans. Each includes the brilliant colors, intense taste and familiar white Jelly Belly brand printed on one side.Grab a handful, come up with your own fun combinations or pick and choose individual jelly beans! Our bulk Jelly Belly 49 flavors mix bags give you more of the candy you love with every order! Stay stocked up in case guests or a demanding sweet tooth show up. Our assortment includes multiple individual bags that feature beautiful Jelly Belly branding that\'s perfect for gift giving.Use them as stocking stuffers, add to Easter basket candy for the kids or include in a gourmet gift basket. Jelly Belly candy is made with love to ensure the best quality and eating experience no matter how many beans you order!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', '1929~jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags'),
(1930, 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/r/dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '1930~dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'dr-pepper-licorice-twists-bags'),
(1931, 'Starburst Peg Bag', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Starburst fruit chews are the sweetest way to get your fruit fix. Each piece is square and includes a soft, chewy texture that feels smooth and tastes amazing!Our bulk Starburst fruit chews include multiple peg bags with individually wrapped blocks of confectionary goodness. Sink your teeth into juicy strawberry, orange, cherry or lemon or combine two flavors for a mouthful of fun!The original Starburst candies were introduced in 1959 as Opal Fruits under the Mars brand in the United Kingdom. They were later renamed Starburst and made available for sale in the United States. Needless to say, Starburst fruit chews were a big hit here in the states!Today they are one of the most popular confections available in grocery stores and candy shops all over the country. Now you can get larger quantities for parties, events, holidays or at home snacking by ordering our convenient bulk Starburst packs!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/starburstpegbag.jpg', '1931~starburstpegbag.jpg', 'starburst-peg-bag-12ct'),
(1932, 'Jelly Belly 20 Flavor Jelly Beans Bags', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly 20 Flavor Jelly Beans Bags - 24ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_20_flavor_jelly_beans_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '1932~jelly_belly_20_flavor_jelly_beans_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-20-flavor-jelly-beans-bags'),
(1933, 'Vidal Ocean Gummies', 18.99, '18', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Make a big splash at snack time by giving the kids a taste of Vidal\'s Ocean Gummies! This fun candy is not only tasty, but also exciting to see. While regular gummy bears usually feature a solid color look, our gummy ocean creatures present a brilliant color with bright exciting colors.Each piece is shaped into a different sea creature. Our bulk package includes 18 4 count packs so the gummies are always fresh â€“ even if you don\'t open it right away! Vidal Ocean Gummies are convenient for gift giving, sharing and casual snacking.Keep a pack anywhere you might crave something sweet, like in the car, at your desk or in the pantry. Open up a few packs and pour into a candy dish to offer guests or use your gummy ocean creatures to decorate cakes and cookies for an ocean or beach themed birthday party!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/i/vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', '1933~vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', 'vidal-ocean-gummies-peg-bag'),
(1934, 'Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties Bags', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'You can almost hear the breath-freshening aaaaah of these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties. That\'s because they\'re both satisfying and low in calories. With melty chocolate covering a potently peppermint center, these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties are a serious breath of fresh air. If you love Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties but want to try a lower calorie option, these are a great choice for you! Bring some home to keep in your office drawer, put into lunch boxes or serve alongside dessert for guests to eat if they\'re watching their waistlines. Individually wrapped, these glimmering silver wrappers are ready to be ripped open so that you can devour the goodness that awaits inside!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', '1934~sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', 'sf-york-peppermint-patties'),
(1935, 'Claey\'s Horehound Drop Bags', 34.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Old fashioned Claeyâ€™s Horehound Drops are one of the most unique and timeless treats you can put in your mouth. This version helps sooth the throat with a confection thatâ€™s fat free. Each hard candy features the classic round shape produced using a mold and drop method. Horehound is produced using an herb tea thatâ€™s steeped in a copper kettle to bring out the unique mint and licorice taste of Claeyâ€™s Drops.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '1935~claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'claeys-horehound-drop-bags'),
(1936, 'Apple O\'s Gummi Rings Bag', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Trolli Apple O\'s gummy rings are the perfect candy when you\'re craving something sweet and chewy. Trolli is a longstanding favorite in the candy world. The brand was formed in 1948 and originally sold pasta and noodles.Throughout the next decade, Trolli would expand to offer a selection of jelly fruits and cream drops. Today it is a brand that is most commonly known for its delicious gummy candy!Apple O\'s gummy rings are similar to peach rings with a sour apple flavor. Each piece is round with an open center. One side is white and the other is vibrant green, just like the skin on a Granny Smith apple!Take a bite and enjoy sweet apple flavor with a touch of tangy sugar. Bulk gummy rings are a great treat to serve at events or to use in party favors. Kids love snacking with them and adults will enjoy the unique sweet and sour flavor that makes Trolli gummies so tasty!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/p/apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', '1936~apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', 'apple-os-gummi-rings-bag'),
