(1944, 'Haribo Sour Gummi Spaghetti', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo Sour S\'ghetti is unlike any pasta you have ever eaten! Don\'t worry, you won\'t need to twirl these noodles on a fork. They are enjoyed cool and can be picked up by hand. Each bag features a generous collection of wiggly, wobbly slender lengths that are similar to classic spaghetti.Each piece comes in red, white or yellow. Our bulk sour gummy spaghetti is a great choice for after school snacks, lunches or special events. Sweeten any day by grabbing a handful of chewy spaghetti gummies when you\'re craving something sweet. Each bite features the taste of sugary gummy candy that\'s smothered in a coating of sour sugar.Your taste buds will tingle when they experience this one-of-a-kind confection! Kids won\'t be able to resist playing with the long noodle-y pieces which jiggle and bend. Add to birthday party favors or find fun ways to decorate cakes and cookies with Haribo sour gummy spaghetti!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', '1944~haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', 'haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti'),
(1945, 'Hershey\'s Mini Chocolate Candy Bars', 34.99, '5', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'These bulk bags of mixed mini chocolate bars are the great, great, great, great, great grandkids of the first Hershey chocolate bars. We may have missed a few \'\'greats\'\' in there, but with the origination of the Hershey chocolate company in 1894, these confections have an impressive history that precedes us all. If you love a surprise, this mixed bag of mini Hershey\'s chocolate bars is right up your alley. Complete with a selection of Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate, Mr. Goodbar, Hershey\'s Dark Chocolate, and Krackel, you can expect something different every time you snack. With decades of success, we\'re positive that you\'ll love indulging in this famous brand.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hershey-mini-bars-small.jpg', '1945~hershey-mini-bars-small.jpg', 'hersheys-mini-chocolate-candy-bars'),
(1946, 'Peanut Butter Bars', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'Peanut butter bars candy brings you all the best parts of peanuts without all the bad stuff. Each bar includes high quality peanuts that are slow roasted until they become gold brown to bring out the natural nutty flavor. Each bite is truly an experience, with the crispy, flaky crunch that everyone loves. If you are a peanut butter fanatic, then this bar candy is your dream come true!Every peanut butter bar is individually wrapped so it\'s easy to store and share. Each includes a simple white wrapper with black stripes, gold star and a classic logo that gives each piece a nostalgic look. Keep a handful in your purse or pocket or use the in favor bags for parties and holiday events. Each tasty tidbit is packed with all the rich peanut flavor you can handle in a convenient package that you can take anywhere! Our bulk candy packs are great for school events, businesses and carnivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', '1946~peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', 'peanut-butter-bars'),
(1947, 'Hot Tamales Minis', 9.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Hold on to your taste buds! These red Hot Tamales Minis are ready to singe every last one of \'em off of your tongue. Though they may be packed in miniature movie theater boxes, every pack of these tamales are ready with a fiery punch of cinnamon that will blow you away. If you can\'t beat the heat, try adding them to a cup of tea or cocoa for a milder cinnamon fix. But if you\'re prepared for a spice that can\'t be beat, pop a few of these into your mouth at a time and feel the fire. Whatever you do, you\'ll set your mouth a-blaze with this bulk supply.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', '1947~hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', 'hot-tamales-minis'),
(1948, 'Skittles Fun Size Bulk', 99.99, '22', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'A color and flavor for every taste bud. Pack these fun size Skittles into a pinata, add them to a stocking, or slip one into your kid\'s lunchbox for a delicious afternoon surprise. Whatever you choose, everyone will love to \'\'Taste the Rainbow.\'\' Skittles have been in the US since 1979 and have evolved into a quirky brand and a household name. Their original flavors of orange, lemon, lime, grape and strawberry got a revamp in 1989 with the introduction of tropical fruit flavors. Since then, 1 new Skittles lines have been created and amazed the mouths of people all over the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-fun-size.jpg', '1948~skittles-fun-size.jpg', 'skittles-fun-size-bulk'),
(1949, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Prepare to be spoiled rotten with an overdose of creamy caramel and sugary sweetness! These Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops are an American classic that have had customers smacking their lips for years. Invented in 1925, it wasn\'t until 1932 that these famous pop got their sugary name. Give your family a taste of the olden days with some of these delicious caramels. Bring them to a party, add some to a candy buffet bar, or use them as a yummy, melty stirrer for hot chocolate. With over 48 caramel pops per box, get ready to indulge your family and friends for a long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', '1949~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops'),
(1950, 'Toblerone Mini Chocolate Bars', 45.99, '80', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Toblerone mini chocolate bars are a great idea for any party or occasion. These are small bars that have a total of three peaks made of chocolate; they are then filled using creamy nougat for a treat that is mouth watering and good. Each one of the bars is wrapped individually to help ensure that they are fresh. The shape of these bars is fun because they are not like many of the other typical candy bars that you find. Instead they are more interactive and have a lot to offer. The wrapper of these bars is a yellow color with red writing which means it can tie into many different themes if you find that you want to use it for a party. If you have never tried one of these great candies before then you have no idea just what you are missing. Your mouth is sure to be pleased when you take a bite of this wonderful candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/toblerone_mini.jpg', '1950~toblerone_mini.jpg', 'toblerone-mini-chocolate-bars'),
(1951, 'Giant Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars', 29.50, '12', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Someone must have been eating their \'\'Wheaties\'\' because these Giant Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars are ridiculously humungous and even more delicious! Have a friend who is a major chocolate fan? Want to stock up on s\'mores supplies that will last you all summer? Want to impress friends and family with a thoughtful and delicious gift basket addition? These gigantic, rich, melty chocolates can do all that and more. Around since 1894, Hershey\'s first opened their delicious doors in Pennsylvania. And ever since, their culinary perfection of some of the world\'s most famous confections has satisfied candy lovers around the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheyxl_bars.jpg', '1951~hersheyxl_bars.jpg', 'giant-hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars'),
(1952, 'Nut Goodie Bars', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Nostalgic. Classic. Vintage. You\'re a special kind of candy fan who appreciates where every sweet got its roots. With these Nut Goodie\'s, you can enjoy a taste of yesteryear in every milk chocolatey, nutty bite! Introduced in 1912, Nut Goodie hit candy store shelves for a whopping 5 cents! To this day, not much has changed about the delicious, salty, sweet nut clusters including their vintage wrapper. Add these to a 2\'s themed party for a tasty treat, share a bit of history with loved ones, or surprise your grandmother or grandfather with a taste of their youth. Whatever you do, you\'ll love these tried and true confections.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/u/nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', '1952~nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', 'nut-goodie-bars'),
(1953, 'Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'One candy that has been a favorite for many over the years and still is, is the Hershey\'s milk chocolate. These great candy bars are nothing short of delicious. There is just something about the way that these are able to melt in your mouth when you take a bite. They are smooth and wonderful. This is great if you are looking to use them to make s\'mores. They are also great all on their own. These are full sized bars that are wrapped individually. If you are one that has a sweet tooth often then you will really be able to benefit from the bulk 36 count box of them. It will ensure that you have a way to indulge in this wonderful tasting candy bar whenever you decide that you want to or need to. Nothing is better than the sweet chocolaty taste of Hershey\'s. Kids and adults are both able to enjoy this wonderful candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars-36ct_2.gif', '1953~hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars-36ct_2.gif', 'hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars'),
(1954, 'Sixlets 20 Ball Tubes', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Sixlets 20 ball tubes are the most convenient way to enjoy your favorite chocolate candy! Every stick includes a clear wrapper that holds 20 round balls in a straight line. Take a bite out of green, yellow, orange, red or brown.No matter which hue you choose, every Sixlets candy contains a smooth chocolate center surrounded by a hard candy shell. Our bulk Sixlets box contains a generous number of full tubes so you have plenty to take or share.Individually wrapped candy is perfect for traveling and events. Tuck a few in your vehicle\'s glove box, your purse or carry on. You can also display them in glass vases or trays to serve at parties, school activities and other gatherings. Buying Sixlets in bulk is also a great way to ensure that you always have an easy, tasty snack on hand when chocolate cravings hit!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', '1954~sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', 'sixlets-20-ball-tubes'),
(1955, 'Long Boys Coconut', 8.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Long Boys coconut candy sticks are a classic favorite that\'s full of rich flavor! This traditional candy originated in New Orleans, making it a staple for local children.Today, people all over the country rave about the amazing taste of these long, chewy confections. Every piece includes a stick of candy that\'s individually wrapped in a nostalgic red and yellow wrapper.Coconut Long Boys offer a unique blend of caramel and exotic coconut for a snacking experience that\'s memorable and satisfying! Untwist the wrapper and take small bites to fully enjoy the taste of this one-of-a-kind flavor combination! Kids can try stretching their Long Boy candy to see who can make the longest rope!Our bulk Long Boy coconut candy is a great choice for parties, picnics and family reunions. Use them to fill treat bags for birthdays or set out a bowl or box so adults can munch while reminiscing about their favorite childhood sweets!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', '1955~long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', 'long-boys-coconut'),
(1956, 'Snickers Bars', 46.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Full-size Snickers bars will light up practically anyone\'s eyes! A familiar candy bar made from a perfect portion of peanuts sandwiched between soft, melting caramel and delicious creamy nougat, this confection is robed in a smooth milk chocolate for a sweet finish that\'s texturally interesting and satisfying to eat. When you just have to have a mid-morning snack and instant energy is the way to go, you could do much worse than to reach for a delicious Snickers bar!These Snickers candy bars in bulk come packaged in the familiar boldly-lettered, chocolate-hued wrapper, keeping them fresh for your enjoyment. This lot of Snickers is a perfect way to stock up on your family\'s favorite game-night treat or weekend dessert. If you\'re looking to create high perceived value in welcome bags or on a candy buffet, it\'s even better â€“ everyone feels special when they\'re offered a big, nutty chocolate candy bar to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/n/snickers-bars-48ct.gif', '1956~snickers-bars-48ct.gif', 'snickers-bars'),
(1957, 'Charleston Chews Candy Bars Snack Size', 12.99, '120', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Move your feet and clap your hands for this famous confection, Charleston Chews Candy Bars! Created in 1922, this classic candy bar was named after the famous dance, The Charleston. With a chewy, vanilla nougat center covered in melty milk chocolate, these candy bars have been a favorite for years. Bring some home to your family and share a sweet treat any day of the week. They\'re also great to put in a piï¾ata, make your own sundae bar, or to keep around the house to add to the top of cupcakes and other baked treats. Let these candies dance their way into your mouth and heart today when you order this bulk bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charleston-chews-candy-snack-size-120ct_2.jpg', '1957~charleston-chews-candy-snack-size-120ct_2.jpg', 'charleston-chews-candy-snack-size'),
(1958, 'Take 5 Candy Bars', 25.99, '18', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'These are mini Take 5 candy bars that are the same a the larger versions which are already a big hit. People love the way that these taste and they are great when you find that you are craving something sweet. You will find that these are also great when it comes to finding a candy that you want to pass out at Halloween. The middle of these have peanuts and pretzels that have been dipped in peanut butter followed by caramel. It is then coated using milk chocolate. Your mouth is probably watering already and it should be, because there is just something about these that make you want more. You will find that it has a nice soft texture but it is also crunchy. This means that you are able to get the best of both worlds with this candy bar. Not to even mention the fact that you will get a little bit of sweet and salty taste as well.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/a/take_5_18ct.jpeg', '1958~take_5_18ct.jpeg', 'take-five-candy-bars'),
(1959, 'Skor Bars', 21.99, '18', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'It literally only takes one bite to be totally hooked on Skor Bars. If you are already a bit of an addict then you know this firsthand.Just looking at the bar, you think it\'s going to be a simple chocolate bar, but it\'s not. Enrobed in that creamy milk chocolate is a butter toffee center that will make your taste buds sing.You are more than welcome to chew it, if you like, but lovers of Skor Bars will tell you to let the chocolate dissolve on your tongue until the butter toffee is revealed for the full effect. This bulk supply of Skor Bars is perfect to have in the pantry for movie night or just to enjoy as a special treat.They are amazing as a topping, too. Put one in a sealed bag, crush it with a hammer, rolling pin, or whatever you have handy, and sprinkle it on cupcakes, ice-cream, frozen yogurt, and brownies. This is one treat you don\'t want to run out of!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skor-bars-18ct_1.jpg', '1959~skor-bars-18ct_1.jpg', 'skor-bars'),
(1960, 'Candy Buttons Wrapped', 26.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Candy buttons are so fun. These candies look like small buttons and they come on a sheet with three different types of flavors. Some of the great flavors that you can expect are lemon, lime, and cherry. You will also find that the colors that you get are nice with these as well. The colors are yellow, blue, and cherry. You can eat these just the way that they are or you can use this sweet candy in order to decorate a dessert with. There is nothing more fun than having a sheet where you can take off the buttons and pick out the colors that you want off of the sheet. This is fun for kids but adults will be able to enjoy it as well. Each sheet is wrapped individually which is convenient. If you want to find a great treat that you are able to please everyone with then this is certainly the treat for you.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-buttons-necco-candystore.jpg', '1960~candy-buttons-necco-candystore.jpg', 'candy-buttons-wrapped'),
(1961, 'Haribo Gold Bears', 21.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Everyone\'s favorite Haribo gummies are now available in a big gold box! What\'s one of the first sweet treats everyone thinks of when they are hungry for a chewy candy? Why gummy bears of course! Our adorable little bruins come packed with fruity flavor. Each piece includes the recognizable shape that make these a popular go-to snack for kids and adults alike. Our Haribo gummy bears can be purchased in a bulk candy pack! You get more irresistible morsels to enjoy at home or share with guests. This size is perfect for use in treat bags at birthday parties or to distribute at picnics, school events and other gatherings. They are conveniently packaged so you can hide a few in your purse, pocket or include them in your child\'s school lunch. You\'ll never have to go hungry when your sweet tooth craves the soft, juicy taste of classic gummy bears when you buy our bulk candy box!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-original-gold-gummi-bears.jpg', '1961~haribo-original-gold-gummi-bears.jpg', 'haribo-gold-bears-24ct'),
(1962, 'Hershey\'s Assorted Miniature Chocolate Bars', 139.99, '25', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'Good things come in small packages. But they can certainly come in big ones too! And this bulk assortment of Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate, Hershey\'s Dark Chocolate, Mr. Goodbar, and Krackel mini candy bars is definitely an example of a very good thing. Founded in 1894, Hershey has been pumping out delicious candy bars long before any of us were around to enjoy them. That\'s why with their time-tested quality and handcrafted taste, you\'ll be snacking happily for a long time. And now with this bulk bag, you\'ll be able to get your entire family\'s favorite candy bars in one package.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-assorted-miniature-chocolate-bars-25lbs_2.jpg', '1962~hersheys-assorted-miniature-chocolate-bars-25lbs_2.jpg', 'hersheys-miniature-chocolate-bars-bulk-case'),
(1963, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops Large', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Chewy Sugar Daddy caramel pops offer the best of everything when it comes to sweet snacking. These mouthwatering delights produce big flavor that no caramel fanatic can resist! The beauty is in the taste and the design. Each piece includes a generous bar of creamy caramel candy perched atop a convenient disposable stick. Simply peel the bright yellow wrapper and enjoy golden caramel confection to your heart\'s content without the gooey mess!Anytime is a great time to buy Sugar Daddy candy! Give them away during holidays, hide them in party favors or keep them around the pantry for days when you\'re craving something smooth and sweet. Since 1925, Sugar Daddies have been the go-to candy for caramel lovers. New sizes have been introduced over the years, but none compare to the large Sugar Daddy caramel pop. Take your mouth on a saccharine vacation with a box of nostalgic Sugar Daddy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', '1963~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-large'),
(1964, 'Haribo Roulette Candy', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Haribo roulette gummies put a fun spin on snack time! These tempting confections come in convenient tube shaped packages that fit almost anywhere. Every piece forms a chewy disc with round edges and a solid middle. Bite down and experience the soft, smooth texture that makes Haribo gummies so delectable. If that\'s not enough gummy goodness for you, you\'ll also love the different flavors and colors that are included in every pack!Our Haribo roulette candies are the perfect blend of exciting style and practical design for young and old alike. Adults will appreciate how compact and convenient they are while children will love the sugary taste that is packed into every piece. Now you can get all the roulette gummies you want with our bulk candy package! Keep your snack cabinet or pantry well stocked or use them for special events like birthday parties, holiday gatherings, picnics and school activities!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-roulette-gummy-candy.jpg', '1964~haribo-roulette-gummy-candy.jpg', 'roulette-36ct'),
(1965, 'Toblerone Milk Chocolate Bar 12.6oz', 99.99, '10', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'A triangular chocolate bar in a triangular package with lovely retro graphics â€“ with such a striking look, it\'s no wonder Toblerone has stayed so popular. Normally it would be unwise to judge a candy by its wrapper, but Toblerone has proven itself a high-quality chocolate confection, and the alpine motif on the label reminds every chocolate lover that Toblerone confections are part of the reason Swiss chocolates are considered among the world\'s finest.The prism package of the Toblerone milk chocolate bar protects a luxurious chocolate candy bar flavored with delicate additions of honey and almond. Instantly recognizable as a top-of-the-line chocolate brand, each Toblerone bar makes an ideal portable dessert which is perfect for sharing with a friend â€“ if, that is, you can bring yourself to sacrifice a piece of its goodness!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/toblerone_12.6.jpeg', '1965~toblerone_12.6.jpeg', 'toblerone-milk-chocolate-bar'),
(1966, 'Payday Bars', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Cha-ching! The cash is rolling in with every bite of these delectable, crunchy Payday Bars. Filled with crunchy, whole peanuts and a delicious caramel nougat, it\'s no wonder why people around the world look forward to bite after bite of these rich treats. Introduced to candy bar loves for the first time in 1932, customers have been cashing in on these confections ever since! Bring some home to your candy bar and nut-lovers, spoil trick-or-treaters with a handful of these bars, or even crumble them into baked goods for an extra touch of yum! You\'ll feel like you struck it rich with every bite.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/paydaybars-24ct.gif', '1966~paydaybars-24ct.gif', 'payday-bars'),
(1967, 'Big Hunk Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'What a hunk! A Big Hunk Bar that is. These attractive candy bars are a delicious and old fashioned treat from the 1950s. With yummy honey-sweetened nougat and rich roasted peanuts, this candy is also surprisingly low fat! Fall for this handsome candy bar time after time. Bring some to a birthday party to surprise every guest, give some to a loved one on Valentine\'s Day to get a few laughs, or even keep them around the house to crumble into baked goods and make them extra attractive. This delicious candy bar can do it all and more with its muscley, nutty crunch and creamy, chewy nougat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/i/big-hunk-bars-24ct_2.jpg', '1967~big-hunk-bars-24ct_2.jpg', 'big-hunk-bars'),
(1968, 'Sesame Seed Snaps', 19.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Sezme sesame snaps are an amazingly delicious treat that\'s also good for you! If you simply can\'t decide between sweet and salty, you can enjoy both in every bite with these bar shaped confections.Each is packed with savory sesame seed flavor that\'s complemented by a touch of sugary goodness. They come individually wrapped so they stay fresh until it\'s time to snack. Our bulk Sezme sesame snaps are an excellent alternative food to chocolaty or overly sugary treats.Eat better while satisfying your cravings. This Poland-born treat is cholesterol free and gluten free. Take a bite and experience the pleasant crunch and satisfying flavor that taste buds crave. Our bulk sesame snaps box is a must-have for daily snacking.Use them to pack healthier lunches for your family or keep them as a quick and easy after school snack. Sesame seed candy also makes a great Christmas stocking stuffer!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/e/sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', '1968~sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', 'sesame-seed-snaps'),
(1969, 'Giant Smarties 1.2oz', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Giant Smarties candy is the best way to enjoy this popular treat. Each disc shaped piece offers a tart flavor that\'s fun to munch on! Every kid loves to bite down on crunchy, crumbly Smarties. Our large size gives you bigger pieces that last even longer!A generous helping of Smarties are carefully stacked then wrapped in clear plastic which proudly displays the candy\'s name in big red letters. Just untwist an end and prepare for a totally tart treat!Bulk Smarties give you more individual packs to share, give or eat. Stow a box in the pantry as an easy snack when you\'re short on time. You can also keep them at the office to pass around among coworkers. Giant Smarties are a great reward for children as well! Give them out during school activities and events or use them in party favors for kids\' birthdays, family reunions and holidays!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/giant-smarties-12oz-36ct.gif', '1969~giant-smarties-12oz-36ct.gif', 'giant-smarties-box'),
(1970, 'Rocky Road Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Get ready for a bumpy ride! Because this delicious candy bar, Rocky Road, is packed with potholes of deliciousness. Each classic bar is filled with luscious, puffy marshmallow, creamy and delicious milk chocolate, big chunks of roasted cashews, and rich, crispy malt. With 24 candy bars per box, you\'ll have a lot of chewing to do! Bring these to a baseball game for a filling candy that will get you through every inning. Buy some for a cashew and chocolate fan. Even stock yourself up for upcoming Halloween trick-or-treaters. No matter how you enjoy these classic candy bars, your taste buds are in for a wild ride!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rocky-road-bars-24ct_2.gif', '1970~rocky-road-bars-24ct_2.gif', 'rocky-road-bars'),
(1971, 'Twix Bars', 39.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Twix candy bars are sweet, crunchy and sure to satisfy even the most demanding cravings! This hugely popular Mars candy includes a crisp biscuit center that\'s topped in smooth caramel. The outside is smothered in an irresistible blanked of rich milk chocolate.Twix may be considered a modern treat, but its roots date back to the 1960s when it was first sold in the United Kingdom. It arrived in the United States within the next decade and has become a mainstay among candy lovers!Our convenient bulk Twix box is the best way to get more of the confection you love. You get a giant box packed with full sized candy bars. Each is individually wrapped, just like you would buy them at the grocery store! The difference is you get them at a great price and all at once so you always have a Twix candy bar ready to go when you\'re feeling hungry!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/w/twix_bars.jpeg', '1971~twix_bars.jpeg', 'twix-bars'),
(1972, 'Chuckles Candy', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Knee slappers. Lip smackers. Hilarious comics of the candy world. These funny Chuckles Candies are a barrel full of laughs! Chortle with some cherry, orange, lemon, lime, and licorice soft gelly candies dusted with supremely sweet sugar. They are a great way to make your kids smile, look pretty set out in a bowl, and will put all your guests in good humor with every taste of these. With 24 boxes per order, you\'ll be laughing yourself silly for snack times to come! Just see if you can keep a straight face when faced with these delicious, Chuckle\'s Candy jellies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chuckles-candy-24ct.gif', '1972~chuckles-candy-24ct.gif', 'chuckles-box'),
(1973, '100 Grand Bars', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', '1 Grand bars can really make you feel like you have a lot of money. These bars are nothing short of great. They have caramel, milk chocolate, and puffed rice. This means that you can ensure that they taste absolutely wonderful. These would be great when used at a financial event that you were having, or any other event for that matter. Consider even giving them out as Halloween candy, and really leave the trick-or-treaters pleased at what you have given them. There are 36 in a box of these and each bar is wrapped individually with a red colored wrapper. This helps to ensure that you can eat them or use them when it is best for you and still know that the bars will be fresh when you are ready for them. So why not delight your taste buds with one of these great bars of fun candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/n/one-hundred-grand-bars.jpg', '1973~one-hundred-grand-bars.jpg', '100-grand-bars'),
(1974, 'U No Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'U-No bars are a tasty treat made by the Annabelle Candy Company. Every chewy bite is sure to satisfy even the most demanding taste buds. U-No bars also make a great summer treat when frozen. Simply place in the freezer until solid then enjoy as a unique candy-popsicle!Our bulk U-No box will give you many bars to enjoy at home or with a crowd. Serve them to guests, keep them as a quick snack or hand them out as party favors or Halloween candy. They make great stocking stuffers, Easter basket candy or a special candy reward for students.Simply called Ã’Annabelle\'sÃ“, the company was founded in 1950 and named for the owner\'s daughter. Annabelle\'s began producing popular confections including a Rocky Road bar. In 1978 they added a number of products including the U-No bar. This new creation features a truffle style filling combined with crushed almonds. Everything is smothered in silky milk chocolate.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/u/-/u-no-bars-24ct.gif', '1974~u-no-bars-24ct.gif', 'u-no-bars'),
(1975, 'Zero Bars', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Zero candy bars are a delightful treat that brings together flavors that are not often combined. This unique confection was originally created in 1920 and quickly became known for its white color.The surface is covered in a smooth layer of white fudge while the middle is composed of savory caramel, almond nougat and delicious peanut. The Zero Bar we know today began as the Double Zero bar but was later renamed to its current moniker in 1934.Zero started out as part of the Hollywood Brands candy company but changed hands multiple times.Today it belongs to the famous Hershey family of candies. Now you can enjoy the sweet, hearty taste of a Zero bar anytime you like! Just order a bulk candy box so you always have individually wrapped bars ready to serve and enjoy! Zero bars also make great gifts and favors for parties and holiday events!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/z/e/zero-bars-24ct.gif', '1975~zero-bars-24ct.gif', 'zero-bars'),
(1976, 'Whoppers', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Ladies and gentlemen. Boys and girls. What we have here on CandyStore.com is the original malted milk ball, better known as Whoppers! If you\'re clapping you hands with glee and salivating at the thought, then we have another juicy tid bit of information for you: they come in bulk.Stock your pantry full of these Whoppers boxes and you\'ll have enough to grab when your family watches a movie on the couch, you head out to a baseball game or sporting event or just have a colossal sweet tooth to contend with. Order your supply of Whoppers today and start enjoying them ASAP!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/whoppers-24ct.gif', '1976~whoppers-24ct.gif', 'whoppers-packs');
INSERT INTO `candy` (`id`, `title`, `price`, `amount`, `units`, `category`, `description`, `original_image_url`, `local_image`, `page`) VALUES
(1977, 'Rolo', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Rolo\'s have been a favorite candy for many since childhood. It seems that these great candies have been around forever. After all what is not to love about them. They have caramel on the inside and are coated on the outside with wonderful tasting chocolate. These great candies also come in rolls so that you are able to open up, and just starting popping them in to your mouth. These will be great for kids or adults. Many people will find that these are almost addicting as they are able to really please their taste buds. You can give these out as candy for Halloween or even use them for stocking stuffers at Christmas time if you are looking for something that nearly everyone is sure to enjoy. What better way to be able to get the great combine flavor of caramel and chocolate then to partake in Rolo candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rolo-36ct.gif', '1977~rolo-36ct.gif', 'rolo'),
(1978, 'Mountain Bars', 15.99, '15', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'If you\'re afraid of heights, you\'ll just have to get over it and try a taste of our amazing Mountain Bar! These peanut butter, cherry and original Mountain Bars flavors will send your taste buds to a higher elevation of deliciousness.Since Mountain Bars come individually wrapped and in three different flavors, you\'ll be able to make everyone in your home happy when you bring a big box of these candies home. Add some to a dessert table, bring some on a ski trip, or just enjoy these classic candies when you want a sweet fix you\'ll love.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/t/mtn_bar_caddy_peanut_btr_open.jpg', '1978~mtn_bar_caddy_peanut_btr_open.jpg', 'peanut-butter-mountain-bar'),
(1979, 'Skittles Sour', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'If you are looking for a new twist on skittles then you should try the sour skittles. These are fun and exciting for people of all ages. They also come in many different colors such as pink, purple, green, blue, and yellow. This means that you will get to enjoy a variety of colors and flavors. The texture of these is the same as the regular skittles meaning that they are soft but chewy. The main difference that you will notice with these is that they have sour coating on the outside of them that makes for their unique sour taste. The flavors that you get from these are fruity and are much like the classic flavors that you find but they are able to provide you with that extra kick. This is one candy that is sure to get your taste buds going in high gear. If you are looking for something fun this is certainly what you need.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-sour-24ct_1.jpg', '1979~skittles-sour-24ct_1.jpg', 'skittles-sour'),
(1980, 'Abba Zaba Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'This candy\'s name will roll right off your tongue and make you want to come back for more! Abba Zabba Candy Bars are a genius mix of taffy and peanut butter that you will love. Around since the 192s, this historic candy bar has a taxi cab-esque wrapper that will remind you of the \'\'roaring\'\' 2s in New York City. Get yourself some for an upcoming Great Gatsby themed party, to wrap up for a grandparent who loves this nostalgic taste, or to introduce a taste of the past to your family. With 24 candy bars per order, you\'ll have enough to go around!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/b/abba-zabba-bars-24ct_3.jpg', '1980~abba-zabba-bars-24ct_3.jpg', 'abba-zaba-bars'),
(1981, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '1981~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(1982, 'Key Lime Pie Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you pop a piece of key lime pie candy into your mouth, your taste buds will burst with citrus sweetness. It\'s like taking a trip to the beautiful, balmy Florida Keys without even leaving your home or office. These delicious green and white hard candies are perfect for any occasion, whether you want a refreshing tropical taste on a hot summer day or you want to remind yourself of the beach in the middle of winter.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', '1982~key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', 'key-lime-pie-hard-candy'),
(1983, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '1983~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(1984, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '1984~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(1985, 'chocolate starlight mints thumbnail', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Chocolate starlight mints are a new and amazing take on a classic candy. Everyone loves the refreshing flavor of the traditional hard mint, now add chocolate.Starlight mints, which are also sometimes called pinwheel mints, feature a lovely white background with bold red stripes. Our chocolate starlight mints take that same elegant pattern and use it on a dark background with brilliant green stripes instead.Now you can enjoy that delicious minty taste with a touch of savory chocolate. Each round mint is crafted using solid hard candy. This allows them to provide the flavor candy lovers adore in a long lasting treat. Each mint is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can admire their dark beauty before you open the first one up!Pour them into glass jars or candy dishes and serve to guests, use them in the office candy jar or make your gingerbread houses more unique with these tasty decorations!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', '1985~chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', 'chocolate-starlight-mints'),
(1986, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Don\'t bite down on one of these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers! These hard candies are great for savoring a ton of sweetness for a long time.Buy a bulk bag of Jaw Busters hard candies for the little ghouls and goblins coming around the neighborhood on Halloween, or keep them around when you\'re craving something sweet for yourself. You can keep a bag of Jawbreakers in a wide assortment of colors and flavors all year long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', '1986~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-wrapped'),
(1987, 'Bulk Assorted Fruit Lollipops', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Lollipop, lollipop, oh lolli , lolli, lolli  Sorry, we\'re getting carried away with ourselves. It happens a lot here. It\'s just that we\'re so passionate about these scrumptious suckers that it makes us break out in song. They don\'t require a trip to the doctor and they come in bulk, so these pops are the perfect choice for any occasion. Stock up for your child\'s next party or put them in a jar on your desk for lucky coworkers to snack on. You\'ll quickly become a favorite in the office! With a light, sweet, fruity flavor, in a rainbow of colors, everyone can enjoy a mouthful of deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1987~lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'lollipops-bulk-fruit'),
(1988, 'Sour Fruit Balls Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Sour. Check. Colorful. Check. Fruity and delicious. Check, check! We\'ve got everything you need here for the makings of a great bulk candy selection.  Individually wrapped, these candies make tasty treats for parties, as filler candy, or just to have around the house for a qick fix of sweetness.With over 80 hard candies per pound, there\'s enough sweetness to treat all of your friends and family. Every time you snack from this bag, choose from yummy red, orange, yellow, green, and purple. Everyone who hears the crinkle of their wrappers will come running for more. And because of their perfect size, one after another can be enjoyed.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', '1988~sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', 'sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy'),
(1989, 'Andes Mints', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Ande\'s mints make the perfect welcome snack for any home, office, or restaurant. Whether your guests want to freshen their breath after they\'ve had a meal, or you\'d just like to make them feel at home with something sweet, these are the treats for you. A perfect blend of creamy milk chocolate and mint filling make these tiny sandwiches of sweetness the perfect refreshment, and they\'re individually wrapped, so there\'s no danger of spreading anyone\'s germs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', '1989~andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', 'andes-mints'),
(1990, 'Butterscotch Buttons Candy', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'These candies are cute as a button! Maybe that\'s because these Butterscotch Candy Buttons come in beautiful, individually wrapped gold wrappers and are a lovely bright yellow color that candy fans love. Around since the 1800s, butterscotch has built up a tasty reputation throughout the decades and continues to please candy lovers near and far. Try these little, rich sweets out for your next candy buffet bar, crush them and sprinkle them on top of cookies and baked goods for a sweet surprise, or even fill your candy dishes for an olde timey feel every snacker can enjoy. These hard candies are sure to \'\'butter you up\'\' with their irresistible flavor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', '1990~butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'butterscotch-buttons'),
