(1999, 'Spearmint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'A classic concept with a colorful twist. Try our Spearmint Starlight Mints as a complementary addition to your traditional red and white peppermints. Their cool, sharp spearmint flavor in addition to their lovely green and white coloring contrasts to make them a lovely and refreshing selection for any candy bowl. Make your holiday gingerbread house extra special with these green and white mints. Or stash some in your purse for a sweet, minty treat. We can\'t deny the holiday cheer these mints give us and we hope that they will inspire the same, bright happiness in everyone you share them with.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', '1999~spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', 'spearmint-starlight-mints'),
