(2223, 'Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops', 26.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Quite possibly the pretties treat available on CandyStore.com, these Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops are sure to invoke a lot of smiles. What\'s the first thing that comes to mind, when you look at these lollies? A beach ball, right? This makes them perfect for beach-themed parties and weddings. They will cause shrieks of excitement from little ones and they can bring out the inner child in anyone.These Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops are 1 inch in diameter, so they last a really long time. Creamy white balls get swirled in bright pink stripes for a look anyone will be charmed by. These suckers are not just pretty though. Their delicious strawberry flavor will have you reaching into the candy jar a little more often.Decorate a birthday cake with these or make bouquets of them for centerpieces by stabbing the sticks in green floral foam. They are perfect for baby showers, kids\' parties, and Valentine\'s Day.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', '2223~pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', 'pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large'),
(2224, 'Cherry Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Cherry Blow Pops are super sweet and a popular treat for candy lovers of all ages! This exciting snack is actually two confections in one. Each includes a disposable stick tipped in an orb of delightful hard candy.The center is filled with a gob of smooth chewing gum. Lick and nibble away until you reach the chewy middle! Your lollipop will go longer when there\'s bubblegum waiting inside!Blow Pops are one of the most popular types of lollipops sold in the United States. It\'s easy to see why once you taste one for yourself. Our bulk Blow Pops in cherry give you many individually wrapped pieces that are convenient for events, birthday parties and much more!Use them to fill up treat bags for kids or keep them in your pantry as an easy sweet snack. Our Charms Blow Pops are fun, delicious and packed with juicy cherry flavor!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2224~cherry-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'cherry-blow-pops'),
(2225, 'Blow Pops from Charms', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'We have a dozen delicious Blow Pops from Charms flavors for you to choose from here in bulk! Black Cherry, Black Ice, Blue Razzberry, Cherry, Cherry Ice, Kiwi Berry Blast, Mean Green, Sour Apple, Tangerine, Watermelon, Way-2-Sour, and  Mango flavors, if you can pick just one!Whatever you choose, you\'ll have a delicious and famous hard lollipop to suck on and chewy, sweet bubblegum to enjoy once you reach the middle. These Blow Pops from Charms are a real crowd-pleaser, so pick some up and keep them around the house for when your kids\' friends come over or you need something special and sweet to savor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blow-pops-from-charms-48ct_2.jpg', '2225~blow-pops-from-charms-48ct_2.jpg', 'blow-pops-charms-flavors'),
(2226, 'Rainbow Unicorn Pops 12', 139.99, '72', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'They do exist! At least their tasty, rainbow horns do. And we love \'em. With all the colors of the rainbow, a sweet, fruity flavor and beautiful swirls, these Unicorn Pops are a delightful treat with notable heritage. The mythical tales of the unicorn date back to ancient Greece and even the Bible with stories of people glimpsing white, goat-like horses with a single, long horn. The legendary lore depicted the unicorns as a symbol of purity, hope and grace as they would heal ailments and injuries. We think these pops are just as healing as they were originally thought to be. See for yourself why they\'re so magical at your child\'s next birthday party or any special occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-72ct.jpg', '2226~rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-72ct.jpg', 'rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-inch'),
(2227, 'Green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops Lime', 14.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops are an eye-catching treat that is full of powerful sweetness. Our lollipops are made with high quality confection and offer a distinctive look that works for events, school activities and more.Instead of a basic round shape, our green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops include a length of smooth hard candy with a fabulous white and green stripe. The tube is twisted to form a tight coil that\'s long lasting and so irresistible! Bulk lollipops are the best way to get bigger quantities for special celebrations and more. Dress up tables at a birthday party or block party by putting these beautiful lollies out in a jar.Add a ribbon and tag to give as an edible stocking stuffer or Easter basket filler. Our green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops are also a great choice for shower and wedding favors! We also carry other brilliant colors so you can find the perfect twisted lollipop for your event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/e/teslas-tiny-twist-pops-green-yumjunkie.jpg', '2227~teslas-tiny-twist-pops-green-yumjunkie.jpg', 'green-tiny-tesla-twist-pops-lime'),
(2228, 'Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'These pink and blue swirled lollies are perfect for birthday parties and baby showers. You don\'t need an excuse to enjoy one though, and since they are fat-free and only 70 calories, you can indulge in them a lot more often than the real thing.Everyone knows that the best thing about going to the fair is for the sweet, sticky, and delicious cotton candy. Of course, the one bad thing about cotton candy is that it does not last very long. The moment that spun sugar touches your tongue it instantly dissolves.Not to mention, it seems to shrink before your very eyes, if it is hot or humid outside. These Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops taste just like the real thing, only they last a whole lot longer.What do Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops taste like? Well, like you pulled a handful of sticky goodness off both pink and blue rolls and popped them in your mouth together, but these are hard candy suckers, so you get to enjoy the flavor a lot longer. Not to mention, unlike the real thing, Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops are not messy to eat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/l/fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops-48ct.gif', '2228~fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops-48ct.gif', 'fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops'),
(2229, 'Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops are a new take on the classic lollipop. Blow Pops are one of the most famous treats made by Charms.This candy was first introduced during the 1970s and quickly became Charms\' bestselling confection. Each lollipop includes a generous dollop of sweet bubblegum surrounded by a thick hard candy shell perched atop a disposable stick.Lick away then enjoy a good chew with this long lasting candy! While classic Blow Pops are tasty, sometimes you want something more exotic to enjoy. Our kiwi berry lollipops offer that same unique design with a blast of flavor inspired by two sweet fruits.Each features a deep red color that\'s complemented by a matching wrapper. Simply untwist the top and prepare to take a stroll through fruit flavor paradise! Bulk Blow Pops are a must-have for children\'s birthday parties, picnics and school activities. Hand them out during holidays or keep a box at home so you always have Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops ready to eat!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/i/kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2229~kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops'),
(2230, 'Black Cherry Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'One of the newest flavors of Blow Pops is also one of the most fabulous! Bulk, display-packaged Black Cherry Blow Pops contain a heart of bubble gum within a thick shell of dark, glossy black cherry candy. It\'s two kinds of confection on one convenient stick!Popular for classroom rewards, lunch bags, and birthday parties, Blow Pops also make a delicious and nostalgia-inducing treat whenever you need something to pick up your mood. Contained in a display box that\'s great for store counters and retro candy buffets, wholesale Black Cherry Blow Pops are the perfect candy choice when you want something familiar and fun.Not too prosaic in flavor, these pops will jazz up your event or draw people to a fair booth. Bursting with flavor at the start and filled with long-lasting chewing gum, these suckers make a great on-the-go dessert!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-cherry-blow-pops-48ct_2.jpg', '2230~black-cherry-blow-pops-48ct_2.jpg', 'black-cherry-blow-pops'),
(2231, 'Wrapped Smarties Pops Jar', 16.99, '120', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'If you ever wished Smarties were bigger, then consider it granted with these Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars! With traditional Smarties candy sized up to lollipop standards and put on a stick, you can munch and crunch on these classic candies in a whole new way.If you like to mix things up in your candy routine, try these Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars! You can keep them around the kitchen for when you want a sweet snack or to reward a bookworm for a great test grade. You can even order some Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars to sell at concessions stands for school sporting events or give out in goodie bags at parties. Just be smart and order some of these luscious lollipops today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/m/smarties-pops-lollipops-alt-candystore-470x470.jpg', '2231~smarties-pops-lollipops-alt-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'smarties-pops-wrapped-jar'),
(2232, 'Cherry Ice Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Now you can get Charms Blow Pops in bulk! Our enormous box contains many individual lollipops that are a tasty treat anytime â€“ day or night!Take a few lollies with you to enjoy throughout the work day or pack them in lunches as a sweet way to end the midday meal. Our Cherry Ice Blow Pops offer intense flavor that kids and adults will love.This version of the classic Blow Pop lollipop includes the same disposable stick and hard candy shell you love with a chewy gummy center. What makes them so unique is the cool cherry taste packed into every round pop!Hand them out during school or community events or use them as Christmas stocking stuffers or Easter basket filler. Cherry Ice Blow Pops are an easy party favor as well. Add them to a treat bag or tie on a personalized tag to customize your candy gift!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2232~cherry-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'cherry-ice-blow-pops'),
(2233, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '2233~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(2234, 'Gilliam Hard Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Old fashioned hard candy sticks are the ultimate go-to treat for anyone with a sweet tooth. Stick candy has been a favorite of young and old since the mid-1800s, and it\'s no wonder why. Each piece features a unique flavor and fun colors that make every lick a memorable experience! Simply peel away the hard candy wrapper and you are ready to snack. Each piece is individually wrapped so they are easy to store and can be given as party favors or a special treat for the kids!We carry a huge list of exciting flavors so you never get bored. Try exotic pina colada, orange pineapple or rum and butter! If you prefer something simpler, classic bubblegum, peppermint, sassafras or strawberry are just as enticing. You\'ll love watching the striped candy melt away with each bite! Grab the old family photo album and your favorite flavors and relive your childhood memories with Gilliam hard candy sticks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', '2234~stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', 'old-fashioned-stick-candy-box-flavors'),
(2235, 'Peppermint Twists Mints', 19.99, '', '', 'hard-candy', 'Peppermint twists pack all of the flavor of a candy cane into a single bite-sized candy. Just seeing and tasting them will put you in the holiday spirit, no matter what time of year it is. Don\'t miss out on delicious peppermint candies all year round. Get a bag of these individually wrapped peppermint twists and liven up your home or your office. No special occasion is necessary to bring out these delicious peppermint candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', '2235~peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'peppermint-twists'),
(2236, 'Blue Foil Grape Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'These little candies contain a whole lot of flavor. They are blue in color and the wrappers that are used for them are blue as well. However, the flavor that you get from these candies is a pleasant grape flavor. This is a flavor that can be enjoyed by people of all ages and that makes it great for nearly any occasion. Since they are blue you could consider using them for a baby shower if you wanted to as well. These candies are sure to be a hit. They are hard candies and you can either suck on them or crunch on them when eating them which is great for those who like the way that hard candies feel in their mouths when they bit them. They come in a bulk bag which means that there will be plenty to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2236~blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy'),
(2237, 'Jolly Rancher Candy', 89.99, '30', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Howdy, partner. Meet the wildest and most delicious candy in the west, Jolly Ranchers! Their bright, fruity flavors and glossy, hard candy shell are sure to put a spur in your taste buds and make your mouth say, \'\'yeeehaw!\'\' In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Add some to a candy buffet bar, a birthday party goodie bag station, or just keep them around the house for a delicious sweet fix. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-main-470x470_2.jpg', '2237~jolly-ranchers-main-470x470_2.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-candy-bulk-case'),
(2238, 'Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'All kids are looking for sunshine, happiness and rainbows in their lives and when they are given Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy the sunshine is just a shiny wrapper away. It is the wrapper that first draws your attention. Who doesn\'t like a shiny present? It will be exactly like Christmas morning as you hold one of these lemony treats in your hand and start to unwrap it. As the wrapper is opened it will reveal a bright yellow hard candy treat like you dream about right in your hand. You might have wondered what sunshine tastes like, but once you try one of the Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candies you will be pretty sure that it tastes a lot like lemon. With a convenient bulk bag of treats there will be enough sunshine to share with a whole office or classroom or people. People can\'t help but smile and be in a good mood when they eat this delicious treat. This makes it a natural for wedding receptions as all people want to start their new lives with a whole lot of smiles and sunshine.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', '2238~silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', 'silver-foil-lemon-hard-candy'),
(2239, 'Assorted Rods Hard Candy', 63.99, '14.5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Get ready for a mouthful of classic deliciousness! In sour cherry, butterscotch, apple, licorice, tangerine, strawberry, peppermint, pineapple, wild cherry, and lemon, these amazing Assorted Rods Hard Candies will satisfy any sweet tooth. Covered in a crinkly, pretty cellophane wrapper, these little hard candies make a great addition to any gift basket or present. Wrap some up in goodie bags for a little one\'s birthday, set an assortment out in a candy dish, even bring some to a friend\'s house the next time you visit. The fruity rainbow of these hard candies is sure to please candy lovers of all ages.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/s/assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', '2239~assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', 'rods-hard-candy-assorted'),
(2240, 'Hard Candy Twists', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Individually wrapped in clear cellophane with a rainbow of colors within the candy, they can add a big pop of color and taste to any event. Do the twist! The Hard Candy Twists! In all of the gleaming, iridescent glory, these Hard Candy Twists are beautiful candies with huge flavor.Brighten up your household candy dishes at the end of winter in preparation for warmer temperatures that come with springtime with and order of these Hard Candy Twists. They also can be used as gorgeous wedding candy, party favors, gift basket additions, or displayed in glass jars ion your kitchen counter. Who doesn\'t love a candy that looks as lovely as it tastes?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruitie-tootie-hard-candy-twists-atkinson.jpg', '2240~fruitie-tootie-hard-candy-twists-atkinson.jpg', 'hard-candy-twists-fruitie-tootie'),
