(2243, 'Runts Candy', 94.99, '30', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Runts candy made its first appearance in the 1980s. While its fruity lineup has changed since then, its popularity has not. Every kid can recognize the fun shapes and bright colors that make Runts so unique. Our extensive collection of bulk candy includes this childhood favorite so you can get your fill of sweet fruity goodness anytime you want! Serve at kid\'s parties, take as a non-perishable snack on camping trips or set some aside to hide away at home for moments when you need a sweet fix!Our Runts candy package include all the current flavors and shapes. You\'ll love biting down on a yellow banana or savoring a tart cherry piece. Each order also includes blue raspberry, watermelon and lime. Try the smooth, sweet taste of your favorite fruits followed by the tantalizing tanginess that makes Runts candies so delectable. You don\'t have to go to a vending machine to find your favorite treat because we have Runts in bulk and ready to ship right to you!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts30lbs.jpg', '2243~runts30lbs.jpg', 'runts-bulk'),
(2244, 'Green Foil Lime Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'If you were blindfolded, you might think that this bright, citrusy candy was made from freshest, just-squeezed limes in all the land. That\'s because these Green Foil Lime Hard Candies have such a powerful lime flavor that it\'s hard to tell. Wrapped in a bright green foil, these candies make the perfect addition to a St. Patrick\'s Day party or springtime event. They look lovely tucked away in an Easter basket too and make a great filler for a green candy display. If your friends and family love the taste of lime and a beautiful emerald green color, these are the perfect candies for you.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-foil-lime-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2244~green-foil-lime-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'green-foil-lime-hard-candy'),
(2245, 'Gold Foil Orange Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Many people love the hard candies that come wrapped in foil. If you are one of these people then you will find that the orange flavored hard candy may be just what you have been looking for. These are a great color of orange and are wrapped in a foil that is gold in color which is able to make them unique and can also make you feel like you are really rolling in the money. Since the color is a festive color you will find that these will look great for any occasion that you want to use them for. This means you can use them at a party, wedding, or even a candy bar. Who would have thought that hard candies could be so full of flavor and color? These are certain to be a hit among almost everyone who has the great pleasure of being able to try them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2245~gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy'),
(2246, 'Citrus Slices Candy Assorted', 44.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Finally! We\'ve discovered a delicious candy that does grow on trees! These Citrus Slices Candies have all the delicious flavor of some of your favorite fruits and are a beautiful treat to look at. Individually wrapped, each grapefruit, lemon, lime, orange, and tangerine candy treat in green, yellow, pink, orange will make every snacker smile. Bring some to a beach party for a summery, festive treat, add some to a punch to add a burst of bright color and sweet flavor, or even wrap some up in a gift bag for a fruity surprise. These classic citrus slice candies will please every boy and girl.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/citrus-slices-candy-bulk-10lb_1.jpg', '2246~citrus-slices-candy-bulk-10lb_1.jpg', 'citrus-slices-candy'),
(2247, 'Lifesavers Hard Candy 5 Flavors 41oz', 13.99, '', '', 'hard-candy', 'Lifesavers hard candy brings big flavor in a little package. There\'s a lot to love in every bag of Lifesavers, especially if you have hard time picking out just one flavor. You can taste all your favorites with our enormous bulk Lifesaver bag! This package offers a great value with more of the hard candy you love. Order for at home or bring a bag into the office or worksite so you can share with everyone! Teachers can reward their students with a sweet treat and parents can fill treat bags with lifesavers for parties and other events.Lifesavers are more than just a hard candy: they are an edible piece of the past. These renowned sweets were originally made in 1913. Things were different back then and it wasn\'t until 1925 that the iconic hole was added to each disc. Today you can get all the fruity flavor you want with our bulk Lifesaver package!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/f/5flavors41oz.jpg', '2247~5flavors41oz.jpg', 'lifesavers-hard-candy-41ct'),
(2248, 'Claey\'s Root Beer Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'We\'re rooting for these classic candies. That\'s because Claey\'s Root beer Old-Fashioned Candy Drops are completely coated in crystally, crunchy sugar granules that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Beyond the saccharine coating, lies a delicious hard candy. They\'ll take you back to a warm, summer\'s day of sipping a refreshing root beer float. Stock up on some to add to root beer treats, add to a gift basket, or put out on the Thanksgiving table. Among root beer, Claey\'s favorite flavors include green apple, licorice, natural horehound, watermelon, lemon, and wild cherry. They\'ll look lovely in your coffee table candy dish or set out in a jar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', '2248~root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', 'root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2249, 'C. Howard\'s Mints', 22.99, '24', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Get a taste of the olden days with this bulk selection of C. Howard\'s Mints! In vintage flavors of lemon, peppermint, spearmint, and unique violet, you\'ll have the pleasure of tasting a bit of history. Their cute, retro wrappers add a vintage feel to their deliciousness and make them perfect for a nostalgic candy selection. These little candies have been around since the 1930s and have graced both old and new candy store shelves. Give your friends and family a sample of a tried and true candy that has stood the test of time with a box of these today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-howards-mints-24ct_2.gif', '2249~c-howards-mints-24ct_2.gif', 'c-howards-mints'),
(2250, 'Napoleon Sour Bon Bons Candy', 49.99, '7', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'If you love bonbons and sour candy, now you can have both in a single bite-sized confection! This exciting treat is sure to make even the most resilient lips pucker up.Every piece consists of a delightful round orb of solid candy with a gentle texture that\'s pleasantly tart on the tongue. Each assortment of Napoleon sour bon bons comes in a number of eye-catching colors, like yellow, orange, green and white.Every Napoleon bon bon is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can see the colorful candy inside before you open the next piece. The wrapper includes a classic logo printed on one side with elegant stripes along each side.All it takes is a quick twist to reveal the delicious treat and experience super sour flavor. Our bulk Napoleon sour bon bons gives you many candies that are perfect for businesses, guests, special events and party favors.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/s/assorted-napoleons-bon-bons.jpg', '2250~assorted-napoleons-bon-bons.jpg', 'napoleon-sour-bon-bons-candy'),
(2251, 'Life Savers Candy', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Laver Savers candies have been around for many years. They are enjoyed by everyone from children to adults. These great candies are available in many different colors such as red, purple, green, orange, white, and even yellow. You can get many different flavors such as wild cherry, grape, lime, pineapple, orange, and even butter rum. You are sure to find a flavor that you are able to enjoy. You are also sure to find that these small hard, crunchy candies are able to provide a great deal of taste that you are sure to be pleased with. These candies are great for birthday parties, Halloween, weddings, and more. They come in rolls and you can choose from multi-flavored rolls, or the ones that one has a single flavor depending on your preference. There is nothing that can take you back to your childhood more than the great taste of Life Savers.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', '2251~life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', 'life-savers-rolls'),
(2252, 'Charms Sour Balls Tins', 42.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'When it comes to making friends, candy is a great ice breaker. Choosing the right candy will determine how successful you are at this endeavor. Charms Sour Balls are definitely the right candy. These delicious hard candy treats make the young happy and the old nostalgic. There is a power in the sour ball that will win friends because it is the perfect combination of both sweet and sour that appeal to everyone. They come in cherry, grape, lemon, lime and of course orange. When you see a tin of these delicious treats, you can\'t help think of Christmas and other celebrations. Once a can is open it is nearly impossible to stop the smiles and good times. With a whole tin of this candy on your side, you will be able to win a whole lot of new friends and in the end, would you want to be friends with someone who didn\'t like Charms Sour Balls?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', '2252~charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', 'charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz'),
(2253, 'Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags', 39.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Leave it to Jolly Ranchers to provide a delicious, colorful and fun treat that is also good for you. While providing all of the expected value expected from Jolly Rancher, they upped the ante by making their snacks sugar free as well! The classic candy comes individually wrapped to keep in the unique freshness. Each piece of candy provides a classic blast of fruit refreshment without the worry of taking in any extra sugar that will make parents and dentists smile. This treat can be enjoyed all by yourself or with a bunch of your friends. Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags make it always seem like a party. Enjoy the explosion of fruit flavor in your mouth without any of the guilt. Get the best Jolly Rancher hard candy that has your favorite flavor, watermelon, apple, grape or raspberry. Not only are these treats sugar free but each candy contains only 1 calories, which means that you can enjoy your fruity flavored candies all day long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', '2253~jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-sugar-free-candy-bags'),
(2254, 'Claey\'s Watermelon Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'We think these candies are \'\'de-vine.\'\' That\'s because these amazing Watermelon Cherry Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops are the most delicious candy in the patch! Dusted in powdery, sweet sugar, these bright red candies pack a serious punch of watermelon flavor that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Bring some to a holiday gathering that needs a dose of festive red, drop a few into a cold lemonade or punch for a sweeter, fruity flavor, add them to a Fourth of July dessert table, or make a Valentine\'s Day gift even yummier. With this 1 pound order of watermelon candies, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.gif', '2254~watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.gif', 'watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2255, 'Charms Squares Candy', 24.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Cherry, Grape, Lemon, Lime, Orange, and Raspberry combine to make one incredibly delicious pack of treats in this Charms Squares Candy order. You\'ll be in for a surprise every time you unwrap one of the packet\'s 10 candies and stuff it into your mouth.Charms are known for their sour sweet treats and this supply isn\'t short in any of the above. If this sounds like a match made in heaven for you, then why not order yourself some of our Charms Squares Candies today? They\'ll wow all of your guests, impress your family and keep you snacking with a smile on your face for days and days.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-squares-candy-20ct.gif', '2255~charms-squares-candy-20ct.gif', 'charms-squares'),
(2256, 'Aquarium Hard Candy Fish', 49.99, '15', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Where does the fish keep his money? In the river bank! These Aquarium Hard Candies are a lovely reminder of summertime and the beautiful ocean and will make every candy lover smile. They\'re just as intricate as the natural ocean variety, but a million times more delicious. In a variety of colors and flavors from under the sea there\'s a flavor for every beach-lover. Use them for a luau-themed party. Throw a beachside bash for all of your friends. Even enjoy one while you\'re sitting on the hot sand. Or give them to a fishing fanatic you know. Just make sure you\'re not \'\'shellfish\'\' with these delicious candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/q/aquarium-hard-candy-fish-candystore.jpg', '2256~aquarium-hard-candy-fish-candystore.jpg', 'aquarium-hard-candy-fish'),
(2257, 'Runts Theater Size', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Runts theater boxes are a fun way to enjoy this fruit candy. There are so many reasons to love this Willy Wonka favorite.Runts are small hard candies that are shaped to resemble their real fruit counterparts. Each package contains brilliantly colored bananas, berries and much more! You\'ll find classic flavors like lime, strawberry and banana combined with two new flavors: watermelon and blue raspberry!Our bulk Runts pack contains many individual theater boxes that are ideal for gift giving, events and much more! Make family movie night even more exciting by serving up theater box candy Ã just like the kind they sell at the cinema concession stands!Spread the fruity love by giving Runts as Christmas stocking stuffers or use them to add unique style when decorating cakes, cookies and other baked goods. There\'s so much just one little Runts can do! Also check out our other Willy Wonka theater box candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts---theater-size-12ct_1.jpg', '2257~runts---theater-size-12ct_1.jpg', 'runts-theater-size'),
(2258, 'Lite Pink Foil Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Treat your taste buds to tutti frutti flavor with our light pink foil wrapped hard candies! This simple treat is great for any occasion. Hard candy is popular because it last a long time and is really easy to take with you.Grab a handful and bring along while running errands. Hide them in your desk drawer so you have an easy sweet snack while at work. Our hard candy comes individually wrapped in a gorgeous metallic foil. This version features a brilliant pink hue that makes each piece look luxurious.Hard candy wrapped in foil looks stunning in candy dishes and jars. Offer to customers by leaving them at the counter (or wherever you do business). Use them to create beautiful wedding favors or add them to baby shower favors for girls! Our bulk pink hard candy package gives you plenty of bite-sized pieces for gift giving, sharing or simple snacking.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lightpinkfoilwrapped.jpeg', '2258~lightpinkfoilwrapped.jpeg', 'pink-foil-peach-hard-candy'),
(2259, 'Life Savers Pep O Mint', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Is your mouth screaming \'\'SOS\'\' for a breath freshening treat? Well, these Life Savers Pep-O-Mint and Wint-O-Green are here to save the day! Let them toss you a life preserver for your taste buds with their fresh minty flavor and classic \'\'O\'\' shaped form. This hero of the candy world has been around since 1912 and has saved mouths all over the world. Pep-O-Mint was the first flavor and quickly made an impression in the mouths of many. Since then, a variety of fruity and other mint flavors have been invented. Try these minty rolls on for size and see for yourself if you think they\'re worthy of their heroic name!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', '2259~mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', 'mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct'),
(2260, 'Green Apple Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Claey\'s old-fashioned green apple candy drops are a tasty treat that comes with history. The brand has been producing high quality classic treats since 1919. For three generations, Claey\'s Candy has been giving the world some of the best old time confections available.Their selection includes a number of nostalgic favorites, like fudge, Chocolate Charlie and irresistible old fashioned candy drops. Green apple candy drops are available in bulk quantities so you get more juicy flavor in every package! These round little tidbits are a great choice for family gatherings like reunions, picnics and birthday parties.Share them with loved ones when they come to visit or keep a sweet stash on hand to satisfy apple and sugar cravings. Candy has become a longstanding tradition in the Claey family, and now it can become a tradition in your family! Order your bulk green apple candy drops today and enjoy the memories packed into every piece.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_1.jpg', '2260~green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_1.jpg', 'green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2261, 'Lifesavers Butterrum', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Butter rum Lifesavers candy is a sweet treat with classic personality. While it may not be as outrageous as wild cherry or as refreshing as wint-o-green, butter rum is packed with tasty sweetness that satisfies like no other candy can. This rich blend of flavors is even better when packed into each hard candy hoop. Lifesavers are easy to enjoy and come in a convenient tube package that you can place in a purse, pocket, desk drawer or wherever you may be when cravings hit!The history of the Lifesaver candy begins in 1912 when Clarence Crane invented the hard mint version. At the time he needed a pill manufacturer to produce the shape of each piece. It wasn\'t until 1925 that the familiar hole was added, creating the popular donut shape we all know and love today. Our bulk Lifesaver candy boxes are a great choice for offices, schools or anyone planning an event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lifesaversbutterrum.jpg', '2261~lifesaversbutterrum.jpg', 'lifesavers-butterrum-20ct'),
(2262, 'Spree Candy', 37.99, '36', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'It is a dilemma as old as Spree candies themselves: eat just one and enjoy its sweet-and-sour flavor individually, or snack your way through the whole roll?The carefree name and colorful purple-based packaging make it no surprise that Spree is one of the Willy Wonka Candy Company confections, and there are some sweet tooths among us who feel that the candy disks unique texture and bold flavor make them the best. This box of bulk Spree rolls offers the colorful sweets in a convenient form great for traveling.Each cylindrical package is a party favor or picnic dessert in itself! The bright colors of this oh-so-simple sour sweet are instantly appealing to kids â€“ and nostalgic to those who grew up in the days of rainbow confections gorgeously assorted in sweet-shop jars.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spree-candy-36ct_1.gif', '2262~spree-candy-36ct_1.gif', 'spree-candy'),
(2263, 'Altoids Cinnamon', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Altoids cinnamon candy are more than just a curiously strong mint. These refreshing treats are a confection that comes with a long, rich history. The original recipe was created by a London-based company in the 1780s, when King George III sat on the throne. The product\'s high concentration of peppermint oil is what inspired the popular slogan we all know and love today. Altoids are currently available in six different flavors, including cinnamon. The storage tin was introduced in the 1920s and still helps keep each mint fresh and clean, even while on the go. Our bulk mint package is a convenient option for anyone who never wants to go without their favorite candy! Hide a tin in your purse or pocket or keep them in the glove box. The larger quantity is also great to share at the office or while on the job. Invigorate your mouth with Altoids cinnamon mints!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoidscinnamon.jpg', '2263~altoidscinnamon.jpg', 'altoids-cinnamon-12ct'),
(2264, 'Lifesavers Wild Cherry', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Wild cherry Lifesavers is a quick and easy snack that everyone can enjoy! Each hard candy piece is filled with sweet cherry flavor. Just open the end and treat your taste buds to the irresistible taste of fresh picked cherry sweetness! Lifesavers aren\'t just delicious â€“ they are also convenient! Each box contains individual packages that you can keep anywhere. Hide them in your desk, purse, pocket or car so you always have something to satisfy your sweet tooth!Lifesavers candy is a classic confection that was created in 1912. The original hard mints were later expanded upon with wintergreen, clove, chocolate, cinnamon and violet flavors. Today we can enjoy a huge list of Lifesavers, including succulent wild cherry! Our bulk candy box makes these treats even better because you can get more hard candy to store or share. Just order a box or two and you will always have something to give guests, coworkers or clients!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/i/wildcherrylifesavers.jpg', '2264~wildcherrylifesavers.jpg', 'lifesavers-wild-cherry-20ct'),
(2265, 'Banana Heads Candy', 99.99, '30', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'What was Beethoven\'s favorite fruit? Ba-na-na-naaa. Ba-na-na-naa. We may have slipped up with that cheesy joke, but we\'re just such big fans of these Banana Heads Candies that we can\'t help ourselves! These adorable, little yellow banana hard candies are a great treat that everyone can enjoy. Bring some home for your little monkeys to munch on. Stock up on these to add to a summertime tropical pool party. Even keep these around the house to add as decoration to the top of baked goods and ice cream sundaes. You\'ll love these little yellow fruits no matter what you do with them. Plus, they look just like Banana Runts.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/banana-heads-candy-30lbs_2.jpg', '2265~banana-heads-candy-30lbs_2.jpg', 'banana-heads-candy-bulk'),
(2266, 'SweeTarts Candy Rolls', 37.99, '36', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Make snack time more interesting with the tangy and sweet taste of SweeTarts candy! Our SweeTarts candy rolls offer the classic flavor you love in a bigger package. Each roll is individually wrapped to form a tube that fits easily into a pocket, purse or wherever you prefer to keep it.Simply tear open one end and grab a disc shaped piece from inside! SweeTarts were introduced in 1962. They were inspired by powdery Lik-M-Aid and Pixy Stix. The decision to create a compressed version came when parents complained that powdery candies were too messy. Now kids can enjoy that same tangy taste without getting powder all over their hands, clothes and faces!Our bulk SweeTarts candy rolls are perfect for special events and much more. Use them to fill up birthday party treat bags or give as a special treat during the holidays. From stocking stuffers to prizes for games, our SweeTarts are a delicious confection for the young and young at heart!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/sweetarts-candy-rolls-36ct_1.gif', '2266~sweetarts-candy-rolls-36ct_1.gif', 'sweetarts-candy-rolls'),
(2267, 'Jones Soda Carbonated Candy', 20.99, '8', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Jones Soda carbonated candy offers a new way to enjoy your favorite beverage! Classic Jones Soda is a popular choice because it is made using cane sugar instead of unhealthy high fructose corn syrup.If you enjoy a cold, refreshing Jones Soda, then you must try these unique candies. Each package includes small pill shaped pieces that are sweet and tangy with a touch of tingly carbonation. Along with a one-of-a-kind taste, Jones Soda carbonated candy also comes in an elegant branded tin. Each tine includes a black background with Jones in shimmering silver. The tin container keeps your mints fresh and easy to carry.Hide a pack in your pocket, purse, glove box or desk drawer. Jones Soda carbonated candy also makes a great gift or stocking stuffer. You can get larger quantities with our convenient Jones Soda carbonated candy in bulk! Keep a box at home or take to the office to share with coworkers and clients.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jones-soda-carbonated-candy.jpg', '2267~jones-soda-carbonated-candy.jpg', 'jones-soda-carbonated-candy-green-apple'),
(2268, 'Chocolate Covered Espresso Beans', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Did somebody order a wake up call? This double whammy of eye-opening espresso and chocolate will definitely get the job done. With their creamy dark chocolate coating and bite of brittle espresso beans, these Chocolate Covered Espresso Beans are a \'\'wowza\'\' in your mouth. Make your own ice cream and sprinkle a few handfuls of these beans into the mixer, chop them up and add them to biscotti, even drop a few in your morning cup of coffee or set them around the house for light snacking. You won\'t want to set the snooze button with a bite of one of these delectable morsels.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-espresso-beans-5lb.jpg', '2268~chocolate-covered-espresso-beans-5lb.jpg', 'espresso-beans-chocolate-covered'),
(2269, 'German Raspberries', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo German raspberries recreate the sweet taste of this popular fruit in an irresistible confection! Each bag contains a combination of red and black berry candies. Instead of sticking with plain gummies, Haribo creates a smooth, chewy center that\'s covered in dainty orbs of sugary goodness. Every bite presents two distinct textures in one tasty tidbit! Order our bulk raspberry candies for special events or snacking at home. Whether you\'re hosting a party, picnic, school event or wedding, our German raspberries are a great choice! Haribo has been serving up some of the most delectable gummy candies for nearly a century. Today their catalog includes many unique confections that offer mouthwatering flavor in little bite sized pieces. Our bulk German raspberries are easy to store so you can hide a bag in your favorite snacking spots so you\'re ready the next time your sweet tooth strikes! Haribo gummy candy will tempt taste buds and satisfy cravings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/e/germanraspberries.jpeg', '2269~germanraspberries.jpeg', 'german-raspberries-12ct');
