(2293, 'Vidal Ocean Gummies', 18.99, '18', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Make a big splash at snack time by giving the kids a taste of Vidal\'s Ocean Gummies! This fun candy is not only tasty, but also exciting to see. While regular gummy bears usually feature a solid color look, our gummy ocean creatures present a brilliant color with bright exciting colors.Each piece is shaped into a different sea creature. Our bulk package includes 18 4 count packs so the gummies are always fresh â€“ even if you don\'t open it right away! Vidal Ocean Gummies are convenient for gift giving, sharing and casual snacking.Keep a pack anywhere you might crave something sweet, like in the car, at your desk or in the pantry. Open up a few packs and pour into a candy dish to offer guests or use your gummy ocean creatures to decorate cakes and cookies for an ocean or beach themed birthday party!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/i/vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', '2293~vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', 'vidal-ocean-gummies-peg-bag'),
(2294, 'Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties Bags', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'You can almost hear the breath-freshening aaaaah of these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties. That\'s because they\'re both satisfying and low in calories. With melty chocolate covering a potently peppermint center, these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties are a serious breath of fresh air. If you love Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties but want to try a lower calorie option, these are a great choice for you! Bring some home to keep in your office drawer, put into lunch boxes or serve alongside dessert for guests to eat if they\'re watching their waistlines. Individually wrapped, these glimmering silver wrappers are ready to be ripped open so that you can devour the goodness that awaits inside!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', '2294~sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', 'sf-york-peppermint-patties'),
(2295, 'Claey\'s Horehound Drop Bags', 34.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Old fashioned Claeyâ€™s Horehound Drops are one of the most unique and timeless treats you can put in your mouth. This version helps sooth the throat with a confection thatâ€™s fat free. Each hard candy features the classic round shape produced using a mold and drop method. Horehound is produced using an herb tea thatâ€™s steeped in a copper kettle to bring out the unique mint and licorice taste of Claeyâ€™s Drops.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '2295~claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'claeys-horehound-drop-bags'),
(2296, 'Apple O\'s Gummi Rings Bag', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Trolli Apple O\'s gummy rings are the perfect candy when you\'re craving something sweet and chewy. Trolli is a longstanding favorite in the candy world. The brand was formed in 1948 and originally sold pasta and noodles.Throughout the next decade, Trolli would expand to offer a selection of jelly fruits and cream drops. Today it is a brand that is most commonly known for its delicious gummy candy!Apple O\'s gummy rings are similar to peach rings with a sour apple flavor. Each piece is round with an open center. One side is white and the other is vibrant green, just like the skin on a Granny Smith apple!Take a bite and enjoy sweet apple flavor with a touch of tangy sugar. Bulk gummy rings are a great treat to serve at events or to use in party favors. Kids love snacking with them and adults will enjoy the unique sweet and sour flavor that makes Trolli gummies so tasty!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/p/apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', '2296~apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', 'apple-os-gummi-rings-bag'),
(2297, 'Claey\'s Lemon Drop Bags', 34.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Claeyâ€™s Lemon Drops are a longstanding favorite that have been satisfying sweet cravings for decades. This traditional treat includes a bite-sized morsel of hard candy with refreshing lemon citrus flavor. Claeyâ€™s makes their confections the natural way, using California lemons. Each piece is poured into a mold then dropped to produce a unique fruit shape. Enjoy fat free hard candy anytime with Claeyâ€™s Lemon Drops!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys_lemon_drop_bags_-_24ct.png', '2297~claeys_lemon_drop_bags_-_24ct.png', 'claeys-lemon-drop-bags'),
(2298, 'Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings Bags', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Fruity and mild, the flavor of Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings is like no other candy, and the soft, chewy texture is one of the best of the gummy varieties!A bulk package of market-size Peachie O\'s bags makes these fun candy rings easy to pack for car trips and family picnics, and the bags are the perfect size for the movie theater, too! These gummi peach slices are an economical way to enjoy gummi candies on the go. Each Peachie O\'s gummi candy is dusted with sugar and consists of two pretty layers, one yellow and one two-toned red and orange to mimic the hues of real peach fuzz.They make a pretty addition to a warmly-hued candy buffet in summer or fall. Cover a layer cake in Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings for a playful (and edible) geometric decoration Ã or just slide a Peachie O on every finger and wave to your friends.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peachie-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bags_1.gif', '2298~peachie-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bags_1.gif', 'peachie-os-gummi-rings-bags'),
