(2300, 'Hawaiian Punch Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Hawaiian Punch Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/hawaiian_punch_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '2300~hawaiian_punch_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'hawaiian-punch-licorice-twists-bags'),
(2301, 'Neon Squiggles Gummi Worms', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Neon Squiggles gummy worms are fun, colorful and always ready to eat! Everyone loves the soft, chewy taste of classic gummy worms. This popular treat was actually created to honor the 60th birthday of the gummy bear.Even though they came later, gummy worms are just as delicious and preferred by many candy lovers because of their long, bendable shape! Each gummy worm includes a narrow body with rounded ends. The back is covered in a segmented pattern that looks similar to the body of a real worm. The bottom is flat so it sits upright on flat surfaces. You get multiple colors in every worm!Taste yellow, red, white and green in every Trolli Squiggles bag! Our bulk gummy worms are convenient for birthday parties and more. Use them to fill party favors or add a fun touch by decorating cakes with these chewy worm candies. Everyone will love the sweet taste and playful look of Trolli Neon Squiggles gummy worms!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/e/neon-squiggles-gummi-worms-12ct_1.gif', '2301~neon-squiggles-gummi-worms-12ct_1.gif', 'neon-squiggles-gummi-worms'),
(2302, 'Jelly Belly Assorted Sugar Free Jelly Beans Bags', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly makes it even easier to enjoy their famous jellybeans and stick to a sugar-free diet. This colorful assortment features all sugar-free jellybeans in your favorite flavors. Each piece includes the familiar coffee bean shape and smooth texture along with the authentic brand logo printed on the side. Splenda is added to the recipe to produce a sweet tasting bean without the added sugar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_assorted_sugar_free_jelly_beans_bags_-_12ct.jpg', '2302~jelly_belly_assorted_sugar_free_jelly_beans_bags_-_12ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-assorted-sugar-free-jelly-beans-bags'),
(2303, 'Grape Crush Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Grape Crush Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape_crush_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '2303~grape_crush_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'grape-crush-licorice-twists-bags'),
(2304, 'Haribo Sour Gummi Spaghetti', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo Sour S\'ghetti is unlike any pasta you have ever eaten! Don\'t worry, you won\'t need to twirl these noodles on a fork. They are enjoyed cool and can be picked up by hand. Each bag features a generous collection of wiggly, wobbly slender lengths that are similar to classic spaghetti.Each piece comes in red, white or yellow. Our bulk sour gummy spaghetti is a great choice for after school snacks, lunches or special events. Sweeten any day by grabbing a handful of chewy spaghetti gummies when you\'re craving something sweet. Each bite features the taste of sugary gummy candy that\'s smothered in a coating of sour sugar.Your taste buds will tingle when they experience this one-of-a-kind confection! Kids won\'t be able to resist playing with the long noodle-y pieces which jiggle and bend. Add to birthday party favors or find fun ways to decorate cakes and cookies with Haribo sour gummy spaghetti!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', '2304~haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', 'haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti'),
(2305, 'Hershey\'s Mini Chocolate Candy Bars', 34.99, '5', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'These bulk bags of mixed mini chocolate bars are the great, great, great, great, great grandkids of the first Hershey chocolate bars. We may have missed a few \'\'greats\'\' in there, but with the origination of the Hershey chocolate company in 1894, these confections have an impressive history that precedes us all. If you love a surprise, this mixed bag of mini Hershey\'s chocolate bars is right up your alley. Complete with a selection of Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate, Mr. Goodbar, Hershey\'s Dark Chocolate, and Krackel, you can expect something different every time you snack. With decades of success, we\'re positive that you\'ll love indulging in this famous brand.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hershey-mini-bars-small.jpg', '2305~hershey-mini-bars-small.jpg', 'hersheys-mini-chocolate-candy-bars'),
(2306, 'Peanut Butter Bars', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'Peanut butter bars candy brings you all the best parts of peanuts without all the bad stuff. Each bar includes high quality peanuts that are slow roasted until they become gold brown to bring out the natural nutty flavor. Each bite is truly an experience, with the crispy, flaky crunch that everyone loves. If you are a peanut butter fanatic, then this bar candy is your dream come true!Every peanut butter bar is individually wrapped so it\'s easy to store and share. Each includes a simple white wrapper with black stripes, gold star and a classic logo that gives each piece a nostalgic look. Keep a handful in your purse or pocket or use the in favor bags for parties and holiday events. Each tasty tidbit is packed with all the rich peanut flavor you can handle in a convenient package that you can take anywhere! Our bulk candy packs are great for school events, businesses and carnivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', '2306~peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', 'peanut-butter-bars'),
(2307, 'Hot Tamales Minis', 9.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Hold on to your taste buds! These red Hot Tamales Minis are ready to singe every last one of \'em off of your tongue. Though they may be packed in miniature movie theater boxes, every pack of these tamales are ready with a fiery punch of cinnamon that will blow you away. If you can\'t beat the heat, try adding them to a cup of tea or cocoa for a milder cinnamon fix. But if you\'re prepared for a spice that can\'t be beat, pop a few of these into your mouth at a time and feel the fire. Whatever you do, you\'ll set your mouth a-blaze with this bulk supply.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', '2307~hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', 'hot-tamales-minis'),
(2308, 'Skittles Fun Size Bulk', 99.99, '22', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'A color and flavor for every taste bud. Pack these fun size Skittles into a pinata, add them to a stocking, or slip one into your kid\'s lunchbox for a delicious afternoon surprise. Whatever you choose, everyone will love to \'\'Taste the Rainbow.\'\' Skittles have been in the US since 1979 and have evolved into a quirky brand and a household name. Their original flavors of orange, lemon, lime, grape and strawberry got a revamp in 1989 with the introduction of tropical fruit flavors. Since then, 1 new Skittles lines have been created and amazed the mouths of people all over the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-fun-size.jpg', '2308~skittles-fun-size.jpg', 'skittles-fun-size-bulk'),
(2309, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Prepare to be spoiled rotten with an overdose of creamy caramel and sugary sweetness! These Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops are an American classic that have had customers smacking their lips for years. Invented in 1925, it wasn\'t until 1932 that these famous pop got their sugary name. Give your family a taste of the olden days with some of these delicious caramels. Bring them to a party, add some to a candy buffet bar, or use them as a yummy, melty stirrer for hot chocolate. With over 48 caramel pops per box, get ready to indulge your family and friends for a long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', '2309~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops'),
(2310, 'Toblerone Mini Chocolate Bars', 45.99, '80', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Toblerone mini chocolate bars are a great idea for any party or occasion. These are small bars that have a total of three peaks made of chocolate; they are then filled using creamy nougat for a treat that is mouth watering and good. Each one of the bars is wrapped individually to help ensure that they are fresh. The shape of these bars is fun because they are not like many of the other typical candy bars that you find. Instead they are more interactive and have a lot to offer. The wrapper of these bars is a yellow color with red writing which means it can tie into many different themes if you find that you want to use it for a party. If you have never tried one of these great candies before then you have no idea just what you are missing. Your mouth is sure to be pleased when you take a bite of this wonderful candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/toblerone_mini.jpg', '2310~toblerone_mini.jpg', 'toblerone-mini-chocolate-bars'),
(2311, 'Giant Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars', 29.50, '12', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Someone must have been eating their \'\'Wheaties\'\' because these Giant Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars are ridiculously humungous and even more delicious! Have a friend who is a major chocolate fan? Want to stock up on s\'mores supplies that will last you all summer? Want to impress friends and family with a thoughtful and delicious gift basket addition? These gigantic, rich, melty chocolates can do all that and more. Around since 1894, Hershey\'s first opened their delicious doors in Pennsylvania. And ever since, their culinary perfection of some of the world\'s most famous confections has satisfied candy lovers around the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheyxl_bars.jpg', '2311~hersheyxl_bars.jpg', 'giant-hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars'),
(2312, 'Nut Goodie Bars', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Nostalgic. Classic. Vintage. You\'re a special kind of candy fan who appreciates where every sweet got its roots. With these Nut Goodie\'s, you can enjoy a taste of yesteryear in every milk chocolatey, nutty bite! Introduced in 1912, Nut Goodie hit candy store shelves for a whopping 5 cents! To this day, not much has changed about the delicious, salty, sweet nut clusters including their vintage wrapper. Add these to a 2\'s themed party for a tasty treat, share a bit of history with loved ones, or surprise your grandmother or grandfather with a taste of their youth. Whatever you do, you\'ll love these tried and true confections.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/u/nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', '2312~nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', 'nut-goodie-bars'),
(2313, 'Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'One candy that has been a favorite for many over the years and still is, is the Hershey\'s milk chocolate. These great candy bars are nothing short of delicious. There is just something about the way that these are able to melt in your mouth when you take a bite. They are smooth and wonderful. This is great if you are looking to use them to make s\'mores. They are also great all on their own. These are full sized bars that are wrapped individually. If you are one that has a sweet tooth often then you will really be able to benefit from the bulk 36 count box of them. It will ensure that you have a way to indulge in this wonderful tasting candy bar whenever you decide that you want to or need to. Nothing is better than the sweet chocolaty taste of Hershey\'s. Kids and adults are both able to enjoy this wonderful candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars-36ct_2.gif', '2313~hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars-36ct_2.gif', 'hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars'),
(2314, 'Sixlets 20 Ball Tubes', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Sixlets 20 ball tubes are the most convenient way to enjoy your favorite chocolate candy! Every stick includes a clear wrapper that holds 20 round balls in a straight line. Take a bite out of green, yellow, orange, red or brown.No matter which hue you choose, every Sixlets candy contains a smooth chocolate center surrounded by a hard candy shell. Our bulk Sixlets box contains a generous number of full tubes so you have plenty to take or share.Individually wrapped candy is perfect for traveling and events. Tuck a few in your vehicle\'s glove box, your purse or carry on. You can also display them in glass vases or trays to serve at parties, school activities and other gatherings. Buying Sixlets in bulk is also a great way to ensure that you always have an easy, tasty snack on hand when chocolate cravings hit!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', '2314~sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', 'sixlets-20-ball-tubes'),
(2315, 'Long Boys Coconut', 8.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Long Boys coconut candy sticks are a classic favorite that\'s full of rich flavor! This traditional candy originated in New Orleans, making it a staple for local children.Today, people all over the country rave about the amazing taste of these long, chewy confections. Every piece includes a stick of candy that\'s individually wrapped in a nostalgic red and yellow wrapper.Coconut Long Boys offer a unique blend of caramel and exotic coconut for a snacking experience that\'s memorable and satisfying! Untwist the wrapper and take small bites to fully enjoy the taste of this one-of-a-kind flavor combination! Kids can try stretching their Long Boy candy to see who can make the longest rope!Our bulk Long Boy coconut candy is a great choice for parties, picnics and family reunions. Use them to fill treat bags for birthdays or set out a bowl or box so adults can munch while reminiscing about their favorite childhood sweets!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', '2315~long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', 'long-boys-coconut'),
(2316, 'Snickers Bars', 46.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Full-size Snickers bars will light up practically anyone\'s eyes! A familiar candy bar made from a perfect portion of peanuts sandwiched between soft, melting caramel and delicious creamy nougat, this confection is robed in a smooth milk chocolate for a sweet finish that\'s texturally interesting and satisfying to eat. When you just have to have a mid-morning snack and instant energy is the way to go, you could do much worse than to reach for a delicious Snickers bar!These Snickers candy bars in bulk come packaged in the familiar boldly-lettered, chocolate-hued wrapper, keeping them fresh for your enjoyment. This lot of Snickers is a perfect way to stock up on your family\'s favorite game-night treat or weekend dessert. If you\'re looking to create high perceived value in welcome bags or on a candy buffet, it\'s even better â€“ everyone feels special when they\'re offered a big, nutty chocolate candy bar to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/n/snickers-bars-48ct.gif', '2316~snickers-bars-48ct.gif', 'snickers-bars'),
(2317, 'Charleston Chews Candy Bars Snack Size', 12.99, '120', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Move your feet and clap your hands for this famous confection, Charleston Chews Candy Bars! Created in 1922, this classic candy bar was named after the famous dance, The Charleston. With a chewy, vanilla nougat center covered in melty milk chocolate, these candy bars have been a favorite for years. Bring some home to your family and share a sweet treat any day of the week. They\'re also great to put in a piï¾ata, make your own sundae bar, or to keep around the house to add to the top of cupcakes and other baked treats. Let these candies dance their way into your mouth and heart today when you order this bulk bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charleston-chews-candy-snack-size-120ct_2.jpg', '2317~charleston-chews-candy-snack-size-120ct_2.jpg', 'charleston-chews-candy-snack-size'),
(2318, 'Take 5 Candy Bars', 25.99, '18', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'These are mini Take 5 candy bars that are the same a the larger versions which are already a big hit. People love the way that these taste and they are great when you find that you are craving something sweet. You will find that these are also great when it comes to finding a candy that you want to pass out at Halloween. The middle of these have peanuts and pretzels that have been dipped in peanut butter followed by caramel. It is then coated using milk chocolate. Your mouth is probably watering already and it should be, because there is just something about these that make you want more. You will find that it has a nice soft texture but it is also crunchy. This means that you are able to get the best of both worlds with this candy bar. Not to even mention the fact that you will get a little bit of sweet and salty taste as well.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/a/take_5_18ct.jpeg', '2318~take_5_18ct.jpeg', 'take-five-candy-bars'),
(2319, 'Skor Bars', 21.99, '18', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'It literally only takes one bite to be totally hooked on Skor Bars. If you are already a bit of an addict then you know this firsthand.Just looking at the bar, you think it\'s going to be a simple chocolate bar, but it\'s not. Enrobed in that creamy milk chocolate is a butter toffee center that will make your taste buds sing.You are more than welcome to chew it, if you like, but lovers of Skor Bars will tell you to let the chocolate dissolve on your tongue until the butter toffee is revealed for the full effect. This bulk supply of Skor Bars is perfect to have in the pantry for movie night or just to enjoy as a special treat.They are amazing as a topping, too. Put one in a sealed bag, crush it with a hammer, rolling pin, or whatever you have handy, and sprinkle it on cupcakes, ice-cream, frozen yogurt, and brownies. This is one treat you don\'t want to run out of!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skor-bars-18ct_1.jpg', '2319~skor-bars-18ct_1.jpg', 'skor-bars');
