(2467, 'White Gummi Bears Strawberry Banana', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Don\'t let their pristine, white color fool you. Or their dainty size. These petite Gummi Bears have the powerful strawberry banana flavor of a giant grizzly. Roar! Pretty enough for a wedding candy display, they also are right at home in a five star candy buffet or as a neutral filler candy in gift bags. With an average of 145 bears per pound, you will have an entire forest-full of flavorful friends to share with friends and family. Chewy and fruity, these Gummies are crowd pleasers. And we would like to think of them as way tastier than the average bear.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears_1.jpg', '2467~white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears_1.jpg', 'white-strawberry-banana-gummi-bears'),
(2468, 'Haribo Gummi Raspberries', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Haribo gummi raspberries look like real raspberries! Put them in a candy dish at your next gathering and watch your guests get surprised with a gummi taste explosion when they pick one up. These delicious fruity snacks come as a mix of red and black in a big bulk bag. Be careful opening them up, though. Once you start, you won\'t want to stop eating these sweet raspberry gummies. Get them for your candy dish at home or the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', '2468~haribo-raspberries-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-raspberries'),
(2469, 'Sour Gummi Poppers', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Try not to drool. These Sour Gummi Poppers have a tart flavor that will make your mouth water! With a bright pastel selection of red, blue, yellow, green, and orange candies, there\'s an entire rainbow of sour for you to choose from. Every candy is coated in a tangy sugar that leads to a sweet, fruity center. Use a handful of these colorful pucker-makers for a candy dish on your coffee table, put some in a glass jar and enjoy looking at them as much as eating them, or even add some to a candy buffet bar for guests to enjoy at their own leisure. We\'re sure you\'ll love puckering with these poppable candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', '2469~sour-gummi-poppers-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sour-gummi-poppers'),
(2470, 'Gummi Frogs', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Everyone will jump for joy when they get a taste of Haribo gummy frogs! These little green candies aren\'t slippery and slimy, but they offer a smooth, soft texture that\'s pleasant on the tongue. Each piece includes fun details that recreate this popular amphibian â€“ right down to its folded legs, round head and raised back. Our gummy frogs are solid green and arrive fresh in sealed bags that are ready to enjoy! Hide gummi frogs around the house or save them to put in school lunches for the kids. These charming croakers are also great for serving at birthday parties, picnics and school events. Put them in a bowl or use them to dress up cakes, cupcakes, cookies and more! No matter how you display them, our Haribo gummy candies will entice children of all ages. Order our bulk candy pack so you have plenty of chewy frogs for any occasion!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', '2470~haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', 'gummi-frogs-12ct'),
(2471, 'Gummi Bears', 15.49, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Why didn\'t the teddy bear eat his lunch? Because he was stuffed! You\'ll be stuffed after eating mouthful after mouthful of these assorted gummi bears. In a big bulk bag of rainbow fruity cuties, you\'ll have a lot to chew about. Bring these little cubs to a birthday party. Put them in a sparkling punch at a backyard barbeque. Spoil your little ones by tucking some of these away in their lunch boxes. Or even fill goodie bags with a handful of these yummy gummies. Whatever you do, you\'ll love sampling the rainbow of colors and flavors. They\'re \'\'bear-resistable!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummi-bears-5lbs_2.jpg', '2471~gummi-bears-5lbs_2.jpg', 'gummi-bears'),
(2472, 'Fruit Slices Candy', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Fruit slices gummies are a fabulous treat that comes in many exciting flavors! If you love chewy gummy candy but want more options when it comes to taste, this is a must-try.Our delicious fruit slices candy include a flat wedge shape slab of confection with a flat end and curved side. A white line runs along the curved edge, creating the look of a fruit rind.Every fruit slice is different based on its flavor. Grape is all purple while black cherry includes a red middle with blue â€œrindâ€. We carry a huge variety of juicy flavors that also include lemon lime, cherry, strawberry banana, orange, pink grapefruit, peach, watermelon, sour apple, red raspberry and blue raspberry.If you can\'t decide on just one, you can instead choose our amazing assorted bulk fruit slices pack! This mouthwatering blend contains a little bit of everything so you can sample all your chewy favorites!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', '2472~albanese-fruit-slices-main.jpg', 'fruit-slices-candy'),
(2473, 'Orange Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Orange you excited about these? Because we are! A real knee-slapper, we know. But in all seriousness, these pint sized, orange Gummi Bears are packed with crisp citrus flavor that will have you smacking your lips with every chew. Use them to make a thematic Halloween display or drop them into a refreshing summer punch. They make delightful gift bag stuffers and even cake toppers, too. A popular and well-known chew among candy lovers, these make a great choice in satisfying all of your friends and family. Whatever occasion you can dream up, let these adorable bears brighten your day.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '2473~orange-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'orange-gummi-bears'),
(2474, 'Gumdrops', 11.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'If all the rain drops were lemon drops and gumdrops, then we\'d be out of business! However, you can still feel like it\'s raining gumdrops with this bulk bag of gummy candies. A classic addition for holiday baked goods, stockings, and fancy gingerbread houses, you will be stocked up for the season with this bag. In a variety of colors and fruity flavors, savor the sweetness as the sugary coating melts in your mouth. Then get ready to chew \'til you drop with a yummy gummy center. The holidays just aren\'t complete without a few mouthfuls of these sugary sweets.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gumdrops-5lbs.gif', '2474~gumdrops-5lbs.gif', 'gumdrops'),
(2475, 'Haribo Gummi Peaches', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'You\'re a peach! Well, actually these Haribo Gummi Peaches are. In a sugary coating and delicious light peach flavor, bite into these chewy gummies for a taste of the summertime. Bring some to a warm weather BBQ, add some as a pretty drink garnish to lemonade and adult drinks, or even use them to decorate the top of a strawberry shortcake! Haribo bears first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany. To this day, they\'re one of the biggest manufacturers of gummies and supply happy snackers all around the world. See for yourself why they earned the slogan, \'\'Kids and grown-ups love it so _ the happy world of Haribo!\'\'', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', '2475~haribo-peaches-icon.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-peaches'),
(2476, 'Mini Neon Sour Gummy Worms', 14.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'They\'re creepy. They\'re crawly. And they\'re also delicious? Yeah, we know. An unexpected turn to what you thought these Mini Neon Sour Gummy Worms might be. But rest assured, these little wrigglers are so yummy!In a rainbow of colors, these colorful mini gummy worms are packed with fruity flavor and a burst of sour sugar flavor that will make you pucker. Make your next Halloween bash even creepier with these night crawlers. You can set them out in a dish, add them to the top of a special Halloween cake, or just munch on them to gross out your little ones.Or if you\'re planning on a birthday party for boys and girls who love bugs and all things crawly, then order yourself a bulk bag of these Mini Neon Sour Gummy Worms for that!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mini-neon-sour-gummy-worms-470x470_3.jpg', '2476~mini-neon-sour-gummy-worms-470x470_3.jpg', 'mini-neon-sour-gummy-worms'),
(2477, 'Red Cherry Gummy Rings Candy', 15.99, '4.5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'We\'re seeing red. Red Cherry Gummy Rings, to be exact! These glistening gummies are coated with sweet specks of sugar for you to enjoy as they melt away in your mouth. Their bright red and white coloring is pleasing to the eye as well to the taste buds. Bite into these mini rings for a healthy dose of sweet cherry flavor that will make your mouth water. Put them on your fingers and pop them in your mouth one at a time. Add them to a holiday display. Even set some out for wedding or birthday party guests to munch on. Whatever you do, these red cherry gummy rings are coated with enough sugar and taste to make everyone smile, chew after chew.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', '2477~cherry-rings-gummy-candy-bulk-5lb_1.jpg', 'cherry-rings-gummy-candy'),
(2478, 'Swedish Fish Assorted', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Swedish Fish are one of the world\'s most classic and recognizable gummy candies. The red candy fish are instantly recognizable, and they\'re guaranteed to get your mouth watering. As if that wasn\'t good enough, you can get a big bulk bag of assorted flavors and colors of the classic gummy candy fish. That\'s right; you can get them in red, yellow, green, and orange, too. It\'s a simple and delicious twist on an old favorite.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/swedish-fish-assorted-5lbs_2.jpg', '2478~swedish-fish-assorted-5lbs_2.jpg', 'swedish-fish-assorted'),
(2479, 'Swedish Fish Red Mini', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'They may be the size of sardines, but these Swedish Fish Red Minis have a punch of cherry burst that rivals some of the biggest fish in the sea. The original flavor and shape of their brand, these little swimmers have swam their way into the hearts and stomachs of thousands of candy lovers. With a soft, chewy bite and gummy center, they\'ve quickly become the biggest fish in the pond and a beloved candy staple for people around the world. Dive into this bulk bag of Swedish Fish Red Minis and \'\'sea\'\' for yourself what all the fuss is about.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/swedish-fish-red-mini-5lbs_2.jpg', '2479~swedish-fish-red-mini-5lbs_2.jpg', 'swedish-fish-red-mini'),
(2480, 'Watermelon Gummi Bears', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Who doesn\'t love the flavor of watermelon? This gummies have the great flavor that you love as well as the fun and exciting color of pink. The texture is fun and chewy. This is a great item for children and even adults. It will be fun to add to a candy buffet for your next birthday party.If you are looking for the fun and exciting flavor of watermelon without the mess, pain of cutting the watermelon, and the seeds that come with real fresh watermelon then this is what you need. These great gummy bears are approximately one inch each in size. This is sure to make your mouth water and keep you coming back for more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-pink-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', '2480~watermelon-pink-gummi-bears-5lbs_1.jpg', 'watermelon-pink-gummi-bears'),
(2481, 'Gummi Fruit Salad', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'gummy', 'Haribo gummi fruit salad combines all your favorite flavors in one convenient package! Since 1920, Haribo has been producing new confections for the world to enjoy. Their current selection features a number of the most popular sugary snacks, including our irresistible gummy fruit salad! Every bag contains a selection of brightly colored chewy pieces that feature recognizable shapes that make mouths water.Reach into a bag of gummy fruit salad and enjoy the sweet sensation of orange, lime, cherry and more! Every piece is brightly colored in red, green, orange and other hues that match their fruity counterparts. This fat free candy is covered in a generous dusting of sugar for added texture and taste. Enjoy it as a guilt-free snack at home or buy our bulk candy pack and get plenty of Haribo fruit pieces to serve at any event. This nature-inspired confection is a big hit at picnics, parties, summer events and school activities!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/0/108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', '2481~108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', 'gummi-fruit-salad-12ct'),
(2482, 'Gummi Penguins', 11.99, '2.2', 'lb', 'gummy', 'It\'s the \'\'march of the penguin\'\' gummies! These curious little penguins are full of funny antics and will make your next snack even more charming and delicious! In every bag of these Penguin Gummies, these white and black treats will waddle, splash, and swim into your mouths. They\'re a great snack for kids to play with and an even more adorable treat to look at! These fancy tuxedo clad birds make a cute addition to any black tie, formal affair, wedding reception, or even as a gift to a penguin-loving friend or family lover. Get a taste of the arctic with this gummy, fruity snack today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', '2482~gummi-penguins-5lbs_1.jpg', 'gummi-penguins'),
(2483, 'Fruit Slices Lemon', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'gummy', 'Want a candy that is able to look just like a lemon slice? If so, then you have found it. These lemon candies look almost like really lemon slices. They have a nice yellow color to them and then have a white curve through them to make it appear like the skin is still on the lemon. They texture is smooth and this great candy is able to combine sweetness with the taste of citrus. You can tell just by looking at them that they are going to please your mouth as you get to take part in eating them. These candies would make a great garnishment and they would be great all on their own as well. You could use them at some special event or party that you were having or just buy them to keep around the house. Children and adults are both sure to enjoy the great taste of these.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruit-slices-lemon-5lb_2.jpg', '2483~fruit-slices-lemon-5lb_2.jpg', 'fruit-slices-lemon'),
(2484, 'Blueberry Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Get ready for your tongues to turn blue! These Blueberry Old Fashioned Candy Sticks have enough blueberry power to dye your mouth and satisfy your sweet tooth. Having a blue themed birthday party for a family member or friend? Celebrating the birth of a baby boy? Want to add some pop of flavor to typical punches and lemonades? These classic candy sticks can do that all and more with a delicious, long lasting flavor. With 80 individually wrapped candy sticks in each box, you\'ll have enough to go around. Get a taste of summertime\'s favorite berry with your order of these tasty sticks today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blueberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', '2484~blueberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', 'blueberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2485, 'Gilliam Hard Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned hard candy sticks are the ultimate go-to treat for anyone with a sweet tooth. Stick candy has been a favorite of young and old since the mid-1800s, and it\'s no wonder why. Each piece features a unique flavor and fun colors that make every lick a memorable experience! Simply peel away the hard candy wrapper and you are ready to snack. Each piece is individually wrapped so they are easy to store and can be given as party favors or a special treat for the kids!We carry a huge list of exciting flavors so you never get bored. Try exotic pina colada, orange pineapple or rum and butter! If you prefer something simpler, classic bubblegum, peppermint, sassafras or strawberry are just as enticing. You\'ll love watching the striped candy melt away with each bite! Grab the old family photo album and your favorite flavors and relive your childhood memories with Gilliam hard candy sticks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', '2485~stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', 'old-fashioned-stick-candy-box-flavors'),
(2486, 'Spearmint Leaves Candy', 10.99, '5', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned spearmint leaves gummies are a chewy treat that will invigorate your taste buds! This elegant candy features a tapered leaf shape, with a narrow tip and wider base.The sides include subtle scalloping Ã must like real foliage! A short stem extends from the base, adding even more detail to these eye-catching candies. Every piece is covered in a gentle green hue that looks even more enticing covered in sugar crystals!Every bite is packed with amazing spearmint flavor. Give your mouth something cool and refreshing to chew on with these all-purpose leaf gummies. Spearmint leaves are also a unique way to decorate cakes, cupcakes and cookies.Add realistic elements to your gingerbread houses or use them to enhance edible dÅ½cor. Our bulk spearmint leaves candy gives you many pounds so you have plenty of individual pieces to experiment with. Or you can keep things simple by pouring spearmint gummies into a bowl to serve any guests who stop by!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/brachs-spearmint-leaves-small-img.jpg', '2486~brachs-spearmint-leaves-small-img.jpg', 'spearmint-leaves-candy'),
(2487, 'Grape Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Grape candy sticks are the best way to enjoy this popular flavor any time you want it! Hard candy sticks are tasty and convenient. Each arrives individually wrapped so you can hide them anywhere â€“ in your purse, in a drawer or in the candy jar! Each piece includes a length of tube shaped hard candy in dark plumb with a distinctive white stripe that spirals from end to end.Our hard candy sticks offer a great taste that lasts a long time. Savor every lick of grapey-goodness when you enjoy one of these irresistible sweets! Break one in half for a quick snack or sit down and relax with an entire stick. Every piece offers the nostalgic appeal of old fashioned candy in a product that\'s just as sweet and tempting as any modern confection. Place your grape sticks in a glass jar and take them to the office, a party or leave them at home so you\'re always ready to satisfy sugary cravings!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', '2487~grape-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', 'grape-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2488, 'Mary Jane Candy', 20.99, '', '', 'old-fashioned', 'When you\'re in the mood for something extra chewy, try our sweet Mary Jane candies! These delectable delights are small bars of smooth taffy treats. Each is flavored with rich molasses and peanut butter to give it that memorable taste that kids of all ages have been asking for since 1914. The candy is a historic favorite that was named after its creator\'s beloved aunt â€“ a worthy choice for such a nostalgic confection!Each taffy candy is covered in a bright yellow wrapper with a bold red stripe and classic logo printed around both sides. You\'ll love Mary Janes even more when you buy our bulk candy package! Order larger quantities so you have plenty to share at family gatherings and other events. Use them to fill the office candy jar or use them to fill treat bags for birthdays and more! Our bulk Mary Janes are also convenient to hand out on trick or treat night around Halloween!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', '2488~mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'mary-janes-candy'),
(2489, 'Pina Colada Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned hard candy is a timeless treat that you can take anywhere â€“ even the beach! Imagine sitting back on a lounge chair while sun bathing along the seashore with a pina colada candy stick in hand. Our famous Gilliam candy sticks are easy to pack because they come individually wrapped. Just grab a few and tuck away in your beach tote! Each piece includes a sunny yellow color with a thick white stripe that can be displayed in a glass jar to brighten the kitchen.Our bulk hard candy package includes enough sticks to go around - even when hosting a large event like a wedding or birthday celebration! Bring a little slice of paradise to the occasion with these delectable confections. You can also include them in party or wedding favors so guests can take the tropical fun with them after the festivities have concluded. Enjoy the flavors of an exotic paradise everywhere you go with our pina colada hard candy sticks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pina-colada-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2489~pina-colada-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'pina-colada-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2490, 'Blue Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Feeling blue never felt so sweet! Stock up with these pint-sized, blue raspberry sticks for a color-themed party, birth of a baby boy, or to place around your home. They\'re even great for a winter-themed party or Hanukkah event. At half the size of regular candy sticks, they\'re the perfect fruity affair for a midday treat or any occasion you can think up. Candy sticks look lovely displayed in a glass jar and can give any candy bar buffet a retro feel. Suck on one of these for an explosion of fruity flavor that your friends and family are sure to love.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '2490~blue-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'blue-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(2491, 'Blackberry Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Enjoy an all-time, American favorite berry without having to combat any of the prickers or seeds in your teeth! These Old Fashioned Blackberry Candy Sticks have a lovely and girly swirl of pink between the dark black candy, making them an ideal addition to any baby shower, wedding reception, dessert display, or even little or teen girl birthday parties. The delicious blackberry flavor will remind you of warm summer days picking berries and can make a great addition to a lemonade or daiquiri! Use your imagination and decide how you\'d like to use these delectable sticks to make your life yummier.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blackberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2491~blackberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'blackberry-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2492, 'Licorice Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'When it comes to class and dignity there is nothing like a black tie affair. Now there is a candy that is tailor made for these fancy occasions.  Old Fashioned Licorice Candy Sticks add class and sophistication to any occasion. They have elegant black color with delicate white stripes running through them. Each licorice stick comes individually wrapped and will look formal in a display or in a person\'s pocket just waiting to be eaten. Put a glass jar of these delicious treats on your coffee table and people will start to wear a tie when they come for a visit. These hard candy sticks will provide the elegance and grace to any formal gathering that all event planners are looking for.  This is five inches of traditional candy goodness that will put the smile back on a person\'s face and make all people realize the class and dignity that you possess!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2492~licorice-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'licorice-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2493, 'Tangerine Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Tangerine candy sticks will make your taste buds tingle with citrusy goodness! Gilliam old fashioned candy sticks are a must-have treat for all candy lovers. This popular confection is reminiscent of classic candy shops and fond childhood memories.Our tangerine hard candy includes a deep orange hue that\'s accentuated by a pure white stripe that twists from end to end like a barbershop pole. Gilliam hard candy sticks aren\'t just beautiful to look at, they amazing to taste! Each is individually wrapped so they stay fresh and ready to enjoy.Tear one end and experience the exciting taste of tangerine along with the smoothness of quality hard candy. Use alone or combine with our other bulk candy stick packages to display in jars, vases and more. Candy sticks are also a great choice for wedding favors, shower favors, after school snacks and can be given as a special reward for students.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/a/tangerine_stick_candy.jpg', '2493~tangerine_stick_candy.jpg', 'tangerine-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2494, 'IBC Root Beer Barrels Candy', 34.99, '8', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'Ladies and gentlemen, boys and girls, we present you with the 8th wonder of the world, IBC rootbeer barrel candies! At least we think it\'s a wonder that IBC found a way to mimic their frothy, refreshing, world-famous root beer in a tiny hard candy. You\'ll feel like you\'re sipping a bubbly fountain soda on a hot summer day every time you pop one of these into your mouth. The adorable barrels make an exceptional and thematic display at beer festivals and are a timeless choice for your candy dishes. See for yourself why people can\'t get enough of this groundbreaking treat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rootbeerbarrels.jpg', '2494~rootbeerbarrels.jpg', 'ibc-root-beer-barrels-candy'),
(2495, 'Lemon Lime Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Lemon and lime. Undoubtedly, one of the most famous duos to ever hit our taste buds. Now combined with a classic candy shoppe treat, these Lemon Lime Old Fashioned Candy Sticks are here to continue a tradition of fabulous citrusy flavor. Their green and yellow colored swirls are a perfect complement to their bright, fruity taste. Stock up on these for a fantastic lemonade stirrer or summertime punch garnish, use them as a bright addition to any candy buffet bar, or just have some around the house for any of your classic candy fans to enjoy. With 8 individually wrapped candy sticks in each box, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/e/lemon-lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2495~lemon-lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'lemon-lime-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2496, 'Bubblegum Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Bubblegum, bubblegum in a dish. How many pieces do you wish? Apparently, you\'re wishing for a whole 80 count bag of Bubblegum Old Fashioned Candy Sticks! With a rainbow of red, yellow, blue, green, and white, these sticks are tasty as they are beautiful. Their hard candy crunch and colorful style make them the perfect candy for amongst any event you can dream up. Stick one in a cool fruity drink as an adorable and unique stirrer. Display these in a glass vase on your kitchen counter for a lovely look. Even bring these to a party and set them out on the dessert table as a different and delicious treat! You\'ll love these bubblegum sticks no matter what you do.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bubblegum_stick_candy.jpg', '2496~bubblegum_stick_candy.jpg', 'bubblegum-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2497, 'Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates Tub', 22.99, '240', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'When you think of classy candy then immediately Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates jump to mind. These delicious treats have been sold in a delightful and recognizable green wrapping. When a person sees that wrapping they know that wherever they are, it is a place filled with class. It could be a restaurant that provides a free snack with the bill. It could be left on the pillow in a hotel. Even if it is in your own home the person who sees the shiny green wrapper will know that they are dealing with a person and a place that knows class. The chocolate treat is the reason for this as it provides a delicious chocolate treat with the blast of creamy goodness that shakes your taste buds and zaps them awake. There is just the right minty freshness to allow you to feel refreshed. There will always be enough class around with a tub of Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub-240ct_1.jpg', '2497~andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub-240ct_1.jpg', 'andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub'),
(2498, 'Wintergreen Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Wintergreen Candy Sticks are an excellent addition to any holiday, Christmas, or Birthday party. These Candy Sticks are made using natural and artificial flavorings, they are gluten free and certified kosher. Wintergreen Candy Sticks are a perfect on the go treat, and a great way to tell your customers thank you. Place these Candy Sticks in an old fashioned jar for a nostalgic feel, in a decorative mug for easy access, or treat bags for that extra special addition. Wintergreen Sticks are flavorful and provide a long lasting peppermint flavor. Grab a Wintergreen Candy Stick for an afternoon pick me up, the delicious peppermint will awaken your senses and heighten alertness. Wintergreen Candy Sticks are 5  long making them just the right size for decorative swag on Christmas presents, or in any hot beverage for stirring, and flavor. No matter the use these Wintergreen Candy Sticks are sure to please.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/i/wintergreen_sticks.jpg', '2498~wintergreen_sticks.jpg', 'wintergreen-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2499, 'Tutti Frutti Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'This candy has a name that\'s almost as fun to say as the candy is to eat! However, we still think it\'s fruity, sweet flavor is the best part. Try these Tutti Fruiti Old Fashioned Candy Sticks for a delicious burst of bright, fruity flavor. Their beautiful yellow, pink, and green swirls make them a perfect addition to a Mardi Gras party or even for New Years Eve! Try these crunchy, hard candy sticks in cold lemonade or punch for a dose of extra sweetness and fresh, fruity flavor. Even bring some to a party with friends as a delicious dessert or pack them up in a present for a flavor flashback everyone can enjoy. With 8 sticks per order, you\'ll have enough to do it all.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/u/tutti-fruitti-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct.jpg', '2499~tutti-fruitti-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct.jpg', 'tutti-fruitti-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2500, 'Nut Goodie Bars', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Nostalgic. Classic. Vintage. You\'re a special kind of candy fan who appreciates where every sweet got its roots. With these Nut Goodie\'s, you can enjoy a taste of yesteryear in every milk chocolatey, nutty bite! Introduced in 1912, Nut Goodie hit candy store shelves for a whopping 5 cents! To this day, not much has changed about the delicious, salty, sweet nut clusters including their vintage wrapper. Add these to a 2\'s themed party for a tasty treat, share a bit of history with loved ones, or surprise your grandmother or grandfather with a taste of their youth. Whatever you do, you\'ll love these tried and true confections.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/u/nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', '2500~nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', 'nut-goodie-bars'),
(2501, 'Claey\'s Wild Cherry Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'What\'s red, sweet, and delicious all over? These Wild Cherry Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops! Dusted in crystalized, sweet sugar, these bright red candies pack a serious punch of wild cherry flavor that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Bring some to a holiday gathering that needs a dose of festive red, use some to decorate a gingerbread house with a delicious treat, add them to a Fourth of July dessert table, or add a yummy, fruity treat to a Valentine\'s Day gift. With this 1 pound order of wild cherry candies, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys-cherry-candy-drops-small.jpg', '2501~claeys-cherry-candy-drops-small.jpg', 'wild-cherry-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2502, 'Orange Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Candy sticks are a favorite of many. These great candy sticks are hard candy that is in the shape of a stick. They are orange in flavor. They also have a great orange color to them that would blend well when use for almost any occasion. You will find that these might really work great around Halloween as each one is individually wrapped, so if you are giving them out to children that you don\'t know then the parents are not as likely to be concerned with it. You can either suck on the sticks until they are gone, or if you are one that likes to crunch then you will be able to do this as well. However, you should know that it is not good for your teeth so do this at your own risks. However, you decide to enjoy your sticks you are sure to find that they will hit the spot.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange_stick_candy.jpg', '2502~orange_stick_candy.jpg', 'orange-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2503, 'Long Boys Coconut', 8.99, '48', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Long Boys coconut candy sticks are a classic favorite that\'s full of rich flavor! This traditional candy originated in New Orleans, making it a staple for local children.Today, people all over the country rave about the amazing taste of these long, chewy confections. Every piece includes a stick of candy that\'s individually wrapped in a nostalgic red and yellow wrapper.Coconut Long Boys offer a unique blend of caramel and exotic coconut for a snacking experience that\'s memorable and satisfying! Untwist the wrapper and take small bites to fully enjoy the taste of this one-of-a-kind flavor combination! Kids can try stretching their Long Boy candy to see who can make the longest rope!Our bulk Long Boy coconut candy is a great choice for parties, picnics and family reunions. Use them to fill treat bags for birthdays or set out a bowl or box so adults can munch while reminiscing about their favorite childhood sweets!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', '2503~long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', 'long-boys-coconut'),
(2504, 'Chocolate Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Chocolate candy sticks are the long lasting treat that\'s delicious and nostalgic! For generations, kids have hurried to their local candy shop to enjoy the sweet taste of flavorful hard candy.Now you can relive those fond memories with your favorite flavor! Gilliam\'s old fashioned candy sticks are simple, elegant and absolutely irresistible.Each lengthy piece includes a solid tube of delectable hard candy with a rich chocolate flavor. This version comes in a dark, deep brown with a brilliant white stripe that runs from end to end. The clear wrapper, emblazoned with the famous Gilliam\'s logo, allows the beautiful pattern to show through. Match our classic candy sticks up with a special event or theme.They are gorgeous when placed upright in jars or vases at showers. Send guests off with something sweet by adding these chocolaty sticks to your wedding favors! Keep them at home as a quick sugar fix or take them to the office and share the Gilliam\'s hard candy stick love with your colleagues and clients.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2504~chocolate-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'chocolate-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2505, 'Butterscotch Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Butterscotch and candy sticks: two classics that have finally united to bring you a nostalgic taste of yesteryear! Bring back the happy, memory-filled days of yore with a lick of one of these Butterscotch Old Fashioned Candy Sticks. Their golden yellow and honey colored swirls are a perfect complement to their rich, buttery taste. Stock up on these for a festive Thanksgiving dessert addition, use them as a delicious hot chocolate stirrer, or just have some around the house for any of your classic candy fans to enjoy. With 8 individually wrapped candy sticks in each box, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/butterscotch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', '2505~butterscotch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_2.jpg', 'butterscotch-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2506, 'Rum & Butter Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'We\'re positive that these candies will \'\'butter you up!\'\' That\'s because these Rum Butter Old Fashioned Candy Sticks pack a supremely rich and delicious taste that you won\'t be able to resist. In bright yellow, these little rays of sunshine look like a beautiful pat of butter on a slice of toast. Bring some to your next outdoor party, or even use some in the colder months to stir into a cup of hot cocoa for a warm, rich flavor in a cheerful color. With 8 sticks per order, you\'ll be able to snack happily and decadently for a long, long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/rum-butter-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct-inset.jpg', '2506~rum-butter-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct-inset.jpg', 'rum-butter-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2507, 'Green Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Have a lick of one of these Green and White Mini Candy Sticklettes and you\'ll be hooked! Its bright, lime flavor and citrusy burst is an addictive combination that our customers love. Individually wrapped and at half the size of regular candy sticks, these little wonders will make a delightful snack, time after time. Try them for a St. Patrick\'s Day party, a spring backyard barbeque, or even on a gingerbread house as cute little columns! Their bright green and white swirls are a lovely combination and stand out on candy shelves. They make a great candy choice at any time of the year.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '2507~green-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'green-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(2508, 'Island Punch Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Things are going to get tropical when you try our exotic Island Punch candy sticks! This timeless treat has been enjoyed for decades.Adults and children alike savor the sweet flavor that comes with every delicious stick! Whisk your taste buds off to fruity paradise with each rainbow colored tube of solid hard candy! Gilliam\'s old fashioned candy sticks are known for their superb flavor and elegant design.Each Island Punch candy stick includes vibrant orange, yellow, red and green in lovely spirals that reach from one end to the other. The clear plastic wrapper allows the beautiful pattern to show through, making these hard candies an excellent choice for wedding favors, showers and other special events.Place a handful in a glass vase or jar or add them to an edible gift and impress guests! Our Island Punch candy sticks will conjure images of seaside vacations spent lazing along the sun-kissed sands.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/i/s/island-punch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2508~island-punch-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'island-punch-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2509, 'Pineapple Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'A pretty yellow candy stick gets swirled with a green stripe to create the fun visual display of this Pineapple Old-Fashioned Stick Candy. Dress up your Pina Colada with one or put them in glasses of punch or lemonade for kids. They are great for Easter and St. Patrick\'s Day, and if you know someone trying to kick the nicotine habit, these long-lasting candies might be exactly what they need.They are sweet, easy to eat, and as long as you resist the urge to bite, they last a really long time. Each Pineapple Old-fashioned Stick Candy is individually wrapped. This makes them perfect to hand out at parties, share with friends at the campground, or use at Halloween for trick-or-treaters. Their tropical look and taste makes them ideal for beach-themed parties for folks of all ages. They are kosher certified, too.Finding pineapple-flavored candy is not easy. If you have ever specifically looked for it then you know this is a tall order to fill. This is unfortunate, considering it is one of the sweetest and most delicious island fruits. Well, your search is over! This Pineapple Old-Fashioned Stick Candy is exactly what you are looking for and appropriate for any occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pineapple-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2509~pineapple-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'pineapple-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2510, 'Peaches & Cream Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Old fashioned candy sticks by Gilliam are a must-have treat for any confectionary connoisseur. These delightful sticks of flavor conjure images of simpler times when children rushed to the candy shop to buy their favorite sweets for a few coins.Today you can enjoy that same great taste with Gilliam peaches and cream candy sticks! Each length is packed with enormous fruit flavor and the smooth texture you know and love. Our Gilliam hard candy sticks arrive individually packaged in clear wrappers. This allows you to admire the brilliant hues that decorate each piece.Our Peaches and cream hard candy features a rich blend of bright orange and sunshine yellow that twists from top to bottom. These creamy-sweet candy sticks look fabulous whether you prop them up in a glass vase, candy bowl or use them to fill up party favors! Our bulk old fashioned candy stick pack gives you large quantities that are perfect for holidays, events and other special occasions.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peaches-and-cream-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', '2510~peaches-and-cream-old-fashioned-stick-candy-80ct_1.jpg', 'peaches-cream-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2511, 'Orange Candy Sticks Mini Sticklettes', 25.99, '250', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Good things come in small packages. Especially in this Orange and White Mini Sticklette Candy! Feel like you\'re biting into a fresh orange with a burst of juicy flavor in every bite. And enjoy looking at the vibrant orange color every time you snack. Individually wrapped and at half the size of regular candy sticks, these little wonders will make a delightful treat time after time. Spice up a brunch display with by using these little Sticklettes as orange juice stirrers, put them in an orange-themed candy display, or keep them around the house for a cheerful treat. Whatever you do with this mini sticklettes, you\'ll love stirring, licking, and chomping them as much as looking at them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', '2511~orange-white-candy-sticks-mini-sticklettes-250ct_1.jpg', 'orange-white-sticklettes-mini-sticks'),
(2512, 'Sesame Seed Snaps', 19.99, '24', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'Sezme sesame snaps are an amazingly delicious treat that\'s also good for you! If you simply can\'t decide between sweet and salty, you can enjoy both in every bite with these bar shaped confections.Each is packed with savory sesame seed flavor that\'s complemented by a touch of sugary goodness. They come individually wrapped so they stay fresh until it\'s time to snack. Our bulk Sezme sesame snaps are an excellent alternative food to chocolaty or overly sugary treats.Eat better while satisfying your cravings. This Poland-born treat is cholesterol free and gluten free. Take a bite and experience the pleasant crunch and satisfying flavor that taste buds crave. Our bulk sesame snaps box is a must-have for daily snacking.Use them to pack healthier lunches for your family or keep them as a quick and easy after school snack. Sesame seed candy also makes a great Christmas stocking stuffer!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/e/sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', '2512~sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', 'sesame-seed-snaps'),
(2513, 'Claey\'s Root Beer Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'old-fashioned', 'We\'re rooting for these classic candies. That\'s because Claey\'s Root beer Old-Fashioned Candy Drops are completely coated in crystally, crunchy sugar granules that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Beyond the saccharine coating, lies a delicious hard candy. They\'ll take you back to a warm, summer\'s day of sipping a refreshing root beer float. Stock up on some to add to root beer treats, add to a gift basket, or put out on the Thanksgiving table. Among root beer, Claey\'s favorite flavors include green apple, licorice, natural horehound, watermelon, lemon, and wild cherry. They\'ll look lovely in your coffee table candy dish or set out in a jar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', '2513~root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', 'root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2514, 'Spearmint Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'old-fashioned', 'The green that swirls through the sweet, suckable Spearmint Old Fashioned Stick Candy is refreshing to the eye, just as the burst of spearmint flavor it provides is refreshing to the mouth! Finish a meal by providing after-dinner mints in a nostalgic form that will send your guests into raptures of reminiscing delight.Candy sticks remind everyone of childhood trips to the county fair or the farm market, and their stripes are always a dose of high contrast in a display. Sharp spearmint was once much more common in candies than it is today, but a few manufacturers keep the flavor tradition alive!Old-fashioned yet gluten-free and nut-free, these candy sticks are an instant dose of nostalgia when you include them in a selection of elegant emerald-green candy. The possibilities for styling an inventive dessert with the classic sweets are as endless as the rush of freshness in these minty candy sticks.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spearmint_sticks.jpg', '2514~spearmint_sticks.jpg', 'spearmint-old-fashioned-stick-candy');
