(2612, 'Pink Striped Ball Petite Lollipops', 26.99, '400', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Strawberry fields forever. We know the famous Beatles song and drew inspiration from their lyrics to create an almost endless bag of Strawberry Striped Ball Lollipops. With 4 strawberry suckers in every order, you will feel like you have the sun on your back while picking wild berries with every lick. Have a daughter or friend who just loves pink or a fruity, strawberry flavor? Have a party coming up that needs the pretty punch of this white and pink swirl to dress it up? Want to stick these into the top of a strawberry shortcake dessert to make it extra special and beautiful? These pops can do it all and please every taste bud.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', '2612~pink-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', 'pink-striped-ball-lollipops-petite'),
(2613, 'Large Blue Striped Ball Lollipops', 26.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Like miniature beach balls flying through the air on a warm, summer day on the sand, these Blue Striped Ball Lollipops will add some fun to your candy repertoire. Individually wrapped in a package of 1, these blue and white striped lollipops have a bursting blueberry flavor that will make your taste buds say, \'\'wow!\'\' These bright pops look lovely in a homemade candy bouquet for a special event, set out on a table for a Fourth of July picnic, or even in goodie bags for your little ones\' birthday parties. Enjoying these suckers will be fun and delicious, time after time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', '2613~blue-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', 'blue-striped-ball-lollipops-large'),
(2614, 'Rainbow Whirly Pops 5.25', 129.99, '36', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Suckers are always fun whether you are getting them for a child or an adult. There is just something to be said about Whirly Pops however. These giant suckers are 5.25 inches which means that it could take you quite a while to finish them off. You will also find that they are swirled with many different colors such as blue, red, orange, yellow, white, and green. This would make a fun gift for someone, and would also be a great party favor. These would even look great in a homemade arrangement because they are so large. Whatever you decide to do with them you are sure to be pleased and with a count of 36 of them there is sure to be plenty for everyone. These suckers are hard in texture but are sweet and sure to be able to please anyone who is lucky enough to get to take part in eating one.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/rainbow-whirly-pops-525-36ct_2.jpg', '2614~rainbow-whirly-pops-525-36ct_2.jpg', 'rainbow-whirly-pops-5-quarter-inch'),
(2615, 'Super Blow Pops from Charms', 18.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Super-sized, two candies in one, Super Blow Pops from Charms combine the long lasting sugary goodness of suckers with the satisfying slow burn of sweet gum. These tasty twofers are perfect for weddings, birthday parties, and classrooms. Super Blow Pops are easily formed into bouquets, trees, and any other imaginable design for that super sweet decoration. Super Pops make great Trick-R-Treat giveaways, and party favors for any themed party. Super Pops can even be used for party games. These delicious treats are also great for break rooms, and grab baskets in companies. They provide a thank you to customers and a pick me up for employees. Super Blow Pops also make great fundraisers to help your company meet its\' goals. These pops are great for personal snacking when only the sweetest treat will do. 48 assorted flavors come in each classic display box, ensuring everyone gets their favorite, every time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/super_blow_pops.jpg', '2615~super_blow_pops.jpg', 'super-blow-pops-charms'),
(2616, 'Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops', 26.99, '400', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'There\'s no reason to feel blue about these Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops. In their pristine white and bright blue stripes, these are some of the happiest candies around. On a snow white stick, these little lollies are full of fruity flavor that will wake your taste buds up and put a smile on your face.Having a baby boy and want to celebrate with a thematic treat? These Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops are perfect for that sort of occasion. They also work well when paired with red candies on the Fourth of July, make Hanukah extra special, or can be bought for a special dad on Father\'s Day. Blue Striped Ball Petite Lollipops are delicious and good looking enough for almost any event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', '2616~blue-striped-ball-lollipops-petite-bulk_1.jpg', 'blue-striped-ball-lollipops-petite'),
(2617, 'What A Melon Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Charms Blow Pops are absolutely irresistible! No matter how old you get, you\'ll always love licking one of these delicious lollies! Our What A Melon Blow Pops offer that same two-candy combination you love with the fresh taste of juicy watermelon.Each includes a thick shell of hard candy that surrounds a mouthful of sweet chewing gum, all perched neatly atop a disposable lollipop stick.Our bulk What A Melon Blow Pops are individually wrapped so they stay fresh until it\'s time to snack. Each box contains many lollipops so you have plenty to enjoy and share. Bulk Blow Pops are a must-have for kids\' birthday parties. Use them as Christmas stocking stuffers or keep them as a fast after school snack on busy days.No matter what season it is, our What A Melon Blow Pops are always ripe and ready to eat! Also check out our other single-flavor Blow Pop boxes so you can mix and match your favorites.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/what-a-watermelon-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2617~what-a-watermelon-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'what-a-watermelon-blow-pops'),
(2618, 'Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops', 26.99, '100', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Quite possibly the pretties treat available on CandyStore.com, these Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops are sure to invoke a lot of smiles. What\'s the first thing that comes to mind, when you look at these lollies? A beach ball, right? This makes them perfect for beach-themed parties and weddings. They will cause shrieks of excitement from little ones and they can bring out the inner child in anyone.These Large Pink Striped Ball Lollipops are 1 inch in diameter, so they last a really long time. Creamy white balls get swirled in bright pink stripes for a look anyone will be charmed by. These suckers are not just pretty though. Their delicious strawberry flavor will have you reaching into the candy jar a little more often.Decorate a birthday cake with these or make bouquets of them for centerpieces by stabbing the sticks in green floral foam. They are perfect for baby showers, kids\' parties, and Valentine\'s Day.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', '2618~pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large-bulk_1.jpg', 'pink-striped-ball-lollipops-large'),
(2619, 'Cherry Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Cherry Blow Pops are super sweet and a popular treat for candy lovers of all ages! This exciting snack is actually two confections in one. Each includes a disposable stick tipped in an orb of delightful hard candy.The center is filled with a gob of smooth chewing gum. Lick and nibble away until you reach the chewy middle! Your lollipop will go longer when there\'s bubblegum waiting inside!Blow Pops are one of the most popular types of lollipops sold in the United States. It\'s easy to see why once you taste one for yourself. Our bulk Blow Pops in cherry give you many individually wrapped pieces that are convenient for events, birthday parties and much more!Use them to fill up treat bags for kids or keep them in your pantry as an easy sweet snack. Our Charms Blow Pops are fun, delicious and packed with juicy cherry flavor!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2619~cherry-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'cherry-blow-pops'),
(2620, 'Blow Pops from Charms', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'We have a dozen delicious Blow Pops from Charms flavors for you to choose from here in bulk! Black Cherry, Black Ice, Blue Razzberry, Cherry, Cherry Ice, Kiwi Berry Blast, Mean Green, Sour Apple, Tangerine, Watermelon, Way-2-Sour, and  Mango flavors, if you can pick just one!Whatever you choose, you\'ll have a delicious and famous hard lollipop to suck on and chewy, sweet bubblegum to enjoy once you reach the middle. These Blow Pops from Charms are a real crowd-pleaser, so pick some up and keep them around the house for when your kids\' friends come over or you need something special and sweet to savor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blow-pops-from-charms-48ct_2.jpg', '2620~blow-pops-from-charms-48ct_2.jpg', 'blow-pops-charms-flavors'),
(2621, 'Rainbow Unicorn Pops 12', 139.99, '72', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'They do exist! At least their tasty, rainbow horns do. And we love \'em. With all the colors of the rainbow, a sweet, fruity flavor and beautiful swirls, these Unicorn Pops are a delightful treat with notable heritage. The mythical tales of the unicorn date back to ancient Greece and even the Bible with stories of people glimpsing white, goat-like horses with a single, long horn. The legendary lore depicted the unicorns as a symbol of purity, hope and grace as they would heal ailments and injuries. We think these pops are just as healing as they were originally thought to be. See for yourself why they\'re so magical at your child\'s next birthday party or any special occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-72ct.jpg', '2621~rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-72ct.jpg', 'rainbow-unicorn-pops-12-inch'),
(2622, 'Green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops Lime', 14.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops are an eye-catching treat that is full of powerful sweetness. Our lollipops are made with high quality confection and offer a distinctive look that works for events, school activities and more.Instead of a basic round shape, our green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops include a length of smooth hard candy with a fabulous white and green stripe. The tube is twisted to form a tight coil that\'s long lasting and so irresistible! Bulk lollipops are the best way to get bigger quantities for special celebrations and more. Dress up tables at a birthday party or block party by putting these beautiful lollies out in a jar.Add a ribbon and tag to give as an edible stocking stuffer or Easter basket filler. Our green Tiny Tesla Twist Pops are also a great choice for shower and wedding favors! We also carry other brilliant colors so you can find the perfect twisted lollipop for your event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/e/teslas-tiny-twist-pops-green-yumjunkie.jpg', '2622~teslas-tiny-twist-pops-green-yumjunkie.jpg', 'green-tiny-tesla-twist-pops-lime'),
(2623, 'Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'These pink and blue swirled lollies are perfect for birthday parties and baby showers. You don\'t need an excuse to enjoy one though, and since they are fat-free and only 70 calories, you can indulge in them a lot more often than the real thing.Everyone knows that the best thing about going to the fair is for the sweet, sticky, and delicious cotton candy. Of course, the one bad thing about cotton candy is that it does not last very long. The moment that spun sugar touches your tongue it instantly dissolves.Not to mention, it seems to shrink before your very eyes, if it is hot or humid outside. These Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops taste just like the real thing, only they last a whole lot longer.What do Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops taste like? Well, like you pulled a handful of sticky goodness off both pink and blue rolls and popped them in your mouth together, but these are hard candy suckers, so you get to enjoy the flavor a lot longer. Not to mention, unlike the real thing, Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy Pops are not messy to eat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/l/fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops-48ct.gif', '2623~fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops-48ct.gif', 'fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-pops'),
(2624, 'Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops are a new take on the classic lollipop. Blow Pops are one of the most famous treats made by Charms.This candy was first introduced during the 1970s and quickly became Charms\' bestselling confection. Each lollipop includes a generous dollop of sweet bubblegum surrounded by a thick hard candy shell perched atop a disposable stick.Lick away then enjoy a good chew with this long lasting candy! While classic Blow Pops are tasty, sometimes you want something more exotic to enjoy. Our kiwi berry lollipops offer that same unique design with a blast of flavor inspired by two sweet fruits.Each features a deep red color that\'s complemented by a matching wrapper. Simply untwist the top and prepare to take a stroll through fruit flavor paradise! Bulk Blow Pops are a must-have for children\'s birthday parties, picnics and school activities. Hand them out during holidays or keep a box at home so you always have Kiwi Berry Blast Blow Pops ready to eat!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/i/kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2624~kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'kiwi-berry-blast-blow-pops'),
(2625, 'Black Cherry Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'One of the newest flavors of Blow Pops is also one of the most fabulous! Bulk, display-packaged Black Cherry Blow Pops contain a heart of bubble gum within a thick shell of dark, glossy black cherry candy. It\'s two kinds of confection on one convenient stick!Popular for classroom rewards, lunch bags, and birthday parties, Blow Pops also make a delicious and nostalgia-inducing treat whenever you need something to pick up your mood. Contained in a display box that\'s great for store counters and retro candy buffets, wholesale Black Cherry Blow Pops are the perfect candy choice when you want something familiar and fun.Not too prosaic in flavor, these pops will jazz up your event or draw people to a fair booth. Bursting with flavor at the start and filled with long-lasting chewing gum, these suckers make a great on-the-go dessert!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-cherry-blow-pops-48ct_2.jpg', '2625~black-cherry-blow-pops-48ct_2.jpg', 'black-cherry-blow-pops'),
(2626, 'Wrapped Smarties Pops Jar', 16.99, '120', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'If you ever wished Smarties were bigger, then consider it granted with these Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars! With traditional Smarties candy sized up to lollipop standards and put on a stick, you can munch and crunch on these classic candies in a whole new way.If you like to mix things up in your candy routine, try these Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars! You can keep them around the kitchen for when you want a sweet snack or to reward a bookworm for a great test grade. You can even order some Smarties Pops Wrapped Jars to sell at concessions stands for school sporting events or give out in goodie bags at parties. Just be smart and order some of these luscious lollipops today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/m/smarties-pops-lollipops-alt-candystore-470x470.jpg', '2626~smarties-pops-lollipops-alt-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'smarties-pops-wrapped-jar'),
(2627, 'Cherry Ice Blow Pops', 10.99, '48', 'ct', 'lollipops-suckers', 'Now you can get Charms Blow Pops in bulk! Our enormous box contains many individual lollipops that are a tasty treat anytime â€“ day or night!Take a few lollies with you to enjoy throughout the work day or pack them in lunches as a sweet way to end the midday meal. Our Cherry Ice Blow Pops offer intense flavor that kids and adults will love.This version of the classic Blow Pop lollipop includes the same disposable stick and hard candy shell you love with a chewy gummy center. What makes them so unique is the cool cherry taste packed into every round pop!Hand them out during school or community events or use them as Christmas stocking stuffers or Easter basket filler. Cherry Ice Blow Pops are an easy party favor as well. Add them to a treat bag or tie on a personalized tag to customize your candy gift!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2627~cherry-ice-blow-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'cherry-ice-blow-pops'),
(2628, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '2628~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(2629, 'Gilliam Hard Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Old fashioned hard candy sticks are the ultimate go-to treat for anyone with a sweet tooth. Stick candy has been a favorite of young and old since the mid-1800s, and it\'s no wonder why. Each piece features a unique flavor and fun colors that make every lick a memorable experience! Simply peel away the hard candy wrapper and you are ready to snack. Each piece is individually wrapped so they are easy to store and can be given as party favors or a special treat for the kids!We carry a huge list of exciting flavors so you never get bored. Try exotic pina colada, orange pineapple or rum and butter! If you prefer something simpler, classic bubblegum, peppermint, sassafras or strawberry are just as enticing. You\'ll love watching the striped candy melt away with each bite! Grab the old family photo album and your favorite flavors and relive your childhood memories with Gilliam hard candy sticks!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', '2629~stick-candy-assorted-candystore_1_1.jpg', 'old-fashioned-stick-candy-box-flavors'),
(2630, 'Peppermint Twists Mints', 19.99, '', '', 'hard-candy', 'Peppermint twists pack all of the flavor of a candy cane into a single bite-sized candy. Just seeing and tasting them will put you in the holiday spirit, no matter what time of year it is. Don\'t miss out on delicious peppermint candies all year round. Get a bag of these individually wrapped peppermint twists and liven up your home or your office. No special occasion is necessary to bring out these delicious peppermint candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', '2630~peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'peppermint-twists'),
(2631, 'Blue Foil Grape Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'These little candies contain a whole lot of flavor. They are blue in color and the wrappers that are used for them are blue as well. However, the flavor that you get from these candies is a pleasant grape flavor. This is a flavor that can be enjoyed by people of all ages and that makes it great for nearly any occasion. Since they are blue you could consider using them for a baby shower if you wanted to as well. These candies are sure to be a hit. They are hard candies and you can either suck on them or crunch on them when eating them which is great for those who like the way that hard candies feel in their mouths when they bit them. They come in a bulk bag which means that there will be plenty to go around no matter what occasion you are using them for.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2631~blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'blue-foil-raspberry-hard-candy'),
(2632, 'Jolly Rancher Candy', 89.99, '30', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Howdy, partner. Meet the wildest and most delicious candy in the west, Jolly Ranchers! Their bright, fruity flavors and glossy, hard candy shell are sure to put a spur in your taste buds and make your mouth say, \'\'yeeehaw!\'\' In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Add some to a candy buffet bar, a birthday party goodie bag station, or just keep them around the house for a delicious sweet fix. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-main-470x470_2.jpg', '2632~jolly-ranchers-main-470x470_2.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-candy-bulk-case'),
(2633, 'Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'All kids are looking for sunshine, happiness and rainbows in their lives and when they are given Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candy the sunshine is just a shiny wrapper away. It is the wrapper that first draws your attention. Who doesn\'t like a shiny present? It will be exactly like Christmas morning as you hold one of these lemony treats in your hand and start to unwrap it. As the wrapper is opened it will reveal a bright yellow hard candy treat like you dream about right in your hand. You might have wondered what sunshine tastes like, but once you try one of the Silver Foil Lemon Hard Candies you will be pretty sure that it tastes a lot like lemon. With a convenient bulk bag of treats there will be enough sunshine to share with a whole office or classroom or people. People can\'t help but smile and be in a good mood when they eat this delicious treat. This makes it a natural for wedding receptions as all people want to start their new lives with a whole lot of smiles and sunshine.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', '2633~silver_foil_lemon_hard_candy.jpeg', 'silver-foil-lemon-hard-candy'),
(2634, 'Assorted Rods Hard Candy', 63.99, '14.5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Get ready for a mouthful of classic deliciousness! In sour cherry, butterscotch, apple, licorice, tangerine, strawberry, peppermint, pineapple, wild cherry, and lemon, these amazing Assorted Rods Hard Candies will satisfy any sweet tooth. Covered in a crinkly, pretty cellophane wrapper, these little hard candies make a great addition to any gift basket or present. Wrap some up in goodie bags for a little one\'s birthday, set an assortment out in a candy dish, even bring some to a friend\'s house the next time you visit. The fruity rainbow of these hard candies is sure to please candy lovers of all ages.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/s/assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', '2634~assorted-rods-hard-candy-14lb_1.jpg', 'rods-hard-candy-assorted'),
(2635, 'Hard Candy Twists', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Individually wrapped in clear cellophane with a rainbow of colors within the candy, they can add a big pop of color and taste to any event. Do the twist! The Hard Candy Twists! In all of the gleaming, iridescent glory, these Hard Candy Twists are beautiful candies with huge flavor.Brighten up your household candy dishes at the end of winter in preparation for warmer temperatures that come with springtime with and order of these Hard Candy Twists. They also can be used as gorgeous wedding candy, party favors, gift basket additions, or displayed in glass jars ion your kitchen counter. Who doesn\'t love a candy that looks as lovely as it tastes?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruitie-tootie-hard-candy-twists-atkinson.jpg', '2635~fruitie-tootie-hard-candy-twists-atkinson.jpg', 'hard-candy-twists-fruitie-tootie'),
(2636, 'Red Foil Cherry Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'We\'ve only got eyes for you. That\'s because this Red Foil Cherry Hard Candy is so loveable, it\'s hard for us to love another as much! Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Red Foil Cherry Hard Candies is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-foil-cherry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2636~red-foil-cherry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'red-foil-cherry-hard-candy'),
(2637, 'Claey\'s Wild Cherry Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'What\'s red, sweet, and delicious all over? These Wild Cherry Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops! Dusted in crystalized, sweet sugar, these bright red candies pack a serious punch of wild cherry flavor that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Bring some to a holiday gathering that needs a dose of festive red, use some to decorate a gingerbread house with a delicious treat, add them to a Fourth of July dessert table, or add a yummy, fruity treat to a Valentine\'s Day gift. With this 1 pound order of wild cherry candies, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys-cherry-candy-drops-small.jpg', '2637~claeys-cherry-candy-drops-small.jpg', 'wild-cherry-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2638, 'Runts Candy', 94.99, '30', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Runts candy made its first appearance in the 1980s. While its fruity lineup has changed since then, its popularity has not. Every kid can recognize the fun shapes and bright colors that make Runts so unique. Our extensive collection of bulk candy includes this childhood favorite so you can get your fill of sweet fruity goodness anytime you want! Serve at kid\'s parties, take as a non-perishable snack on camping trips or set some aside to hide away at home for moments when you need a sweet fix!Our Runts candy package include all the current flavors and shapes. You\'ll love biting down on a yellow banana or savoring a tart cherry piece. Each order also includes blue raspberry, watermelon and lime. Try the smooth, sweet taste of your favorite fruits followed by the tantalizing tanginess that makes Runts candies so delectable. You don\'t have to go to a vending machine to find your favorite treat because we have Runts in bulk and ready to ship right to you!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts30lbs.jpg', '2638~runts30lbs.jpg', 'runts-bulk'),
(2639, 'Green Foil Lime Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'If you were blindfolded, you might think that this bright, citrusy candy was made from freshest, just-squeezed limes in all the land. That\'s because these Green Foil Lime Hard Candies have such a powerful lime flavor that it\'s hard to tell. Wrapped in a bright green foil, these candies make the perfect addition to a St. Patrick\'s Day party or springtime event. They look lovely tucked away in an Easter basket too and make a great filler for a green candy display. If your friends and family love the taste of lime and a beautiful emerald green color, these are the perfect candies for you.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-foil-lime-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2639~green-foil-lime-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'green-foil-lime-hard-candy'),
(2640, 'Gold Foil Orange Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Many people love the hard candies that come wrapped in foil. If you are one of these people then you will find that the orange flavored hard candy may be just what you have been looking for. These are a great color of orange and are wrapped in a foil that is gold in color which is able to make them unique and can also make you feel like you are really rolling in the money. Since the color is a festive color you will find that these will look great for any occasion that you want to use them for. This means you can use them at a party, wedding, or even a candy bar. Who would have thought that hard candies could be so full of flavor and color? These are certain to be a hit among almost everyone who has the great pleasure of being able to try them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2640~gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'gold-foil-strawberry-hard-candy'),
(2641, 'Citrus Slices Candy Assorted', 44.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Finally! We\'ve discovered a delicious candy that does grow on trees! These Citrus Slices Candies have all the delicious flavor of some of your favorite fruits and are a beautiful treat to look at. Individually wrapped, each grapefruit, lemon, lime, orange, and tangerine candy treat in green, yellow, pink, orange will make every snacker smile. Bring some to a beach party for a summery, festive treat, add some to a punch to add a burst of bright color and sweet flavor, or even wrap some up in a gift bag for a fruity surprise. These classic citrus slice candies will please every boy and girl.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/citrus-slices-candy-bulk-10lb_1.jpg', '2641~citrus-slices-candy-bulk-10lb_1.jpg', 'citrus-slices-candy'),
(2642, 'Lifesavers Hard Candy 5 Flavors 41oz', 13.99, '', '', 'hard-candy', 'Lifesavers hard candy brings big flavor in a little package. There\'s a lot to love in every bag of Lifesavers, especially if you have hard time picking out just one flavor. You can taste all your favorites with our enormous bulk Lifesaver bag! This package offers a great value with more of the hard candy you love. Order for at home or bring a bag into the office or worksite so you can share with everyone! Teachers can reward their students with a sweet treat and parents can fill treat bags with lifesavers for parties and other events.Lifesavers are more than just a hard candy: they are an edible piece of the past. These renowned sweets were originally made in 1913. Things were different back then and it wasn\'t until 1925 that the iconic hole was added to each disc. Today you can get all the fruity flavor you want with our bulk Lifesaver package!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/f/5flavors41oz.jpg', '2642~5flavors41oz.jpg', 'lifesavers-hard-candy-41ct'),
(2643, 'Claey\'s Root Beer Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'We\'re rooting for these classic candies. That\'s because Claey\'s Root beer Old-Fashioned Candy Drops are completely coated in crystally, crunchy sugar granules that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Beyond the saccharine coating, lies a delicious hard candy. They\'ll take you back to a warm, summer\'s day of sipping a refreshing root beer float. Stock up on some to add to root beer treats, add to a gift basket, or put out on the Thanksgiving table. Among root beer, Claey\'s favorite flavors include green apple, licorice, natural horehound, watermelon, lemon, and wild cherry. They\'ll look lovely in your coffee table candy dish or set out in a jar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', '2643~root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.jpg', 'root-beer-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2644, 'C. Howard\'s Mints', 22.99, '24', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Get a taste of the olden days with this bulk selection of C. Howard\'s Mints! In vintage flavors of lemon, peppermint, spearmint, and unique violet, you\'ll have the pleasure of tasting a bit of history. Their cute, retro wrappers add a vintage feel to their deliciousness and make them perfect for a nostalgic candy selection. These little candies have been around since the 1930s and have graced both old and new candy store shelves. Give your friends and family a sample of a tried and true candy that has stood the test of time with a box of these today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-howards-mints-24ct_2.gif', '2644~c-howards-mints-24ct_2.gif', 'c-howards-mints'),
(2645, 'Napoleon Sour Bon Bons Candy', 49.99, '7', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'If you love bonbons and sour candy, now you can have both in a single bite-sized confection! This exciting treat is sure to make even the most resilient lips pucker up.Every piece consists of a delightful round orb of solid candy with a gentle texture that\'s pleasantly tart on the tongue. Each assortment of Napoleon sour bon bons comes in a number of eye-catching colors, like yellow, orange, green and white.Every Napoleon bon bon is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can see the colorful candy inside before you open the next piece. The wrapper includes a classic logo printed on one side with elegant stripes along each side.All it takes is a quick twist to reveal the delicious treat and experience super sour flavor. Our bulk Napoleon sour bon bons gives you many candies that are perfect for businesses, guests, special events and party favors.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/s/assorted-napoleons-bon-bons.jpg', '2645~assorted-napoleons-bon-bons.jpg', 'napoleon-sour-bon-bons-candy'),
(2646, 'Life Savers Candy', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Laver Savers candies have been around for many years. They are enjoyed by everyone from children to adults. These great candies are available in many different colors such as red, purple, green, orange, white, and even yellow. You can get many different flavors such as wild cherry, grape, lime, pineapple, orange, and even butter rum. You are sure to find a flavor that you are able to enjoy. You are also sure to find that these small hard, crunchy candies are able to provide a great deal of taste that you are sure to be pleased with. These candies are great for birthday parties, Halloween, weddings, and more. They come in rolls and you can choose from multi-flavored rolls, or the ones that one has a single flavor depending on your preference. There is nothing that can take you back to your childhood more than the great taste of Life Savers.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', '2646~life-savers-candy-20ct.jpg', 'life-savers-rolls'),
(2647, 'Charms Sour Balls Tins', 42.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'When it comes to making friends, candy is a great ice breaker. Choosing the right candy will determine how successful you are at this endeavor. Charms Sour Balls are definitely the right candy. These delicious hard candy treats make the young happy and the old nostalgic. There is a power in the sour ball that will win friends because it is the perfect combination of both sweet and sour that appeal to everyone. They come in cherry, grape, lemon, lime and of course orange. When you see a tin of these delicious treats, you can\'t help think of Christmas and other celebrations. Once a can is open it is nearly impossible to stop the smiles and good times. With a whole tin of this candy on your side, you will be able to win a whole lot of new friends and in the end, would you want to be friends with someone who didn\'t like Charms Sour Balls?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', '2647~charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz-12ct_1.jpg', 'charms-sour-balls-tins-12oz'),
(2648, 'Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags', 39.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Leave it to Jolly Ranchers to provide a delicious, colorful and fun treat that is also good for you. While providing all of the expected value expected from Jolly Rancher, they upped the ante by making their snacks sugar free as well! The classic candy comes individually wrapped to keep in the unique freshness. Each piece of candy provides a classic blast of fruit refreshment without the worry of taking in any extra sugar that will make parents and dentists smile. This treat can be enjoyed all by yourself or with a bunch of your friends. Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags make it always seem like a party. Enjoy the explosion of fruit flavor in your mouth without any of the guilt. Get the best Jolly Rancher hard candy that has your favorite flavor, watermelon, apple, grape or raspberry. Not only are these treats sugar free but each candy contains only 1 calories, which means that you can enjoy your fruity flavored candies all day long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', '2648~jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-sugar-free-candy-bags'),
(2649, 'Claey\'s Watermelon Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'We think these candies are \'\'de-vine.\'\' That\'s because these amazing Watermelon Cherry Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops are the most delicious candy in the patch! Dusted in powdery, sweet sugar, these bright red candies pack a serious punch of watermelon flavor that will make your taste buds jump for joy. Bring some to a holiday gathering that needs a dose of festive red, drop a few into a cold lemonade or punch for a sweeter, fruity flavor, add them to a Fourth of July dessert table, or make a Valentine\'s Day gift even yummier. With this 1 pound order of watermelon candies, you\'ll have enough to go around.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.gif', '2649~watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_2.gif', 'watermelon-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2650, 'Charms Squares Candy', 24.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Cherry, Grape, Lemon, Lime, Orange, and Raspberry combine to make one incredibly delicious pack of treats in this Charms Squares Candy order. You\'ll be in for a surprise every time you unwrap one of the packet\'s 10 candies and stuff it into your mouth.Charms are known for their sour sweet treats and this supply isn\'t short in any of the above. If this sounds like a match made in heaven for you, then why not order yourself some of our Charms Squares Candies today? They\'ll wow all of your guests, impress your family and keep you snacking with a smile on your face for days and days.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charms-squares-candy-20ct.gif', '2650~charms-squares-candy-20ct.gif', 'charms-squares'),
(2651, 'Aquarium Hard Candy Fish', 49.99, '15', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Where does the fish keep his money? In the river bank! These Aquarium Hard Candies are a lovely reminder of summertime and the beautiful ocean and will make every candy lover smile. They\'re just as intricate as the natural ocean variety, but a million times more delicious. In a variety of colors and flavors from under the sea there\'s a flavor for every beach-lover. Use them for a luau-themed party. Throw a beachside bash for all of your friends. Even enjoy one while you\'re sitting on the hot sand. Or give them to a fishing fanatic you know. Just make sure you\'re not \'\'shellfish\'\' with these delicious candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/q/aquarium-hard-candy-fish-candystore.jpg', '2651~aquarium-hard-candy-fish-candystore.jpg', 'aquarium-hard-candy-fish'),
(2652, 'Runts Theater Size', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Runts theater boxes are a fun way to enjoy this fruit candy. There are so many reasons to love this Willy Wonka favorite.Runts are small hard candies that are shaped to resemble their real fruit counterparts. Each package contains brilliantly colored bananas, berries and much more! You\'ll find classic flavors like lime, strawberry and banana combined with two new flavors: watermelon and blue raspberry!Our bulk Runts pack contains many individual theater boxes that are ideal for gift giving, events and much more! Make family movie night even more exciting by serving up theater box candy Ã just like the kind they sell at the cinema concession stands!Spread the fruity love by giving Runts as Christmas stocking stuffers or use them to add unique style when decorating cakes, cookies and other baked goods. There\'s so much just one little Runts can do! Also check out our other Willy Wonka theater box candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts---theater-size-12ct_1.jpg', '2652~runts---theater-size-12ct_1.jpg', 'runts-theater-size'),
(2653, 'Lite Pink Foil Hard Candy', 18.49, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Treat your taste buds to tutti frutti flavor with our light pink foil wrapped hard candies! This simple treat is great for any occasion. Hard candy is popular because it last a long time and is really easy to take with you.Grab a handful and bring along while running errands. Hide them in your desk drawer so you have an easy sweet snack while at work. Our hard candy comes individually wrapped in a gorgeous metallic foil. This version features a brilliant pink hue that makes each piece look luxurious.Hard candy wrapped in foil looks stunning in candy dishes and jars. Offer to customers by leaving them at the counter (or wherever you do business). Use them to create beautiful wedding favors or add them to baby shower favors for girls! Our bulk pink hard candy package gives you plenty of bite-sized pieces for gift giving, sharing or simple snacking.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lightpinkfoilwrapped.jpeg', '2653~lightpinkfoilwrapped.jpeg', 'pink-foil-peach-hard-candy'),
(2654, 'Life Savers Pep O Mint', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Is your mouth screaming \'\'SOS\'\' for a breath freshening treat? Well, these Life Savers Pep-O-Mint and Wint-O-Green are here to save the day! Let them toss you a life preserver for your taste buds with their fresh minty flavor and classic \'\'O\'\' shaped form. This hero of the candy world has been around since 1912 and has saved mouths all over the world. Pep-O-Mint was the first flavor and quickly made an impression in the mouths of many. Since then, a variety of fruity and other mint flavors have been invented. Try these minty rolls on for size and see for yourself if you think they\'re worthy of their heroic name!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', '2654~mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', 'mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct'),
(2655, 'Green Apple Claey\'s Old Fashioned Candy Drops', 29.99, '10', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Claey\'s old-fashioned green apple candy drops are a tasty treat that comes with history. The brand has been producing high quality classic treats since 1919. For three generations, Claey\'s Candy has been giving the world some of the best old time confections available.Their selection includes a number of nostalgic favorites, like fudge, Chocolate Charlie and irresistible old fashioned candy drops. Green apple candy drops are available in bulk quantities so you get more juicy flavor in every package! These round little tidbits are a great choice for family gatherings like reunions, picnics and birthday parties.Share them with loved ones when they come to visit or keep a sweet stash on hand to satisfy apple and sugar cravings. Candy has become a longstanding tradition in the Claey family, and now it can become a tradition in your family! Order your bulk green apple candy drops today and enjoy the memories packed into every piece.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_1.jpg', '2655~green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops-10lb_1.jpg', 'green-apple-claeys-old-fashioned-candy-drops'),
(2656, 'Lifesavers Butterrum', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Butter rum Lifesavers candy is a sweet treat with classic personality. While it may not be as outrageous as wild cherry or as refreshing as wint-o-green, butter rum is packed with tasty sweetness that satisfies like no other candy can. This rich blend of flavors is even better when packed into each hard candy hoop. Lifesavers are easy to enjoy and come in a convenient tube package that you can place in a purse, pocket, desk drawer or wherever you may be when cravings hit!The history of the Lifesaver candy begins in 1912 when Clarence Crane invented the hard mint version. At the time he needed a pill manufacturer to produce the shape of each piece. It wasn\'t until 1925 that the familiar hole was added, creating the popular donut shape we all know and love today. Our bulk Lifesaver candy boxes are a great choice for offices, schools or anyone planning an event.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lifesaversbutterrum.jpg', '2656~lifesaversbutterrum.jpg', 'lifesavers-butterrum-20ct'),
(2657, 'Spree Candy', 37.99, '36', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'It is a dilemma as old as Spree candies themselves: eat just one and enjoy its sweet-and-sour flavor individually, or snack your way through the whole roll?The carefree name and colorful purple-based packaging make it no surprise that Spree is one of the Willy Wonka Candy Company confections, and there are some sweet tooths among us who feel that the candy disks unique texture and bold flavor make them the best. This box of bulk Spree rolls offers the colorful sweets in a convenient form great for traveling.Each cylindrical package is a party favor or picnic dessert in itself! The bright colors of this oh-so-simple sour sweet are instantly appealing to kids â€“ and nostalgic to those who grew up in the days of rainbow confections gorgeously assorted in sweet-shop jars.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spree-candy-36ct_1.gif', '2657~spree-candy-36ct_1.gif', 'spree-candy'),
(2658, 'Altoids Cinnamon', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Altoids cinnamon candy are more than just a curiously strong mint. These refreshing treats are a confection that comes with a long, rich history. The original recipe was created by a London-based company in the 1780s, when King George III sat on the throne. The product\'s high concentration of peppermint oil is what inspired the popular slogan we all know and love today. Altoids are currently available in six different flavors, including cinnamon. The storage tin was introduced in the 1920s and still helps keep each mint fresh and clean, even while on the go. Our bulk mint package is a convenient option for anyone who never wants to go without their favorite candy! Hide a tin in your purse or pocket or keep them in the glove box. The larger quantity is also great to share at the office or while on the job. Invigorate your mouth with Altoids cinnamon mints!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoidscinnamon.jpg', '2658~altoidscinnamon.jpg', 'altoids-cinnamon-12ct');
