(2659, 'Lifesavers Wild Cherry', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Wild cherry Lifesavers is a quick and easy snack that everyone can enjoy! Each hard candy piece is filled with sweet cherry flavor. Just open the end and treat your taste buds to the irresistible taste of fresh picked cherry sweetness! Lifesavers aren\'t just delicious â€“ they are also convenient! Each box contains individual packages that you can keep anywhere. Hide them in your desk, purse, pocket or car so you always have something to satisfy your sweet tooth!Lifesavers candy is a classic confection that was created in 1912. The original hard mints were later expanded upon with wintergreen, clove, chocolate, cinnamon and violet flavors. Today we can enjoy a huge list of Lifesavers, including succulent wild cherry! Our bulk candy box makes these treats even better because you can get more hard candy to store or share. Just order a box or two and you will always have something to give guests, coworkers or clients!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/i/wildcherrylifesavers.jpg', '2659~wildcherrylifesavers.jpg', 'lifesavers-wild-cherry-20ct'),
(2660, 'Banana Heads Candy', 99.99, '30', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'What was Beethoven\'s favorite fruit? Ba-na-na-naaa. Ba-na-na-naa. We may have slipped up with that cheesy joke, but we\'re just such big fans of these Banana Heads Candies that we can\'t help ourselves! These adorable, little yellow banana hard candies are a great treat that everyone can enjoy. Bring some home for your little monkeys to munch on. Stock up on these to add to a summertime tropical pool party. Even keep these around the house to add as decoration to the top of baked goods and ice cream sundaes. You\'ll love these little yellow fruits no matter what you do with them. Plus, they look just like Banana Runts.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/banana-heads-candy-30lbs_2.jpg', '2660~banana-heads-candy-30lbs_2.jpg', 'banana-heads-candy-bulk'),
(2661, 'SweeTarts Candy Rolls', 37.99, '36', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Make snack time more interesting with the tangy and sweet taste of SweeTarts candy! Our SweeTarts candy rolls offer the classic flavor you love in a bigger package. Each roll is individually wrapped to form a tube that fits easily into a pocket, purse or wherever you prefer to keep it.Simply tear open one end and grab a disc shaped piece from inside! SweeTarts were introduced in 1962. They were inspired by powdery Lik-M-Aid and Pixy Stix. The decision to create a compressed version came when parents complained that powdery candies were too messy. Now kids can enjoy that same tangy taste without getting powder all over their hands, clothes and faces!Our bulk SweeTarts candy rolls are perfect for special events and much more. Use them to fill up birthday party treat bags or give as a special treat during the holidays. From stocking stuffers to prizes for games, our SweeTarts are a delicious confection for the young and young at heart!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/sweetarts-candy-rolls-36ct_1.gif', '2661~sweetarts-candy-rolls-36ct_1.gif', 'sweetarts-candy-rolls'),
(2662, 'Jones Soda Carbonated Candy', 20.99, '8', 'ct', 'hard-candy', 'Jones Soda carbonated candy offers a new way to enjoy your favorite beverage! Classic Jones Soda is a popular choice because it is made using cane sugar instead of unhealthy high fructose corn syrup.If you enjoy a cold, refreshing Jones Soda, then you must try these unique candies. Each package includes small pill shaped pieces that are sweet and tangy with a touch of tingly carbonation. Along with a one-of-a-kind taste, Jones Soda carbonated candy also comes in an elegant branded tin. Each tine includes a black background with Jones in shimmering silver. The tin container keeps your mints fresh and easy to carry.Hide a pack in your pocket, purse, glove box or desk drawer. Jones Soda carbonated candy also makes a great gift or stocking stuffer. You can get larger quantities with our convenient Jones Soda carbonated candy in bulk! Keep a box at home or take to the office to share with coworkers and clients.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jones-soda-carbonated-candy.jpg', '2662~jones-soda-carbonated-candy.jpg', 'jones-soda-carbonated-candy-green-apple'),
(2663, 'Chocolate Covered Espresso Beans', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'hard-candy', 'Did somebody order a wake up call? This double whammy of eye-opening espresso and chocolate will definitely get the job done. With their creamy dark chocolate coating and bite of brittle espresso beans, these Chocolate Covered Espresso Beans are a \'\'wowza\'\' in your mouth. Make your own ice cream and sprinkle a few handfuls of these beans into the mixer, chop them up and add them to biscotti, even drop a few in your morning cup of coffee or set them around the house for light snacking. You won\'t want to set the snooze button with a bite of one of these delectable morsels.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-espresso-beans-5lb.jpg', '2663~chocolate-covered-espresso-beans-5lb.jpg', 'espresso-beans-chocolate-covered'),
(2664, 'German Raspberries', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo German raspberries recreate the sweet taste of this popular fruit in an irresistible confection! Each bag contains a combination of red and black berry candies. Instead of sticking with plain gummies, Haribo creates a smooth, chewy center that\'s covered in dainty orbs of sugary goodness. Every bite presents two distinct textures in one tasty tidbit! Order our bulk raspberry candies for special events or snacking at home. Whether you\'re hosting a party, picnic, school event or wedding, our German raspberries are a great choice! Haribo has been serving up some of the most delectable gummy candies for nearly a century. Today their catalog includes many unique confections that offer mouthwatering flavor in little bite sized pieces. Our bulk German raspberries are easy to store so you can hide a bag in your favorite snacking spots so you\'re ready the next time your sweet tooth strikes! Haribo gummy candy will tempt taste buds and satisfy cravings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/e/germanraspberries.jpeg', '2664~germanraspberries.jpeg', 'german-raspberries-12ct'),
(2665, 'Haribo Gummi Gold Bears Mini Bags Tub', 13.99, '54', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'We sure think that these gummies are \'\'tastier than the average bear!\'\' That\'s because these classic Haribo Gold Gummi Bears are here in a bulk bag to bring you even more of the delicious flavors you love. In a selection of red, orange, yellow, green, and white, everyone in your family will find a cub to love. Sprinkle a few in Jell-O for a \'\'beary\'\' good surprise, add some to a make your own sundae bar, or wrap some up for a loved one to make their day extra special. Haribo first made their chewy debut in 1922 in Germany with the creation of the famous Gummi Bear.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', '2665~haribo-gold-bears-54ct.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-gold-bears-mini-bags-tub'),
(2666, 'Gummi Frogs', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Everyone will jump for joy when they get a taste of Haribo gummy frogs! These little green candies aren\'t slippery and slimy, but they offer a smooth, soft texture that\'s pleasant on the tongue. Each piece includes fun details that recreate this popular amphibian â€“ right down to its folded legs, round head and raised back. Our gummy frogs are solid green and arrive fresh in sealed bags that are ready to enjoy! Hide gummi frogs around the house or save them to put in school lunches for the kids. These charming croakers are also great for serving at birthday parties, picnics and school events. Put them in a bowl or use them to dress up cakes, cupcakes, cookies and more! No matter how you display them, our Haribo gummy candies will entice children of all ages. Order our bulk candy pack so you have plenty of chewy frogs for any occasion!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', '2666~haribo-gummy-frogs.jpg', 'gummi-frogs-12ct'),
(2667, 'Gummi Fruit Salad', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo gummi fruit salad combines all your favorite flavors in one convenient package! Since 1920, Haribo has been producing new confections for the world to enjoy. Their current selection features a number of the most popular sugary snacks, including our irresistible gummy fruit salad! Every bag contains a selection of brightly colored chewy pieces that feature recognizable shapes that make mouths water.Reach into a bag of gummy fruit salad and enjoy the sweet sensation of orange, lime, cherry and more! Every piece is brightly colored in red, green, orange and other hues that match their fruity counterparts. This fat free candy is covered in a generous dusting of sugar for added texture and taste. Enjoy it as a guilt-free snack at home or buy our bulk candy pack and get plenty of Haribo fruit pieces to serve at any event. This nature-inspired confection is a big hit at picnics, parties, summer events and school activities!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/0/108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', '2667~108015-haribo-fruit-salad-gummy-candy.jpg', 'gummi-fruit-salad-12ct'),
(2668, 'Gummi Happy Cola Bottles', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo Happy Cola bottle candies are a fun way to enjoy the fizzy flavor of a soda without a glass. This unique confection includes classic bottle-shaped pieces that are reminiscent of antique Coke bottles. The top half is clear with detailed bands around the middle and a narrow top where the cap would normally be. The bottom half is dark amber brown, just like a refreshing drink of cola on a hot summer\'s day!Our Haribo Happy Cola gummies will put a smile on everyone\'s face as the bite down on the distinct taste of their favorite sugary beverage! Now you can get bulk cola bottle candies so you get more fizzy fun with your order. Save them for snack time and school lunches or put them out as a special treat for guests at birthday parties, picnics and family reunions. No matter what you\'re celebrating, Haribo Happy cola bottle gummies will make the event more exciting!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-happycola.jpg', '2668~haribo-happycola.jpg', 'gummi-happy-cola-bottles-12ct'),
(2669, 'Gummi Peaches', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Life\'s a peach when you have Haribo gummy candies! This company made itself famous for introducing some of the most fun and tasty chewy snacks to the world, including their irresistible peaches. This fruity candy includes round peach-shaped pieces in orange and red. Each is covered in a delicious dusting of sugar and includes sweet, succulent flavor that excites the taste buds. Take a bite and let your mind wander through sprawling orchards with plump, fresh picked peaches waiting in bushel baskets. Unlike the real thing, our Haribo gummy peaches never over ripen. Every bite is just as delectable as the last! Now you can get your fill of peachy goodness because we offer a bulk candy pack that gives you more ounces. Order for picnics, parties, school events or simply to enjoy anytime your craving something sweet and savory. Keep your candy dish full with Haribo peach gummy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-peaches.jpg', '2669~haribo-peaches.jpg', 'gummi-peaches-12ct'),
(2670, 'Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags', 39.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Leave it to Jolly Ranchers to provide a delicious, colorful and fun treat that is also good for you. While providing all of the expected value expected from Jolly Rancher, they upped the ante by making their snacks sugar free as well! The classic candy comes individually wrapped to keep in the unique freshness. Each piece of candy provides a classic blast of fruit refreshment without the worry of taking in any extra sugar that will make parents and dentists smile. This treat can be enjoyed all by yourself or with a bunch of your friends. Jolly Rancher Sugar Free Candy Bags make it always seem like a party. Enjoy the explosion of fruit flavor in your mouth without any of the guilt. Get the best Jolly Rancher hard candy that has your favorite flavor, watermelon, apple, grape or raspberry. Not only are these treats sugar free but each candy contains only 1 calories, which means that you can enjoy your fruity flavored candies all day long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', '2670~jolly_rancher_sugar_free.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-sugar-free-candy-bags'),
(2671, 'Haribo Gummi Alphabet Letters 5oz Bag', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo always finds a way to make everyone\'s favorite gummy candy even better! Now you can order a large package of our extra tasty Haribo gummy letters! This alphabet-inspired snack is sweet, chewy and â€“ best of all â€“ educational! Help little ones learn their consonants and vowels by turning snack time into reading time! Each package contains an assortment of edible letters in bright colors. Your child will love spelling out vocabulary words that they can eat!Our gummy alphabet treats are a must-have for school lunches and events. They are the perfect fat free candy for child care businesses and others who work with little ones. Whether you\'re a teacher, parent or simply someone who loves the fruity taste of gummies, you will love our Haribo letters! Each bulk candy pack contains a generous number of gummy pieces so you have enough to share at picnics, classroom parties or family events!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/alphabetletters.jpg', '2671~alphabetletters.jpg', 'haribo-gummi-alphabet-letters-5oz-bag-12ct'),
(2672, 'Life Savers Pep O Mint', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Is your mouth screaming \'\'SOS\'\' for a breath freshening treat? Well, these Life Savers Pep-O-Mint and Wint-O-Green are here to save the day! Let them toss you a life preserver for your taste buds with their fresh minty flavor and classic \'\'O\'\' shaped form. This hero of the candy world has been around since 1912 and has saved mouths all over the world. Pep-O-Mint was the first flavor and quickly made an impression in the mouths of many. Since then, a variety of fruity and other mint flavors have been invented. Try these minty rolls on for size and see for yourself if you think they\'re worthy of their heroic name!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', '2672~mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct_2.gif', 'mint-life-savers-pep-o-mint-20ct'),
(2673, 'Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars 12 Bags', 39.99, '', '', 'bagged-candy', 'You won\'t find a smidgen of guilt in this bulk supply of Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars. These mouthwatering treats have only 32 calories each, and are perfect for chocoholics with diabetes. Hershey made these divine treats as part of its Special Dietary Needs line.They are sweetened with sugar alcohols, which coincidently are not sugar or alcohol, but a natural product with a unique chemical structure that resembles both sugar and alcohol. Each one of the Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars is individually wrapped, so you can easily share, slip them in lunches, and stash them in your desk.All you have to do is see that iconic dark brown logo and taste buds start getting a little crazy. Then, you notice the words Sugar Free, and assume you must be dreaming. Is it possible to enjoy melt-in-your-mouth, creamy chocolate without all the sugar? Well, you might not think it\'s possible, but our Hershey\'s Sugar Free Milk Chocolate Bars prove dreams really do come true.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-sugar-free-milk-chocolate-bars-12-bags_1.jpg', '2673~hersheys-sugar-free-milk-chocolate-bars-12-bags_1.jpg', 'hersheys-sugar-free-milk-chocolate-bars-bags'),
(2674, 'Red Vines Sugar Free Strawberry Licorice Vines', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Sugar free Vines licorice is the best way to enjoy your favorite childhood treat! Everyone loves the smooth, chewy taste of classic licorice. It\'s been around for decades and has become a fast favorite among the young and young at heart.Our Red Vines licorice makes the experience even better because you can enjoy the same sweet strawberry taste with no fat so every snacking session is guilt-free! Each piece includes a length of irresistible red licorice with a juicy strawberry flavor. The vines include flat ends with a twisted design that runs from top to bottom, adding unique texture to every bite.Our bulk red licorice pack includes individual bags that are great for travel or sharing. Simply hide a bag of licorice wherever you need it so you always have a treat within reach. Tuck one in the glove box before a long car ride or stow red licorice in luggage so you have an easy snack while away from home!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-vines-sugar-free-strawberry-licorice-vines-12ct.jpg', '2674~red-vines-sugar-free-strawberry-licorice-vines-12ct.jpg', 'red-vines-sugar-free-strawberry-licorice-vines'),
(2675, 'Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Box', 19.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Feel like you\'re sitting on a stool at your neighborhood ice cream shoppe every time you take a candy out of one these Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Boxes. If you love the original malted milk ball, these sweet strawberry coated candies will blow your mind.Since these Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Boxes are a lovely shade of light pink, it makes them perfect for gift baskets for about to be moms of little girls. They also fit right in among bachelorette candy or breast cancer awareness events. Keep these Whoppers Strawberry Milkshake Theatre Boxes closed or dump the candy out into dishes to add a pretty and tasty treat to your candy jars.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/whoppers_strawberry_milkshake.jpg', '2675~whoppers_strawberry_milkshake.jpg', 'strawberry-milkshake-whoppers-theatre-box'),
(2676, 'Ginger Lemon Gummi Peg Bags', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Zesty and tangy, our ginger lemon gummies are the perfect way to wake up your taste buds! These unusual sweet treats combine two popular flavors into one original snack. Each piece is made using Haribo\'s soft and chewy recipe so you know you\'re getting a high quality candy that\'s full of irresistible flavor! Each piece is covered in a sugary coating to tempt the senses and enhance the experience found in each bite. Our ginger lemon candy is truly a one-of-a-kind Haribo creation! These round morsels come in a soft, pale yellow color and are reminiscent of soothing cough drops. Once hugely popular in Europe, now you can buy them anywhere when you order online with us! Our bulk gummy package gives you more ginger lemon drop pieces so you have enough to last. Enjoy them at home or put them out as a unique snack to share with friends and family. Haribo ginger lemon gummy candies are fat-free and delicious!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-lemon-ginger-bags-icon.jpg', '2676~haribo-lemon-ginger-bags-icon.jpg', 'ginger-lemon-gummi-peg-pags-12ct'),
(2677, 'Brite Sour Gummi Candy 12ct Bags', 23.99, 'Octop', 'us', 'bagged-candy', 'Why didn\'t the octopus go to the zoo? He had an \'\'ink-ling\'\' that it would rain! These Trolli Brite Octopus Sour Gummi Candy are as funny as they are delicious and we\'re sure you\'ll love them from first bite. With 8 legs of delicious, sour gummy chew, you\'ll have a ton of snacking to do with every candy.Bring some home if you have a family who loves everything aquatic. Add some to a pinata to make the little ones squeal. Even give them to someone as a gag gift if they get the heeby jeebies from these creepy sea crawlers. Whatever you do, you\'ll love these tentacles of delicious flavor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/brite-octopus-sour-gummi-candy-12ct-bags_1.gif', '2677~brite-octopus-sour-gummi-candy-12ct-bags_1.gif', 'brite-octopus-sour-gummi-octopi-bags'),
(2678, 'Fizzy Cola Bags', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Your taste buds will dance with delight when they feel the tingly sensation that comes with each bite of our Haribo fizzy cola gummies! These soda pop candies are guaranteed to be a big hit with any age group! Serve them up at birthday parties, holiday events, picnics or any other occasion you want to make a little sweeter. When you can\'t have a gulp of your favorite cola beverage, you can always reach for Haribo fizzy cola candy!Each piece includes a classic shape with a clear white top and rich brown bottom, just like a half full glass bottle of your favorite cola! You never have to twist off a cap or worry about recycling a bottle with these tasty tidbits. Just bite down and enjoy every mouthful of fizzy goodness! You\'ll love the unique blend of tangy, sweet and sour flavor that comes with our Haribo fizzy cola gummies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/i/fizzycola.jpg', '2678~fizzycola.jpg', 'fizzy-cola-bags-12ct'),
(2679, 'Gummi Bears 12 Flavor Peg Bag 9oz', 19.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Taste the difference high quality ingredients make when you enjoy Albanese gummy bears! This candy company knows how to bring out the best in the confections it produces.For more than 30 years, Albanese has been improving its recipes and techniques to bring candy lovers across the world a collection of the finest gummy candy available. Now you can get more of the Albanese gummy bears you love in one convenient order! Our bulk gummy bears include several peg bags that are wonderful for storage and sharing. Keep a bag in the car, your desk drawer at work or wherever you like to snack at home. Give them out as a gift to friends and family or use them to fill the office candy jar.Everyone will love the 12 exciting flavors packed into every peg bag! Our Albanese gummy bears offer chewy pieces that feature a dozen intense flavors, including green apple, blue raspberry, lime, lemon, pineapple, grape, mango, orange, pink grapefruit, wild cherry and strawberry.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/2/12-flavor-wild-fruit-bears_albanese_peg_bag_9oz.jpg', '2679~12-flavor-wild-fruit-bears_albanese_peg_bag_9oz.jpg', 'gummi-bears-12-flavor-peg-bag-9oz'),
(2680, 'Brite Crawlers Sour Gummi Worms Theater Bags', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Once upon a time, a bunch of worms crawled into a nuclear power plant site and ate radioactive dirt. From that day forward, they grew and grew until they became sour, neon and gummy! Who knows if the folklore is true, but we can tell you one thing: that these Brite Crawlers Sour Gummi Worms sure seem like a crazy science experiment!That\'s because these Brite Crawlers come in a rainbow of neon colors and are coated in a super sour sugar. If you\'re up to the task of gobbling down sour as can be gummi worms in bright as the sun hues, then order yourself a bulk supply. They\'re sure to wriggly, crawl and slither down your throat and make you smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/brite-crawlers-sour-gummi-worms-12ct-bags_1.gif', '2680~brite-crawlers-sour-gummi-worms-12ct-bags_1.gif', 'brite-crawlers-sour-gummi-worms-bags'),
(2681, 'Fluffy Stuff Cotton Candy 2.5oz', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'No candy store is complete without a selection of light, fluffy, and sweet cotton candy. It has come to be trademark of the summer fun and sweetness and you do not want to miss out on it!  Available in sweet flavors, our cotton candy will bring smiles to the faces of all who enjoy it and everyone who craves that melt in your mouth sensation .Our specially packaged bulk order will give you 12 bags of 25 ounce cotton candy ready to be displayed and ready to sell. Give your customers what they are looking for and make sure to include some of our cotton candy on your next order!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/l/fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-25oz-12ct.gif', '2681~fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-25oz-12ct.gif', 'fluffy-stuff-cotton-candy-bags'),
(2682, 'Sugar Free Reeses Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bag', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'These Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bags are almost too good to be true. With the savory peanut butter filling Reese\'s is famous for and the crinkle cut chocolate exterior, you\'ll feel like you\'re breaking your diet but you won\'t be!Inside every Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bag are individually wrapped mini Reese\'s Cups that are just waiting to be devoured by you. If you love sweets, but don\'t want to eat too much of them, then these are a great candy choice for you. You can sprinkle them on non fat yogurt or ice cream for added deliciousness or even pack some into lunch boxes for a low calorie dessert. Whatever you do, Sugar Free Reese\'s Peanut Butter Cups Peg Bags will keep you coming back for more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar_free_reeses_pegbag.jpg', '2682~sugar_free_reeses_pegbag.jpg', 'sugar-free-reeses-peanut-butter-cups-peg-bag'),
(2683, 'Rainbow Mini Frogs Bag', 20.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Our Haribo rainbow mini frog gummies are ready to hop right in and make snack time even tastier! These fun fruit snacks come in a rainbow of fun colors, including yellow, red and green â€“ of course! Every piece includes a white back that\'s just as soft and chewy. Who doesn\'t love munching on tiny frog candy pieces? These delectable sweets will prove that not all amphibians are covered in slime!Enjoy our rainbow frog gummy pieces alone or use them to decorate birthday cakes, cupcakes, cookies and other baked treats. Our bulk candy package makes it so easy to get larger quantities of chewy frogs to serve at parties, picnics and school events. Pour them in a dish and let guests dive right in or include a handful in party favors. No one will be able to resist the adorable shape and sweet taste that makes Haribo gummies so delightful!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/minirainbowfrogs.jpg', '2683~minirainbowfrogs.jpg', 'rainbow-mini-frogs-bag-12ct'),
(2684, 'Jelly Belly 49 Flavors Mix Bags', 64.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'If you just can\'t decide on one Jelly Belly jelly bean flavor, you need to reach for the 49 flavors assortment! This handsome Jelly Belly bag contains a diverse collection of their finest beans. Each includes the brilliant colors, intense taste and familiar white Jelly Belly brand printed on one side.Grab a handful, come up with your own fun combinations or pick and choose individual jelly beans! Our bulk Jelly Belly 49 flavors mix bags give you more of the candy you love with every order! Stay stocked up in case guests or a demanding sweet tooth show up. Our assortment includes multiple individual bags that feature beautiful Jelly Belly branding that\'s perfect for gift giving.Use them as stocking stuffers, add to Easter basket candy for the kids or include in a gourmet gift basket. Jelly Belly candy is made with love to ensure the best quality and eating experience no matter how many beans you order!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', '2684~jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags'),
(2685, 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/r/dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '2685~dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'dr-pepper-licorice-twists-bags'),
(2686, 'Starburst Peg Bag', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Starburst fruit chews are the sweetest way to get your fruit fix. Each piece is square and includes a soft, chewy texture that feels smooth and tastes amazing!Our bulk Starburst fruit chews include multiple peg bags with individually wrapped blocks of confectionary goodness. Sink your teeth into juicy strawberry, orange, cherry or lemon or combine two flavors for a mouthful of fun!The original Starburst candies were introduced in 1959 as Opal Fruits under the Mars brand in the United Kingdom. They were later renamed Starburst and made available for sale in the United States. Needless to say, Starburst fruit chews were a big hit here in the states!Today they are one of the most popular confections available in grocery stores and candy shops all over the country. Now you can get larger quantities for parties, events, holidays or at home snacking by ordering our convenient bulk Starburst packs!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/starburstpegbag.jpg', '2686~starburstpegbag.jpg', 'starburst-peg-bag-12ct'),
(2687, 'Jelly Belly 20 Flavor Jelly Beans Bags', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly 20 Flavor Jelly Beans Bags - 24ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_20_flavor_jelly_beans_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '2687~jelly_belly_20_flavor_jelly_beans_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-20-flavor-jelly-beans-bags'),
(2688, 'Vidal Ocean Gummies', 18.99, '18', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Make a big splash at snack time by giving the kids a taste of Vidal\'s Ocean Gummies! This fun candy is not only tasty, but also exciting to see. While regular gummy bears usually feature a solid color look, our gummy ocean creatures present a brilliant color with bright exciting colors.Each piece is shaped into a different sea creature. Our bulk package includes 18 4 count packs so the gummies are always fresh â€“ even if you don\'t open it right away! Vidal Ocean Gummies are convenient for gift giving, sharing and casual snacking.Keep a pack anywhere you might crave something sweet, like in the car, at your desk or in the pantry. Open up a few packs and pour into a candy dish to offer guests or use your gummy ocean creatures to decorate cakes and cookies for an ocean or beach themed birthday party!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/i/vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', '2688~vidal-ocean-gummies-candy-store.jpg', 'vidal-ocean-gummies-peg-bag'),
(2689, 'Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties Bags', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'You can almost hear the breath-freshening aaaaah of these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties. That\'s because they\'re both satisfying and low in calories. With melty chocolate covering a potently peppermint center, these Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties are a serious breath of fresh air. If you love Sugar Free York Peppermint Patties but want to try a lower calorie option, these are a great choice for you! Bring some home to keep in your office drawer, put into lunch boxes or serve alongside dessert for guests to eat if they\'re watching their waistlines. Individually wrapped, these glimmering silver wrappers are ready to be ripped open so that you can devour the goodness that awaits inside!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', '2689~sugar_free_peppermint_patties_peg.jpg', 'sf-york-peppermint-patties'),
(2690, 'Claey\'s Horehound Drop Bags', 34.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Old fashioned Claeyâ€™s Horehound Drops are one of the most unique and timeless treats you can put in your mouth. This version helps sooth the throat with a confection thatâ€™s fat free. Each hard candy features the classic round shape produced using a mold and drop method. Horehound is produced using an herb tea thatâ€™s steeped in a copper kettle to bring out the unique mint and licorice taste of Claeyâ€™s Drops.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '2690~claeys_horehound_drop_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'claeys-horehound-drop-bags'),
(2691, 'Apple O\'s Gummi Rings Bag', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Trolli Apple O\'s gummy rings are the perfect candy when you\'re craving something sweet and chewy. Trolli is a longstanding favorite in the candy world. The brand was formed in 1948 and originally sold pasta and noodles.Throughout the next decade, Trolli would expand to offer a selection of jelly fruits and cream drops. Today it is a brand that is most commonly known for its delicious gummy candy!Apple O\'s gummy rings are similar to peach rings with a sour apple flavor. Each piece is round with an open center. One side is white and the other is vibrant green, just like the skin on a Granny Smith apple!Take a bite and enjoy sweet apple flavor with a touch of tangy sugar. Bulk gummy rings are a great treat to serve at events or to use in party favors. Kids love snacking with them and adults will enjoy the unique sweet and sour flavor that makes Trolli gummies so tasty!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/p/apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', '2691~apple-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bag_1.jpg', 'apple-os-gummi-rings-bag'),
(2692, 'Claey\'s Lemon Drop Bags', 34.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Claeyâ€™s Lemon Drops are a longstanding favorite that have been satisfying sweet cravings for decades. This traditional treat includes a bite-sized morsel of hard candy with refreshing lemon citrus flavor. Claeyâ€™s makes their confections the natural way, using California lemons. Each piece is poured into a mold then dropped to produce a unique fruit shape. Enjoy fat free hard candy anytime with Claeyâ€™s Lemon Drops!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/claeys_lemon_drop_bags_-_24ct.png', '2692~claeys_lemon_drop_bags_-_24ct.png', 'claeys-lemon-drop-bags'),
(2693, 'Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings Bags', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Fruity and mild, the flavor of Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings is like no other candy, and the soft, chewy texture is one of the best of the gummy varieties!A bulk package of market-size Peachie O\'s bags makes these fun candy rings easy to pack for car trips and family picnics, and the bags are the perfect size for the movie theater, too! These gummi peach slices are an economical way to enjoy gummi candies on the go. Each Peachie O\'s gummi candy is dusted with sugar and consists of two pretty layers, one yellow and one two-toned red and orange to mimic the hues of real peach fuzz.They make a pretty addition to a warmly-hued candy buffet in summer or fall. Cover a layer cake in Peachie O\'s Gummi Rings for a playful (and edible) geometric decoration Ã or just slide a Peachie O on every finger and wave to your friends.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peachie-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bags_1.gif', '2693~peachie-os-gummi-rings-12ct-bags_1.gif', 'peachie-os-gummi-rings-bags'),
(2694, 'Jelly Belly Super Hero Bags', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly Super Hero Bags - 24ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_super_hero_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '2694~jelly_belly_super_hero_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-super-hero-bags'),
(2695, 'Hawaiian Punch Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Hawaiian Punch Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/hawaiian_punch_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '2695~hawaiian_punch_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'hawaiian-punch-licorice-twists-bags'),
(2696, 'Neon Squiggles Gummi Worms', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Neon Squiggles gummy worms are fun, colorful and always ready to eat! Everyone loves the soft, chewy taste of classic gummy worms. This popular treat was actually created to honor the 60th birthday of the gummy bear.Even though they came later, gummy worms are just as delicious and preferred by many candy lovers because of their long, bendable shape! Each gummy worm includes a narrow body with rounded ends. The back is covered in a segmented pattern that looks similar to the body of a real worm. The bottom is flat so it sits upright on flat surfaces. You get multiple colors in every worm!Taste yellow, red, white and green in every Trolli Squiggles bag! Our bulk gummy worms are convenient for birthday parties and more. Use them to fill party favors or add a fun touch by decorating cakes with these chewy worm candies. Everyone will love the sweet taste and playful look of Trolli Neon Squiggles gummy worms!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/e/neon-squiggles-gummi-worms-12ct_1.gif', '2696~neon-squiggles-gummi-worms-12ct_1.gif', 'neon-squiggles-gummi-worms'),
(2697, 'Jelly Belly Assorted Sugar Free Jelly Beans Bags', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly makes it even easier to enjoy their famous jellybeans and stick to a sugar-free diet. This colorful assortment features all sugar-free jellybeans in your favorite flavors. Each piece includes the familiar coffee bean shape and smooth texture along with the authentic brand logo printed on the side. Splenda is added to the recipe to produce a sweet tasting bean without the added sugar.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_assorted_sugar_free_jelly_beans_bags_-_12ct.jpg', '2697~jelly_belly_assorted_sugar_free_jelly_beans_bags_-_12ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-assorted-sugar-free-jelly-beans-bags'),
(2698, 'Grape Crush Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Grape Crush Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape_crush_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '2698~grape_crush_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'grape-crush-licorice-twists-bags'),
(2699, 'Haribo Sour Gummi Spaghetti', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Haribo Sour S\'ghetti is unlike any pasta you have ever eaten! Don\'t worry, you won\'t need to twirl these noodles on a fork. They are enjoyed cool and can be picked up by hand. Each bag features a generous collection of wiggly, wobbly slender lengths that are similar to classic spaghetti.Each piece comes in red, white or yellow. Our bulk sour gummy spaghetti is a great choice for after school snacks, lunches or special events. Sweeten any day by grabbing a handful of chewy spaghetti gummies when you\'re craving something sweet. Each bite features the taste of sugary gummy candy that\'s smothered in a coating of sour sugar.Your taste buds will tingle when they experience this one-of-a-kind confection! Kids won\'t be able to resist playing with the long noodle-y pieces which jiggle and bend. Add to birthday party favors or find fun ways to decorate cakes and cookies with Haribo sour gummy spaghetti!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', '2699~haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti-12ct.gif', 'haribo-sour-gummi-spaghetti'),
(2700, 'Hershey\'s Mini Chocolate Candy Bars', 34.99, '5', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'These bulk bags of mixed mini chocolate bars are the great, great, great, great, great grandkids of the first Hershey chocolate bars. We may have missed a few \'\'greats\'\' in there, but with the origination of the Hershey chocolate company in 1894, these confections have an impressive history that precedes us all. If you love a surprise, this mixed bag of mini Hershey\'s chocolate bars is right up your alley. Complete with a selection of Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate, Mr. Goodbar, Hershey\'s Dark Chocolate, and Krackel, you can expect something different every time you snack. With decades of success, we\'re positive that you\'ll love indulging in this famous brand.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hershey-mini-bars-small.jpg', '2700~hershey-mini-bars-small.jpg', 'hersheys-mini-chocolate-candy-bars'),
(2701, 'Peanut Butter Bars', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'Peanut butter bars candy brings you all the best parts of peanuts without all the bad stuff. Each bar includes high quality peanuts that are slow roasted until they become gold brown to bring out the natural nutty flavor. Each bite is truly an experience, with the crispy, flaky crunch that everyone loves. If you are a peanut butter fanatic, then this bar candy is your dream come true!Every peanut butter bar is individually wrapped so it\'s easy to store and share. Each includes a simple white wrapper with black stripes, gold star and a classic logo that gives each piece a nostalgic look. Keep a handful in your purse or pocket or use the in favor bags for parties and holiday events. Each tasty tidbit is packed with all the rich peanut flavor you can handle in a convenient package that you can take anywhere! Our bulk candy packs are great for school events, businesses and carnivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', '2701~peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', 'peanut-butter-bars'),
(2702, 'Hot Tamales Minis', 9.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Hold on to your taste buds! These red Hot Tamales Minis are ready to singe every last one of \'em off of your tongue. Though they may be packed in miniature movie theater boxes, every pack of these tamales are ready with a fiery punch of cinnamon that will blow you away. If you can\'t beat the heat, try adding them to a cup of tea or cocoa for a milder cinnamon fix. But if you\'re prepared for a spice that can\'t be beat, pop a few of these into your mouth at a time and feel the fire. Whatever you do, you\'ll set your mouth a-blaze with this bulk supply.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', '2702~hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', 'hot-tamales-minis'),
(2703, 'Skittles Fun Size Bulk', 99.99, '22', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'A color and flavor for every taste bud. Pack these fun size Skittles into a pinata, add them to a stocking, or slip one into your kid\'s lunchbox for a delicious afternoon surprise. Whatever you choose, everyone will love to \'\'Taste the Rainbow.\'\' Skittles have been in the US since 1979 and have evolved into a quirky brand and a household name. Their original flavors of orange, lemon, lime, grape and strawberry got a revamp in 1989 with the introduction of tropical fruit flavors. Since then, 1 new Skittles lines have been created and amazed the mouths of people all over the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-fun-size.jpg', '2703~skittles-fun-size.jpg', 'skittles-fun-size-bulk'),
(2704, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Prepare to be spoiled rotten with an overdose of creamy caramel and sugary sweetness! These Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops are an American classic that have had customers smacking their lips for years. Invented in 1925, it wasn\'t until 1932 that these famous pop got their sugary name. Give your family a taste of the olden days with some of these delicious caramels. Bring them to a party, add some to a candy buffet bar, or use them as a yummy, melty stirrer for hot chocolate. With over 48 caramel pops per box, get ready to indulge your family and friends for a long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', '2704~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops'),
(2705, 'Toblerone Mini Chocolate Bars', 45.99, '80', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Toblerone mini chocolate bars are a great idea for any party or occasion. These are small bars that have a total of three peaks made of chocolate; they are then filled using creamy nougat for a treat that is mouth watering and good. Each one of the bars is wrapped individually to help ensure that they are fresh. The shape of these bars is fun because they are not like many of the other typical candy bars that you find. Instead they are more interactive and have a lot to offer. The wrapper of these bars is a yellow color with red writing which means it can tie into many different themes if you find that you want to use it for a party. If you have never tried one of these great candies before then you have no idea just what you are missing. Your mouth is sure to be pleased when you take a bite of this wonderful candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/toblerone_mini.jpg', '2705~toblerone_mini.jpg', 'toblerone-mini-chocolate-bars'),
(2706, 'Giant Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars', 29.50, '12', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Someone must have been eating their \'\'Wheaties\'\' because these Giant Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars are ridiculously humungous and even more delicious! Have a friend who is a major chocolate fan? Want to stock up on s\'mores supplies that will last you all summer? Want to impress friends and family with a thoughtful and delicious gift basket addition? These gigantic, rich, melty chocolates can do all that and more. Around since 1894, Hershey\'s first opened their delicious doors in Pennsylvania. And ever since, their culinary perfection of some of the world\'s most famous confections has satisfied candy lovers around the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheyxl_bars.jpg', '2706~hersheyxl_bars.jpg', 'giant-hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars'),
(2707, 'Nut Goodie Bars', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Nostalgic. Classic. Vintage. You\'re a special kind of candy fan who appreciates where every sweet got its roots. With these Nut Goodie\'s, you can enjoy a taste of yesteryear in every milk chocolatey, nutty bite! Introduced in 1912, Nut Goodie hit candy store shelves for a whopping 5 cents! To this day, not much has changed about the delicious, salty, sweet nut clusters including their vintage wrapper. Add these to a 2\'s themed party for a tasty treat, share a bit of history with loved ones, or surprise your grandmother or grandfather with a taste of their youth. Whatever you do, you\'ll love these tried and true confections.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/u/nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', '2707~nut-goodie-bar-24ct_1.jpg', 'nut-goodie-bars'),
(2708, 'Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate Bars', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'One candy that has been a favorite for many over the years and still is, is the Hershey\'s milk chocolate. These great candy bars are nothing short of delicious. There is just something about the way that these are able to melt in your mouth when you take a bite. They are smooth and wonderful. This is great if you are looking to use them to make s\'mores. They are also great all on their own. These are full sized bars that are wrapped individually. If you are one that has a sweet tooth often then you will really be able to benefit from the bulk 36 count box of them. It will ensure that you have a way to indulge in this wonderful tasting candy bar whenever you decide that you want to or need to. Nothing is better than the sweet chocolaty taste of Hershey\'s. Kids and adults are both able to enjoy this wonderful candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars-36ct_2.gif', '2708~hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars-36ct_2.gif', 'hersheys-milk-chocolate-bars');
INSERT INTO `candy` (`id`, `title`, `price`, `amount`, `units`, `category`, `description`, `original_image_url`, `local_image`, `page`) VALUES
(2709, 'Sixlets 20 Ball Tubes', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Sixlets 20 ball tubes are the most convenient way to enjoy your favorite chocolate candy! Every stick includes a clear wrapper that holds 20 round balls in a straight line. Take a bite out of green, yellow, orange, red or brown.No matter which hue you choose, every Sixlets candy contains a smooth chocolate center surrounded by a hard candy shell. Our bulk Sixlets box contains a generous number of full tubes so you have plenty to take or share.Individually wrapped candy is perfect for traveling and events. Tuck a few in your vehicle\'s glove box, your purse or carry on. You can also display them in glass vases or trays to serve at parties, school activities and other gatherings. Buying Sixlets in bulk is also a great way to ensure that you always have an easy, tasty snack on hand when chocolate cravings hit!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', '2709~sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', 'sixlets-20-ball-tubes'),
(2710, 'Long Boys Coconut', 8.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Long Boys coconut candy sticks are a classic favorite that\'s full of rich flavor! This traditional candy originated in New Orleans, making it a staple for local children.Today, people all over the country rave about the amazing taste of these long, chewy confections. Every piece includes a stick of candy that\'s individually wrapped in a nostalgic red and yellow wrapper.Coconut Long Boys offer a unique blend of caramel and exotic coconut for a snacking experience that\'s memorable and satisfying! Untwist the wrapper and take small bites to fully enjoy the taste of this one-of-a-kind flavor combination! Kids can try stretching their Long Boy candy to see who can make the longest rope!Our bulk Long Boy coconut candy is a great choice for parties, picnics and family reunions. Use them to fill treat bags for birthdays or set out a bowl or box so adults can munch while reminiscing about their favorite childhood sweets!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', '2710~long-boys-coconut-48ct_3.jpg', 'long-boys-coconut'),
(2711, 'Snickers Bars', 46.99, '48', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Full-size Snickers bars will light up practically anyone\'s eyes! A familiar candy bar made from a perfect portion of peanuts sandwiched between soft, melting caramel and delicious creamy nougat, this confection is robed in a smooth milk chocolate for a sweet finish that\'s texturally interesting and satisfying to eat. When you just have to have a mid-morning snack and instant energy is the way to go, you could do much worse than to reach for a delicious Snickers bar!These Snickers candy bars in bulk come packaged in the familiar boldly-lettered, chocolate-hued wrapper, keeping them fresh for your enjoyment. This lot of Snickers is a perfect way to stock up on your family\'s favorite game-night treat or weekend dessert. If you\'re looking to create high perceived value in welcome bags or on a candy buffet, it\'s even better â€“ everyone feels special when they\'re offered a big, nutty chocolate candy bar to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/n/snickers-bars-48ct.gif', '2711~snickers-bars-48ct.gif', 'snickers-bars'),
(2712, 'Charleston Chews Candy Bars Snack Size', 12.99, '120', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Move your feet and clap your hands for this famous confection, Charleston Chews Candy Bars! Created in 1922, this classic candy bar was named after the famous dance, The Charleston. With a chewy, vanilla nougat center covered in melty milk chocolate, these candy bars have been a favorite for years. Bring some home to your family and share a sweet treat any day of the week. They\'re also great to put in a piï¾ata, make your own sundae bar, or to keep around the house to add to the top of cupcakes and other baked treats. Let these candies dance their way into your mouth and heart today when you order this bulk bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/charleston-chews-candy-snack-size-120ct_2.jpg', '2712~charleston-chews-candy-snack-size-120ct_2.jpg', 'charleston-chews-candy-snack-size'),
(2713, 'Take 5 Candy Bars', 25.99, '18', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'These are mini Take 5 candy bars that are the same a the larger versions which are already a big hit. People love the way that these taste and they are great when you find that you are craving something sweet. You will find that these are also great when it comes to finding a candy that you want to pass out at Halloween. The middle of these have peanuts and pretzels that have been dipped in peanut butter followed by caramel. It is then coated using milk chocolate. Your mouth is probably watering already and it should be, because there is just something about these that make you want more. You will find that it has a nice soft texture but it is also crunchy. This means that you are able to get the best of both worlds with this candy bar. Not to even mention the fact that you will get a little bit of sweet and salty taste as well.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/a/take_5_18ct.jpeg', '2713~take_5_18ct.jpeg', 'take-five-candy-bars'),
(2714, 'Skor Bars', 21.99, '18', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'It literally only takes one bite to be totally hooked on Skor Bars. If you are already a bit of an addict then you know this firsthand.Just looking at the bar, you think it\'s going to be a simple chocolate bar, but it\'s not. Enrobed in that creamy milk chocolate is a butter toffee center that will make your taste buds sing.You are more than welcome to chew it, if you like, but lovers of Skor Bars will tell you to let the chocolate dissolve on your tongue until the butter toffee is revealed for the full effect. This bulk supply of Skor Bars is perfect to have in the pantry for movie night or just to enjoy as a special treat.They are amazing as a topping, too. Put one in a sealed bag, crush it with a hammer, rolling pin, or whatever you have handy, and sprinkle it on cupcakes, ice-cream, frozen yogurt, and brownies. This is one treat you don\'t want to run out of!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skor-bars-18ct_1.jpg', '2714~skor-bars-18ct_1.jpg', 'skor-bars'),
(2715, 'Candy Buttons Wrapped', 26.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Candy buttons are so fun. These candies look like small buttons and they come on a sheet with three different types of flavors. Some of the great flavors that you can expect are lemon, lime, and cherry. You will also find that the colors that you get are nice with these as well. The colors are yellow, blue, and cherry. You can eat these just the way that they are or you can use this sweet candy in order to decorate a dessert with. There is nothing more fun than having a sheet where you can take off the buttons and pick out the colors that you want off of the sheet. This is fun for kids but adults will be able to enjoy it as well. Each sheet is wrapped individually which is convenient. If you want to find a great treat that you are able to please everyone with then this is certainly the treat for you.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-buttons-necco-candystore.jpg', '2715~candy-buttons-necco-candystore.jpg', 'candy-buttons-wrapped'),
(2716, 'Haribo Gold Bears', 21.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Everyone\'s favorite Haribo gummies are now available in a big gold box! What\'s one of the first sweet treats everyone thinks of when they are hungry for a chewy candy? Why gummy bears of course! Our adorable little bruins come packed with fruity flavor. Each piece includes the recognizable shape that make these a popular go-to snack for kids and adults alike. Our Haribo gummy bears can be purchased in a bulk candy pack! You get more irresistible morsels to enjoy at home or share with guests. This size is perfect for use in treat bags at birthday parties or to distribute at picnics, school events and other gatherings. They are conveniently packaged so you can hide a few in your purse, pocket or include them in your child\'s school lunch. You\'ll never have to go hungry when your sweet tooth craves the soft, juicy taste of classic gummy bears when you buy our bulk candy box!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-original-gold-gummi-bears.jpg', '2716~haribo-original-gold-gummi-bears.jpg', 'haribo-gold-bears-24ct'),
(2717, 'Hershey\'s Assorted Miniature Chocolate Bars', 139.99, '25', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'Good things come in small packages. But they can certainly come in big ones too! And this bulk assortment of Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate, Hershey\'s Dark Chocolate, Mr. Goodbar, and Krackel mini candy bars is definitely an example of a very good thing. Founded in 1894, Hershey has been pumping out delicious candy bars long before any of us were around to enjoy them. That\'s why with their time-tested quality and handcrafted taste, you\'ll be snacking happily for a long time. And now with this bulk bag, you\'ll be able to get your entire family\'s favorite candy bars in one package.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-assorted-miniature-chocolate-bars-25lbs_2.jpg', '2717~hersheys-assorted-miniature-chocolate-bars-25lbs_2.jpg', 'hersheys-miniature-chocolate-bars-bulk-case'),
(2718, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops Large', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Chewy Sugar Daddy caramel pops offer the best of everything when it comes to sweet snacking. These mouthwatering delights produce big flavor that no caramel fanatic can resist! The beauty is in the taste and the design. Each piece includes a generous bar of creamy caramel candy perched atop a convenient disposable stick. Simply peel the bright yellow wrapper and enjoy golden caramel confection to your heart\'s content without the gooey mess!Anytime is a great time to buy Sugar Daddy candy! Give them away during holidays, hide them in party favors or keep them around the pantry for days when you\'re craving something smooth and sweet. Since 1925, Sugar Daddies have been the go-to candy for caramel lovers. New sizes have been introduced over the years, but none compare to the large Sugar Daddy caramel pop. Take your mouth on a saccharine vacation with a box of nostalgic Sugar Daddy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', '2718~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-large'),
(2719, 'Haribo Roulette Candy', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Haribo roulette gummies put a fun spin on snack time! These tempting confections come in convenient tube shaped packages that fit almost anywhere. Every piece forms a chewy disc with round edges and a solid middle. Bite down and experience the soft, smooth texture that makes Haribo gummies so delectable. If that\'s not enough gummy goodness for you, you\'ll also love the different flavors and colors that are included in every pack!Our Haribo roulette candies are the perfect blend of exciting style and practical design for young and old alike. Adults will appreciate how compact and convenient they are while children will love the sugary taste that is packed into every piece. Now you can get all the roulette gummies you want with our bulk candy package! Keep your snack cabinet or pantry well stocked or use them for special events like birthday parties, holiday gatherings, picnics and school activities!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-roulette-gummy-candy.jpg', '2719~haribo-roulette-gummy-candy.jpg', 'roulette-36ct'),
(2720, 'Toblerone Milk Chocolate Bar 12.6oz', 99.99, '10', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'A triangular chocolate bar in a triangular package with lovely retro graphics â€“ with such a striking look, it\'s no wonder Toblerone has stayed so popular. Normally it would be unwise to judge a candy by its wrapper, but Toblerone has proven itself a high-quality chocolate confection, and the alpine motif on the label reminds every chocolate lover that Toblerone confections are part of the reason Swiss chocolates are considered among the world\'s finest.The prism package of the Toblerone milk chocolate bar protects a luxurious chocolate candy bar flavored with delicate additions of honey and almond. Instantly recognizable as a top-of-the-line chocolate brand, each Toblerone bar makes an ideal portable dessert which is perfect for sharing with a friend â€“ if, that is, you can bring yourself to sacrifice a piece of its goodness!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/toblerone_12.6.jpeg', '2720~toblerone_12.6.jpeg', 'toblerone-milk-chocolate-bar'),
(2721, 'Payday Bars', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Cha-ching! The cash is rolling in with every bite of these delectable, crunchy Payday Bars. Filled with crunchy, whole peanuts and a delicious caramel nougat, it\'s no wonder why people around the world look forward to bite after bite of these rich treats. Introduced to candy bar loves for the first time in 1932, customers have been cashing in on these confections ever since! Bring some home to your candy bar and nut-lovers, spoil trick-or-treaters with a handful of these bars, or even crumble them into baked goods for an extra touch of yum! You\'ll feel like you struck it rich with every bite.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/paydaybars-24ct.gif', '2721~paydaybars-24ct.gif', 'payday-bars'),
(2722, 'Big Hunk Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'What a hunk! A Big Hunk Bar that is. These attractive candy bars are a delicious and old fashioned treat from the 1950s. With yummy honey-sweetened nougat and rich roasted peanuts, this candy is also surprisingly low fat! Fall for this handsome candy bar time after time. Bring some to a birthday party to surprise every guest, give some to a loved one on Valentine\'s Day to get a few laughs, or even keep them around the house to crumble into baked goods and make them extra attractive. This delicious candy bar can do it all and more with its muscley, nutty crunch and creamy, chewy nougat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/i/big-hunk-bars-24ct_2.jpg', '2722~big-hunk-bars-24ct_2.jpg', 'big-hunk-bars'),
(2723, 'Sesame Seed Snaps', 19.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Sezme sesame snaps are an amazingly delicious treat that\'s also good for you! If you simply can\'t decide between sweet and salty, you can enjoy both in every bite with these bar shaped confections.Each is packed with savory sesame seed flavor that\'s complemented by a touch of sugary goodness. They come individually wrapped so they stay fresh until it\'s time to snack. Our bulk Sezme sesame snaps are an excellent alternative food to chocolaty or overly sugary treats.Eat better while satisfying your cravings. This Poland-born treat is cholesterol free and gluten free. Take a bite and experience the pleasant crunch and satisfying flavor that taste buds crave. Our bulk sesame snaps box is a must-have for daily snacking.Use them to pack healthier lunches for your family or keep them as a quick and easy after school snack. Sesame seed candy also makes a great Christmas stocking stuffer!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/e/sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', '2723~sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', 'sesame-seed-snaps'),
(2724, 'Giant Smarties 1.2oz', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Giant Smarties candy is the best way to enjoy this popular treat. Each disc shaped piece offers a tart flavor that\'s fun to munch on! Every kid loves to bite down on crunchy, crumbly Smarties. Our large size gives you bigger pieces that last even longer!A generous helping of Smarties are carefully stacked then wrapped in clear plastic which proudly displays the candy\'s name in big red letters. Just untwist an end and prepare for a totally tart treat!Bulk Smarties give you more individual packs to share, give or eat. Stow a box in the pantry as an easy snack when you\'re short on time. You can also keep them at the office to pass around among coworkers. Giant Smarties are a great reward for children as well! Give them out during school activities and events or use them in party favors for kids\' birthdays, family reunions and holidays!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/giant-smarties-12oz-36ct.gif', '2724~giant-smarties-12oz-36ct.gif', 'giant-smarties-box'),
(2725, 'Rocky Road Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Get ready for a bumpy ride! Because this delicious candy bar, Rocky Road, is packed with potholes of deliciousness. Each classic bar is filled with luscious, puffy marshmallow, creamy and delicious milk chocolate, big chunks of roasted cashews, and rich, crispy malt. With 24 candy bars per box, you\'ll have a lot of chewing to do! Bring these to a baseball game for a filling candy that will get you through every inning. Buy some for a cashew and chocolate fan. Even stock yourself up for upcoming Halloween trick-or-treaters. No matter how you enjoy these classic candy bars, your taste buds are in for a wild ride!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rocky-road-bars-24ct_2.gif', '2725~rocky-road-bars-24ct_2.gif', 'rocky-road-bars'),
(2726, 'Twix Bars', 39.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Twix candy bars are sweet, crunchy and sure to satisfy even the most demanding cravings! This hugely popular Mars candy includes a crisp biscuit center that\'s topped in smooth caramel. The outside is smothered in an irresistible blanked of rich milk chocolate.Twix may be considered a modern treat, but its roots date back to the 1960s when it was first sold in the United Kingdom. It arrived in the United States within the next decade and has become a mainstay among candy lovers!Our convenient bulk Twix box is the best way to get more of the confection you love. You get a giant box packed with full sized candy bars. Each is individually wrapped, just like you would buy them at the grocery store! The difference is you get them at a great price and all at once so you always have a Twix candy bar ready to go when you\'re feeling hungry!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/w/twix_bars.jpeg', '2726~twix_bars.jpeg', 'twix-bars'),
(2727, 'Chuckles Candy', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Knee slappers. Lip smackers. Hilarious comics of the candy world. These funny Chuckles Candies are a barrel full of laughs! Chortle with some cherry, orange, lemon, lime, and licorice soft gelly candies dusted with supremely sweet sugar. They are a great way to make your kids smile, look pretty set out in a bowl, and will put all your guests in good humor with every taste of these. With 24 boxes per order, you\'ll be laughing yourself silly for snack times to come! Just see if you can keep a straight face when faced with these delicious, Chuckle\'s Candy jellies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chuckles-candy-24ct.gif', '2727~chuckles-candy-24ct.gif', 'chuckles-box'),
(2728, '100 Grand Bars', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', '1 Grand bars can really make you feel like you have a lot of money. These bars are nothing short of great. They have caramel, milk chocolate, and puffed rice. This means that you can ensure that they taste absolutely wonderful. These would be great when used at a financial event that you were having, or any other event for that matter. Consider even giving them out as Halloween candy, and really leave the trick-or-treaters pleased at what you have given them. There are 36 in a box of these and each bar is wrapped individually with a red colored wrapper. This helps to ensure that you can eat them or use them when it is best for you and still know that the bars will be fresh when you are ready for them. So why not delight your taste buds with one of these great bars of fun candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/n/one-hundred-grand-bars.jpg', '2728~one-hundred-grand-bars.jpg', '100-grand-bars'),
(2729, 'U No Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'U-No bars are a tasty treat made by the Annabelle Candy Company. Every chewy bite is sure to satisfy even the most demanding taste buds. U-No bars also make a great summer treat when frozen. Simply place in the freezer until solid then enjoy as a unique candy-popsicle!Our bulk U-No box will give you many bars to enjoy at home or with a crowd. Serve them to guests, keep them as a quick snack or hand them out as party favors or Halloween candy. They make great stocking stuffers, Easter basket candy or a special candy reward for students.Simply called Ã’Annabelle\'sÃ“, the company was founded in 1950 and named for the owner\'s daughter. Annabelle\'s began producing popular confections including a Rocky Road bar. In 1978 they added a number of products including the U-No bar. This new creation features a truffle style filling combined with crushed almonds. Everything is smothered in silky milk chocolate.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/u/-/u-no-bars-24ct.gif', '2729~u-no-bars-24ct.gif', 'u-no-bars'),
(2730, 'Zero Bars', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Zero candy bars are a delightful treat that brings together flavors that are not often combined. This unique confection was originally created in 1920 and quickly became known for its white color.The surface is covered in a smooth layer of white fudge while the middle is composed of savory caramel, almond nougat and delicious peanut. The Zero Bar we know today began as the Double Zero bar but was later renamed to its current moniker in 1934.Zero started out as part of the Hollywood Brands candy company but changed hands multiple times.Today it belongs to the famous Hershey family of candies. Now you can enjoy the sweet, hearty taste of a Zero bar anytime you like! Just order a bulk candy box so you always have individually wrapped bars ready to serve and enjoy! Zero bars also make great gifts and favors for parties and holiday events!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/z/e/zero-bars-24ct.gif', '2730~zero-bars-24ct.gif', 'zero-bars'),
(2731, 'Whoppers', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Ladies and gentlemen. Boys and girls. What we have here on CandyStore.com is the original malted milk ball, better known as Whoppers! If you\'re clapping you hands with glee and salivating at the thought, then we have another juicy tid bit of information for you: they come in bulk.Stock your pantry full of these Whoppers boxes and you\'ll have enough to grab when your family watches a movie on the couch, you head out to a baseball game or sporting event or just have a colossal sweet tooth to contend with. Order your supply of Whoppers today and start enjoying them ASAP!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/whoppers-24ct.gif', '2731~whoppers-24ct.gif', 'whoppers-packs'),
(2732, 'Rolo', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Rolo\'s have been a favorite candy for many since childhood. It seems that these great candies have been around forever. After all what is not to love about them. They have caramel on the inside and are coated on the outside with wonderful tasting chocolate. These great candies also come in rolls so that you are able to open up, and just starting popping them in to your mouth. These will be great for kids or adults. Many people will find that these are almost addicting as they are able to really please their taste buds. You can give these out as candy for Halloween or even use them for stocking stuffers at Christmas time if you are looking for something that nearly everyone is sure to enjoy. What better way to be able to get the great combine flavor of caramel and chocolate then to partake in Rolo candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rolo-36ct.gif', '2732~rolo-36ct.gif', 'rolo'),
(2733, 'Mountain Bars', 15.99, '15', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'If you\'re afraid of heights, you\'ll just have to get over it and try a taste of our amazing Mountain Bar! These peanut butter, cherry and original Mountain Bars flavors will send your taste buds to a higher elevation of deliciousness.Since Mountain Bars come individually wrapped and in three different flavors, you\'ll be able to make everyone in your home happy when you bring a big box of these candies home. Add some to a dessert table, bring some on a ski trip, or just enjoy these classic candies when you want a sweet fix you\'ll love.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/t/mtn_bar_caddy_peanut_btr_open.jpg', '2733~mtn_bar_caddy_peanut_btr_open.jpg', 'peanut-butter-mountain-bar'),
(2734, 'Skittles Sour', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'If you are looking for a new twist on skittles then you should try the sour skittles. These are fun and exciting for people of all ages. They also come in many different colors such as pink, purple, green, blue, and yellow. This means that you will get to enjoy a variety of colors and flavors. The texture of these is the same as the regular skittles meaning that they are soft but chewy. The main difference that you will notice with these is that they have sour coating on the outside of them that makes for their unique sour taste. The flavors that you get from these are fruity and are much like the classic flavors that you find but they are able to provide you with that extra kick. This is one candy that is sure to get your taste buds going in high gear. If you are looking for something fun this is certainly what you need.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-sour-24ct_1.jpg', '2734~skittles-sour-24ct_1.jpg', 'skittles-sour'),
(2735, 'Abba Zaba Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'This candy\'s name will roll right off your tongue and make you want to come back for more! Abba Zabba Candy Bars are a genius mix of taffy and peanut butter that you will love. Around since the 192s, this historic candy bar has a taxi cab-esque wrapper that will remind you of the \'\'roaring\'\' 2s in New York City. Get yourself some for an upcoming Great Gatsby themed party, to wrap up for a grandparent who loves this nostalgic taste, or to introduce a taste of the past to your family. With 24 candy bars per order, you\'ll have enough to go around!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/b/abba-zabba-bars-24ct_3.jpg', '2735~abba-zabba-bars-24ct_3.jpg', 'abba-zaba-bars'),
(2736, 'Caramel Apple Pops', 9.99, '48', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Enjoy the bounty of the autumn harvest without setting foot in an orchard. A play on a classic fall favorite, these classic green apple lollies are slathered in a creamy, chewy, caramel coating that has been greedily gobbled up for years. Bring them to a fall party, use them as Halloween treats, or remind yourself of autumn any time of the year. Every snacker will feel like you\'re on a tractor ride, traversing a corn maze, and smelling fresh bales of hay every time you eat one of these. And the best part is, these tart treats are here all year \'round.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-apple-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '2736~caramel-apple-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'caramel-apple-pops'),
(2737, 'Caramel Candy Squares', 16.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Don\'t be such a square! Unless you want to be a delicious, creamy Caramel Square. These tawny, creamy cubes are amazing little morsels that will melt away in your mouth and leave a smile on your face. Individually wrapped in clear cellophane, they make a great addition to a candy buffet bar, as a candy dish go-to, or even to keep around the house and melt into hot chocolate and baked goods. Caramel has been around for centuries and transforms typical granulated sugar into this famous form of ooey, gooey chewiness when heated at a high heat. We\'d like give the culinary geniuses who came up with this fantastic candy a pat on the back!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-squares-5lb_1.jpg', '2737~caramel-squares-5lb_1.jpg', 'caramel-squares-wrapped'),
(2738, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Prepare to be spoiled rotten with an overdose of creamy caramel and sugary sweetness! These Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops are an American classic that have had customers smacking their lips for years. Invented in 1925, it wasn\'t until 1932 that these famous pop got their sugary name. Give your family a taste of the olden days with some of these delicious caramels. Bring them to a party, add some to a candy buffet bar, or use them as a yummy, melty stirrer for hot chocolate. With over 48 caramel pops per box, get ready to indulge your family and friends for a long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', '2738~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops'),
(2739, 'Caramel Cream Bulls Eyes', 35.99, '', '', 'caramel', 'Each Caramel Cream (or Bull\'s Eye), starts with a white cream filling at the center. The outside includes a generous layer of high quality caramel to create a round treat. Our bulk Caramel Creams arrive individually wrapped with nostalgic red Goetze branding.Caramel Cream Bulls Eyes are the crowning jewel in the Goetze\'s catalog. The Goetze brand goes way back to 1895. By 1917, the family-owned company introduced its first soft caramel candies, much to the delight of candy lovers!Today, Caramel Creams are considered Goetze\'s signature creation, and it\'s easy to see why once you sink your teeth into one! Keep them in the candy jar at home, take them to the office to share or add to a gourmet gift basket! Caramel Creams are also a wonderful choice for shower and wedding favors. Their sweet, creamy taste and classic look appeals to candy lovers of all ages! Find out what makes Goetze so delicious by adding Caramel Creams to your next gathering.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-creams-bulls-eyes-goetze-candy-store-470x470.jpg', '2739~caramel-creams-bulls-eyes-goetze-candy-store-470x470.jpg', 'bulls-eyes-caramel-creams'),
(2740, 'Cow Tales Caramel Sticks', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Our bulk box of Cow Tales contains a very generous quantity of individually wrapped caramel pieces. Candy lovers of all ages will love the chewy texture and smooth cream filling. Order your choice of original vanilla, strawberry cream or chocolate or try multiple boxes so you can sample a combination of Cow Tale flavors!Cow Tales are the creation of Goetze\'s Candy. The company began in 1895 as the Baltimore Chewing Gum Company. The company\'s signature Caramel Cream was created in 1917 followed by the classic Cow Tale.This confection was very similar to the Caramel Cream, but instead of a small disc of chewy caramel it featured a long tube (or tail) with delectable cream running through the middle. Different flavors have been added, including strawberry, vanilla, chocolate and caramel apple, but the classic version is still often considered the best!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/cow-tales-original-caramel--cream-sticks-36ct.jpg', '2740~cow-tales-original-caramel--cream-sticks-36ct.jpg', 'cow-tales-original-caramel-cream-sticks'),
(2741, 'Caramel Block Bulk', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'When it comes to creating delicious treats at home the number one ingredient is going to be yummy candy. When you buy a bulk caramel block then you will have enough delicious goodness to create a whole kitchen full of treats that will feed an army. One of the best things about this caramel product is that it will make anything into a treat. Eating fruit can be a difficult thing to get kids to do, well learn how to cover it in caramel and you have created a fruit snack that no kid can resist. This has been the secret recipe for caramel apples for many years. Simply heat up the caramel put an apple on a stick and dip. Once the candy coating has cooled, you have created a snack that will be remembered forever. This works for other fruit as well. Some cover strawberries and some will cover bananas but probably the best selection is to offer a plate of fruit and the melted candy as a dipping sauce. More fruit will disappear than you believed possible.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulk-caramel-block-5lb_2.jpg', '2741~bulk-caramel-block-5lb_2.jpg', 'bulk-caramel-block'),
(2742, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops Large', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Chewy Sugar Daddy caramel pops offer the best of everything when it comes to sweet snacking. These mouthwatering delights produce big flavor that no caramel fanatic can resist! The beauty is in the taste and the design. Each piece includes a generous bar of creamy caramel candy perched atop a convenient disposable stick. Simply peel the bright yellow wrapper and enjoy golden caramel confection to your heart\'s content without the gooey mess!Anytime is a great time to buy Sugar Daddy candy! Give them away during holidays, hide them in party favors or keep them around the pantry for days when you\'re craving something smooth and sweet. Since 1925, Sugar Daddies have been the go-to candy for caramel lovers. New sizes have been introduced over the years, but none compare to the large Sugar Daddy caramel pop. Take your mouth on a saccharine vacation with a box of nostalgic Sugar Daddy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', '2742~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-large'),
(2743, 'Caramel Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Caramel swirl salt water taffy is a rich, chewy treat that you\'ll love to eat! Anyone who adores the sweet, savory flavor of classic caramel must experience the taste of our salt water taffy. Each piece recreates the feeling of eating a bite-sized piece of high quality caramel but with that taffy texture you know and love.Our salt water taffy is available in single-flavor packages so you get exactly what you want every time you order! Bulk caramel swirl salt water taffy can be used for events and much more. Fill treat bags or wedding favors with these elegant little pinwheels. Each includes a toasty brown hue that\'s accented by a slender spiral swirl of white.Each piece arrives individually wrapped so it stays fresh and enjoyable. Order our caramel saltwater taffy for your next event or keep a package at home or at the office to eat as a quick snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2743~caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(2744, 'Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', '\'\'Mooo-ve\'\' over for these Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffies. With their beautiful white and black cow spots and creamy flavor, you won\'t ever want to put these down or put them out to pasture. This snack is a classic that has satisfied candy lovers for years.Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice_caramel.jpg', '2744~licorice_caramel.jpg', 'licorice-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(2745, 'Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'One classic confection with the flavor of another: it is a novelty with the appeal of a tradition! Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy has a bright green center that looks bright as springtime when you use it as a table scatter or to fill an heirloom dish.A symbol of playful days and sunny summers by the sea, bulk saltwater taffy is beloved by kids and adults for its soft, chewy, flavorful composition, and the individual wrappers on these green and brown taffy delicacies make them perfect for candy buffets, treat bags, and pantry stockpiles of tasty sweets.The tart green apple flavor in this wholesale caramel apple taffy combines with a creamy, sweet caramel taste that is reminiscent of the original molasses recipe from which modern taffy flavors evolved. Apple flavor, too, takes your taste buds straight to the autumn orchards, too. The combination of classic taste appeals makes caramel apple saltwater taffy an especially evocative little treat!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2745~caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy'),
(2746, 'Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy is unbelievable, and sure to become one of your favorite treats. It blends sweet and savory in every single bite.You can probably guess just by looking at the cowhide design of these candies that your taste buds are going to be in for a special treat. In fact, you probably don\'t even need to read their name to know that you are about to indulge in a flavor combination of sweet, decadent caramel and creamy vanilla.Unwrap one, pop it in your mouth, and enjoy a long-lasting sweet that retains its flavor right down until the last speck has been dissolved. Since these kosher certified Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy candies are individually wrapped, they are perfect for candy dishes for any occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla_caramel_taffy.jpeg', '2746~vanilla_caramel_taffy.jpeg', 'vanilla-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(2747, 'Chocolate Caramel Mocha Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'So you are dedicated to upscale flavors like chocolate, coffee, and caramel, but you want to put a nostalgic spin on a dinner-party dessert or movie-night treat. What to do? Chocolate Caramel Mocha Salt Water Taffy, of course!Wonderfully munchable, individually-wrapped pieces of soft and delicious saltwater taffy in a rich combination of three flavors makes a striking addition to a candy buffet as well. The look is perfectly timeless, and the flavor is sophisticated â€“ bulk candy does not get much better than this! Individual wrappers that are easy to open, plus a bold brown and white color mix in each flavorful piece, make chocolate caramel mocha salt water taffy a delicious choice for setting on the napkin at every place setting.Or for offering in a huge bowl for endless sweet luxury. The soft taffy texture of these classically-made pieces is a little harder to find than many sweets, making them the stuff of special occasions and childhood vacations for many candy lovers!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2747~chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(2748, 'Chocolate Caramel Squares Candy', 42.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'We love that these Chocolate Caramel Squares Candies come wrapped in cellophane so we can see right through to the deliciousness! And why would anyone want to cover up a candy that features a delicious milk chocolate square of amazingness and a melty, chewy caramel center inside?Are you a major proponent for Chocolate Caramel Square Candies? Then you\'ve hit the jackpot here on CandyStore.com because we have huge bulk orders of them at budget friendly prices. This means you can bring home hundreds of these Chocolate Caramel Square Candies to chow down on for weeks to come. Or however long your sweet tooth allows.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-caramel-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '2748~chocolate-caramel-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'chocolate-caramel-squares'),
(2749, 'Mini Cow Tales Caramel Creams', 57.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Those who love Cow Tales will certainly love these many Cow Tales. These are able to offer the same great caramel and cream flavor but are just smaller in size. They also come individually wrapped so that they are sure to stay as fresh as possible for as long as possible. These are great for treat bags, snacks, Halloween, and many of occasionsCow Tales offer a great chewy caramel flavor on the outside and the inside is a smooth but creamy center. These are sure to please almost anyone. They are also great for adults as well as children. The best part about it is that you are able to get either a chocolate or vanilla flavor for these great Cow Tales. If you are having a medium sized party then you are sure to find this would be enough for your party as well.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb_1.jpg', '2749~mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb_1.jpg', 'mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb'),
(2750, 'Caramel Corn Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Sometimes too much of one thing is a bad thing. But we don\'t think a double dose of creamy and deliciousness could ever be bad with this Caramel Corn Salt Water Taffy! This rich candy is a great selection for any affair and especially looks nice around the holidays. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2750~caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy'),
(2751, 'Caramel Cheesecake Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'At the risk of sounding cheesy, we\'ll admit to all of you that these Caramel Cheesecake Salt Water Taffies make our hearts melt. That\'s because they\'re so creamy, rich and delicious! Bring them to a party with your closest gal pals, put some on a dessert table, or keep them in the cabinet when a sweet tooth strikes. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2751~caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy'),
(2752, 'Pecan Caramel Pattie Chocolates', 75.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Pecan Caramel Pattie Chocolates are the ultimate indulgence of the chocolate world, combining three decadent tastes and three individual textures into an utterly luscious gourmet candy.Always tempting treats when laid out on trays on a dessert table, these high-quality bulk chocolates bring out the flavorful appeal of pecans and the creamy, slightly chewy warmth of caramel by half-drowning both of them in the thick coating of delicious chocolate.Maybe you want to make gift baskets feel more thoughtful yet keep them relatively economical by tucking in a cellophane bag of these wholesale candies. Maybe you have a corporate event coming up and you want to sweeten your guests outlook with a lovable chocolate caramel treat.Maybe you just like to keep a rich, self-contained dessert on hand in the pantry for unexpected guests. Whatever your need, these pecan caramel pattie chocolates are a distinctly delicious solution.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates-5lbs.gif', '2752~pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates-5lbs.gif', 'pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates'),
(2753, 'Licorice Caramels', 40.99, '4.4', 'lb', 'caramel', 'The mad scientists of the candy world have created a magical hybrid of flavors! We\'re talking about our licorice caramels and can\'t wait for you to bring some home and take a bite.In a dark chocolatey brown, these cellophane wrapped black caramels have the delicious creaminess of caramel and the bite of licorice so the flavor and texture experience is one of the most exciting. Give your mouth a relaxing job to do by popping one of these licorice caramels in and letting is melt away slowly. Now that\'s what we like to call R&R; in the candy world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', '2753~licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', 'licorice-caramels'),
(2754, 'Bull\'s Eye Caramel Creams Theater Box', 22.99, '12', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Bulls-Eyes caramel candies are one of the smoothest, chewiest treats you can add to your candy collection! This classic confection brings together two delicious ingredients.Each piece is round, bite-sized and arrives individually wrapped in clear plastic with the familiar red Goetze\'s logo right at the center. Our theater candy boxes are convenient and contain plenty of pieces for one or two people!Every Bulls-Eyes caramel includes two main parts. The outside is a thick ring of delectable caramel. The middle includes a circle of rich creamy confection. Each bite gives you a bit of both flavors to produce the most irresistible combination for anyone who adores the sweet, savory taste of caramel!Our bulk caramel candy package contains several theater boxes so you have plenty to use as party favors or a quick snack at home. Host your own movie night complete with sweet concessions or take a theater box with you as an easy snack at work!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-box-12ct.gif', '2754~bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-box-12ct.gif', 'bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-boxes'),
(2755, 'Slapstix Caramel Pops', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'What could be better than a giant lollipop? How about one that\'s made with creamy caramel! Our Slapstix caramel pops are a delicious treat that is sure to satisfy your carving for smooth, sweet caramel.Each piece includes a generous block of confection with a gentle swirl of flavor that\'s perched on a disposable stick. Enjoy ooey gooey caramel without sticky fingers! If you\'re looking for a lollipop that\'s unique and chewy, this is a must-try confection!Each comes individually wrapped so the rectangle caramel lollipop stays fresh and ready to enjoy. Order boxes for birthday parties, events and more! Everyone will love receiving these at school activities and community events.Slapstix lollipops also make great stocking stuffers at Christmas time. Whether you\'re filling treat bags for a birthday party or looking for an easy sweet treat to enjoy at home, you will love the rich taste of caramel lollipops!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/l/slapstix-caramel-pops-24ct.gif', '2755~slapstix-caramel-pops-24ct.gif', 'slapstix-caramel-pops');
