(2756, 'Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars', 38.99, '14', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Bite size pieces of pure bliss is what you enjoy with this bulk supply of Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars. Each of the bars has 18 individual squares that are easy to break or cut apart.So, you can serve them to your guests on a tray for dessert, if you can bring yourself to share. Although originated in the United Kingdom, today The Hershey Company has a license to manufacture the divine line of Cadbury products in the United States.Whether you buy them in America or the UK, they are the same mouthwatering, melt-in-your-mouth bars of delicious goodness. Decadent milk chocolate is poured over creamy caramel and hardened.So, although the chocolate is firm on the outside, when you bite into them the gooey caramel comes oozing out. Your taste buds will be dancing. These large Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars make great stocking stuffers or last minute gifts for coworkers.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars-24ct_1.jpg', '2756~cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars-24ct_1.jpg', 'cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars'),
(2757, 'Black Cow Bar', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Chocolate and caramel surely are a decadent combo. With these Black Cow Bars, you\'ll get all of that in one incredible bite. And with this bulk box, you\'ll have a ton of savoring to do!Being a black sheep is never a good thing, but being a black cow certainly is! These Black Cow Bars are full of amazing chewy chocolate caramel that will keep your mouth moving like a cow grazing in the pasture. Pour some of these Black Cow Bars into a trick-or-treating candy bowl for Halloween, bring some home for a barn-themed wedding or party or order some if you just love caramel and chocolate. There\'s no wrong reason to order these tasty treats!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blackcowbar.jpg', '2757~blackcowbar.jpg', 'black-cow-bar'),
(2758, 'Slo Poke Bar', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'If the name is any hint, you should slow down and enjoy this delicious caramel candy. That\'s because Slo Poke Bars are made of incredible salty and sweet caramel that melts in your mouth slowly so you can delight in the flavor for longer.If you\'re a fan of caramels, then these Slo Poke Bars are a candy we\'re sure you\'ll adore. In a bulk size box, these Slo Poke Bars will provide you with hours of sweet satisfaction. Stock your pantry with some of these incredible caramels to use in baking, give out in gift baskets or enjoy piece by piece. If you\'re having a stressful day, indulging in one of these bars will surely slow down the pace and help you relax.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/l/slopokebar.jpg', '2758~slopokebar.jpg', 'slo-poke-bar'),
(2759, 'Chocolate Covered Caramel and Marshmallow', 66.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Goodness gracious. Just when you didn\'t think something more delicious than chocolate covered caramel could come around, these chocolate-covered caramel and marshmallows come out to surprise you!In a ridiculously fluffy, chewy, melty and delicious combination of caramel, milk chocolate and marshmallow, these candies will melt in your mouth and melt your heart at the same time. If you want gourmet-tasting candy for an economical price, bring home a bulk supply of our Chocolate Covered Caramel and Marshmallow candies and you can munch on tasty treats that seem like they\'re out of a glass case of a fine chocolatier\'s store. Serve these on your next party\'s dessert platter and wow your guests with the deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-caramel-and-marshmallow-6lbs_4.gif', '2759~chocolate-covered-caramel-and-marshmallow-6lbs_4.gif', 'caramel-marshmallow-chocolate-covered'),
(2760, 'Black Cow Bite Size', 59.99, '15', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Moooo-ve over other candies. These Black Cow Bite Size treats are a crowd favorite with their chocolate flavored chewy caramel. Wrapped in fun sizes, they\'re a perfect little dessert you can graze on between any meal. Bite in for a chewy, gooey and ooey texture and flavor you\'ll never want to put to pasture. Milk this bulk bag of Black Cow Bite Size candy for all its worth by indulging on decadent chocolate caramel after chocolate caramel. Whether you like to enjoy your sweets solo or add them to other recipes, this Black Cow Bite Size candy can do it all and more. Add some to a candy buffet bar. Unwrap a few to use atop cupcakes and other sweets. Even dice some up to add to the top of an ice cream sundae.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black_cow_bites_bulk.jpg', '2760~black_cow_bites_bulk.jpg', 'black-cow-bite-size'),
(2761, 'Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels', 64.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'We did a double take when we first saw these Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels, too! That\'s because with a double dose of incredible chocolate in every square, these little morsels pack enough sweet, savory and melty deliciousness into every bite. In either milk or dark chocolate, these Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels are an incredible treat. Order a bulk supply and you can make your very own Valentine\'s Day boxes for the people you love most. Or, you can be content to know that a yummy and spectacular treat awaits you whenever you need a sweet fix.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', '2761~chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramels'),
(2762, 'Chocolate Covered Vanilla Caramels', 64.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Chocolate, vanilla and caramel are three of the most popular flavors in the candy world. Our delicious chocolate collection brings you a one-of-a-kind confection that combines all three in the most delightful way!Our chocolate covered vanilla caramels are sure to satisfy even the most demanding sugar cravings with a combination of richness and sweetness. Every bite-sized piece includes a generous filling packed with solid caramel flavored with a hint of delectable vanilla.The outside is covered in a smooth blanket of milk chocolate accented by alternating chocolate drizzle. Not only are these chocolate candies delicious, but they\'re also very elegant to look at.Arrange them on a tray for guests or add to wedding favors to send your guests off with an edible gift that includes high quality gourmet chocolate! Our bulk candy pack makes it so easy to get the quantity you need for events of any size.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', '2762~chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramels'),
(2763, 'Caramel Truffle', 69.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'If you adore chocolate and caramel, the caramel truffle are the ultimate treat for you! This delectable confection combines two rich, savory ingredients into one gourmet candy. Each piece includes an elegant shape that adds to the eating experience. The bottom is flat with smooth, rounded sides that include angular edges. The top is flat with a white chocolate tulip raised at the center, complete with petal detail.Bulk caramel truffles give you large quantities for snacking or celebrations. Keep them in the pantry as a quick snack when you\'re craving something with a little class (and a lot of sweetness). Or share them with guests.These charming truffles look fabulous when displayed on platters or trays with cookies and other desserts. Use them to fill out a gourmet gift basket or add to this year\'s stocking stuffer candy. Decadent caramel truffles are a delicious candy for any season or event!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-truffle-6lbs_2.gif', '2763~caramel-truffle-6lbs_2.gif', 'caramel-truffles'),
(2764, 'Riesen Dark Chocolate Caramel Candy', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'You would have to eat an entire cake pan full of brownies to make your taste buds as happy as they will be with just one Riesen Dark Chocolate Caramel Candy. The second your teeth break through the decadent dark chocolate and are greeted by gooey, sweet caramel, you will understand why this German classic has been a favorite of many around the world for many years.Riesen Candy was first introduced in the 1930s, only back then it was a wrapped and branded as caramel. By the 1940s, a chocolate-caramel blend was created, but it was not until the late 1908s that the caramel was covered in rich dark chocolate. Stock up on Riesen Dark Chocolate Caramel Candy, and you can satisfy your sweet tooth with one small piece, rather than a plate full of cake!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/i/riesen-dark-chocolate-caramel-candy-24ct_1.jpg', '2764~riesen-dark-chocolate-caramel-candy-24ct_1.jpg', 'riesen-dark-chocolate'),
(2765, 'Caramel Sugar Free Hard Candy', 45.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'If you love caramel flavor but want less sugar in your daily diet, our hard candy is a great choice! These sugar free confections offer big taste in a small package. Every morsel features the savory sweetness of a creamy piece of real caramel.Each is smooth, hard and completely sugar-free so you never feel guilty for indulging. Our bulk sugar free hard candy package is a convenient way to ensure you never run out when cravings hit! Our sugar free caramel candy arrives individually wrapped in bronze foil. Each includes an appealing shiny appearance with subtle polka dotted sides.A quick twist of the wrapper and you are ready to enjoy classic caramel goodness! Use these sugar free candies to fill the office candy jar or store them at home, at your desk or wherever cravings are likely to strike. Our handsome sugar free caramel hard candy is also ideal for weddings, showers, birthdays, holidays and other events.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-caramel-5lb_2.jpg', '2765~golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-caramel-5lb_2.jpg', 'caramel-golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy'),
(2766, 'Black Cow Bites Changemaker Jar', 12.99, '160', 'ct', 'caramel', 'At just half the size, these little Black Cow Bite Size Changemaker Jar candies are more like a calf than their bigger bovine candy equivalents. However, they don\'t skimp on any of the delicious chocolate caramel flavor or salty sweet chew that Black Cow candies are famous for!With this big supply of Black Cow Bite Size Changemaker Jar candies, you\'ll be able to snack happily for days and days. If you\'re having a raffle, try auctioning off some of these Black Cow Bite Size Changemaker Jar candies. People will love the classic taste, flavor and style and you\'ll be able to pull in more money for a good cause. You can even use these for a candy buffet bar at home or to keep in the kitchen for a quick lunchbox stuffer the kids have a cow over!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-cow-bite-size-216ct.jpg', '2766~black-cow-bite-size-216ct.jpg', 'black-cow-bite-size-changemaker-jar'),
(2767, 'Caramel Corn Jelly Belly', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Now you can savor the delicious, warm taste of classic caramel corn in a chewy jelly bean! Jelly Belly caramel corn jelly beans are a small candy that\'s big on flavor.Each piece is packed with a winning combination of sweet, creamy caramel and delicious popcorn! What make this Jelly Belly creation even more exciting is the gorgeous pattern featured one very dainty bean.Our caramel corn jelly beans are a pale, ivory color with golden speckles that represent smooth, melted caramel drizzle. Each jelly bean is also printed with the white Jelly Belly logo, so you know it\'s an authentic confection! Our single-flavor jelly bean packs are the easiest way to get the beans you love without having to pick through an assortment.Caramel corn jelly beans are a great choice for birthday parties, wedding favors and holidays! Order one bulk jelly bean pack or check out our other Jelly Belly flavors and build your own custom candy mix.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-corn-jelly-belly-10lbs_1.jpg', '2767~caramel-corn-jelly-belly-10lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-corn-jelly-belly'),
(2768, 'Vanilla Chocolate Caramels', 40.99, '4.4', 'lb', 'caramel', 'With a swirl of vanilla and chocolate inside a melty caramel, these Vanilla Chocolate Caramels are truly divine. Plus, their see-through cellophane wrapper allows you to see the beauty of the candy before you snack. You can\'t knock a classic. And these Vanilla Chocolate Caramels are definitely something no one will be able to slander once they take a taste. Since these candies are wrapped individually, they make a perfect sweet for candy bowls for your family to frequent, they look great scattered in gift baskets, they also are perfect for putting in your purse or office desk drawer to snack on whenever you need a pick-me-up. If you\'re a fan of caramels and the classic flavors of vanilla and chocolate, then Vanilla Chocolate Caramels are going to make you and your taste buds very happy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla-chocolate-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', '2768~vanilla-chocolate-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', 'vanilla-chocolate-caramels'),
(2769, 'Nestle Crunch Bars with Caramel', 19.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Nestle Crunch bars with caramel offer a new way to enjoy this classic candy. Since 1937, Crunch candy bars have been serving up chocolaty goodness to kids and adults across the country.The original recipe included a solid bar of milk chocolate with crisped rice for extra crunch. As if that wasn\'t enough, Nestle has created something even more exciting for candy lovers with their Nestle Crunch with Caramel bar!This version takes a similar approach but adds something creamy and delicious to the mix! Each bar includes convenient break-lines to form individual bite-sized pieces. Inside each piece is a blanket of smooth, rich caramel over a bed of classic Crunch bar chocolate and crisped rice.Our bulk Nestle Crunch Bars with Caramel come individually wrapped so they are easy to take with you everywhere you go! Keep a few Crunch bars the office or hide them in the pantry as a quick evening snack.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/e/nestle-crunch-bars-with-caramel-24ct.gif', '2769~nestle-crunch-bars-with-caramel-24ct.gif', 'nestle-crunch-bars-caramel'),
(2770, 'Mint Licorice Caramels', 40.99, '4.4', 'lb', 'caramel', 'If the hypnotizing swirl doesn\'t do it for you, then the delicious minty, chewy, sweet flavor sure will! Black and white and wrapped individually in cellophane, Mint Licorice Caramels are both refreshing and addicting with a big bite of chew and sugary sweetness.If you\'re having a black and white event, a black tie wedding, formal affair, Halloween party or practically anything else, then these Mint Licorice Caramels would make an incredible statement for you. Stock up on a bulk bag and you\'ll be able to put them out in candy dishes, give them away to friends, keep them around the house, or serve them on a dessert platter. These Mint Licorice Caramels are so tasty they can do it all and more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', '2770~mint-licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', 'mint-licorice-caramels'),
(2771, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '2771~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(2772, 'Atomic Fireballs Wrapped', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'T-minus, 1, 9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1... Prepare for total taste bud annihilation! These Atomic Fireballs may be small, but don\'t let their unassuming size fool you. Their explosive shell and spicy interior bring the heat of a five alarm fire.With about 50 blazing pieces per pound, there\'s enough candy here to nuke your mouth into oblivion and back again. But if you can summon the courage to put out the blaze, you\'ll be treated to a mild, sweet cinnamon finish that will be well worth the challenge. Just beware. Only the strong mouthed will survive to beat this atomic heat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/t/atomic-fireballs-wrapped-medium-470x470.jpg', '2772~atomic-fireballs-wrapped-medium-470x470.jpg', 'atomic-fireballs-wrapped'),
(2773, 'Cinnamon Imperial Hearts', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Our hearts are beating out of our chests for these Cinnamon Imperial Hearts! With a spicy, hot cinnamon flavor and chewy candy texture, your heart is sure to start pitter pattering for these loveable treats with your first bite. Bring them to a Valentine\'s Day party to share some spice that\'s extra nice with loved ones, stock up to keep your candy dishes full throughout February, or get some of these to add into a Cupid-themed candy buffet bar. The bright, red color of these vibrant hearts and delicious cinnamony flavor is something your eyes will love just as much as your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-hearts.jpg', '2773~cinnamon-hearts.jpg', 'cinnamon-imperial-hearts'),
(2774, 'Hot Tamales Minis', 9.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Hold on to your taste buds! These red Hot Tamales Minis are ready to singe every last one of \'em off of your tongue. Though they may be packed in miniature movie theater boxes, every pack of these tamales are ready with a fiery punch of cinnamon that will blow you away. If you can\'t beat the heat, try adding them to a cup of tea or cocoa for a milder cinnamon fix. But if you\'re prepared for a spice that can\'t be beat, pop a few of these into your mouth at a time and feel the fire. Whatever you do, you\'ll set your mouth a-blaze with this bulk supply.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', '2774~hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', 'hot-tamales-minis'),
(2775, 'Cinnamon Imperials Candy', 20.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'These red hot little cinnamon mouth explosions are great for any candy dish! Cinnamon Imperials candies have a classic taste that everyone remembers from childhood, and they\'re great for all kinds of occasions.Include them as a sweet treat for your Valentine. Add them to an assortment of fruity and spicy candies at a party, or just keep them in the candy dish at home for guests who happen to drop by.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', '2775~cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', 'cinnamon-imperials'),
(2776, 'cinnamon swirl salt water taffy in a white bowl', 19.49, '', '', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'If you have never tried cinnamon salt water taffy then you don\'t know what you are missing out on. The flavor of these is perfect. They have a cinnamon blend that is spicy and works just right with the sweet flavor that they have as well. There is nothing better than the tasty of salt water taffy and when you combine it with cinnamon the flavor really seems to explode. The candies are pink in color and are sure to look great for a many different occasions. You will also like to know that each piece is wrapped individually which is very helpful in making sure that they stay fresh as long as possible. There is just something about the chewy texture of taffy that is able to please so many people. This is a great tasting candy with a great texture that is hard to beat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '2776~cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'cinnamon-salt-water-taffy'),
(2777, 'Cinnamon Sugar Free Hard Candy', 45.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'When was the last time you were able to make your dentist and your mouth happy at the same time? Now you can with these sugar-free cinnamon hard candies! With the traditional, spicy cinnamon bite and lovely red color, these candies are the perfect everyday treat for you and your loved ones without all the calories. Soothe a sore throat with a dose of cinnamon spice, add a couple candies to your afternoon cup of tea, or even take them to work to surprise coworkers. This package has is crammed with about 120 pieces per pound, so you\'ll have fresh breath and a well-stocked candy supply for a long, long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-cinnamon-5lb_2.jpg', '2777~golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-cinnamon-5lb_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy'),
(2778, 'Cinnamon Taffy', 9.90, '3', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Don\'t let your guard down, because these Cinnamon Taffies may look pretty, but they pack a spicy punch that may surprise you! These beautiful pink and red striped taffies have the chewy texture that taffy lovers worship and the spicy kick that only cinnamon can deliver. Stock up your supply to enjoy these little taffies in a variety of ways. Add them to a cup of steaming hot cocoa and let them melt away to add some spice to every sip, bring these to a little girl\'s baby shower for a festive pink look and feisty cinnamon flavor, or even keep them around the house to snack on when you please.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-taffy-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', '2778~cinnamon-taffy-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', 'cinnamon-taffy-sweets'),
(2779, 'Cinnamon Roll Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Hold the phone. This Cinnamon Roll Salt Water Taffy cannot be real! It\'s just too delicious to be true. However, don\'t pinch us if we\'re dreaming because we love the taste of these sweet and sugary Cinnamon Roll Salt Water Taffies that we don\'t want to be interrupted from enjoying their intense flavor.If you\'re a fan of this famous breakfast food, then try it in taffy form. Adding that soft chew to the warm and buttery Cinnamon Roll flavor to Salt Water Taffy makes it the most delicious and decadent treat. Serve some of these at your next family brunch or on the dessert platter alongside coffee and tea.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-roll-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2779~cinnamon-roll-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cinnamon-roll-salt-water-taffy'),
(2780, 'Cinnamon Bears', 18.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Get your cinnamon fix with our delicious gummy bears! Each piece offers serious cinnamon flavor with a look that\'s sure to entice. Just like traditional gummy bears, these handsome teddy\'s have a large head with round ears, adorable paws and an endearing face.Every piece is made of solid gummy candy in a bright red hue that grabs attention and hints at the irresistible flavor that awaits! Take a bite and enjoy your favorite soft candy with a touch of warm spice! Our bulk cinnamon bears are a must-have for events, holidays and parties!Combine with a green candy to create a festive Christmas mix or surprise guests by mixing with other gummy bears in a candy dish. We carry a variety of other single color candies so you can build a custom assortment for any event. Make beautiful wedding favors with a red theme or spice up your birthday party treat bags with our bulk cinnamon bears!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-bears.jpg', '2780~cinnamon-bears.jpg', 'cinnamon-bears-bulk'),
(2781, 'Hot Tamales Theater Boxes', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'We were just talking about Hot Tamales Theater Boxes and how much heat they\'ll pack into our next trip to the movies. Also amazing for when you lay down on the couch to watch a feature film. So good!If you love spicy cinnamon heat, then you\'ll love stocking up with this bulk supply of Hot Tamales movie size boxes. If you\'re going to have a viewing party with friends, spice up the night with some of these for guests to munch on. Even bring Hot Tamales Theater Boxes home to stuff into gift baskets or give away at a raffle. Whatever you do, remember these candies are hot, hot, hot!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-theater-boxes-12ct.gif', '2781~hot-tamales-theater-boxes-12ct.gif', 'hot-tamales-theater-boxes'),
(2782, 'Xtreme Hot Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Sound the alarm! This Xtreme Hot Salt Water Taffy isn\'t playing around with its volcanic heat. Bubbling and boiling in this molten taffy is a hotter-than-heck cinnamon flavor that will blow your socks off and stun your taste buds.As you devour this red and white spicy taffy, you\'ll come across specks of extreme heat that will erupt on your tongue. If you\'re up to the challenge, order yourself a bulk bag today and start snacking with a seriously hot treat. But if this hasn\'t scared you off, then you\'re definitely ready for these Xtreme Hot Salt Water Taffy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/x/t/xtreme-hot-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2782~xtreme-hot-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'xtreme-hot-salt-water-taffy'),
(2783, 'Cinnamon Jelly Belly', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Sugar, spice, and all that\'s nice! These cinnamon Jelly Belly jelly beans are a breath freshening, spicy classic. Their vibrant red color and vivid flavor has made this hot and spicy mini a favorite for years. Drop a few into hot tea, apple cider or enjoy them simply as they are. There\'s no wrong way to indulge with these tasty beans. The Jelly Belly company has been around since 1976 and has showed their talent in producing tantilizing flavors that have pleased customers for decades This cinnamon bean is part of the Jelly Belly family\'s 5 official flavors, and is available to light mouths on fire all year \'round.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', '2783~cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-jelly-belly'),
(2784, 'Altoids Cinnamon', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Altoids cinnamon candy are more than just a curiously strong mint. These refreshing treats are a confection that comes with a long, rich history. The original recipe was created by a London-based company in the 1780s, when King George III sat on the throne. The product\'s high concentration of peppermint oil is what inspired the popular slogan we all know and love today. Altoids are currently available in six different flavors, including cinnamon. The storage tin was introduced in the 1920s and still helps keep each mint fresh and clean, even while on the go. Our bulk mint package is a convenient option for anyone who never wants to go without their favorite candy! Hide a tin in your purse or pocket or keep them in the glove box. The larger quantity is also great to share at the office or while on the job. Invigorate your mouth with Altoids cinnamon mints!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoidscinnamon.jpg', '2784~altoidscinnamon.jpg', 'altoids-cinnamon-12ct'),
(2785, 'Altoids Mints', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Altoids mints are one of the most popular brands available today. If you want a mint with some kick to it, then Altoids is a great choice. They are called the curiously strong mint for a good reason!Each piece is round and features a simple white color that is rather unassuming, until you actually taste the intense peppermint flavor. Each mint is made using a high concentration of invigorating peppermint oil to produce the trademark flavor that made Altoids famous.Along with a distinctively minty flavor, Altoids mints also feature nostalgic packaging. Each box contains many tins with a red border and classic fonts and imagery. Your mints stay fresh and ready to eat and they are easy to carry with you!Keep a tin in your desk drawer, pocket, purse or car. Our bulk Altoids mints box gives you many tins so you can use them for special events, party favors and stocking stuffers!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoids-mints-12ct_2.gif', '2785~altoids-mints-12ct_2.gif', 'altoids-mints'),
(2786, 'Hot Cinnamon Gummi Bears', 64.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'If you love the taste of cinnamon and the chewy texture of gummies, you should be hoarding these hot cinnamon gummy bears stat! As they come in a bright red color, they definitely make for the best holiday treats. Whether you plan to play Santa or not, there\'s absolutely no doubt you\'d be spreading the holiday cheer with these little guys!Plus, not only do these Hot Cinnamon Gummi Bears make for the best stocking stuffers during the Christmas season, they also work well for any kind of occasion â€“ be it a Sweet 16 Birthday Party, an office mixer or a themed ladies\' only bachelorette celebration. Truth is - you don\'t need any occasion to brighten up someone\'s day with these cinnamon-flavored goodies. So, delight all your loved ones with these Hot Cinnamon Gummi Bears and make every day feel like a holiday!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-cinnamon-gummi-bears-10lbs_2.jpg', '2786~hot-cinnamon-gummi-bears-10lbs_2.jpg', 'hot-cinnamon-gummi-bears'),
(2787, 'Altoids Cinnamon Smalls', 16.99, '9', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Get your Altoid fix with cinnamon Smalls! These mint candies feature the same rich personality as regular Altoids in a smaller package. Each bite is packed with powerful cinnamon flavor. Pop one in your mouth to give your taste buds a little pick me up. Altoids Smalls are sugar-free so you can enjoy them anytime without feeling the guilt that comes with sugary candy. Altoids Smalls are one of the newest creations to from the historic Altoids brand. The recipe for the original product was created during the reign of King George III in the 1780s. These unique lozenges gained popularity in England because of the high amounts of peppermint oil they contained. Today the famous Altoids name can be found all over the globe with many new flavors added to the list. Cinnamon fanatics will love the convenience and taste that comes with each tin of Altoids Smalls candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoidscinnamonsmalls.jpg', '2787~altoidscinnamonsmalls.jpg', 'altoids-cinnamon-smalls-9ct'),
(2788, 'Red Hots Theater Boxes', 19.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Red Hots candy are a traditional treat that packs a powerful punch of fiery flavor! This nostalgic treat is full of cinnamon for a snacking experience that sizzles. This is one confection that\'s not intended for the weak of heart (or the weak of taste bud!).Each piece includes a dainty round morsel in bright red. Try just one or test your mettle by grabbing a handful and letting them all smother your tongue with intense cinnamon taste! The Red Hots we know and love today have been around for a very long time. This treat was introduced by the Ferrara Pan Company during the 1930s.Their popularity has grown tremendously since then. Red Hots are a popular choice for use as a decoration for cakes, cookies or homemade candies. They are even used in apple sauce recipes! Our bulk Red Hots package contains many theater boxes that are perfect for holidays, events or family movie night.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-hots-theatre-boxes-12ct.gif', '2788~red-hots-theatre-boxes-12ct.gif', 'red-hots-theater-boxes'),
(2789, 'Sizzling Cinnamon Jelly Belly', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Danger, danger! These Sizzling Cinnamon Jelly Belly Jelly Beans should come with caution tape! That\'s because they\'re packing some serious heat in every little bean! If you love cinnamon flavored candy with a big bite, then try these sizzling jelly beans.In a beautiful red shell complete with orange speckles, these red hot beans also do some damage on the eye balls with their bold brightness. If you\'re getting ready for Christmas and want a thematic red treat but with a serious dose of holiday spice, then try these Jelly Belly Sizzling Cinnamon Jelly Beans. They\'re spark conversation, light up the night and ignite more fun every time you take a bite.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sizzling-cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', '2789~sizzling-cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', 'sizzling-cinnamon-jelly-belly'),
(2790, 'Reeds Cinnamon Rolls Hard Candy Rolls', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Reeds Cinnamon Rolls Hard Candy Rolls - 24ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/reeds_cinnamon_rolls_hard_candy_rolls_-_24ct.jpg', '2790~reeds_cinnamon_rolls_hard_candy_rolls_-_24ct.jpg', 'reeds-cinnamon-rolls-hard-candy-rolls'),
(2791, 'Habanero Lix Lollipops', 44.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'You may need to turn up the air-conditioning, wipe the sweat from your brow, and have a tall glass of water handy when you eat one of these Habanero Lix Lollipops.Someone definitely turned up the heat in these unique candies, and by someone, we mean Hotlix, the candy creator of everything unusual and creepy. These Habanero Lix Lollipops taste just like you are eating a superhot pepper.Habanero Lix Lollipops are about 2 inches long, so they last a pretty long time. They are also on a stick that is over 4 inches long, so they are comfortable to hold. Do you have a friend who always orders the hottest wings and spiciest chili when you go out? These Habanero Lix Lollipops would make the perfect gift for them. Break these out at your next summer barbeque with friends to see who can manage to get to the end. They are also perfect to leave in your candy dish at work. When you see someone hanging out at the water cooler, you will know who has been sneaking in and taking your candy while you are out to lunch!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/habanero-lix-lollipops-24ct.gif', '2791~habanero-lix-lollipops-24ct.gif', 'habanero-lix-lollipops'),
(2792, 'Chocolate Cinnamon Bears', 129.99, '27', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Give your taste buds a whole new flavor experience with our amazing chocolate cinnamon bears! These adorable candies are like two snacks in one. Have you ever eaten a red hot cinnamon gummy bear?They are chewy, spicy and very satisfying! Now imagine taking that tangy teddy and smothering it in a layer of rich, smooth chocolate. That\'s what you get when you try our one-of-a-kind chocolate cinnamon bears! Each piece is an outer layer of chocolate surrounding a cinnamon gummy bear.Liven things up by adding our chocolate cinnamon bears to your pantry. Enjoy them as a quick snack or save them for special occasions. They make a great conversation candy that guests will love.Pour into bowls or the candy jar or use to fill party favors! Sneak them in as a surprise with other chocolate covered confections. Our bulk chocolate cinnamon bears includes large quantities that are perfect for gatherings of all sizes.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-cinnamon-bear.jpg', '2792~chocolate-cinnamon-bear.jpg', 'chocolate-cinnamon-bears-bulk'),
(2793, 'Cinna Pix Cinnamon Toothpicks', 25.99, '15', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Cinna-Pix Cinnamon Toothpicks - 15ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinna-pix_cinnamon_toothpicks_-_15ct.jpg', '2793~cinna-pix_cinnamon_toothpicks_-_15ct.jpg', 'cinna-pix-cinnamon-toothpicks'),
(2794, 'Cinnamon Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'With the charm of an old barbershop pole, the spicy sweetness of cinnamon, and a hard candy crunch this old fashioned stick has it all. You can satisfy a spicy and sweet craving, stir them into a cup of hot cocoa or hot mulled cider for a unique twist, and even use them as an adorable decoration on a gingerbread house! There are just so many possibilities. And with 8 sticks in every package, there are enough to do it all. These classic sticks have been around for generations and still have the gusto to wow your friends and family.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-sticks-cinnamon.jpg', '2794~candy-sticks-cinnamon.jpg', 'cinnamon-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(2795, 'Cinnamon Toothpicks', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Nothing tops off a good meal like a Cinnamon Toothpick to clean your teeth! Sit back, relax, and freshen your breath with these cinnamon flavored sticks. They are a great, flavorful tool to keep around the house for guests, to keep in your purse if you need one, or just to chew on if you love the cinnamony flavor! In reusable tubes, these pointy picks can be stored safely without worry of poking yourself or others. And when you\'re done, you can use the tube again to store some more! Bring some of these home today to help you attain a cleaner mouth and enjoy a taste of spicy cinnamon every time you use them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-toothpicks-20ct.gif', '2795~cinnamon-toothpicks-20ct.gif', 'cinnamon-toothpicks-20ct'),
(2796, 'Hot Tamales', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Jumpstart your taste buds with the spicy flavor of Hot Tamales candy! This classic treat is another Just Born creation. They are similar to the famous Mike & Ike candies, with a capsule shape and smooth texture.Each piece is delightfully chewy and soft, so they are easy to bite and enjoy. Unlike Mike & Ikes, Hot Tamales feature an intense cinnamon flavor that will set your tongue on fire (in a good way!).Our bulk Hot Tamales are a popular choice for events, gatherings and casual snacking. Each box contains many individual bags that are convenient for sharing, giving and eating. Take a bag or two with you so you always have a quick treat to eat while on the go.Use them to fill up party favors for birthday parties and other celebrations. Hot Tamales also make a great addition to this year\'s Halloween candy bowl. Order today and make your mouth tingle with the amazing taste of sizzling Hot Tamales!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-24ct_1.gif', '2796~hot-tamales-24ct_1.gif', 'hot-tamales-packs'),
(2797, 'Sugar Free Cinnamon Bears', 36.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Sugar free gummies? Is it really even possible? It sure is, and these chewy, bright red gummi bears pack a powerful cinnamon punch. They are hot enough to turn up the heat, but definitely not so hot that you want to stop with only one. We\'re sorry, but you\'re on your own to try to muster up self-control. :)These Sugar Free Cinnamon Bears are kosher certified, sweetened with Maltitol syrup and made in the USA. They are also the perfect candy dish companion for Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, and black tie events.Most people just need to hear the words cinnamon and gummi for their heart to start racing a little faster. Of course, for many, consuming sugar-laden candy is out of the question, so that excitement quickly turns to a blend of disappointment and sadness, sprinkled with a hint of anger. If this sounds like you, prepare to be doing cartwheels over this bulk supply of Sugar Free Cinnamon Bears.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-cinnamon-bears-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', '2797~sugar-free-cinnamon-bears-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-cinnamon-bears-sweets'),
(2798, 'Cinnamon Squares', 18.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Spice up your day with the irresistible taste of cinnamon squares candy! This unique treat will make your taste buds tingle while satisfying your sweet tooth! Each piece features a handsome square shape formed out of a delicious jelly candy.The outside is smothered in a generous dusting of sugar granules. Each bite starts with a sugary texture followed by smooth, chewy gummy candy! Watch out because these enticing little red squares pack a sizzling bite! Each is packed with cinnamon flavor that warms your mouth with spiciness.Make any occasion a little more exciting by serving our cinnamon squares to guests. Pour into a candy dish and you have a quick and easy snack when surprise visitors arrive.The beautiful red color is also a great choice when making wedding favors. Whether you\'re looking for a tasty Valentine\'s Day candy or a new stocking stuffer at Christmas, our cinnamon squares are sure to please!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-squares-sweets.jpg', '2798~cinnamon-squares-sweets.jpg', 'cinnamon-squares-bulk'),
(2799, 'Sweets Hot Shots', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'When sweet snacks won\'t do, you need to try our Sweets Hot Shots! This is the ultimate candy for anyone who loves spicy flavor. Don\'t be fooled by their small size and cute round shape.These bite-sized confections are real firecrackers! Each includes a solid orb of bright red deliciousness. Pop one in your mouth and experience the sizzling effects of this intense cinnamon candy!Make sure you have enough to put your friends to the cinnamon test by ordering Hot Shots in bulk! You receive many individual pieces that are perfect for parties, picnics and other gatherings. Pour them into a bowl then tempt your friends with the promise of something cinnamon-y.Or use them to make fun party favors to give out after a big event! Sweets Hot Shots are also an eye-catching way to decorate cakes, cookies and other baked goods. No matter how you serve them, Hot Shots is one cinnamon candy that is sure to heat things up!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/sweets-hot-shots.jpg', '2799~sweets-hot-shots.jpg', 'sweets-hot-shots'),
(2800, 'Tic Tac Candy', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Classic Tic Tac mints in their awesome share-enducing dispensers. Give it a shake, tip your head back and enjoy the immense flavor of Tic Tac Candy! This bulk supply will allow you to do that over and over again until you have candy whiplash.With classic flavors of mint and orange, you can decide which one you love most and bring home a big supply of Tic Tac Candy. Drop a few boxes into your purse to freshen up your breath on the go, stash a box or two in your desk to snack on during the day, even keep some in the pantry at home to enjoy when you need a flavorful pick-me-up. When you stock up on these tasty Tic Tac Candies you\'ll have a ton of deliciousness for weeks to come.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/i/tic-tac-candy-24ct_1.jpg', '2800~tic-tac-candy-24ct_1.jpg', 'tic-tacs-packs'),
(2801, 'Ball of Fire Gumballs', 49.99, '1080', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Fire in the hole! These Ball of Fire Gumballs pack the heat of an active volcano and are ready to blow the top off of the roof of your mouth. Still interested? Then we think you\'re strong enough to handle this severe blaze.Created with a hotter than heck cinnamon flavor, you\'ll have to suck on these balls of fire until the inferno gives way to a sweeter cinnamon, gumball center. If you can last that long through the heat, then you\'ll be able to reward yourself with another, because this supply comes with tons and tons of red hot gumballs for you to eat.Now get ready to light a fire that just can\'t be extinguished when you order these incredibly spicy Ball of Fire Gumballs today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/ball-of-fire-gumballs-1080-ct_2.jpg', '2801~ball-of-fire-gumballs-1080-ct_2.jpg', 'gumballs-ball-of-fire'),
(2802, 'Juju Cinnamon Bears', 13.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Juju Cinnamon Bears - 5lb', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/juju_cinnamon_bears_-_5lb.jpg', '2802~juju_cinnamon_bears_-_5lb.jpg', 'juju-cinnamon-bears'),
(2803, 'Gimbals Jelly Beans Spicy Cinnamon', 59.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'If the bright red color didn\'t give to a hint then let us. These Gimbals Spicy Cinnamon Jelly Beans are hot, hot, hot! With a bold and spicy cinnamon flavor, get ready to set your mouth ablaze as soon as you crunch down on the hard candy shell of these spicy jelly beans.Whether you chew fast or slow, you\'ll feel the burn until you\'ve successfully made it past the melting point and into the delicious sweet cinnamon reprieve that finishes off this bean\'s brazen flavor. Get ready for Christmas with a bulk order of our Gimbals Spicy Cinnamon Jelly Beans and dress up your candy dishes. Just make sure you give your guests a heads up before they head straight into the inferno that these beans light in your mouth!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/gimbals-jelly-beans-spicy-cinnamon-bulk_1.jpg', '2803~gimbals-jelly-beans-spicy-cinnamon-bulk_1.jpg', 'spicy-cinnamon-jelly-beans-gimbals'),
(2804, 'Sugar Free Cinnamon Hard Candy', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Your taste buds will tingle when they experience the flavor of GoLightly sugar free cinnamon hard candy! It\'s not easy to find treats that are healthy but still full of the flavors you love.GoLightly has created some of the most irresistible confections that fit the bill perfectly. You get the amazing taste you love in a convenient candy that\'s also sugar free and gluten free! Make dieting easier by using GoLightly sugar free hard candy as your go-to snack when sweet cravings start. Don\'t struggle and feel deprived all day lone when you can satisfy your sweet tooth with these unique little morsels.Our bulk GoLightly candy is the easiest way to get larger quantities so you never have to go without your emergency sugar fix! When you feel satisfied, you are more likely to stick to your diet and achieve your health goals. Try our delicious cinnamon hard candy or any of our other GoLightly sugar free flavors!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-cinnamon-peg-bag.jpg', '2804~sugar-free-cinnamon-peg-bag.jpg', 'sugar-free-cinnamon-hard-candy-go-lightly');
