(2986, 'Red Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in shiny, metallic red wrappers, these little Red Foil Chocolate Balls are sure to make your eyes pop as your mouth waters for what\'s inside. Inside is a solid ball of melty milk chocolate. It\'s up to you whether you want to chomp, chew or let this little sphere melt away. Red Foil Chocolate Balls are the perfect color and candy for Christmas, the Fourth of July, and a birthday party for someone who adores the color. Stock up on these Red Foil Chocolate Balls and mix and match with other flavors and colors or enjoy them all by themselves. Whatever you do, you\'ll love unwrapping these chocolate balls one after the other.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '2986~red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(2987, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '2987~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(2988, 'Assorted Salt Water Taffy Mix', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Assorted salt water taffy mix. Do you remember those amazing trips to the beach with your family when you were a kid? Vacation was never complete without a trip to the candy store and a big bag of salt water taffy. Bring those great memories to life in your mouth any time you like with these assorted salt water taffy candies. Set them out in a candy dish at home or work and share the sweet experience.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', '2988~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(2989, 'Vanilla Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When was the last time your hard working mouth took a vacation? Treat it with a lovely retreat to the salty shores of the boardwalk-lined coast with these saltwater taffys. Complete with a soft, chewy texture and light vanilla taste, you\'ll remember why it\'s so good to get away for a while. Feel like the breeze is in your hair, the sand is between your toes and the jubilant hubub of the boardwalk is buzzing around you bite after bite. In the late 1800s, salt water taffy was discovered when a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be for generations to come.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2989~vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'vanilla-salt-water-taffy'),
(2990, 'Grape Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Beach bums, get ready for a treat that will remind you of the summer heat! This grape salt water taffy has been stretched, chewed, and loved for years. Inspired by the sunny boardwalk, these individually wrapped candies can bring back summertime memories whenever you wish.Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2990~grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'grape-salt-water-taffy'),
(2991, 'Raspberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Sally may sell sea shells by the seashore, but we sell savory salt water taffy that gives her a run for her money! A summertime classic, this raspberry flavored taffy is ready to take you back to the boardwalk any time of the year. Individually wrapped, they are the perfect solution to a sweet tooth or to be used as a party favor. You can almost hear the surf as you let these morsels melt away. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2991~raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'raspberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(2992, 'Peppermint Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When days at the beach get hot, you can do more than jumping in the waves for a cool-down. Try our refreshing Peppermint Salt Water Taffy to beat the heat. The individually wrapped morsels make them ideal to pack in a beach bag or cooler. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2992~peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'peppermint-salt-water-taffy'),
(2993, 'Strawberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'What happens when you combine creamy saltwater taffy with the juicy flavor of ripe red strawberries? You get one of the most mouthwatering confections found on land or in the sea! Saltwater taffy is a classic treat that hails from the sundrenched boardwalks of Atlantic City, NJ. This classic confection has been around for decades and has become a popular souvenir at many seaside destinations. Our strawberry saltwater taffy is easy to get because you don\'t have to go on vacation to buy it!The blend of molasses, sea salt and strawberry flavorings gives our saltwater taffy an irresistibly soft, smooth taste. Every piece is individually wrapped so you can easily separate servings for snacking or place a few in a party or wedding favor! The gentle pink taffy color includes deep red stripes around the sides that make this treat perfect for Valentine\'s Day, anniversaries or any special occasion that celebrates love!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2993~strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'strawberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(2994, 'Laffy Taffy Candy', 37.99, '8.5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Laffy Taffy is such a well-recognized candy that hip-hop artist D4L has immortalized its name in song. You don\'t have to be a fan of rap to enjoy these chewy soft candies, though. Each individually wrapped Laffy Taffy candy comes with a joke written on the wrapper for you to share with your friends. You\'ll laugh with your friends as you satisfy your sweet tooth for this delicious taffy candy. They\'re so good, though, that you might want to share the jokes, but you won\'t ever want to share the candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', '2994~laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-pieces-bulk'),
(2995, 'Tropical Assorted Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'This seashore classic is now heading to the tropics with these Assorted Tropical Salt Water Taffies! Feel the sun on your face, the wind in your hair, and hear the crash of the ocean waves with every bite of these colorful taffies. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/r/tropical_assorted.jpg', '2995~tropical_assorted.jpg', 'tropical-salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(2996, 'Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Prepare to hypnotize your taste buds with these Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffies. In a stark contrast of black and white swirls, these candies are as yummy to eat as they are to look at. Use them for a thematic addition to Halloween or a formal wedding reception. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '2996~licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(2997, 'Key Lime Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Don\'t you just love the light, refreshing sweetness that comes with biting into a slice of key lime pie? How about the fun, chewy tastiness of salt water taffy? Well, you can have the best of both worlds with Key Lime Salt Water Taffy!These individually wrapped goodies have a classic taste that everyone loves and a great chewy texture, too. Put them in a candy dish for your guests at home or your coworkers at the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2997~key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'key-lime-salt-water-taffy'),
(2998, 'Cherry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Cherry salt water taffy is sure to take you back to your childhood vacations to the beach. These red and pink chewy candies will be a huge hit anywhere you take them. Put them out in a candy dish at home, or take them to share the sweet taffy goodness at work or at a party. Cherry salt water taffy makes a great addition to a Valentine\'s Day gift bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2998~cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-salt-water-taffy'),
(2999, 'Blueberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Blueberry saltwater taffy combines all the goodness of fresh picked berries with the seaside nostalgia of this timeless treat! Our soft taffy candy is just as smooth as a soft sandy beach with flavor that\'s as powerful as the ocean waves. The first saltwater taffy was born right along the seashore in Atlantic City, New Jersey. Over 100 years later we still savor the luxuriously smooth texture and mouthwatering taste that comes with each piece. Our bulk saltwater taffy pack includes all the blueberry candy you can handle, individually packaged. Each piece is protected by a clear wrapper that shows its pleasant blue color. Eating is easy: just untwist the ends and take a bite of timeless saltwater taffy! Our blue version is perfect for baby showers, wedding favors, birthday celebrations, 4th of July events and any occasion that features azure hues. Try just one bulk candy bag or order other flavors to create an attractive contrast at parties and picnics!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blueberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '2999~blueberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'blueberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(3000, 'Banana Taffy Taffy Town', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you love to visit the zoo then this is the perfect candy for you to enjoy. This Banana Salt Water Taffy has such a real banana flavor that each and even monkeys can be fooled about their authenticity. Salt water taffy is going to make you feel great about yourself anyway, because it provides a person with a bit of nostalgia. There is no other treat which screams about summer more than salt water taffy. This sweet banana taste is going to make eating one of these treats an impossibility but no need to worry as they come in a hefty bulk bag. That should be enough to keep you munching for hours. The real banana taste is going to make you want to visit the local zoo, because you will want to share them with all the other primates. Candy is always best when it is shared with someone who appreciates it and primates of all ages will absolutely love this!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3000~banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'banana-salt-water-taffy'),
(3001, 'Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lite', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Summertime and the living\'s easy. And now, sugar free! Try these Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lites for a healthier fix of the boardwalk classic and all the scrumptious taste of the original recipe. In blue-raspberry, strawberry, lemon, chocolate, orange, and vanilla, let these little morsels melt away as you remember digging your toes into the sand and letting the sun shine in your hair. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', '3001~sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite'),
(3002, 'cinnamon swirl salt water taffy in a white bowl', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you have never tried cinnamon salt water taffy then you don\'t know what you are missing out on. The flavor of these is perfect. They have a cinnamon blend that is spicy and works just right with the sweet flavor that they have as well. There is nothing better than the tasty of salt water taffy and when you combine it with cinnamon the flavor really seems to explode. The candies are pink in color and are sure to look great for a many different occasions. You will also like to know that each piece is wrapped individually which is very helpful in making sure that they stay fresh as long as possible. There is just something about the chewy texture of taffy that is able to please so many people. This is a great tasting candy with a great texture that is hard to beat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3002~cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'cinnamon-salt-water-taffy');
