(3147, 'Haribo Gold Bears', 21.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Everyone\'s favorite Haribo gummies are now available in a big gold box! What\'s one of the first sweet treats everyone thinks of when they are hungry for a chewy candy? Why gummy bears of course! Our adorable little bruins come packed with fruity flavor. Each piece includes the recognizable shape that make these a popular go-to snack for kids and adults alike. Our Haribo gummy bears can be purchased in a bulk candy pack! You get more irresistible morsels to enjoy at home or share with guests. This size is perfect for use in treat bags at birthday parties or to distribute at picnics, school events and other gatherings. They are conveniently packaged so you can hide a few in your purse, pocket or include them in your child\'s school lunch. You\'ll never have to go hungry when your sweet tooth craves the soft, juicy taste of classic gummy bears when you buy our bulk candy box!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-original-gold-gummi-bears.jpg', '3147~haribo-original-gold-gummi-bears.jpg', 'haribo-gold-bears-24ct'),
(3148, 'Hershey\'s Assorted Miniature Chocolate Bars', 139.99, '25', 'lb', 'candy-bars', 'Good things come in small packages. But they can certainly come in big ones too! And this bulk assortment of Hershey\'s Milk Chocolate, Hershey\'s Dark Chocolate, Mr. Goodbar, and Krackel mini candy bars is definitely an example of a very good thing. Founded in 1894, Hershey has been pumping out delicious candy bars long before any of us were around to enjoy them. That\'s why with their time-tested quality and handcrafted taste, you\'ll be snacking happily for a long time. And now with this bulk bag, you\'ll be able to get your entire family\'s favorite candy bars in one package.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hersheys-assorted-miniature-chocolate-bars-25lbs_2.jpg', '3148~hersheys-assorted-miniature-chocolate-bars-25lbs_2.jpg', 'hersheys-miniature-chocolate-bars-bulk-case'),
(3149, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops Large', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Chewy Sugar Daddy caramel pops offer the best of everything when it comes to sweet snacking. These mouthwatering delights produce big flavor that no caramel fanatic can resist! The beauty is in the taste and the design. Each piece includes a generous bar of creamy caramel candy perched atop a convenient disposable stick. Simply peel the bright yellow wrapper and enjoy golden caramel confection to your heart\'s content without the gooey mess!Anytime is a great time to buy Sugar Daddy candy! Give them away during holidays, hide them in party favors or keep them around the pantry for days when you\'re craving something smooth and sweet. Since 1925, Sugar Daddies have been the go-to candy for caramel lovers. New sizes have been introduced over the years, but none compare to the large Sugar Daddy caramel pop. Take your mouth on a saccharine vacation with a box of nostalgic Sugar Daddy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', '3149~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-large'),
(3150, 'Haribo Roulette Candy', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Haribo roulette gummies put a fun spin on snack time! These tempting confections come in convenient tube shaped packages that fit almost anywhere. Every piece forms a chewy disc with round edges and a solid middle. Bite down and experience the soft, smooth texture that makes Haribo gummies so delectable. If that\'s not enough gummy goodness for you, you\'ll also love the different flavors and colors that are included in every pack!Our Haribo roulette candies are the perfect blend of exciting style and practical design for young and old alike. Adults will appreciate how compact and convenient they are while children will love the sugary taste that is packed into every piece. Now you can get all the roulette gummies you want with our bulk candy package! Keep your snack cabinet or pantry well stocked or use them for special events like birthday parties, holiday gatherings, picnics and school activities!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/haribo-roulette-gummy-candy.jpg', '3150~haribo-roulette-gummy-candy.jpg', 'roulette-36ct'),
(3151, 'Toblerone Milk Chocolate Bar 12.6oz', 99.99, '10', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'A triangular chocolate bar in a triangular package with lovely retro graphics â€“ with such a striking look, it\'s no wonder Toblerone has stayed so popular. Normally it would be unwise to judge a candy by its wrapper, but Toblerone has proven itself a high-quality chocolate confection, and the alpine motif on the label reminds every chocolate lover that Toblerone confections are part of the reason Swiss chocolates are considered among the world\'s finest.The prism package of the Toblerone milk chocolate bar protects a luxurious chocolate candy bar flavored with delicate additions of honey and almond. Instantly recognizable as a top-of-the-line chocolate brand, each Toblerone bar makes an ideal portable dessert which is perfect for sharing with a friend â€“ if, that is, you can bring yourself to sacrifice a piece of its goodness!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/toblerone_12.6.jpeg', '3151~toblerone_12.6.jpeg', 'toblerone-milk-chocolate-bar'),
(3152, 'Payday Bars', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Cha-ching! The cash is rolling in with every bite of these delectable, crunchy Payday Bars. Filled with crunchy, whole peanuts and a delicious caramel nougat, it\'s no wonder why people around the world look forward to bite after bite of these rich treats. Introduced to candy bar loves for the first time in 1932, customers have been cashing in on these confections ever since! Bring some home to your candy bar and nut-lovers, spoil trick-or-treaters with a handful of these bars, or even crumble them into baked goods for an extra touch of yum! You\'ll feel like you struck it rich with every bite.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/paydaybars-24ct.gif', '3152~paydaybars-24ct.gif', 'payday-bars'),
(3153, 'Big Hunk Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'What a hunk! A Big Hunk Bar that is. These attractive candy bars are a delicious and old fashioned treat from the 1950s. With yummy honey-sweetened nougat and rich roasted peanuts, this candy is also surprisingly low fat! Fall for this handsome candy bar time after time. Bring some to a birthday party to surprise every guest, give some to a loved one on Valentine\'s Day to get a few laughs, or even keep them around the house to crumble into baked goods and make them extra attractive. This delicious candy bar can do it all and more with its muscley, nutty crunch and creamy, chewy nougat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/i/big-hunk-bars-24ct_2.jpg', '3153~big-hunk-bars-24ct_2.jpg', 'big-hunk-bars'),
(3154, 'Sesame Seed Snaps', 19.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Sezme sesame snaps are an amazingly delicious treat that\'s also good for you! If you simply can\'t decide between sweet and salty, you can enjoy both in every bite with these bar shaped confections.Each is packed with savory sesame seed flavor that\'s complemented by a touch of sugary goodness. They come individually wrapped so they stay fresh until it\'s time to snack. Our bulk Sezme sesame snaps are an excellent alternative food to chocolaty or overly sugary treats.Eat better while satisfying your cravings. This Poland-born treat is cholesterol free and gluten free. Take a bite and experience the pleasant crunch and satisfying flavor that taste buds crave. Our bulk sesame snaps box is a must-have for daily snacking.Use them to pack healthier lunches for your family or keep them as a quick and easy after school snack. Sesame seed candy also makes a great Christmas stocking stuffer!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/e/sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', '3154~sesame-seed-snaps-24ct_2.gif', 'sesame-seed-snaps'),
(3155, 'Giant Smarties 1.2oz', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Giant Smarties candy is the best way to enjoy this popular treat. Each disc shaped piece offers a tart flavor that\'s fun to munch on! Every kid loves to bite down on crunchy, crumbly Smarties. Our large size gives you bigger pieces that last even longer!A generous helping of Smarties are carefully stacked then wrapped in clear plastic which proudly displays the candy\'s name in big red letters. Just untwist an end and prepare for a totally tart treat!Bulk Smarties give you more individual packs to share, give or eat. Stow a box in the pantry as an easy snack when you\'re short on time. You can also keep them at the office to pass around among coworkers. Giant Smarties are a great reward for children as well! Give them out during school activities and events or use them in party favors for kids\' birthdays, family reunions and holidays!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/giant-smarties-12oz-36ct.gif', '3155~giant-smarties-12oz-36ct.gif', 'giant-smarties-box'),
(3156, 'Rocky Road Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Get ready for a bumpy ride! Because this delicious candy bar, Rocky Road, is packed with potholes of deliciousness. Each classic bar is filled with luscious, puffy marshmallow, creamy and delicious milk chocolate, big chunks of roasted cashews, and rich, crispy malt. With 24 candy bars per box, you\'ll have a lot of chewing to do! Bring these to a baseball game for a filling candy that will get you through every inning. Buy some for a cashew and chocolate fan. Even stock yourself up for upcoming Halloween trick-or-treaters. No matter how you enjoy these classic candy bars, your taste buds are in for a wild ride!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rocky-road-bars-24ct_2.gif', '3156~rocky-road-bars-24ct_2.gif', 'rocky-road-bars'),
(3157, 'Twix Bars', 39.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Twix candy bars are sweet, crunchy and sure to satisfy even the most demanding cravings! This hugely popular Mars candy includes a crisp biscuit center that\'s topped in smooth caramel. The outside is smothered in an irresistible blanked of rich milk chocolate.Twix may be considered a modern treat, but its roots date back to the 1960s when it was first sold in the United Kingdom. It arrived in the United States within the next decade and has become a mainstay among candy lovers!Our convenient bulk Twix box is the best way to get more of the confection you love. You get a giant box packed with full sized candy bars. Each is individually wrapped, just like you would buy them at the grocery store! The difference is you get them at a great price and all at once so you always have a Twix candy bar ready to go when you\'re feeling hungry!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/w/twix_bars.jpeg', '3157~twix_bars.jpeg', 'twix-bars'),
(3158, 'Chuckles Candy', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Knee slappers. Lip smackers. Hilarious comics of the candy world. These funny Chuckles Candies are a barrel full of laughs! Chortle with some cherry, orange, lemon, lime, and licorice soft gelly candies dusted with supremely sweet sugar. They are a great way to make your kids smile, look pretty set out in a bowl, and will put all your guests in good humor with every taste of these. With 24 boxes per order, you\'ll be laughing yourself silly for snack times to come! Just see if you can keep a straight face when faced with these delicious, Chuckle\'s Candy jellies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chuckles-candy-24ct.gif', '3158~chuckles-candy-24ct.gif', 'chuckles-box'),
(3159, '100 Grand Bars', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', '1 Grand bars can really make you feel like you have a lot of money. These bars are nothing short of great. They have caramel, milk chocolate, and puffed rice. This means that you can ensure that they taste absolutely wonderful. These would be great when used at a financial event that you were having, or any other event for that matter. Consider even giving them out as Halloween candy, and really leave the trick-or-treaters pleased at what you have given them. There are 36 in a box of these and each bar is wrapped individually with a red colored wrapper. This helps to ensure that you can eat them or use them when it is best for you and still know that the bars will be fresh when you are ready for them. So why not delight your taste buds with one of these great bars of fun candy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/n/one-hundred-grand-bars.jpg', '3159~one-hundred-grand-bars.jpg', '100-grand-bars'),
(3160, 'U No Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'U-No bars are a tasty treat made by the Annabelle Candy Company. Every chewy bite is sure to satisfy even the most demanding taste buds. U-No bars also make a great summer treat when frozen. Simply place in the freezer until solid then enjoy as a unique candy-popsicle!Our bulk U-No box will give you many bars to enjoy at home or with a crowd. Serve them to guests, keep them as a quick snack or hand them out as party favors or Halloween candy. They make great stocking stuffers, Easter basket candy or a special candy reward for students.Simply called Ã’Annabelle\'sÃ“, the company was founded in 1950 and named for the owner\'s daughter. Annabelle\'s began producing popular confections including a Rocky Road bar. In 1978 they added a number of products including the U-No bar. This new creation features a truffle style filling combined with crushed almonds. Everything is smothered in silky milk chocolate.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/u/-/u-no-bars-24ct.gif', '3160~u-no-bars-24ct.gif', 'u-no-bars'),
(3161, 'Zero Bars', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Zero candy bars are a delightful treat that brings together flavors that are not often combined. This unique confection was originally created in 1920 and quickly became known for its white color.The surface is covered in a smooth layer of white fudge while the middle is composed of savory caramel, almond nougat and delicious peanut. The Zero Bar we know today began as the Double Zero bar but was later renamed to its current moniker in 1934.Zero started out as part of the Hollywood Brands candy company but changed hands multiple times.Today it belongs to the famous Hershey family of candies. Now you can enjoy the sweet, hearty taste of a Zero bar anytime you like! Just order a bulk candy box so you always have individually wrapped bars ready to serve and enjoy! Zero bars also make great gifts and favors for parties and holiday events!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/z/e/zero-bars-24ct.gif', '3161~zero-bars-24ct.gif', 'zero-bars'),
(3162, 'Whoppers', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Ladies and gentlemen. Boys and girls. What we have here on CandyStore.com is the original malted milk ball, better known as Whoppers! If you\'re clapping you hands with glee and salivating at the thought, then we have another juicy tid bit of information for you: they come in bulk.Stock your pantry full of these Whoppers boxes and you\'ll have enough to grab when your family watches a movie on the couch, you head out to a baseball game or sporting event or just have a colossal sweet tooth to contend with. Order your supply of Whoppers today and start enjoying them ASAP!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/whoppers-24ct.gif', '3162~whoppers-24ct.gif', 'whoppers-packs'),
(3163, 'Rolo', 35.99, '36', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'Rolo\'s have been a favorite candy for many since childhood. It seems that these great candies have been around forever. After all what is not to love about them. They have caramel on the inside and are coated on the outside with wonderful tasting chocolate. These great candies also come in rolls so that you are able to open up, and just starting popping them in to your mouth. These will be great for kids or adults. Many people will find that these are almost addicting as they are able to really please their taste buds. You can give these out as candy for Halloween or even use them for stocking stuffers at Christmas time if you are looking for something that nearly everyone is sure to enjoy. What better way to be able to get the great combine flavor of caramel and chocolate then to partake in Rolo candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/o/rolo-36ct.gif', '3163~rolo-36ct.gif', 'rolo'),
(3164, 'Mountain Bars', 15.99, '15', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'If you\'re afraid of heights, you\'ll just have to get over it and try a taste of our amazing Mountain Bar! These peanut butter, cherry and original Mountain Bars flavors will send your taste buds to a higher elevation of deliciousness.Since Mountain Bars come individually wrapped and in three different flavors, you\'ll be able to make everyone in your home happy when you bring a big box of these candies home. Add some to a dessert table, bring some on a ski trip, or just enjoy these classic candies when you want a sweet fix you\'ll love.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/t/mtn_bar_caddy_peanut_btr_open.jpg', '3164~mtn_bar_caddy_peanut_btr_open.jpg', 'peanut-butter-mountain-bar'),
(3165, 'Skittles Sour', 27.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'If you are looking for a new twist on skittles then you should try the sour skittles. These are fun and exciting for people of all ages. They also come in many different colors such as pink, purple, green, blue, and yellow. This means that you will get to enjoy a variety of colors and flavors. The texture of these is the same as the regular skittles meaning that they are soft but chewy. The main difference that you will notice with these is that they have sour coating on the outside of them that makes for their unique sour taste. The flavors that you get from these are fruity and are much like the classic flavors that you find but they are able to provide you with that extra kick. This is one candy that is sure to get your taste buds going in high gear. If you are looking for something fun this is certainly what you need.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-sour-24ct_1.jpg', '3165~skittles-sour-24ct_1.jpg', 'skittles-sour'),
(3166, 'Abba Zaba Bars', 28.99, '24', 'ct', 'candy-bars', 'This candy\'s name will roll right off your tongue and make you want to come back for more! Abba Zabba Candy Bars are a genius mix of taffy and peanut butter that you will love. Around since the 192s, this historic candy bar has a taxi cab-esque wrapper that will remind you of the \'\'roaring\'\' 2s in New York City. Get yourself some for an upcoming Great Gatsby themed party, to wrap up for a grandparent who loves this nostalgic taste, or to introduce a taste of the past to your family. With 24 candy bars per order, you\'ll have enough to go around!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/b/abba-zabba-bars-24ct_3.jpg', '3166~abba-zabba-bars-24ct_3.jpg', 'abba-zaba-bars'),
(3167, 'Caramel Apple Pops', 9.99, '48', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Enjoy the bounty of the autumn harvest without setting foot in an orchard. A play on a classic fall favorite, these classic green apple lollies are slathered in a creamy, chewy, caramel coating that has been greedily gobbled up for years. Bring them to a fall party, use them as Halloween treats, or remind yourself of autumn any time of the year. Every snacker will feel like you\'re on a tractor ride, traversing a corn maze, and smelling fresh bales of hay every time you eat one of these. And the best part is, these tart treats are here all year \'round.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-apple-pops-48ct_1.jpg', '3167~caramel-apple-pops-48ct_1.jpg', 'caramel-apple-pops'),
(3168, 'Caramel Candy Squares', 16.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Don\'t be such a square! Unless you want to be a delicious, creamy Caramel Square. These tawny, creamy cubes are amazing little morsels that will melt away in your mouth and leave a smile on your face. Individually wrapped in clear cellophane, they make a great addition to a candy buffet bar, as a candy dish go-to, or even to keep around the house and melt into hot chocolate and baked goods. Caramel has been around for centuries and transforms typical granulated sugar into this famous form of ooey, gooey chewiness when heated at a high heat. We\'d like give the culinary geniuses who came up with this fantastic candy a pat on the back!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-squares-5lb_1.jpg', '3168~caramel-squares-5lb_1.jpg', 'caramel-squares-wrapped'),
(3169, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Prepare to be spoiled rotten with an overdose of creamy caramel and sugary sweetness! These Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops are an American classic that have had customers smacking their lips for years. Invented in 1925, it wasn\'t until 1932 that these famous pop got their sugary name. Give your family a taste of the olden days with some of these delicious caramels. Bring them to a party, add some to a candy buffet bar, or use them as a yummy, melty stirrer for hot chocolate. With over 48 caramel pops per box, get ready to indulge your family and friends for a long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', '3169~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-48ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops'),
(3170, 'Caramel Cream Bulls Eyes', 35.99, '', '', 'caramel', 'Each Caramel Cream (or Bull\'s Eye), starts with a white cream filling at the center. The outside includes a generous layer of high quality caramel to create a round treat. Our bulk Caramel Creams arrive individually wrapped with nostalgic red Goetze branding.Caramel Cream Bulls Eyes are the crowning jewel in the Goetze\'s catalog. The Goetze brand goes way back to 1895. By 1917, the family-owned company introduced its first soft caramel candies, much to the delight of candy lovers!Today, Caramel Creams are considered Goetze\'s signature creation, and it\'s easy to see why once you sink your teeth into one! Keep them in the candy jar at home, take them to the office to share or add to a gourmet gift basket! Caramel Creams are also a wonderful choice for shower and wedding favors. Their sweet, creamy taste and classic look appeals to candy lovers of all ages! Find out what makes Goetze so delicious by adding Caramel Creams to your next gathering.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-creams-bulls-eyes-goetze-candy-store-470x470.jpg', '3170~caramel-creams-bulls-eyes-goetze-candy-store-470x470.jpg', 'bulls-eyes-caramel-creams'),
(3171, 'Cow Tales Caramel Sticks', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Our bulk box of Cow Tales contains a very generous quantity of individually wrapped caramel pieces. Candy lovers of all ages will love the chewy texture and smooth cream filling. Order your choice of original vanilla, strawberry cream or chocolate or try multiple boxes so you can sample a combination of Cow Tale flavors!Cow Tales are the creation of Goetze\'s Candy. The company began in 1895 as the Baltimore Chewing Gum Company. The company\'s signature Caramel Cream was created in 1917 followed by the classic Cow Tale.This confection was very similar to the Caramel Cream, but instead of a small disc of chewy caramel it featured a long tube (or tail) with delectable cream running through the middle. Different flavors have been added, including strawberry, vanilla, chocolate and caramel apple, but the classic version is still often considered the best!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/cow-tales-original-caramel--cream-sticks-36ct.jpg', '3171~cow-tales-original-caramel--cream-sticks-36ct.jpg', 'cow-tales-original-caramel-cream-sticks'),
(3172, 'Caramel Block Bulk', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'When it comes to creating delicious treats at home the number one ingredient is going to be yummy candy. When you buy a bulk caramel block then you will have enough delicious goodness to create a whole kitchen full of treats that will feed an army. One of the best things about this caramel product is that it will make anything into a treat. Eating fruit can be a difficult thing to get kids to do, well learn how to cover it in caramel and you have created a fruit snack that no kid can resist. This has been the secret recipe for caramel apples for many years. Simply heat up the caramel put an apple on a stick and dip. Once the candy coating has cooled, you have created a snack that will be remembered forever. This works for other fruit as well. Some cover strawberries and some will cover bananas but probably the best selection is to offer a plate of fruit and the melted candy as a dipping sauce. More fruit will disappear than you believed possible.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulk-caramel-block-5lb_2.jpg', '3172~bulk-caramel-block-5lb_2.jpg', 'bulk-caramel-block'),
(3173, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops Large', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Chewy Sugar Daddy caramel pops offer the best of everything when it comes to sweet snacking. These mouthwatering delights produce big flavor that no caramel fanatic can resist! The beauty is in the taste and the design. Each piece includes a generous bar of creamy caramel candy perched atop a convenient disposable stick. Simply peel the bright yellow wrapper and enjoy golden caramel confection to your heart\'s content without the gooey mess!Anytime is a great time to buy Sugar Daddy candy! Give them away during holidays, hide them in party favors or keep them around the pantry for days when you\'re craving something smooth and sweet. Since 1925, Sugar Daddies have been the go-to candy for caramel lovers. New sizes have been introduced over the years, but none compare to the large Sugar Daddy caramel pop. Take your mouth on a saccharine vacation with a box of nostalgic Sugar Daddy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', '3173~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-large'),
(3174, 'Caramel Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Caramel swirl salt water taffy is a rich, chewy treat that you\'ll love to eat! Anyone who adores the sweet, savory flavor of classic caramel must experience the taste of our salt water taffy. Each piece recreates the feeling of eating a bite-sized piece of high quality caramel but with that taffy texture you know and love.Our salt water taffy is available in single-flavor packages so you get exactly what you want every time you order! Bulk caramel swirl salt water taffy can be used for events and much more. Fill treat bags or wedding favors with these elegant little pinwheels. Each includes a toasty brown hue that\'s accented by a slender spiral swirl of white.Each piece arrives individually wrapped so it stays fresh and enjoyable. Order our caramel saltwater taffy for your next event or keep a package at home or at the office to eat as a quick snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3174~caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(3175, 'Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', '\'\'Mooo-ve\'\' over for these Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffies. With their beautiful white and black cow spots and creamy flavor, you won\'t ever want to put these down or put them out to pasture. This snack is a classic that has satisfied candy lovers for years.Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice_caramel.jpg', '3175~licorice_caramel.jpg', 'licorice-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(3176, 'Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'One classic confection with the flavor of another: it is a novelty with the appeal of a tradition! Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy has a bright green center that looks bright as springtime when you use it as a table scatter or to fill an heirloom dish.A symbol of playful days and sunny summers by the sea, bulk saltwater taffy is beloved by kids and adults for its soft, chewy, flavorful composition, and the individual wrappers on these green and brown taffy delicacies make them perfect for candy buffets, treat bags, and pantry stockpiles of tasty sweets.The tart green apple flavor in this wholesale caramel apple taffy combines with a creamy, sweet caramel taste that is reminiscent of the original molasses recipe from which modern taffy flavors evolved. Apple flavor, too, takes your taste buds straight to the autumn orchards, too. The combination of classic taste appeals makes caramel apple saltwater taffy an especially evocative little treat!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3176~caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy'),
(3177, 'Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy is unbelievable, and sure to become one of your favorite treats. It blends sweet and savory in every single bite.You can probably guess just by looking at the cowhide design of these candies that your taste buds are going to be in for a special treat. In fact, you probably don\'t even need to read their name to know that you are about to indulge in a flavor combination of sweet, decadent caramel and creamy vanilla.Unwrap one, pop it in your mouth, and enjoy a long-lasting sweet that retains its flavor right down until the last speck has been dissolved. Since these kosher certified Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy candies are individually wrapped, they are perfect for candy dishes for any occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla_caramel_taffy.jpeg', '3177~vanilla_caramel_taffy.jpeg', 'vanilla-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(3178, 'Chocolate Caramel Mocha Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'So you are dedicated to upscale flavors like chocolate, coffee, and caramel, but you want to put a nostalgic spin on a dinner-party dessert or movie-night treat. What to do? Chocolate Caramel Mocha Salt Water Taffy, of course!Wonderfully munchable, individually-wrapped pieces of soft and delicious saltwater taffy in a rich combination of three flavors makes a striking addition to a candy buffet as well. The look is perfectly timeless, and the flavor is sophisticated â€“ bulk candy does not get much better than this! Individual wrappers that are easy to open, plus a bold brown and white color mix in each flavorful piece, make chocolate caramel mocha salt water taffy a delicious choice for setting on the napkin at every place setting.Or for offering in a huge bowl for endless sweet luxury. The soft taffy texture of these classically-made pieces is a little harder to find than many sweets, making them the stuff of special occasions and childhood vacations for many candy lovers!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3178~chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(3179, 'Chocolate Caramel Squares Candy', 42.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'We love that these Chocolate Caramel Squares Candies come wrapped in cellophane so we can see right through to the deliciousness! And why would anyone want to cover up a candy that features a delicious milk chocolate square of amazingness and a melty, chewy caramel center inside?Are you a major proponent for Chocolate Caramel Square Candies? Then you\'ve hit the jackpot here on CandyStore.com because we have huge bulk orders of them at budget friendly prices. This means you can bring home hundreds of these Chocolate Caramel Square Candies to chow down on for weeks to come. Or however long your sweet tooth allows.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-caramel-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '3179~chocolate-caramel-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'chocolate-caramel-squares'),
(3180, 'Mini Cow Tales Caramel Creams', 57.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Those who love Cow Tales will certainly love these many Cow Tales. These are able to offer the same great caramel and cream flavor but are just smaller in size. They also come individually wrapped so that they are sure to stay as fresh as possible for as long as possible. These are great for treat bags, snacks, Halloween, and many of occasionsCow Tales offer a great chewy caramel flavor on the outside and the inside is a smooth but creamy center. These are sure to please almost anyone. They are also great for adults as well as children. The best part about it is that you are able to get either a chocolate or vanilla flavor for these great Cow Tales. If you are having a medium sized party then you are sure to find this would be enough for your party as well.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb_1.jpg', '3180~mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb_1.jpg', 'mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb'),
(3181, 'Caramel Corn Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Sometimes too much of one thing is a bad thing. But we don\'t think a double dose of creamy and deliciousness could ever be bad with this Caramel Corn Salt Water Taffy! This rich candy is a great selection for any affair and especially looks nice around the holidays. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3181~caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy'),
(3182, 'Caramel Cheesecake Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'At the risk of sounding cheesy, we\'ll admit to all of you that these Caramel Cheesecake Salt Water Taffies make our hearts melt. That\'s because they\'re so creamy, rich and delicious! Bring them to a party with your closest gal pals, put some on a dessert table, or keep them in the cabinet when a sweet tooth strikes. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3182~caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy'),
(3183, 'Pecan Caramel Pattie Chocolates', 75.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Pecan Caramel Pattie Chocolates are the ultimate indulgence of the chocolate world, combining three decadent tastes and three individual textures into an utterly luscious gourmet candy.Always tempting treats when laid out on trays on a dessert table, these high-quality bulk chocolates bring out the flavorful appeal of pecans and the creamy, slightly chewy warmth of caramel by half-drowning both of them in the thick coating of delicious chocolate.Maybe you want to make gift baskets feel more thoughtful yet keep them relatively economical by tucking in a cellophane bag of these wholesale candies. Maybe you have a corporate event coming up and you want to sweeten your guests outlook with a lovable chocolate caramel treat.Maybe you just like to keep a rich, self-contained dessert on hand in the pantry for unexpected guests. Whatever your need, these pecan caramel pattie chocolates are a distinctly delicious solution.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates-5lbs.gif', '3183~pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates-5lbs.gif', 'pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates'),
(3184, 'Licorice Caramels', 40.99, '4.4', 'lb', 'caramel', 'The mad scientists of the candy world have created a magical hybrid of flavors! We\'re talking about our licorice caramels and can\'t wait for you to bring some home and take a bite.In a dark chocolatey brown, these cellophane wrapped black caramels have the delicious creaminess of caramel and the bite of licorice so the flavor and texture experience is one of the most exciting. Give your mouth a relaxing job to do by popping one of these licorice caramels in and letting is melt away slowly. Now that\'s what we like to call R&R; in the candy world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', '3184~licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', 'licorice-caramels'),
(3185, 'Bull\'s Eye Caramel Creams Theater Box', 22.99, '12', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Bulls-Eyes caramel candies are one of the smoothest, chewiest treats you can add to your candy collection! This classic confection brings together two delicious ingredients.Each piece is round, bite-sized and arrives individually wrapped in clear plastic with the familiar red Goetze\'s logo right at the center. Our theater candy boxes are convenient and contain plenty of pieces for one or two people!Every Bulls-Eyes caramel includes two main parts. The outside is a thick ring of delectable caramel. The middle includes a circle of rich creamy confection. Each bite gives you a bit of both flavors to produce the most irresistible combination for anyone who adores the sweet, savory taste of caramel!Our bulk caramel candy package contains several theater boxes so you have plenty to use as party favors or a quick snack at home. Host your own movie night complete with sweet concessions or take a theater box with you as an easy snack at work!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-box-12ct.gif', '3185~bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-box-12ct.gif', 'bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-boxes'),
(3186, 'Slapstix Caramel Pops', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'What could be better than a giant lollipop? How about one that\'s made with creamy caramel! Our Slapstix caramel pops are a delicious treat that is sure to satisfy your carving for smooth, sweet caramel.Each piece includes a generous block of confection with a gentle swirl of flavor that\'s perched on a disposable stick. Enjoy ooey gooey caramel without sticky fingers! If you\'re looking for a lollipop that\'s unique and chewy, this is a must-try confection!Each comes individually wrapped so the rectangle caramel lollipop stays fresh and ready to enjoy. Order boxes for birthday parties, events and more! Everyone will love receiving these at school activities and community events.Slapstix lollipops also make great stocking stuffers at Christmas time. Whether you\'re filling treat bags for a birthday party or looking for an easy sweet treat to enjoy at home, you will love the rich taste of caramel lollipops!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/l/slapstix-caramel-pops-24ct.gif', '3186~slapstix-caramel-pops-24ct.gif', 'slapstix-caramel-pops'),
(3187, 'Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars', 38.99, '14', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Bite size pieces of pure bliss is what you enjoy with this bulk supply of Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars. Each of the bars has 18 individual squares that are easy to break or cut apart.So, you can serve them to your guests on a tray for dessert, if you can bring yourself to share. Although originated in the United Kingdom, today The Hershey Company has a license to manufacture the divine line of Cadbury products in the United States.Whether you buy them in America or the UK, they are the same mouthwatering, melt-in-your-mouth bars of delicious goodness. Decadent milk chocolate is poured over creamy caramel and hardened.So, although the chocolate is firm on the outside, when you bite into them the gooey caramel comes oozing out. Your taste buds will be dancing. These large Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars make great stocking stuffers or last minute gifts for coworkers.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars-24ct_1.jpg', '3187~cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars-24ct_1.jpg', 'cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars'),
(3188, 'Black Cow Bar', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Chocolate and caramel surely are a decadent combo. With these Black Cow Bars, you\'ll get all of that in one incredible bite. And with this bulk box, you\'ll have a ton of savoring to do!Being a black sheep is never a good thing, but being a black cow certainly is! These Black Cow Bars are full of amazing chewy chocolate caramel that will keep your mouth moving like a cow grazing in the pasture. Pour some of these Black Cow Bars into a trick-or-treating candy bowl for Halloween, bring some home for a barn-themed wedding or party or order some if you just love caramel and chocolate. There\'s no wrong reason to order these tasty treats!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blackcowbar.jpg', '3188~blackcowbar.jpg', 'black-cow-bar'),
(3189, 'Slo Poke Bar', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'If the name is any hint, you should slow down and enjoy this delicious caramel candy. That\'s because Slo Poke Bars are made of incredible salty and sweet caramel that melts in your mouth slowly so you can delight in the flavor for longer.If you\'re a fan of caramels, then these Slo Poke Bars are a candy we\'re sure you\'ll adore. In a bulk size box, these Slo Poke Bars will provide you with hours of sweet satisfaction. Stock your pantry with some of these incredible caramels to use in baking, give out in gift baskets or enjoy piece by piece. If you\'re having a stressful day, indulging in one of these bars will surely slow down the pace and help you relax.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/l/slopokebar.jpg', '3189~slopokebar.jpg', 'slo-poke-bar'),
(3190, 'Chocolate Covered Caramel and Marshmallow', 66.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Goodness gracious. Just when you didn\'t think something more delicious than chocolate covered caramel could come around, these chocolate-covered caramel and marshmallows come out to surprise you!In a ridiculously fluffy, chewy, melty and delicious combination of caramel, milk chocolate and marshmallow, these candies will melt in your mouth and melt your heart at the same time. If you want gourmet-tasting candy for an economical price, bring home a bulk supply of our Chocolate Covered Caramel and Marshmallow candies and you can munch on tasty treats that seem like they\'re out of a glass case of a fine chocolatier\'s store. Serve these on your next party\'s dessert platter and wow your guests with the deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-caramel-and-marshmallow-6lbs_4.gif', '3190~chocolate-covered-caramel-and-marshmallow-6lbs_4.gif', 'caramel-marshmallow-chocolate-covered'),
(3191, 'Black Cow Bite Size', 59.99, '15', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Moooo-ve over other candies. These Black Cow Bite Size treats are a crowd favorite with their chocolate flavored chewy caramel. Wrapped in fun sizes, they\'re a perfect little dessert you can graze on between any meal. Bite in for a chewy, gooey and ooey texture and flavor you\'ll never want to put to pasture. Milk this bulk bag of Black Cow Bite Size candy for all its worth by indulging on decadent chocolate caramel after chocolate caramel. Whether you like to enjoy your sweets solo or add them to other recipes, this Black Cow Bite Size candy can do it all and more. Add some to a candy buffet bar. Unwrap a few to use atop cupcakes and other sweets. Even dice some up to add to the top of an ice cream sundae.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black_cow_bites_bulk.jpg', '3191~black_cow_bites_bulk.jpg', 'black-cow-bite-size'),
(3192, 'Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels', 64.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'We did a double take when we first saw these Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels, too! That\'s because with a double dose of incredible chocolate in every square, these little morsels pack enough sweet, savory and melty deliciousness into every bite. In either milk or dark chocolate, these Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels are an incredible treat. Order a bulk supply and you can make your very own Valentine\'s Day boxes for the people you love most. Or, you can be content to know that a yummy and spectacular treat awaits you whenever you need a sweet fix.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', '3192~chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramels'),
(3193, 'Chocolate Covered Vanilla Caramels', 64.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Chocolate, vanilla and caramel are three of the most popular flavors in the candy world. Our delicious chocolate collection brings you a one-of-a-kind confection that combines all three in the most delightful way!Our chocolate covered vanilla caramels are sure to satisfy even the most demanding sugar cravings with a combination of richness and sweetness. Every bite-sized piece includes a generous filling packed with solid caramel flavored with a hint of delectable vanilla.The outside is covered in a smooth blanket of milk chocolate accented by alternating chocolate drizzle. Not only are these chocolate candies delicious, but they\'re also very elegant to look at.Arrange them on a tray for guests or add to wedding favors to send your guests off with an edible gift that includes high quality gourmet chocolate! Our bulk candy pack makes it so easy to get the quantity you need for events of any size.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', '3193~chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramels');
