(3244, 'Green Watermelon Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'We think these candies are \'\'de-vine.\'\' A real knee-slapper we know, but in all seriousness, these Pink Watermelon Fruit Sours Candies taste like they\'re fresh off the vine. Covered in a beautiful, glossy pink shell and complete with a soft, fruity chew, these candies are cultivated by using some of the sweetest techniques in the candy biz. Use some for a light sweet at a backyard picnic, bring some to a gathering of friends, even use them for a lovely addition to an outdoor wedding. For watermelon and candy enthusiasts, alike, this bag will provide you with hours and hours of happy snacking.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/0/8/08017-_watermelon_sours.png', '3244~08017-_watermelon_sours.png', 'pink-watermelon-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(3245, 'Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 25.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Wooooweee! These tart purple candies deliver an unrelenting pucker with delicious, fruity flavor. If you like a sour shot to the mouth, try our Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy. The sourest candy on the vine, these little pucker-packed candies will please every sour lover. Bring some to a purple themed party, add some to a lemonade for a sour grape flavor addition and pretty garnish, or keep them around the house when you\'re in the mood for a feisty snack. Their deep, purple coloring may look unsuspecting, but get ready for a dose of tartness that will thrill your taste buds!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '3245~purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'purple-grape-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(3246, 'Jelly Belly Jelly Beans', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'coated', 'Oh, behold the possibilities! With 50 original flavors plus even more limited-edition beans, concoct combination after combination of inventive candy recipes with this bulk bag of Jelly Belly jelly beans. Maybe you have a hankering for chocolate covered banana, vanilla espresso or coconut orange. Whatever your signature recipe, you can be the chef with the pick of the littler of hundreds of beans brimming with unique flavor. The Jelly Belly company has been around since 1976 and has honed their talent in producing tantilizing flavors that have pleased customers for years. See why for yourself why they are an American favorite with this bulk bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', '3246~jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', 'jelly-belly-jelly-beans'),
(3247, 'Purple M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Purple purists, unite! Our bulk, mono-hued M&Ms; are just the ticket to satisfy your purple palate. Your friends might wonder how you found the time to sift through bags and bags of candy in search of one color, but you\'ll just sit back, relax, and snack happily knowing it was as simple as purchasing them here. Since M&Ms; launched their line of customizable candies, chocolate lovers around the world have been able to spruce up any event or snacktime with their favorite colors. They make great personalized gifts and add the perfect touch of personality to any home\'s candy bowl.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-mms_1.jpg', '3247~purple-mms_1.jpg', 'purple-mms'),
(3248, 'Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Pucker up, buttercup! These Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy have a mighty mix of sour and sweet to delight the mouths of many. Soft, chewy, tangy, and gorgeous, the bright mix of candy balls is a cheerful dose of sugar and citrus. Use them for an autumn inspired gift basket, on the Thanksgiving dessert table, or even as sour additions to a trick-or-treat stash. They can even make a summertime festival even more special by adding the beautiful color of the hot sun. There is no wrong way for your friends and family to enjoy these fruity, delicious and sour candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '3248~orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'orange-tangerine-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(3249, 'Fun Size M&Ms Milk Chocolate', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Get the party started with these Fun Size Packs of M&Ms;! Great for Halloween trick-or-treating, birthday parties, or just to enjoy as a perfectly portioned snack, this bulk bag is ready to add some delicious flavor to your life and those you share them with.Get your bag today to add some extra deliciousness and magic into your every day snacking. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsize_m_ms.jpg', '3249~funsize_m_ms.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-milk-chocolate'),
(3250, 'Blue M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Mmmmmm. These amazing Blue M&Ms; will put you into a delirium of melty, milk chocolatey bliss for hours and hours. That\'s because this bulk bag is packed with over 45 pieces per pound! That\'s a lot of delicious candy to savor, so they\'re perfect to share with friends and family. Bring them to a baby shower for a boy, a Hanukah celebration, or even a Fourth of July backyard BBQ.Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-mms_1.jpg', '3250~blue-mms_1.jpg', 'blue-mms'),
(3251, 'Skittles Fun Size Bulk', 99.99, '22', 'lb', 'coated', 'A color and flavor for every taste bud. Pack these fun size Skittles into a pinata, add them to a stocking, or slip one into your kid\'s lunchbox for a delicious afternoon surprise. Whatever you choose, everyone will love to \'\'Taste the Rainbow.\'\' Skittles have been in the US since 1979 and have evolved into a quirky brand and a household name. Their original flavors of orange, lemon, lime, grape and strawberry got a revamp in 1989 with the introduction of tropical fruit flavors. Since then, 1 new Skittles lines have been created and amazed the mouths of people all over the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-fun-size.jpg', '3251~skittles-fun-size.jpg', 'skittles-fun-size-bulk'),
(3252, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 79.49, '25', 'lb', 'coated', 'Ouch! Yum! Ouch! Yum! Your mouth might be confused with the tough love these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers dish out, but we don\'t think you\'ll mind because of their delicious flavor. A classic candy with an extremely hard shell, these fruity treats aren\'t as mean as they look. They\'ll slowly melt away in your mouth for hours, treating you to a delicious fruity flavor in a variety of colors. Bring some to a birthday party for a long lasting treat, pack some into a candy machine for a retro look, or set some out on your coffee table for your strong-jawed friends to try. This may be one tough, candy, but we think you\'ll find it\'s nice side, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', '3252~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-bulk-case'),
(3253, 'Red M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Behold, the color of love! These Red M&Ms; will ignite a fire in your heart and fill you with mushy, romantic thoughts. Stock yourself up for Valentine\'s Day to spoil your sweeties, add handfuls of these famous chocolate morsels to holiday baked goods, or even use these vibrant M&Ms; for a wedding to amplify the love between bride and groom. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-mms_1.jpg', '3253~red-mms_1.jpg', 'red-mms'),
(3254, 'Pink M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Did you know that you can buy M&Ms; in single-color bulk bags? Pink M&Ms; are the perfect addition to a baby shower when the mom-to-be is expecting a little girl. These delicious pink chocolates that won\'t melt in your hand are also perfect for birthdays, Easter, wedding showers, and any other occasion that calls for something sweet and pink. You could even put them together with some other delicious pink and red treats for a Valentine\'s Day surprise.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-mms_1.jpg', '3254~pink-mms_1.jpg', 'pink-mms'),
(3255, 'Peanut M&Ms 42oz Bag', 19.99, '', '', 'coated', 'Easy to crave and easy to eat, Peanut M&Ms; are a well-known classic candy for good reason! With their three layers of confection â€“ a colorful candy shell, a rich chocolate filling, and a lovable peanut heart â€“ Peanut M&Ms; provide hunger-satisfying nuts along with sweet-tooth-satisfying coatings. Piled in a dish, these candies quickly disappear, but while they remain their colorful appearance and perfect bite size give a thoughtful, cheery look to your candy bowl.The resealable bag in which these Peanut M&Ms; are packaged makes it easy to keep them on hand for family movie night snacking, or they\'re convenient to stash in a cool spot in the car if you anticipate needing a quick snack on the go. Fresh in their zippered bag, these M&Ms; candies make sure you\'re always ready to offer a sweet treat to unexpected guests, and adding a few to a lunch bag (or improving the morale at a long business meeting) has never been easier than with this bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-mms-42oz-bag_2.jpg', '3255~peanut-mms-42oz-bag_2.jpg', 'peanut-mms-bulk'),
(3256, 'Silver M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Fancy, schmancy. These Silver M&Ms; are exactly that with their illustrious silver sheen and delicious chocolatey crunch. Bring some of these beautiful silver M&Ms; to any event to add some instant drama and glamour. These classic candies make a great selection for wedding candy, look great around the holidays when paired with gold candies, and even can make a winter party even more magical. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-mms_1.jpg', '3256~silver-mms_1.jpg', 'silver-mms'),
(3257, 'Dark Pink M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Pretty in pink. Girly and sweet. Sure are! Mars has taken their product to the next level with this sweet combination of M&Ms; pink candy shell and milky chocolatey center. They make the perfect addition to baby showers, bachelorette parties, and even breast cancer awareness events. Founded in the 1930s, M&Ms; have evolved through the years, getting their signature \'\'M\'\' in the 1950s, adding different flavors along the way, and in the past several years, adding a customizable option with a rainbow of colors. We\'re glad they have added these personalized pink variety and are sure you\'ll love them too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/a/dark-pink-mms_1.jpg', '3257~dark-pink-mms_1.jpg', 'dark-pink-mms'),
(3258, 'M&Ms Milk Chocolate 42oz Bag', 19.99, '', '', 'coated', 'If you love M&M;\'s then you will really love the fact that you are able to get your favorite milk chocolate candy in a bag that contains 42 ounces of candy and is able to be resealed. These candies are bite sized and are great for parties, flights, trips that include long drives, over night parties, game night, and even for a gift basket to tell someone that you hope they get well soon. You are able to get the great taste that you love and be able to reseal the bag to make sure that they stay fresh for as long as possible. If you have a sweet tooth, with a bag this large, you are sure to find that you will be able to meet that sweet tooth time and time again. This means no more trips to the store in the middle of the night but instead you can just reopen the bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/m/mms-milk-chocolate-42oz-bag_2.jpg', '3258~mms-milk-chocolate-42oz-bag_2.jpg', 'mms-milk-chocolate-42oz-bag'),
(3259, 'Orange M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'M&Ms; have been tempting young and old alike for decades. This world-renowned chocolate confection was originally created in the 1930s but really came into its own during World War II, when the design was practical for storing and eating chocolate. The brand has spread immensely since then, with the familiar black M logo added in 1950 and new fillings introduced in the years that followed. No matter how many times they innovate this timeless treat, everyone still look for the classic M&Ms; that made the candy so popular.Our bulk M&M; packages present solid-color quantities for events and more! Our vibrant orange M&Ms; are perfect for autumn parties, Halloween events, birthdays and any other occasion. Use them in party favors or serve in a glass dish to decorate tables and entice guests. We also carry other M&M; colors so you can combine two or more to create the perfect blend of hues for weddings, showers and any other important celebration!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-mms_1.jpg', '3259~orange-mms_1.jpg', 'orange-mms'),
(3260, 'Sixlets 20 Ball Tubes', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'coated', 'Sixlets 20 ball tubes are the most convenient way to enjoy your favorite chocolate candy! Every stick includes a clear wrapper that holds 20 round balls in a straight line. Take a bite out of green, yellow, orange, red or brown.No matter which hue you choose, every Sixlets candy contains a smooth chocolate center surrounded by a hard candy shell. Our bulk Sixlets box contains a generous number of full tubes so you have plenty to take or share.Individually wrapped candy is perfect for traveling and events. Tuck a few in your vehicle\'s glove box, your purse or carry on. You can also display them in glass vases or trays to serve at parties, school activities and other gatherings. Buying Sixlets in bulk is also a great way to ensure that you always have an easy, tasty snack on hand when chocolate cravings hit!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', '3260~sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', 'sixlets-20-ball-tubes'),
(3261, 'Black M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Black M&Ms; are not your typical chocolate candy. This dark and mysterious hue is perfect for a wide range of events. Use with orange or purple M&Ms; for Halloween celebrations or combine with any other color to serve in candy dishes at wedding receptions. Every piece includes the classic chocolate center and hard candy shell that makes M&Ms; such a popular treat. Unlike the candies you buy at the store, our bulk M&Ms; are available in different colors so you can find the perfect pieces to go with any event!There\'s something luxurious and formal about the sleek shine of ebony candy coating. Order a bag to add fine detail to your next event. Whether you serve them at the food table or include them as part of your party or wedding favors, everyone will admire the captivating texture and color that comes with every handful of our exquisite black M&Ms;!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-mms_1.jpg', '3261~black-mms_1.jpg', 'black-mms'),
(3262, 'Runts Candy', 94.99, '30', 'lb', 'coated', 'Runts candy made its first appearance in the 1980s. While its fruity lineup has changed since then, its popularity has not. Every kid can recognize the fun shapes and bright colors that make Runts so unique. Our extensive collection of bulk candy includes this childhood favorite so you can get your fill of sweet fruity goodness anytime you want! Serve at kid\'s parties, take as a non-perishable snack on camping trips or set some aside to hide away at home for moments when you need a sweet fix!Our Runts candy package include all the current flavors and shapes. You\'ll love biting down on a yellow banana or savoring a tart cherry piece. Each order also includes blue raspberry, watermelon and lime. Try the smooth, sweet taste of your favorite fruits followed by the tantalizing tanginess that makes Runts candies so delectable. You don\'t have to go to a vending machine to find your favorite treat because we have Runts in bulk and ready to ship right to you!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts30lbs.jpg', '3262~runts30lbs.jpg', 'runts-bulk'),
(3263, 'Hot Pink Sixlets', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'These glamorous Pink Sixlets chocolates are almost too pretty to eat! Almost... But eat them we shall with their pleasant crunch followed by a creamy milk chocolate center. Tinier than M&Ms; at about a third of the size, these little wonders can still satisfy every sweet tooth  big and small. Set them out in a bowl in your office, use them as a wedding candy buffet item, or add some extra girliness to a baby or bridal shower. Whatever you decide to do with these lovely, little gems, we are sure that you and your friends will love looking at them as much as eating them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3263~sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-pink'),
