(3265, 'Yellow M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Yellow M&Ms; make the perfect spring or summer candy choice. They\'re the color of sunshine and springtime, and they taste just as sweet as feeling a cool breeze on your face in late April. These melt-in-your-mouth classics are perfect for an Easter outing, your candy dish at home or the office, or on a dessert buffet at your next party. They\'ll look especially gorgeous when placed in a pastel setting, pleasing both the eye and the mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/e/yellow-mms_1.jpg', '3265~yellow-mms_1.jpg', 'yellow-mms'),
(3266, 'White Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'White Sixlets are perfect for any occasion and would even look wonderful for a wedding event. These candies contain a white, sugary, crunch, outside coating with smooth chocolate on the inside that is sure to please. The great milk chocolate flavor that this candy offers is hard to beat.It makes a perfect choice for children as well as adults. These are completely round in their shape, like a small ball, but have a taste that is similar to that of M&M;\'s. This is a large bulk bag which means that you can ensure that there will be plenty of these to go around. The taste of these candies is sweet and enjoyable and sure to kick jump your taste buds into high gear. You can also be sure to find that your mouth will be smiling form the great taste after you take part in a few of these wonderful candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-white-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3266~sixlets-white-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-white'),
(3267, 'Royal Blue Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'If you are looking for Sixlets in a fun and exciting color then you may just find that royal blue Sixlets are what you have been looking for. These are fun colored on the outside and the inside is a delicious chocolate center that is sure to please anyone! The outside is a crunchy textured shell and once you make it to the inside you are sure to find the great texture of the sweet and creamy chocolate. This is sure to make your mouth water and please all of your taste buds. This bulk box is great for parties because there is sure to be enough to go around. You will also find that adults like this candy just as much as children do. Aside from a party you can use this great colored candy at a wedding or even at a baby shower for someone who has a little boy on the way!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-royal-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3267~sixlets-royal-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-royal-blue'),
(3268, 'Bulk M&Ms', 129.99, '25', 'lb', 'coated', 'M&Ms; are one of the most popular chocolate candies available today. While this confection is usually considered a tasty modern treat, it\'s actually enjoyed a long, rich history that dates back to the 1930s.During that time, the founder of the Mars candy company noticed that Spanish soldiers would eat chocolate pellets. These included tempered chocolate that was resistant to melting. He decided to take the idea to the next level and created a candy that used Hershey chocolate!Each round M&Ms; candy consists of a delicious chocolate center surrounded by a hard panned coating. Each piece comes in a handful of vibrant colors, including orange, red, yellow, green, dark brown and blue. Our bulk M&Ms; pack includes all the original hues in a large quantity that\'s perfect for events and celebrations.Use them to decorate cakes, cookies and more during the holidays or prepare for a special occasion by creating party or wedding favor with M&Ms;! Anytime is a great time to share the chocolaty taste of classic M&Ms; candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/m/mms-bulk-25-pounds.jpg', '3268~mms-bulk-25-pounds.jpg', 'mms-bulk-case'),
(3269, 'Light Blue M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'If you are planning a baby shower for a boy then this would make a great option to have at the party. These M&M;\'s have a light blue color that looks great! They have the same great taste that everyone loves when it comes to M&M;\'s however and that is a nice milk chocolaty taste. These are must have for any event or occasion, as they would also go well with a birthday party for a boy. Since they are light blue you may even be able to consider using them a girl as well depending on the other colors that were used with them. Adults and children alike love the taste of these great candies and are sure to be pleased with them. There is just something about these candies that are able to tickle your taste buds in just the right way and that is what really makes them a favorite of many.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/light-blue-mms_1.jpg', '3269~light-blue-mms_1.jpg', 'light-blue-mms'),
(3270, 'Navy Blue Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'What better color to have for Sixlets than a navy blue. This is a great color and would be great for any patriotic or military event. You will even find that these would work great for many other special occasions, parties, and events as well. There is just something to be said about the fine taste that you get from these balls of milk chocolate. The texture is great too because of the candy coating. You are able to bite into the candy and have a bit of crunch that is then followed by the great silky milk chocolate that just melts away in your mouth. These can even be great to keep around the house in case you find that you begin to have a craving for something sweet, as these candies are sure to be able to handle the craving that you are having and much more as you enjoy their wonderful taste.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-navy-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3270~sixlets-navy-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-navy-blue'),
(3271, 'Fun Size M&Ms Peanut', 36.99, '5.75', 'lb', 'coated', 'Everyone one loves fun size M&Ms;, they are perfect for a quick sweet treat; just the right size so you don\'t over eat. Fun Size Peanut M&Ms; are one of the most popular candies Mars offers. They are perfect when just a few M&Ms; are needed for added edible decoration. They are the perfect amount for kids treat bags at parties, Trick-R-Treating at Halloween and in classrooms as prizes and incentives. Every teacher knows candy treats are good but, too much equals disaster. These smooth hard shelled candies give the perfect crunch followed by delicious chocolaty goodness and finished with a salty peanut in the center which all adds up to perfection. Fun Size Peanut M&Ms; work as stocking stuffers, in Easter baskets, and can be easily attached to a Valentine.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsizepeanut_1.jpg', '3271~funsizepeanut_1.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-peanut'),
(3272, 'Powder Blue Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'These powder blue Sixlets chocolates are the prettiest belles at the ball! Smaller than M&Ms;, Sixlets are the perfect dose of hard shell crunch and melty milk chocolate in a miniature form. Use some on top of a cake for a pop of powder blue pizazz, add them to a make your own sundae bar, bring them to a celebration of the birth of a baby boy, or even add them to a blue themed event like the Fourth of July! No matter what you decide to do with these lovely, little gems, we are sure that you and your friends will love looking at them as much as eating them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-powder-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3272~sixlets-powder-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-powder-blue'),
(3273, 'Fun Size M&Ms Milk Chocolate Case', 114.99, '20', 'lb', 'coated', 'These little candies are the life of the party! That\'s because these Fun Size M&Ms; are the perfect size to be enjoyed as a special snack any day of the week. These pint size packages make these candies ideal for a Halloween trick-or-treating selection, tucked into a piï¾ata, kept around the house to satisfy a small sweet tooth, or even to be put into gift baskets. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsize_m_ms_1.jpg', '3273~funsize_m_ms_1.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-milk-chocolate-case'),
(3274, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '3274~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(3275, 'Key Lime Pie Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you pop a piece of key lime pie candy into your mouth, your taste buds will burst with citrus sweetness. It\'s like taking a trip to the beautiful, balmy Florida Keys without even leaving your home or office. These delicious green and white hard candies are perfect for any occasion, whether you want a refreshing tropical taste on a hot summer day or you want to remind yourself of the beach in the middle of winter.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', '3275~key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', 'key-lime-pie-hard-candy'),
(3276, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '3276~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(3277, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '3277~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(3278, 'chocolate starlight mints thumbnail', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Chocolate starlight mints are a new and amazing take on a classic candy. Everyone loves the refreshing flavor of the traditional hard mint, now add chocolate.Starlight mints, which are also sometimes called pinwheel mints, feature a lovely white background with bold red stripes. Our chocolate starlight mints take that same elegant pattern and use it on a dark background with brilliant green stripes instead.Now you can enjoy that delicious minty taste with a touch of savory chocolate. Each round mint is crafted using solid hard candy. This allows them to provide the flavor candy lovers adore in a long lasting treat. Each mint is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can admire their dark beauty before you open the first one up!Pour them into glass jars or candy dishes and serve to guests, use them in the office candy jar or make your gingerbread houses more unique with these tasty decorations!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', '3278~chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', 'chocolate-starlight-mints'),
(3279, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Don\'t bite down on one of these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers! These hard candies are great for savoring a ton of sweetness for a long time.Buy a bulk bag of Jaw Busters hard candies for the little ghouls and goblins coming around the neighborhood on Halloween, or keep them around when you\'re craving something sweet for yourself. You can keep a bag of Jawbreakers in a wide assortment of colors and flavors all year long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', '3279~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-wrapped'),
(3280, 'Bulk Assorted Fruit Lollipops', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Lollipop, lollipop, oh lolli , lolli, lolli  Sorry, we\'re getting carried away with ourselves. It happens a lot here. It\'s just that we\'re so passionate about these scrumptious suckers that it makes us break out in song. They don\'t require a trip to the doctor and they come in bulk, so these pops are the perfect choice for any occasion. Stock up for your child\'s next party or put them in a jar on your desk for lucky coworkers to snack on. You\'ll quickly become a favorite in the office! With a light, sweet, fruity flavor, in a rainbow of colors, everyone can enjoy a mouthful of deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3280~lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'lollipops-bulk-fruit'),
(3281, 'Sour Fruit Balls Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Sour. Check. Colorful. Check. Fruity and delicious. Check, check! We\'ve got everything you need here for the makings of a great bulk candy selection.  Individually wrapped, these candies make tasty treats for parties, as filler candy, or just to have around the house for a qick fix of sweetness.With over 80 hard candies per pound, there\'s enough sweetness to treat all of your friends and family. Every time you snack from this bag, choose from yummy red, orange, yellow, green, and purple. Everyone who hears the crinkle of their wrappers will come running for more. And because of their perfect size, one after another can be enjoyed.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', '3281~sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', 'sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy'),
(3282, 'Andes Mints', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Ande\'s mints make the perfect welcome snack for any home, office, or restaurant. Whether your guests want to freshen their breath after they\'ve had a meal, or you\'d just like to make them feel at home with something sweet, these are the treats for you. A perfect blend of creamy milk chocolate and mint filling make these tiny sandwiches of sweetness the perfect refreshment, and they\'re individually wrapped, so there\'s no danger of spreading anyone\'s germs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', '3282~andes-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', 'andes-mints'),
(3283, 'Butterscotch Buttons Candy', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'These candies are cute as a button! Maybe that\'s because these Butterscotch Candy Buttons come in beautiful, individually wrapped gold wrappers and are a lovely bright yellow color that candy fans love. Around since the 1800s, butterscotch has built up a tasty reputation throughout the decades and continues to please candy lovers near and far. Try these little, rich sweets out for your next candy buffet bar, crush them and sprinkle them on top of cookies and baked goods for a sweet surprise, or even fill your candy dishes for an olde timey feel every snacker can enjoy. These hard candies are sure to \'\'butter you up\'\' with their irresistible flavor.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3283~butterscotch-buttons-hard-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'butterscotch-buttons'),
(3284, 'Sunkist Fruit Gems', 69.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a big, sugary smooch with these Sunkist Fruit Gems! Their delicious, gummy chew and bright, fruity flavor will make you want to pucker up for more every time you take a bite. Individually wrapped, these little gummies pack the power of the sun into every chew and show off the beautiful colors of the rainbow.Stock yourself up with some rainy day sunshine with a bag of these. They\'re a great goodie bag stuffer for birthday parties, look lovely at a summertime picnic on the dessert table, and even can be kept to cheer up your little ones on a rainy day. With 42 pieces per pound, there are enough to please every gummy fan!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', '3284~sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'sunkist-fruit-gems-bulk'),
(3285, 'Tootsie Rolls Midgees Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get your candy fix with our Tootsie Rolls midgees candy! Tootsie Roll is one of the oldest treats in the United States. This confection was invented in 1986 when Leo Hirshfield decided to open up a shop in New York City.Today, kids and adults love the chewy texture and chocolaty taste that makes these popular confections so irresistible. They\'re not quite taffy and not quite caramel but very smooth, making snack time even sweeter! Bulk Tootsie Rolls give you more pieces for snacking, parties and sharing.Every roll is individually wrapped in that familiar brown, red and white paper. That allows the candy to remain fresh and ready to enjoy. Take a handful with you as a quick treat on a busy day or use them as an easy after school snack for the kids. Tootsie Rolls also make great treat bag filler for birthday parties, picnics, holiday events and other gatherings.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/o/tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', '3285~tootsie-rolls-midgees-thumbnail-470x470_1.jpg', 'tootsie-rolls-midgees'),
(3286, 'Peppermint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '6', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peppermint Starlight mints make the perfect complimentary candy for almost any occasion, event, or environment. Are you considering putting a candy dish by the door at home? Do you run a restaurant where customers pay at a counter near the front? These Starlight mint hard candies are recognized all over the world as a true classic. They\'ll satisfy your sweet tooth and freshen your breath, too. Put some of these individually wrapped treats out in your home, office, or restaurant today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', '3286~peppermintstarlightmints_1.jpg', 'starlight-mints-peppermint'),
(3287, 'Jumbo Mint Balls Hard Candy', 11.49, '120', 'ct', 'individually-wrapped', 'Make way for a big dose of peppermint flavor! These Jumbo Mint Balls are a sphere full of refreshing minty flavor that your mouth will love. Their beautiful red and white swirls make them the perfect sweet addition to a Christmas candy display, gingerbread house making with your family, a beach party (since these little balls resemble beach balls!), and even a Fourth of July event. With 12 of these flavorful candy balls in every order, there\'s enough to do it all. Use your imagination to decide how you and your close family and friends can enjoy these tasty mints.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', '3287~jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls-120ct_1.jpg', 'jumbo-hard-candy-mint-balls'),
(3288, 'Peanut Butter Bars', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peanut butter bars candy brings you all the best parts of peanuts without all the bad stuff. Each bar includes high quality peanuts that are slow roasted until they become gold brown to bring out the natural nutty flavor. Each bite is truly an experience, with the crispy, flaky crunch that everyone loves. If you are a peanut butter fanatic, then this bar candy is your dream come true!Every peanut butter bar is individually wrapped so it\'s easy to store and share. Each includes a simple white wrapper with black stripes, gold star and a classic logo that gives each piece a nostalgic look. Keep a handful in your purse or pocket or use the in favor bags for parties and holiday events. Each tasty tidbit is packed with all the rich peanut flavor you can handle in a convenient package that you can take anywhere! Our bulk candy packs are great for school events, businesses and carnivals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', '3288~peanut-butter-bars-atkinson-thumb-470x470.jpg', 'peanut-butter-bars'),
(3289, 'Bit O Honey Candy', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Buzzzzzz. These Bit-O-Honey Candies are brimming with the sweet, creamy sugar of an entire hive! That\'s because each delightful candy is made with sweet, honey flavored taffy and complete with soft almond pieces inside. Individually wrapped, these delectable morsels can be enjoyed one, two, or three at a time! They make a perfect addition to a classic candy display, set out on a coffee table for sweet snacking, or packed into a pinata for birthday parties. Treat your busy bees to a sweet treat with a bag of these. Try these out for yourself and see what all the \'\'buzz\'\' is about with an order of these tasty treats!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/i/bit-o-honey-candy-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3289~bit-o-honey-candy-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'bit-o-honey-pieces'),
(3290, 'Tootsie Fruit Rolls Fruit Chews', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Let us get this straight. The classic Tootsie Roll chew that we love comes in a delicious fruity taste, too? We\'ll take it! Try these Fruit Tootsie Rolls and enjoy a whole new taste with this classic candy. Yellow is lemon, blue is vanilla, red is cherry, green is lime, and orange is...orange. Discover a whole new way to love this classic brand.Since 1896, Tootsie has been producing delectable candies that the world has grown to love. With 65 pieces per pound and a bulk bag of these, there\'s nothing tiny about the amount of delectable Tootsie Fruit Chews Rolls you\'ll get to enjoy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/r/fruit-chews-tootsie-rolls-470x470_2.jpg', '3290~fruit-chews-tootsie-rolls-470x470_2.jpg', 'fruit-tootsie-rolls'),
(3291, 'Peppermint Twists Mints', 19.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Peppermint twists pack all of the flavor of a candy cane into a single bite-sized candy. Just seeing and tasting them will put you in the holiday spirit, no matter what time of year it is. Don\'t miss out on delicious peppermint candies all year round. Get a bag of these individually wrapped peppermint twists and liven up your home or your office. No special occasion is necessary to bring out these delicious peppermint candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3291~peppermint-mint-twists-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'peppermint-twists'),
(3292, 'Spearmint Starlight Mints', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'A classic concept with a colorful twist. Try our Spearmint Starlight Mints as a complementary addition to your traditional red and white peppermints. Their cool, sharp spearmint flavor in addition to their lovely green and white coloring contrasts to make them a lovely and refreshing selection for any candy bowl. Make your holiday gingerbread house extra special with these green and white mints. Or stash some in your purse for a sweet, minty treat. We can\'t deny the holiday cheer these mints give us and we hope that they will inspire the same, bright happiness in everyone you share them with.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', '3292~spearmint-starlight-mints-pile-470x470.jpg', 'spearmint-starlight-mints'),
(3293, 'Mary Jane Candy', 20.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you\'re in the mood for something extra chewy, try our sweet Mary Jane candies! These delectable delights are small bars of smooth taffy treats. Each is flavored with rich molasses and peanut butter to give it that memorable taste that kids of all ages have been asking for since 1914. The candy is a historic favorite that was named after its creator\'s beloved aunt â€“ a worthy choice for such a nostalgic confection!Each taffy candy is covered in a bright yellow wrapper with a bold red stripe and classic logo printed around both sides. You\'ll love Mary Janes even more when you buy our bulk candy package! Order larger quantities so you have plenty to share at family gatherings and other events. Use them to fill the office candy jar or use them to fill treat bags for birthdays and more! Our bulk Mary Janes are also convenient to hand out on trick or treat night around Halloween!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3293~mary-janes-candy-bulk-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'mary-janes-candy'),
(3294, 'Bulk Candy Mix', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Having a candy buffet and need the perfect mix to kick off the table.  You have found the perfect product with our bulk candy mix in a five pound bag.  We have included some of our all time favorites in this mix.  Assorted Salt Water taffy is always the perfect start.  Individually wrapped Starbursts are a fan favorite in our office.  Tootsie roll fruit help make the mix really stand out and to top it all off it includes assorted Jolly Rancher Hard CandyWhether for a party or your candy jar in the office or home this mix will be a hit with everyone!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulk_candy_mix_candystore.jpg', '3294~bulk_candy_mix_candystore.jpg', 'bulk-candy-mix'),
(3295, 'Assorted Fruit Starlight Mints', 18.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Our starlight mints are now available with amazing fruit flavors! If you love the smooth texture and fun pinwheel pattern of the classic starlight candy, then you\'ll love these vibrant treats! Each piece features the same look with a color that matches its unique fruity taste. Our bulk fruit starlight mints include an assortment of orange, lime, lemon and cherry. Pour some into a glass candy bowl for guests or share with family at home. Everyone will find a flavor they love!Pinwheel mints are also a fun part of the holidays. If you want to change things up, combine the traditional starlight mint with our fruit candies. These also make great favor bag treats for weddings, birthday parties and other events. With our enormous bulk mint pack, it\'s easy to get all the pieces you need for any occasion. Grab a handful of our assorted fruit starlight mints and share the sweetness!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/starlights-mints-assorted-fruit-5lb_1.jpg', '3295~starlights-mints-assorted-fruit-5lb_1.jpg', 'starlights-mints-assorted-fruit');
