(3431, 'Silver Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Silver milk chocolate hearts aren\'t made of sterling silver metal, but they sure look like they are! These eye-catching heart candies are a superb choice for Valentine\'s Day and major events.Every piece is made of a solid serving of sweet milk chocolate. The smooth surface is protected by a thin layer of shimmering foil. This creates that gorgeous shiny finish that makes these heart candies so stunning!Silver milk chocolate hearts are a convenient choice for wedding favors, shower favors and more. Our bulk candy pack gives you many pieces that are economical for bigger crowds.Arrange them on a cookie tray or pour into a glass candy dish and you have an elegant presentation for guests. This package contains all silver wrappers. Also check out our other milk chocolate heart candy to find additional wrapper colors. Order just one or try 2, 3 or more to create a custom chocolate mix for your event!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', '3431~silver-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lbs_1.jpg', 'silver-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
(3432, 'Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars', 38.99, '14', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'Behold, a 200 year old chocolate. Well, not this one specifically. That would be gross. However, Cadbury has been around since the 1800s and has been making work famous chocolates ever since. Bring these Cadbury Dairy Milk Chocolate Bars home to spoil your family and friends with a taste of the past. With their breakable sections, they\'re great to enjoy in small nibbles or big bites! Get a loved one a bar for Valentine\'s Day, melt a few of these bars into fondue, or just keep them around for delicious baking. Get your chocolate bar today and try out the famous recipe that has been honed over two centuries.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', '3432~cadbury-chocolate-bars-24ct_2.jpg', 'cadbury-chocolate-bars'),
