(3443, 'Purple Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wear your heart on your sleeve with these heavenly chocolates. The indulgent mouthfuls of joy are the perfect message to send the special someone who has your whole heart. Add them to Valentine\'s Day card, give them to a special someone to remind them how much they are loved, or even use them on top of a cake or cupcake to make something sweet all the more special. Whatever occasion you decide to use these adorable chocolate for, this bulk bag of Purple Foil Hearts is here to make a romantic day even more memorable. Make your heart skip a beat for these tasty treats today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '3443~purple-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'purple-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(3444, 'Sour Power Belts Wrapped', 24.99, '150', 'ct', 'chocolate', 'With 150 Sour Power Belts in this big bulk supply you will have plenty of opportunity for flavorful fun. These candies were introduced in 1985, and folks of all ages have not been able to get enough of them.If you love pucker-inducing treats, these Sour Power Belts should definitely be on your shopping list. This box of delicious treats is available in Green Apple, Blue Raspberry, Strawberry, and Watermelon. We recommend getting all four before you drive yourself crazy trying to pick only one.The belts are about 9-inches long and just under 1-inch wide, so they are pretty much the perfect size. Big enough to satisfy, but not so big you get a tummy ache. Since these Sour Power Belts are individually wrapped you can surprise your kids with them in their lunch box and hand them out at Halloween.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', '3444~sour-power-belts-from-dorval-150ct-wrapped_2.gif', 'sour-power-belts-dorval-wrapped'),
(3445, 'Tiffany Blue Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Do you have expensive taste but a budget to stick to? Well, these Tiffany Blue Foil Chocolate Balls might be the perfect candy for you! With the famous, powder blue of the high end jewelry store, Tiffany, and decadent chocolate underneath, you\'ll add a sophistication to every sweet snack break. Bring these to a bridal shower, bachelorette party, or the baby shower for a boy! They even make a great addition to a blue themed candy buffet bar or a wedding reception. These glamorous chocolates come in a bulk bag and will impress your taste buds and guests whenever you serve them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/i/tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '3445~tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'tiffany-blue-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(3446, 'Chocolate Covered Oreo Cookies', 64.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This may be the one time when we encourage people to judge a confection by its cover. Because this cookie\'s cover is a thick layer of creamy, melty chocolate! Chocolate Covered Oreos have become a sensation in recent years, and with this bulk bulk bag, there are over 70 cookies to enjoy. Whether you\'re an Oreo fan who insists on eating the cream first and then the cookie or vice versa, we think you\'ll all agree that savoring the chocolate cookie coating before it all is the best way to go about this particular batch. It\'s a problem we don\'t think you\'ll take issue with while you make your way through mouthwatering layer upon layer of chocolatey, creamy goodness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-oreo-cookie5lbs_2.gif', '3446~chocolate-covered-oreo-cookie5lbs_2.gif', 'oreo-cookies-chocolate-covered'),
(3447, 'White Yogurt Mini Twist Pretzels', 50.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Our white yogurt mini twist pretzels give you a new way to enjoy your favorite baked treat! Pretzels are delicious on their own, with their crunchy texture and salty taste. This version takes miniature knots and smothers them in cool, smooth white yogurt. Itâ€™s an irresistible combination that will please taste buds and calm cravings! Bulk white yogurt pretzels give you more pieces for snacking, sharing, and parties.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/o/yogurt-tiny-pretzels_2.jpg', '3447~yogurt-tiny-pretzels_2.jpg', 'white-yogurt-mini-twist-pretzels-candy'),
(3448, 'Chocolate Soccer Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in foil that looks like a classic black and white soccer ball and with amazing chocolate balls beneath, these Chocolate Soccer Balls are winners for sure! Do you have a friend or family member who plays soccer? Why not make their next game extra special by bringing an order of these Chocolate Soccer Balls by at half time? There are plenty to share with the whole team and can cheer up a losing team or help celebrate an incredible win!Chocolate Soccer Balls also are a great candy for sports-themed birthday parties or soccer training camps. Score big with your friends and family and order some today. Oleee, ole, ole, ole. Get ready to chant the most famous soccer game song of all time with these Chocolate Soccer Balls!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', '3448~chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped-5lb_2.jpg', 'chocolate-soccer-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(3449, 'Chocolate Rocks', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Rocks aren\'t very appetizing, unless they are chocolate rocks! These natural looking candies are absolutely gorgeous to see and so sweet to the taste buds.If you love cocoa flavor, then you will fall in love with these charming little edible pebbles. Each includes a dense chocolate candy that\'s covered in a solid candy coating in a rainbow of earthy colors!What makes chocolate rocks so delicious isn\'t just their taste, but also their appearance. Each stone looks just like the real thing! The candy coating creates lovely texture while each chocolate is uniquely shaped Ã just like real rocks. This assortment includes a variety of hues, ranging from slate blue to burnt orange and black.Grab a handful or enjoy one at a time. No matter which color you choose, each offers the same amazing chocolate taste. Our bulk chocolate rocks are a must-have for cake decorating and special occasions!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolaterocks.jpg', '3449~chocolaterocks.jpg', 'chocolate-rocks-5lb'),
(3450, 'Assorted Sports Chocolate Balls', 49.99, '5', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Golf balls, tennis balls, basketballs, baseballs, soccer balls and footballs, oh my! We\'re sure everyone will want to be on your team when you bring these Assorted Sports Chocolate Balls in bulk supply to your next party or sporting event.That\'s because these sports balls aren\'t only melty milk chocolate and scrumptious, but they\'re also fun to play with! Hit a home run with one of these baseballs and throw it into your mouth. Kick a field goal through your friend\'s fingers and then indulge in chocolate. You\'re going to score big points with whoever you share these Assorted Sports Chocolate balls with, that\'s for sure!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/foil-sports-balls-chocolate.jpg', '3450~foil-sports-balls-chocolate.jpg', 'chocolate-assorted-sports-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(3451, 'Milk Chocolate Gold Coins Medium Size', 136.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'This 5-pound supply of Milk Chocolate Gold Coins is perfect to hand out at nearly any event. Fill a treasure chest with them for a pirate-themed birthday party.Use them as a snack at your next poker party, include them in a gift bag, or hand them out at Halloween. These Milk Chocolate Gold Coins are about the size of a quarter, and the highly detailed gold foil makes them look like real currency. There are hundreds of coins in this bulk supply, which should be more than enough for any celebration.Although great for a party, you don\'t need to be planning a special event to order these Milk Chocolate Gold Coins. Stock your candy jar with them and you\'ll always have a quick bite size snack handy when you need to satisfy a little sugar craving. These medium size yummy chocolate coins are certified kosher, making them an ideal Hanukkah gift, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', '3451~milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', 'milk-chocolate-gold-coins-medium'),
(3452, 'Bright Pink Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Bright pink foil chocolate balls are delightful to look at and pleasing to the taste buds. These simple candies offer big visual appeal. Each piece includes a luxuriously solid orb of milk chocolate with a smooth exterior.The surface is covered in a delicate blanket of foil with a glorious pink shine. It\'s both tasty snack and elegant display that works at home, the office or at events!Pour our bright pink foil chocolate balls into any glass container and you have a beautiful chocolate display!That\'s why our colorful foil wrapped candies are such a great choice for wedding favors, showers and other high class celebrations. We make it easy to get large quantities for a big crowd with our affordable bulk chocolate balls pack. Order just one package of chocolate balls or multiple so you have plenty to go around whether you\'re hosting an event for 10, 100 or 1,000!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/bright-pink-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '3452~bright-pink-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'chocolate-balls-bright-pink-foil-wrapped'),
(3453, 'Red Foil Chocolate Balls', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'chocolate', 'Wrapped in shiny, metallic red wrappers, these little Red Foil Chocolate Balls are sure to make your eyes pop as your mouth waters for what\'s inside. Inside is a solid ball of melty milk chocolate. It\'s up to you whether you want to chomp, chew or let this little sphere melt away. Red Foil Chocolate Balls are the perfect color and candy for Christmas, the Fourth of July, and a birthday party for someone who adores the color. Stock up on these Red Foil Chocolate Balls and mix and match with other flavors and colors or enjoy them all by themselves. Whatever you do, you\'ll love unwrapping these chocolate balls one after the other.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', '3453~red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped-10lb_1.jpg', 'red-chocolate-balls-foil-wrapped'),
(3454, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '3454~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(3455, 'Assorted Salt Water Taffy Mix', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Assorted salt water taffy mix. Do you remember those amazing trips to the beach with your family when you were a kid? Vacation was never complete without a trip to the candy store and a big bag of salt water taffy. Bring those great memories to life in your mouth any time you like with these assorted salt water taffy candies. Set them out in a candy dish at home or work and share the sweet experience.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', '3455~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-mix-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(3456, 'Vanilla Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When was the last time your hard working mouth took a vacation? Treat it with a lovely retreat to the salty shores of the boardwalk-lined coast with these saltwater taffys. Complete with a soft, chewy texture and light vanilla taste, you\'ll remember why it\'s so good to get away for a while. Feel like the breeze is in your hair, the sand is between your toes and the jubilant hubub of the boardwalk is buzzing around you bite after bite. In the late 1800s, salt water taffy was discovered when a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be for generations to come.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3456~vanilla-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'vanilla-salt-water-taffy'),
(3457, 'Grape Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Beach bums, get ready for a treat that will remind you of the summer heat! This grape salt water taffy has been stretched, chewed, and loved for years. Inspired by the sunny boardwalk, these individually wrapped candies can bring back summertime memories whenever you wish.Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3457~grape-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'grape-salt-water-taffy'),
(3458, 'Raspberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Sally may sell sea shells by the seashore, but we sell savory salt water taffy that gives her a run for her money! A summertime classic, this raspberry flavored taffy is ready to take you back to the boardwalk any time of the year. Individually wrapped, they are the perfect solution to a sweet tooth or to be used as a party favor. You can almost hear the surf as you let these morsels melt away. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/a/raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3458~raspberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'raspberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(3459, 'Peppermint Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When days at the beach get hot, you can do more than jumping in the waves for a cool-down. Try our refreshing Peppermint Salt Water Taffy to beat the heat. The individually wrapped morsels make them ideal to pack in a beach bag or cooler. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3459~peppermint-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'peppermint-salt-water-taffy'),
(3460, 'Strawberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'What happens when you combine creamy saltwater taffy with the juicy flavor of ripe red strawberries? You get one of the most mouthwatering confections found on land or in the sea! Saltwater taffy is a classic treat that hails from the sundrenched boardwalks of Atlantic City, NJ. This classic confection has been around for decades and has become a popular souvenir at many seaside destinations. Our strawberry saltwater taffy is easy to get because you don\'t have to go on vacation to buy it!The blend of molasses, sea salt and strawberry flavorings gives our saltwater taffy an irresistibly soft, smooth taste. Every piece is individually wrapped so you can easily separate servings for snacking or place a few in a party or wedding favor! The gentle pink taffy color includes deep red stripes around the sides that make this treat perfect for Valentine\'s Day, anniversaries or any special occasion that celebrates love!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3460~strawberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'strawberry-salt-water-taffy'),
(3461, 'Laffy Taffy Candy', 37.99, '8.5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Laffy Taffy is such a well-recognized candy that hip-hop artist D4L has immortalized its name in song. You don\'t have to be a fan of rap to enjoy these chewy soft candies, though. Each individually wrapped Laffy Taffy candy comes with a joke written on the wrapper for you to share with your friends. You\'ll laugh with your friends as you satisfy your sweet tooth for this delicious taffy candy. They\'re so good, though, that you might want to share the jokes, but you won\'t ever want to share the candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', '3461~laffy-taffy-candy-bulk-8lb_2.jpg', 'laffy-taffy-pieces-bulk'),
(3462, 'Tropical Assorted Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'This seashore classic is now heading to the tropics with these Assorted Tropical Salt Water Taffies! Feel the sun on your face, the wind in your hair, and hear the crash of the ocean waves with every bite of these colorful taffies. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/r/tropical_assorted.jpg', '3462~tropical_assorted.jpg', 'tropical-salt-water-taffy-assorted'),
(3463, 'Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Prepare to hypnotize your taste buds with these Licorice Swirl Salt Water Taffies. In a stark contrast of black and white swirls, these candies are as yummy to eat as they are to look at. Use them for a thematic addition to Halloween or a formal wedding reception. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3463~licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'licorice-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(3464, 'Key Lime Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Don\'t you just love the light, refreshing sweetness that comes with biting into a slice of key lime pie? How about the fun, chewy tastiness of salt water taffy? Well, you can have the best of both worlds with Key Lime Salt Water Taffy!These individually wrapped goodies have a classic taste that everyone loves and a great chewy texture, too. Put them in a candy dish for your guests at home or your coworkers at the office.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3464~key-lime-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'key-lime-salt-water-taffy'),
(3465, 'Cherry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Cherry salt water taffy is sure to take you back to your childhood vacations to the beach. These red and pink chewy candies will be a huge hit anywhere you take them. Put them out in a candy dish at home, or take them to share the sweet taffy goodness at work or at a party. Cherry salt water taffy makes a great addition to a Valentine\'s Day gift bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3465~cherry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cherry-salt-water-taffy'),
