(3467, 'Banana Taffy Taffy Town', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you love to visit the zoo then this is the perfect candy for you to enjoy. This Banana Salt Water Taffy has such a real banana flavor that each and even monkeys can be fooled about their authenticity. Salt water taffy is going to make you feel great about yourself anyway, because it provides a person with a bit of nostalgia. There is no other treat which screams about summer more than salt water taffy. This sweet banana taste is going to make eating one of these treats an impossibility but no need to worry as they come in a hefty bulk bag. That should be enough to keep you munching for hours. The real banana taste is going to make you want to visit the local zoo, because you will want to share them with all the other primates. Candy is always best when it is shared with someone who appreciates it and primates of all ages will absolutely love this!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3467~banana-salt-water-taffy-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'banana-salt-water-taffy'),
(3468, 'Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lite', 29.99, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Summertime and the living\'s easy. And now, sugar free! Try these Sugar Free Salt Water Taffy Lites for a healthier fix of the boardwalk classic and all the scrumptious taste of the original recipe. In blue-raspberry, strawberry, lemon, chocolate, orange, and vanilla, let these little morsels melt away as you remember digging your toes into the sand and letting the sun shine in your hair. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', '3468~sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite-5lbs_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-salt-water-taffy-lite'),
(3469, 'cinnamon swirl salt water taffy in a white bowl', 19.49, '', '', 'salt-water-taffy', 'If you have never tried cinnamon salt water taffy then you don\'t know what you are missing out on. The flavor of these is perfect. They have a cinnamon blend that is spicy and works just right with the sweet flavor that they have as well. There is nothing better than the tasty of salt water taffy and when you combine it with cinnamon the flavor really seems to explode. The candies are pink in color and are sure to look great for a many different occasions. You will also like to know that each piece is wrapped individually which is very helpful in making sure that they stay fresh as long as possible. There is just something about the chewy texture of taffy that is able to please so many people. This is a great tasting candy with a great texture that is hard to beat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3469~cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'cinnamon-salt-water-taffy'),
(3470, 'Watermelon Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Two summer classics unite in this amazing, summery confection. Try our refreshing Watermelon Salt Water Taffy to beat the heat. The individually wrapped morsels make them ideal to pack in a beach bag or cooler and their bright pink and green color combination makes them a lovely addition to any pinata or candy buffet bar. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/watermelon-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3470~watermelon-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'watermelon-salt-water-taffy'),
(3471, 'Green Apple Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Which way to the beach? These delicious Green Apple Salt Water Taffies will make you want to lay on the warm sand with every chew. Their bright green color and tart green apple flavor will please every boardwalk lover and remind you of warmer days to come. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/r/green-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', '3471~green-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lb_1.jpg', 'green-apple-salt-water-taffy'),
(3472, 'Cotton Candy Taffy', 9.99, '3', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Relive your fondest childhood memories with every bite of cotton candy taffy! This irresistible snack offers a nostalgic flavor that\'s sure to please. Recall the excitements of visits to the local candy shop, where you could pick out your favorite chewy taffy treats.Or how about the soft, fluffy taste of cotton candy while spending time at the carnival! Our cotton candy taffy combines both of those wonderful experiences into one bite-sized confection. Our bulk cotton candy taffy includes large quantities that are individually wrapped to ensure freshness and flavor.They are convenient for sharing and giving. Use them to fill up the office candy jar or pour in a bowl to serve guests who stop by. Cotton candy taffy features a lovely light blue hue that looks elegant in wedding favors or can be used to complement a boys baby shower theme! Everyone will love the eye-catching look and sweet taste of our cotton candy taffy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/cotton-candy-taffy-sweets.jpg', '3472~cotton-candy-taffy-sweets.jpg', 'sweets-cotton-candy-taffy'),
(3473, 'Passion Fruit Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'We\'ve got the love and the passion for these Passion Fruit Salt Water Taffies! Let these individually wrapped taffies make your heart pitter patter with their beautiful, bright blue and yellow coloring and citrusy flavor experience. A boardwalk favorite amongst beach vacationers for years, this recipe upholds the high standard of the original. Discovered in the late 1800s when a shop owner\'s candy store was flooded by rising ocean tides, he made the best of it and decided to market the salt-soaked candies to the public and they loved them! Ever since, people haven\'t been able to get enough of these chewy, salty-sweet, creamy taffies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3473~passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'passion-fruit-salt-water-taffy'),
(3474, 'Orange Creme Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'You can almost feel the fresh salty breeze in your hair and hear the roaring of the waves hitting the beach with every bite of these Orange Creme Salt Water Taffies. Their beautiful orange and white swirls will remind you of summer and melt away in your mouth every time you snack. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-cr-me-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', '3474~orange-cr-me-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', 'orange-creme-salt-water-taffy'),
(3475, 'Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'When you can invoke memories with a piece of candy then you must be doing something right. The delicious Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy treats provide a powerful punch of goodness for all to enjoy. The taste of any salt water taffy is going to bring back memories of summer time spent near the shore as you enjoyed the sweet taste of salt water taffy with your friends as you passed the hours of fun in your youth. Then there is the taste of lemon meringue that is going to be a reminder of the wonder and renewal of springtime. The fact that it comes in a bright shiny wrapper will make each piece seem like a gift, and it is a gift of delicious lemony flavor. It is yellow in color which will make you think of the happiness that sunshine can bring you. These Lemon Meringue Salt Water Taffy candies can make any occasion just a little more special. Who doesn\'t remember the taste of homemade pie?', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/e/lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3475~lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'lemon-meringue-salt-water-taffy'),
(3476, 'Chocolate Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'What\'s all the fuss about? \'\'Sea\'\' for yourself with these amazingly creamy and delectable Chocolate Salt Water Taffies. Hit the sand with every bite of these individually wrapped morsels. Surprise your chocolate-loving family with a bag of these. Even drop a few into your hot cocoa for extra chocolatey goodness. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3476~chocolate-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'chocolate-salt-water-taffy'),
(3477, 'Huckleberry Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'salt-water-taffy', 'Well, there is a lot we could say about these delicious treats, but we want to tell you most is that they\'re \'\'berry\'\' good! These Huckleberry Sal Water Taffies are a gorgeous shade of deep purple and white and will delight your family and friends. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/u/huckleberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', '3477~huckleberry-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_2.jpg', 'huckleberry-salt-water-taffy'),
