(3582, 'Jelly Belly 49 Flavors Mix Bags', 64.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'If you just can\'t decide on one Jelly Belly jelly bean flavor, you need to reach for the 49 flavors assortment! This handsome Jelly Belly bag contains a diverse collection of their finest beans. Each includes the brilliant colors, intense taste and familiar white Jelly Belly brand printed on one side.Grab a handful, come up with your own fun combinations or pick and choose individual jelly beans! Our bulk Jelly Belly 49 flavors mix bags give you more of the candy you love with every order! Stay stocked up in case guests or a demanding sweet tooth show up. Our assortment includes multiple individual bags that feature beautiful Jelly Belly branding that\'s perfect for gift giving.Use them as stocking stuffers, add to Easter basket candy for the kids or include in a gourmet gift basket. Jelly Belly candy is made with love to ensure the best quality and eating experience no matter how many beans you order!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', '3582~jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags-12ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-49-flavors-mix-bags'),
(3583, 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags', 9.99, '6', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Dr. Pepper Licorice Twists Bags - 6ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/r/dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', '3583~dr._pepper_licorice_twists_bags_-_6ct.jpg', 'dr-pepper-licorice-twists-bags'),
(3584, 'Starburst Peg Bag', 36.99, '12', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Starburst fruit chews are the sweetest way to get your fruit fix. Each piece is square and includes a soft, chewy texture that feels smooth and tastes amazing!Our bulk Starburst fruit chews include multiple peg bags with individually wrapped blocks of confectionary goodness. Sink your teeth into juicy strawberry, orange, cherry or lemon or combine two flavors for a mouthful of fun!The original Starburst candies were introduced in 1959 as Opal Fruits under the Mars brand in the United Kingdom. They were later renamed Starburst and made available for sale in the United States. Needless to say, Starburst fruit chews were a big hit here in the states!Today they are one of the most popular confections available in grocery stores and candy shops all over the country. Now you can get larger quantities for parties, events, holidays or at home snacking by ordering our convenient bulk Starburst packs!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/starburstpegbag.jpg', '3584~starburstpegbag.jpg', 'starburst-peg-bag-12ct'),
(3585, 'Jelly Belly 20 Flavor Jelly Beans Bags', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'bagged-candy', 'Jelly Belly 20 Flavor Jelly Beans Bags - 24ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly_belly_20_flavor_jelly_beans_bags_-_24ct.jpg', '3585~jelly_belly_20_flavor_jelly_beans_bags_-_24ct.jpg', 'jelly-belly-20-flavor-jelly-beans-bags');
