(3637, 'Caramel Cream Bulls Eyes', 35.99, '', '', 'caramel', 'Each Caramel Cream (or Bull\'s Eye), starts with a white cream filling at the center. The outside includes a generous layer of high quality caramel to create a round treat. Our bulk Caramel Creams arrive individually wrapped with nostalgic red Goetze branding.Caramel Cream Bulls Eyes are the crowning jewel in the Goetze\'s catalog. The Goetze brand goes way back to 1895. By 1917, the family-owned company introduced its first soft caramel candies, much to the delight of candy lovers!Today, Caramel Creams are considered Goetze\'s signature creation, and it\'s easy to see why once you sink your teeth into one! Keep them in the candy jar at home, take them to the office to share or add to a gourmet gift basket! Caramel Creams are also a wonderful choice for shower and wedding favors. Their sweet, creamy taste and classic look appeals to candy lovers of all ages! Find out what makes Goetze so delicious by adding Caramel Creams to your next gathering.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-creams-bulls-eyes-goetze-candy-store-470x470.jpg', '3637~caramel-creams-bulls-eyes-goetze-candy-store-470x470.jpg', 'bulls-eyes-caramel-creams'),
(3638, 'Cow Tales Caramel Sticks', 15.99, '36', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Our bulk box of Cow Tales contains a very generous quantity of individually wrapped caramel pieces. Candy lovers of all ages will love the chewy texture and smooth cream filling. Order your choice of original vanilla, strawberry cream or chocolate or try multiple boxes so you can sample a combination of Cow Tale flavors!Cow Tales are the creation of Goetze\'s Candy. The company began in 1895 as the Baltimore Chewing Gum Company. The company\'s signature Caramel Cream was created in 1917 followed by the classic Cow Tale.This confection was very similar to the Caramel Cream, but instead of a small disc of chewy caramel it featured a long tube (or tail) with delectable cream running through the middle. Different flavors have been added, including strawberry, vanilla, chocolate and caramel apple, but the classic version is still often considered the best!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/cow-tales-original-caramel--cream-sticks-36ct.jpg', '3638~cow-tales-original-caramel--cream-sticks-36ct.jpg', 'cow-tales-original-caramel-cream-sticks'),
(3639, 'Caramel Block Bulk', 26.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'When it comes to creating delicious treats at home the number one ingredient is going to be yummy candy. When you buy a bulk caramel block then you will have enough delicious goodness to create a whole kitchen full of treats that will feed an army. One of the best things about this caramel product is that it will make anything into a treat. Eating fruit can be a difficult thing to get kids to do, well learn how to cover it in caramel and you have created a fruit snack that no kid can resist. This has been the secret recipe for caramel apples for many years. Simply heat up the caramel put an apple on a stick and dip. Once the candy coating has cooled, you have created a snack that will be remembered forever. This works for other fruit as well. Some cover strawberries and some will cover bananas but probably the best selection is to offer a plate of fruit and the melted candy as a dipping sauce. More fruit will disappear than you believed possible.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulk-caramel-block-5lb_2.jpg', '3639~bulk-caramel-block-5lb_2.jpg', 'bulk-caramel-block'),
(3640, 'Sugar Daddy Caramel Pops Large', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Chewy Sugar Daddy caramel pops offer the best of everything when it comes to sweet snacking. These mouthwatering delights produce big flavor that no caramel fanatic can resist! The beauty is in the taste and the design. Each piece includes a generous bar of creamy caramel candy perched atop a convenient disposable stick. Simply peel the bright yellow wrapper and enjoy golden caramel confection to your heart\'s content without the gooey mess!Anytime is a great time to buy Sugar Daddy candy! Give them away during holidays, hide them in party favors or keep them around the pantry for days when you\'re craving something smooth and sweet. Since 1925, Sugar Daddies have been the go-to candy for caramel lovers. New sizes have been introduced over the years, but none compare to the large Sugar Daddy caramel pop. Take your mouth on a saccharine vacation with a box of nostalgic Sugar Daddy candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', '3640~sugar-daddy-caramel-pops---large-24ct_1.gif', 'sugar-daddy-caramel-pops-large'),
(3641, 'Caramel Swirl Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Caramel swirl salt water taffy is a rich, chewy treat that you\'ll love to eat! Anyone who adores the sweet, savory flavor of classic caramel must experience the taste of our salt water taffy. Each piece recreates the feeling of eating a bite-sized piece of high quality caramel but with that taffy texture you know and love.Our salt water taffy is available in single-flavor packages so you get exactly what you want every time you order! Bulk caramel swirl salt water taffy can be used for events and much more. Fill treat bags or wedding favors with these elegant little pinwheels. Each includes a toasty brown hue that\'s accented by a slender spiral swirl of white.Each piece arrives individually wrapped so it stays fresh and enjoyable. Order our caramel saltwater taffy for your next event or keep a package at home or at the office to eat as a quick snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3641~caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-swirl-salt-water-taffy'),
(3642, 'Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', '\'\'Mooo-ve\'\' over for these Licorice Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffies. With their beautiful white and black cow spots and creamy flavor, you won\'t ever want to put these down or put them out to pasture. This snack is a classic that has satisfied candy lovers for years.Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice_caramel.jpg', '3642~licorice_caramel.jpg', 'licorice-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(3643, 'Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'One classic confection with the flavor of another: it is a novelty with the appeal of a tradition! Caramel Apple Salt Water Taffy has a bright green center that looks bright as springtime when you use it as a table scatter or to fill an heirloom dish.A symbol of playful days and sunny summers by the sea, bulk saltwater taffy is beloved by kids and adults for its soft, chewy, flavorful composition, and the individual wrappers on these green and brown taffy delicacies make them perfect for candy buffets, treat bags, and pantry stockpiles of tasty sweets.The tart green apple flavor in this wholesale caramel apple taffy combines with a creamy, sweet caramel taste that is reminiscent of the original molasses recipe from which modern taffy flavors evolved. Apple flavor, too, takes your taste buds straight to the autumn orchards, too. The combination of classic taste appeals makes caramel apple saltwater taffy an especially evocative little treat!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3643~caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-apple-salt-water-taffy'),
(3644, 'Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy', 23.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy is unbelievable, and sure to become one of your favorite treats. It blends sweet and savory in every single bite.You can probably guess just by looking at the cowhide design of these candies that your taste buds are going to be in for a special treat. In fact, you probably don\'t even need to read their name to know that you are about to indulge in a flavor combination of sweet, decadent caramel and creamy vanilla.Unwrap one, pop it in your mouth, and enjoy a long-lasting sweet that retains its flavor right down until the last speck has been dissolved. Since these kosher certified Vanilla Caramel Cowhide Salt Water Taffy candies are individually wrapped, they are perfect for candy dishes for any occasion.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla_caramel_taffy.jpeg', '3644~vanilla_caramel_taffy.jpeg', 'vanilla-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(3645, 'Chocolate Caramel Mocha Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'So you are dedicated to upscale flavors like chocolate, coffee, and caramel, but you want to put a nostalgic spin on a dinner-party dessert or movie-night treat. What to do? Chocolate Caramel Mocha Salt Water Taffy, of course!Wonderfully munchable, individually-wrapped pieces of soft and delicious saltwater taffy in a rich combination of three flavors makes a striking addition to a candy buffet as well. The look is perfectly timeless, and the flavor is sophisticated â€“ bulk candy does not get much better than this! Individual wrappers that are easy to open, plus a bold brown and white color mix in each flavorful piece, make chocolate caramel mocha salt water taffy a delicious choice for setting on the napkin at every place setting.Or for offering in a huge bowl for endless sweet luxury. The soft taffy texture of these classically-made pieces is a little harder to find than many sweets, making them the stuff of special occasions and childhood vacations for many candy lovers!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3645~chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'chocolate-caramel-salt-water-taffy'),
(3646, 'Chocolate Caramel Squares Candy', 42.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'We love that these Chocolate Caramel Squares Candies come wrapped in cellophane so we can see right through to the deliciousness! And why would anyone want to cover up a candy that features a delicious milk chocolate square of amazingness and a melty, chewy caramel center inside?Are you a major proponent for Chocolate Caramel Square Candies? Then you\'ve hit the jackpot here on CandyStore.com because we have huge bulk orders of them at budget friendly prices. This means you can bring home hundreds of these Chocolate Caramel Square Candies to chow down on for weeks to come. Or however long your sweet tooth allows.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-caramel-candy-5lb_1.jpg', '3646~chocolate-caramel-candy-5lb_1.jpg', 'chocolate-caramel-squares'),
(3647, 'Mini Cow Tales Caramel Creams', 57.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Those who love Cow Tales will certainly love these many Cow Tales. These are able to offer the same great caramel and cream flavor but are just smaller in size. They also come individually wrapped so that they are sure to stay as fresh as possible for as long as possible. These are great for treat bags, snacks, Halloween, and many of occasionsCow Tales offer a great chewy caramel flavor on the outside and the inside is a smooth but creamy center. These are sure to please almost anyone. They are also great for adults as well as children. The best part about it is that you are able to get either a chocolate or vanilla flavor for these great Cow Tales. If you are having a medium sized party then you are sure to find this would be enough for your party as well.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb_1.jpg', '3647~mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb_1.jpg', 'mini-cow-tales-caramel-creams10lb'),
(3648, 'Caramel Corn Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Sometimes too much of one thing is a bad thing. But we don\'t think a double dose of creamy and deliciousness could ever be bad with this Caramel Corn Salt Water Taffy! This rich candy is a great selection for any affair and especially looks nice around the holidays. Around since the late 1800s, the history is almost as sweet as the candy itself. When the tides turned and flooded a candy store owner\'s shop, he decided to market his salt water soaked taffys to the public! We\'re sure glad the sea found this taffy and so are the generations of people that have enjoyed it since.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3648~caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-corn-salt-water-taffy'),
(3649, 'Caramel Cheesecake Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'At the risk of sounding cheesy, we\'ll admit to all of you that these Caramel Cheesecake Salt Water Taffies make our hearts melt. That\'s because they\'re so creamy, rich and delicious! Bring them to a party with your closest gal pals, put some on a dessert table, or keep them in the cabinet when a sweet tooth strikes. Discovered in the late 1800s, salt water taffy was the product of an unfortunate event. When a candy store owner\'s shop was flooded with sea water, he decided to market his soaked taffys to the public! What a happy accident this incident turned out to be, because people have incorporated taffy into their summer snacks and memories for generations.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3649~caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-cheesecake-salt-water-taffy'),
(3650, 'Pecan Caramel Pattie Chocolates', 75.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Pecan Caramel Pattie Chocolates are the ultimate indulgence of the chocolate world, combining three decadent tastes and three individual textures into an utterly luscious gourmet candy.Always tempting treats when laid out on trays on a dessert table, these high-quality bulk chocolates bring out the flavorful appeal of pecans and the creamy, slightly chewy warmth of caramel by half-drowning both of them in the thick coating of delicious chocolate.Maybe you want to make gift baskets feel more thoughtful yet keep them relatively economical by tucking in a cellophane bag of these wholesale candies. Maybe you have a corporate event coming up and you want to sweeten your guests outlook with a lovable chocolate caramel treat.Maybe you just like to keep a rich, self-contained dessert on hand in the pantry for unexpected guests. Whatever your need, these pecan caramel pattie chocolates are a distinctly delicious solution.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates-5lbs.gif', '3650~pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates-5lbs.gif', 'pecan-caramel-pattie-chocolates'),
(3651, 'Licorice Caramels', 40.99, '4.4', 'lb', 'caramel', 'The mad scientists of the candy world have created a magical hybrid of flavors! We\'re talking about our licorice caramels and can\'t wait for you to bring some home and take a bite.In a dark chocolatey brown, these cellophane wrapped black caramels have the delicious creaminess of caramel and the bite of licorice so the flavor and texture experience is one of the most exciting. Give your mouth a relaxing job to do by popping one of these licorice caramels in and letting is melt away slowly. Now that\'s what we like to call R&R; in the candy world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', '3651~licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', 'licorice-caramels'),
(3652, 'Bull\'s Eye Caramel Creams Theater Box', 22.99, '12', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Bulls-Eyes caramel candies are one of the smoothest, chewiest treats you can add to your candy collection! This classic confection brings together two delicious ingredients.Each piece is round, bite-sized and arrives individually wrapped in clear plastic with the familiar red Goetze\'s logo right at the center. Our theater candy boxes are convenient and contain plenty of pieces for one or two people!Every Bulls-Eyes caramel includes two main parts. The outside is a thick ring of delectable caramel. The middle includes a circle of rich creamy confection. Each bite gives you a bit of both flavors to produce the most irresistible combination for anyone who adores the sweet, savory taste of caramel!Our bulk caramel candy package contains several theater boxes so you have plenty to use as party favors or a quick snack at home. Host your own movie night complete with sweet concessions or take a theater box with you as an easy snack at work!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-box-12ct.gif', '3652~bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-box-12ct.gif', 'bulls-eye-caramel-creams-theater-boxes'),
(3653, 'Slapstix Caramel Pops', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'What could be better than a giant lollipop? How about one that\'s made with creamy caramel! Our Slapstix caramel pops are a delicious treat that is sure to satisfy your carving for smooth, sweet caramel.Each piece includes a generous block of confection with a gentle swirl of flavor that\'s perched on a disposable stick. Enjoy ooey gooey caramel without sticky fingers! If you\'re looking for a lollipop that\'s unique and chewy, this is a must-try confection!Each comes individually wrapped so the rectangle caramel lollipop stays fresh and ready to enjoy. Order boxes for birthday parties, events and more! Everyone will love receiving these at school activities and community events.Slapstix lollipops also make great stocking stuffers at Christmas time. Whether you\'re filling treat bags for a birthday party or looking for an easy sweet treat to enjoy at home, you will love the rich taste of caramel lollipops!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/l/slapstix-caramel-pops-24ct.gif', '3653~slapstix-caramel-pops-24ct.gif', 'slapstix-caramel-pops'),
(3654, 'Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars', 38.99, '14', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Bite size pieces of pure bliss is what you enjoy with this bulk supply of Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars. Each of the bars has 18 individual squares that are easy to break or cut apart.So, you can serve them to your guests on a tray for dessert, if you can bring yourself to share. Although originated in the United Kingdom, today The Hershey Company has a license to manufacture the divine line of Cadbury products in the United States.Whether you buy them in America or the UK, they are the same mouthwatering, melt-in-your-mouth bars of delicious goodness. Decadent milk chocolate is poured over creamy caramel and hardened.So, although the chocolate is firm on the outside, when you bite into them the gooey caramel comes oozing out. Your taste buds will be dancing. These large Cadbury Caramello Chocolate Bars make great stocking stuffers or last minute gifts for coworkers.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars-24ct_1.jpg', '3654~cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars-24ct_1.jpg', 'cadbury-caramello-chocolate-bars'),
(3655, 'Black Cow Bar', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Chocolate and caramel surely are a decadent combo. With these Black Cow Bars, you\'ll get all of that in one incredible bite. And with this bulk box, you\'ll have a ton of savoring to do!Being a black sheep is never a good thing, but being a black cow certainly is! These Black Cow Bars are full of amazing chewy chocolate caramel that will keep your mouth moving like a cow grazing in the pasture. Pour some of these Black Cow Bars into a trick-or-treating candy bowl for Halloween, bring some home for a barn-themed wedding or party or order some if you just love caramel and chocolate. There\'s no wrong reason to order these tasty treats!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blackcowbar.jpg', '3655~blackcowbar.jpg', 'black-cow-bar'),
(3656, 'Slo Poke Bar', 25.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'If the name is any hint, you should slow down and enjoy this delicious caramel candy. That\'s because Slo Poke Bars are made of incredible salty and sweet caramel that melts in your mouth slowly so you can delight in the flavor for longer.If you\'re a fan of caramels, then these Slo Poke Bars are a candy we\'re sure you\'ll adore. In a bulk size box, these Slo Poke Bars will provide you with hours of sweet satisfaction. Stock your pantry with some of these incredible caramels to use in baking, give out in gift baskets or enjoy piece by piece. If you\'re having a stressful day, indulging in one of these bars will surely slow down the pace and help you relax.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/l/slopokebar.jpg', '3656~slopokebar.jpg', 'slo-poke-bar'),
(3657, 'Chocolate Covered Caramel and Marshmallow', 66.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Goodness gracious. Just when you didn\'t think something more delicious than chocolate covered caramel could come around, these chocolate-covered caramel and marshmallows come out to surprise you!In a ridiculously fluffy, chewy, melty and delicious combination of caramel, milk chocolate and marshmallow, these candies will melt in your mouth and melt your heart at the same time. If you want gourmet-tasting candy for an economical price, bring home a bulk supply of our Chocolate Covered Caramel and Marshmallow candies and you can munch on tasty treats that seem like they\'re out of a glass case of a fine chocolatier\'s store. Serve these on your next party\'s dessert platter and wow your guests with the deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-caramel-and-marshmallow-6lbs_4.gif', '3657~chocolate-covered-caramel-and-marshmallow-6lbs_4.gif', 'caramel-marshmallow-chocolate-covered'),
(3658, 'Black Cow Bite Size', 59.99, '15', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Moooo-ve over other candies. These Black Cow Bite Size treats are a crowd favorite with their chocolate flavored chewy caramel. Wrapped in fun sizes, they\'re a perfect little dessert you can graze on between any meal. Bite in for a chewy, gooey and ooey texture and flavor you\'ll never want to put to pasture. Milk this bulk bag of Black Cow Bite Size candy for all its worth by indulging on decadent chocolate caramel after chocolate caramel. Whether you like to enjoy your sweets solo or add them to other recipes, this Black Cow Bite Size candy can do it all and more. Add some to a candy buffet bar. Unwrap a few to use atop cupcakes and other sweets. Even dice some up to add to the top of an ice cream sundae.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black_cow_bites_bulk.jpg', '3658~black_cow_bites_bulk.jpg', 'black-cow-bite-size'),
(3659, 'Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels', 64.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'We did a double take when we first saw these Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels, too! That\'s because with a double dose of incredible chocolate in every square, these little morsels pack enough sweet, savory and melty deliciousness into every bite. In either milk or dark chocolate, these Chocolate Covered Chocolate Caramels are an incredible treat. Order a bulk supply and you can make your very own Valentine\'s Day boxes for the people you love most. Or, you can be content to know that a yummy and spectacular treat awaits you whenever you need a sweet fix.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', '3659~chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-chocolate-caramels'),
(3660, 'Chocolate Covered Vanilla Caramels', 64.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Chocolate, vanilla and caramel are three of the most popular flavors in the candy world. Our delicious chocolate collection brings you a one-of-a-kind confection that combines all three in the most delightful way!Our chocolate covered vanilla caramels are sure to satisfy even the most demanding sugar cravings with a combination of richness and sweetness. Every bite-sized piece includes a generous filling packed with solid caramel flavored with a hint of delectable vanilla.The outside is covered in a smooth blanket of milk chocolate accented by alternating chocolate drizzle. Not only are these chocolate candies delicious, but they\'re also very elegant to look at.Arrange them on a tray for guests or add to wedding favors to send your guests off with an edible gift that includes high quality gourmet chocolate! Our bulk candy pack makes it so easy to get the quantity you need for events of any size.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', '3660~chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramel-6lbs_2.gif', 'chocolate-covered-vanilla-caramels'),
(3661, 'Caramel Truffle', 69.99, '6', 'lb', 'caramel', 'If you adore chocolate and caramel, the caramel truffle are the ultimate treat for you! This delectable confection combines two rich, savory ingredients into one gourmet candy. Each piece includes an elegant shape that adds to the eating experience. The bottom is flat with smooth, rounded sides that include angular edges. The top is flat with a white chocolate tulip raised at the center, complete with petal detail.Bulk caramel truffles give you large quantities for snacking or celebrations. Keep them in the pantry as a quick snack when you\'re craving something with a little class (and a lot of sweetness). Or share them with guests.These charming truffles look fabulous when displayed on platters or trays with cookies and other desserts. Use them to fill out a gourmet gift basket or add to this year\'s stocking stuffer candy. Decadent caramel truffles are a delicious candy for any season or event!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-truffle-6lbs_2.gif', '3661~caramel-truffle-6lbs_2.gif', 'caramel-truffles'),
(3662, 'Riesen Dark Chocolate Caramel Candy', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'You would have to eat an entire cake pan full of brownies to make your taste buds as happy as they will be with just one Riesen Dark Chocolate Caramel Candy. The second your teeth break through the decadent dark chocolate and are greeted by gooey, sweet caramel, you will understand why this German classic has been a favorite of many around the world for many years.Riesen Candy was first introduced in the 1930s, only back then it was a wrapped and branded as caramel. By the 1940s, a chocolate-caramel blend was created, but it was not until the late 1908s that the caramel was covered in rich dark chocolate. Stock up on Riesen Dark Chocolate Caramel Candy, and you can satisfy your sweet tooth with one small piece, rather than a plate full of cake!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/i/riesen-dark-chocolate-caramel-candy-24ct_1.jpg', '3662~riesen-dark-chocolate-caramel-candy-24ct_1.jpg', 'riesen-dark-chocolate'),
(3663, 'Caramel Sugar Free Hard Candy', 45.99, '5', 'lb', 'caramel', 'If you love caramel flavor but want less sugar in your daily diet, our hard candy is a great choice! These sugar free confections offer big taste in a small package. Every morsel features the savory sweetness of a creamy piece of real caramel.Each is smooth, hard and completely sugar-free so you never feel guilty for indulging. Our bulk sugar free hard candy package is a convenient way to ensure you never run out when cravings hit! Our sugar free caramel candy arrives individually wrapped in bronze foil. Each includes an appealing shiny appearance with subtle polka dotted sides.A quick twist of the wrapper and you are ready to enjoy classic caramel goodness! Use these sugar free candies to fill the office candy jar or store them at home, at your desk or wherever cravings are likely to strike. Our handsome sugar free caramel hard candy is also ideal for weddings, showers, birthdays, holidays and other events.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-caramel-5lb_2.jpg', '3663~golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-caramel-5lb_2.jpg', 'caramel-golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy'),
(3664, 'Black Cow Bites Changemaker Jar', 12.99, '160', 'ct', 'caramel', 'At just half the size, these little Black Cow Bite Size Changemaker Jar candies are more like a calf than their bigger bovine candy equivalents. However, they don\'t skimp on any of the delicious chocolate caramel flavor or salty sweet chew that Black Cow candies are famous for!With this big supply of Black Cow Bite Size Changemaker Jar candies, you\'ll be able to snack happily for days and days. If you\'re having a raffle, try auctioning off some of these Black Cow Bite Size Changemaker Jar candies. People will love the classic taste, flavor and style and you\'ll be able to pull in more money for a good cause. You can even use these for a candy buffet bar at home or to keep in the kitchen for a quick lunchbox stuffer the kids have a cow over!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-cow-bite-size-216ct.jpg', '3664~black-cow-bite-size-216ct.jpg', 'black-cow-bite-size-changemaker-jar'),
(3665, 'Caramel Corn Jelly Belly', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'caramel', 'Now you can savor the delicious, warm taste of classic caramel corn in a chewy jelly bean! Jelly Belly caramel corn jelly beans are a small candy that\'s big on flavor.Each piece is packed with a winning combination of sweet, creamy caramel and delicious popcorn! What make this Jelly Belly creation even more exciting is the gorgeous pattern featured one very dainty bean.Our caramel corn jelly beans are a pale, ivory color with golden speckles that represent smooth, melted caramel drizzle. Each jelly bean is also printed with the white Jelly Belly logo, so you know it\'s an authentic confection! Our single-flavor jelly bean packs are the easiest way to get the beans you love without having to pick through an assortment.Caramel corn jelly beans are a great choice for birthday parties, wedding favors and holidays! Order one bulk jelly bean pack or check out our other Jelly Belly flavors and build your own custom candy mix.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/caramel-corn-jelly-belly-10lbs_1.jpg', '3665~caramel-corn-jelly-belly-10lbs_1.jpg', 'caramel-corn-jelly-belly'),
(3666, 'Vanilla Chocolate Caramels', 40.99, '4.4', 'lb', 'caramel', 'With a swirl of vanilla and chocolate inside a melty caramel, these Vanilla Chocolate Caramels are truly divine. Plus, their see-through cellophane wrapper allows you to see the beauty of the candy before you snack. You can\'t knock a classic. And these Vanilla Chocolate Caramels are definitely something no one will be able to slander once they take a taste. Since these candies are wrapped individually, they make a perfect sweet for candy bowls for your family to frequent, they look great scattered in gift baskets, they also are perfect for putting in your purse or office desk drawer to snack on whenever you need a pick-me-up. If you\'re a fan of caramels and the classic flavors of vanilla and chocolate, then Vanilla Chocolate Caramels are going to make you and your taste buds very happy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/vanilla-chocolate-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', '3666~vanilla-chocolate-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', 'vanilla-chocolate-caramels'),
(3667, 'Nestle Crunch Bars with Caramel', 19.99, '24', 'ct', 'caramel', 'Nestle Crunch bars with caramel offer a new way to enjoy this classic candy. Since 1937, Crunch candy bars have been serving up chocolaty goodness to kids and adults across the country.The original recipe included a solid bar of milk chocolate with crisped rice for extra crunch. As if that wasn\'t enough, Nestle has created something even more exciting for candy lovers with their Nestle Crunch with Caramel bar!This version takes a similar approach but adds something creamy and delicious to the mix! Each bar includes convenient break-lines to form individual bite-sized pieces. Inside each piece is a blanket of smooth, rich caramel over a bed of classic Crunch bar chocolate and crisped rice.Our bulk Nestle Crunch Bars with Caramel come individually wrapped so they are easy to take with you everywhere you go! Keep a few Crunch bars the office or hide them in the pantry as a quick evening snack.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/e/nestle-crunch-bars-with-caramel-24ct.gif', '3667~nestle-crunch-bars-with-caramel-24ct.gif', 'nestle-crunch-bars-caramel'),
(3668, 'Mint Licorice Caramels', 40.99, '4.4', 'lb', 'caramel', 'If the hypnotizing swirl doesn\'t do it for you, then the delicious minty, chewy, sweet flavor sure will! Black and white and wrapped individually in cellophane, Mint Licorice Caramels are both refreshing and addicting with a big bite of chew and sugary sweetness.If you\'re having a black and white event, a black tie wedding, formal affair, Halloween party or practically anything else, then these Mint Licorice Caramels would make an incredible statement for you. Stock up on a bulk bag and you\'ll be able to put them out in candy dishes, give them away to friends, keep them around the house, or serve them on a dessert platter. These Mint Licorice Caramels are so tasty they can do it all and more.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/mint-licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', '3668~mint-licorice-caramels-bulk_2.jpg', 'mint-licorice-caramels'),
(3669, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '3669~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(3670, 'Atomic Fireballs Wrapped', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'T-minus, 1, 9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1... Prepare for total taste bud annihilation! These Atomic Fireballs may be small, but don\'t let their unassuming size fool you. Their explosive shell and spicy interior bring the heat of a five alarm fire.With about 50 blazing pieces per pound, there\'s enough candy here to nuke your mouth into oblivion and back again. But if you can summon the courage to put out the blaze, you\'ll be treated to a mild, sweet cinnamon finish that will be well worth the challenge. Just beware. Only the strong mouthed will survive to beat this atomic heat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/t/atomic-fireballs-wrapped-medium-470x470.jpg', '3670~atomic-fireballs-wrapped-medium-470x470.jpg', 'atomic-fireballs-wrapped'),
(3671, 'Cinnamon Imperial Hearts', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Our hearts are beating out of our chests for these Cinnamon Imperial Hearts! With a spicy, hot cinnamon flavor and chewy candy texture, your heart is sure to start pitter pattering for these loveable treats with your first bite. Bring them to a Valentine\'s Day party to share some spice that\'s extra nice with loved ones, stock up to keep your candy dishes full throughout February, or get some of these to add into a Cupid-themed candy buffet bar. The bright, red color of these vibrant hearts and delicious cinnamony flavor is something your eyes will love just as much as your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-hearts.jpg', '3671~cinnamon-hearts.jpg', 'cinnamon-imperial-hearts'),
(3672, 'Hot Tamales Minis', 9.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Hold on to your taste buds! These red Hot Tamales Minis are ready to singe every last one of \'em off of your tongue. Though they may be packed in miniature movie theater boxes, every pack of these tamales are ready with a fiery punch of cinnamon that will blow you away. If you can\'t beat the heat, try adding them to a cup of tea or cocoa for a milder cinnamon fix. But if you\'re prepared for a spice that can\'t be beat, pop a few of these into your mouth at a time and feel the fire. Whatever you do, you\'ll set your mouth a-blaze with this bulk supply.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', '3672~hot-tamales-minis-36ct.gif', 'hot-tamales-minis'),
(3673, 'Cinnamon Imperials Candy', 20.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'These red hot little cinnamon mouth explosions are great for any candy dish! Cinnamon Imperials candies have a classic taste that everyone remembers from childhood, and they\'re great for all kinds of occasions.Include them as a sweet treat for your Valentine. Add them to an assortment of fruity and spicy candies at a party, or just keep them in the candy dish at home for guests who happen to drop by.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', '3673~cinnamon-imperials-10lbs.gif', 'cinnamon-imperials'),
(3674, 'cinnamon swirl salt water taffy in a white bowl', 19.49, '', '', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'If you have never tried cinnamon salt water taffy then you don\'t know what you are missing out on. The flavor of these is perfect. They have a cinnamon blend that is spicy and works just right with the sweet flavor that they have as well. There is nothing better than the tasty of salt water taffy and when you combine it with cinnamon the flavor really seems to explode. The candies are pink in color and are sure to look great for a many different occasions. You will also like to know that each piece is wrapped individually which is very helpful in making sure that they stay fresh as long as possible. There is just something about the chewy texture of taffy that is able to please so many people. This is a great tasting candy with a great texture that is hard to beat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3674~cinnamon-swirl-salt-water-taffy-town-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'cinnamon-salt-water-taffy'),
(3675, 'Cinnamon Sugar Free Hard Candy', 45.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'When was the last time you were able to make your dentist and your mouth happy at the same time? Now you can with these sugar-free cinnamon hard candies! With the traditional, spicy cinnamon bite and lovely red color, these candies are the perfect everyday treat for you and your loved ones without all the calories. Soothe a sore throat with a dose of cinnamon spice, add a couple candies to your afternoon cup of tea, or even take them to work to surprise coworkers. This package has is crammed with about 120 pieces per pound, so you\'ll have fresh breath and a well-stocked candy supply for a long, long time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-cinnamon-5lb_2.jpg', '3675~golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy-cinnamon-5lb_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-golightly-sugar-free-hard-candy'),
(3676, 'Cinnamon Taffy', 9.90, '3', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Don\'t let your guard down, because these Cinnamon Taffies may look pretty, but they pack a spicy punch that may surprise you! These beautiful pink and red striped taffies have the chewy texture that taffy lovers worship and the spicy kick that only cinnamon can deliver. Stock up your supply to enjoy these little taffies in a variety of ways. Add them to a cup of steaming hot cocoa and let them melt away to add some spice to every sip, bring these to a little girl\'s baby shower for a festive pink look and feisty cinnamon flavor, or even keep them around the house to snack on when you please.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-taffy-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', '3676~cinnamon-taffy-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', 'cinnamon-taffy-sweets'),
(3677, 'Cinnamon Roll Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Hold the phone. This Cinnamon Roll Salt Water Taffy cannot be real! It\'s just too delicious to be true. However, don\'t pinch us if we\'re dreaming because we love the taste of these sweet and sugary Cinnamon Roll Salt Water Taffies that we don\'t want to be interrupted from enjoying their intense flavor.If you\'re a fan of this famous breakfast food, then try it in taffy form. Adding that soft chew to the warm and buttery Cinnamon Roll flavor to Salt Water Taffy makes it the most delicious and decadent treat. Serve some of these at your next family brunch or on the dessert platter alongside coffee and tea.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-roll-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3677~cinnamon-roll-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'cinnamon-roll-salt-water-taffy'),
(3678, 'Cinnamon Bears', 18.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Get your cinnamon fix with our delicious gummy bears! Each piece offers serious cinnamon flavor with a look that\'s sure to entice. Just like traditional gummy bears, these handsome teddy\'s have a large head with round ears, adorable paws and an endearing face.Every piece is made of solid gummy candy in a bright red hue that grabs attention and hints at the irresistible flavor that awaits! Take a bite and enjoy your favorite soft candy with a touch of warm spice! Our bulk cinnamon bears are a must-have for events, holidays and parties!Combine with a green candy to create a festive Christmas mix or surprise guests by mixing with other gummy bears in a candy dish. We carry a variety of other single color candies so you can build a custom assortment for any event. Make beautiful wedding favors with a red theme or spice up your birthday party treat bags with our bulk cinnamon bears!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-bears.jpg', '3678~cinnamon-bears.jpg', 'cinnamon-bears-bulk'),
(3679, 'Hot Tamales Theater Boxes', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'We were just talking about Hot Tamales Theater Boxes and how much heat they\'ll pack into our next trip to the movies. Also amazing for when you lay down on the couch to watch a feature film. So good!If you love spicy cinnamon heat, then you\'ll love stocking up with this bulk supply of Hot Tamales movie size boxes. If you\'re going to have a viewing party with friends, spice up the night with some of these for guests to munch on. Even bring Hot Tamales Theater Boxes home to stuff into gift baskets or give away at a raffle. Whatever you do, remember these candies are hot, hot, hot!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-theater-boxes-12ct.gif', '3679~hot-tamales-theater-boxes-12ct.gif', 'hot-tamales-theater-boxes'),
(3680, 'Xtreme Hot Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Sound the alarm! This Xtreme Hot Salt Water Taffy isn\'t playing around with its volcanic heat. Bubbling and boiling in this molten taffy is a hotter-than-heck cinnamon flavor that will blow your socks off and stun your taste buds.As you devour this red and white spicy taffy, you\'ll come across specks of extreme heat that will erupt on your tongue. If you\'re up to the challenge, order yourself a bulk bag today and start snacking with a seriously hot treat. But if this hasn\'t scared you off, then you\'re definitely ready for these Xtreme Hot Salt Water Taffy.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/x/t/xtreme-hot-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', '3680~xtreme-hot-salt-water-taffy-5lbs_1.jpg', 'xtreme-hot-salt-water-taffy'),
(3681, 'Cinnamon Jelly Belly', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Sugar, spice, and all that\'s nice! These cinnamon Jelly Belly jelly beans are a breath freshening, spicy classic. Their vibrant red color and vivid flavor has made this hot and spicy mini a favorite for years. Drop a few into hot tea, apple cider or enjoy them simply as they are. There\'s no wrong way to indulge with these tasty beans. The Jelly Belly company has been around since 1976 and has showed their talent in producing tantilizing flavors that have pleased customers for decades This cinnamon bean is part of the Jelly Belly family\'s 5 official flavors, and is available to light mouths on fire all year \'round.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', '3681~cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-jelly-belly'),
(3682, 'Altoids Cinnamon', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Altoids cinnamon candy are more than just a curiously strong mint. These refreshing treats are a confection that comes with a long, rich history. The original recipe was created by a London-based company in the 1780s, when King George III sat on the throne. The product\'s high concentration of peppermint oil is what inspired the popular slogan we all know and love today. Altoids are currently available in six different flavors, including cinnamon. The storage tin was introduced in the 1920s and still helps keep each mint fresh and clean, even while on the go. Our bulk mint package is a convenient option for anyone who never wants to go without their favorite candy! Hide a tin in your purse or pocket or keep them in the glove box. The larger quantity is also great to share at the office or while on the job. Invigorate your mouth with Altoids cinnamon mints!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoidscinnamon.jpg', '3682~altoidscinnamon.jpg', 'altoids-cinnamon-12ct'),
(3683, 'Altoids Mints', 29.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Altoids mints are one of the most popular brands available today. If you want a mint with some kick to it, then Altoids is a great choice. They are called the curiously strong mint for a good reason!Each piece is round and features a simple white color that is rather unassuming, until you actually taste the intense peppermint flavor. Each mint is made using a high concentration of invigorating peppermint oil to produce the trademark flavor that made Altoids famous.Along with a distinctively minty flavor, Altoids mints also feature nostalgic packaging. Each box contains many tins with a red border and classic fonts and imagery. Your mints stay fresh and ready to eat and they are easy to carry with you!Keep a tin in your desk drawer, pocket, purse or car. Our bulk Altoids mints box gives you many tins so you can use them for special events, party favors and stocking stuffers!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoids-mints-12ct_2.gif', '3683~altoids-mints-12ct_2.gif', 'altoids-mints');
