(3684, 'Hot Cinnamon Gummi Bears', 64.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'If you love the taste of cinnamon and the chewy texture of gummies, you should be hoarding these hot cinnamon gummy bears stat! As they come in a bright red color, they definitely make for the best holiday treats. Whether you plan to play Santa or not, there\'s absolutely no doubt you\'d be spreading the holiday cheer with these little guys!Plus, not only do these Hot Cinnamon Gummi Bears make for the best stocking stuffers during the Christmas season, they also work well for any kind of occasion â€“ be it a Sweet 16 Birthday Party, an office mixer or a themed ladies\' only bachelorette celebration. Truth is - you don\'t need any occasion to brighten up someone\'s day with these cinnamon-flavored goodies. So, delight all your loved ones with these Hot Cinnamon Gummi Bears and make every day feel like a holiday!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-cinnamon-gummi-bears-10lbs_2.jpg', '3684~hot-cinnamon-gummi-bears-10lbs_2.jpg', 'hot-cinnamon-gummi-bears'),
(3685, 'Altoids Cinnamon Smalls', 16.99, '9', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Get your Altoid fix with cinnamon Smalls! These mint candies feature the same rich personality as regular Altoids in a smaller package. Each bite is packed with powerful cinnamon flavor. Pop one in your mouth to give your taste buds a little pick me up. Altoids Smalls are sugar-free so you can enjoy them anytime without feeling the guilt that comes with sugary candy. Altoids Smalls are one of the newest creations to from the historic Altoids brand. The recipe for the original product was created during the reign of King George III in the 1780s. These unique lozenges gained popularity in England because of the high amounts of peppermint oil they contained. Today the famous Altoids name can be found all over the globe with many new flavors added to the list. Cinnamon fanatics will love the convenience and taste that comes with each tin of Altoids Smalls candy!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/l/altoidscinnamonsmalls.jpg', '3685~altoidscinnamonsmalls.jpg', 'altoids-cinnamon-smalls-9ct'),
(3686, 'Red Hots Theater Boxes', 19.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Red Hots candy are a traditional treat that packs a powerful punch of fiery flavor! This nostalgic treat is full of cinnamon for a snacking experience that sizzles. This is one confection that\'s not intended for the weak of heart (or the weak of taste bud!).Each piece includes a dainty round morsel in bright red. Try just one or test your mettle by grabbing a handful and letting them all smother your tongue with intense cinnamon taste! The Red Hots we know and love today have been around for a very long time. This treat was introduced by the Ferrara Pan Company during the 1930s.Their popularity has grown tremendously since then. Red Hots are a popular choice for use as a decoration for cakes, cookies or homemade candies. They are even used in apple sauce recipes! Our bulk Red Hots package contains many theater boxes that are perfect for holidays, events or family movie night.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-hots-theatre-boxes-12ct.gif', '3686~red-hots-theatre-boxes-12ct.gif', 'red-hots-theater-boxes'),
(3687, 'Sizzling Cinnamon Jelly Belly', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Danger, danger! These Sizzling Cinnamon Jelly Belly Jelly Beans should come with caution tape! That\'s because they\'re packing some serious heat in every little bean! If you love cinnamon flavored candy with a big bite, then try these sizzling jelly beans.In a beautiful red shell complete with orange speckles, these red hot beans also do some damage on the eye balls with their bold brightness. If you\'re getting ready for Christmas and want a thematic red treat but with a serious dose of holiday spice, then try these Jelly Belly Sizzling Cinnamon Jelly Beans. They\'re spark conversation, light up the night and ignite more fun every time you take a bite.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sizzling-cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', '3687~sizzling-cinnamon-jelly-belly-10lbs_2.jpg', 'sizzling-cinnamon-jelly-belly'),
(3688, 'Reeds Cinnamon Rolls Hard Candy Rolls', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Reeds Cinnamon Rolls Hard Candy Rolls - 24ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/reeds_cinnamon_rolls_hard_candy_rolls_-_24ct.jpg', '3688~reeds_cinnamon_rolls_hard_candy_rolls_-_24ct.jpg', 'reeds-cinnamon-rolls-hard-candy-rolls'),
(3689, 'Habanero Lix Lollipops', 44.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'You may need to turn up the air-conditioning, wipe the sweat from your brow, and have a tall glass of water handy when you eat one of these Habanero Lix Lollipops.Someone definitely turned up the heat in these unique candies, and by someone, we mean Hotlix, the candy creator of everything unusual and creepy. These Habanero Lix Lollipops taste just like you are eating a superhot pepper.Habanero Lix Lollipops are about 2 inches long, so they last a pretty long time. They are also on a stick that is over 4 inches long, so they are comfortable to hold. Do you have a friend who always orders the hottest wings and spiciest chili when you go out? These Habanero Lix Lollipops would make the perfect gift for them. Break these out at your next summer barbeque with friends to see who can manage to get to the end. They are also perfect to leave in your candy dish at work. When you see someone hanging out at the water cooler, you will know who has been sneaking in and taking your candy while you are out to lunch!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/habanero-lix-lollipops-24ct.gif', '3689~habanero-lix-lollipops-24ct.gif', 'habanero-lix-lollipops'),
(3690, 'Chocolate Cinnamon Bears', 129.99, '27', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Give your taste buds a whole new flavor experience with our amazing chocolate cinnamon bears! These adorable candies are like two snacks in one. Have you ever eaten a red hot cinnamon gummy bear?They are chewy, spicy and very satisfying! Now imagine taking that tangy teddy and smothering it in a layer of rich, smooth chocolate. That\'s what you get when you try our one-of-a-kind chocolate cinnamon bears! Each piece is an outer layer of chocolate surrounding a cinnamon gummy bear.Liven things up by adding our chocolate cinnamon bears to your pantry. Enjoy them as a quick snack or save them for special occasions. They make a great conversation candy that guests will love.Pour into bowls or the candy jar or use to fill party favors! Sneak them in as a surprise with other chocolate covered confections. Our bulk chocolate cinnamon bears includes large quantities that are perfect for gatherings of all sizes.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-cinnamon-bear.jpg', '3690~chocolate-cinnamon-bear.jpg', 'chocolate-cinnamon-bears-bulk'),
(3691, 'Cinna Pix Cinnamon Toothpicks', 25.99, '15', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Cinna-Pix Cinnamon Toothpicks - 15ct', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinna-pix_cinnamon_toothpicks_-_15ct.jpg', '3691~cinna-pix_cinnamon_toothpicks_-_15ct.jpg', 'cinna-pix-cinnamon-toothpicks'),
(3692, 'Cinnamon Candy Sticks', 15.99, '80', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'With the charm of an old barbershop pole, the spicy sweetness of cinnamon, and a hard candy crunch this old fashioned stick has it all. You can satisfy a spicy and sweet craving, stir them into a cup of hot cocoa or hot mulled cider for a unique twist, and even use them as an adorable decoration on a gingerbread house! There are just so many possibilities. And with 8 sticks in every package, there are enough to do it all. These classic sticks have been around for generations and still have the gusto to wow your friends and family.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/candy-sticks-cinnamon.jpg', '3692~candy-sticks-cinnamon.jpg', 'cinnamon-old-fashioned-stick-candy'),
(3693, 'Cinnamon Toothpicks', 19.99, '20', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Nothing tops off a good meal like a Cinnamon Toothpick to clean your teeth! Sit back, relax, and freshen your breath with these cinnamon flavored sticks. They are a great, flavorful tool to keep around the house for guests, to keep in your purse if you need one, or just to chew on if you love the cinnamony flavor! In reusable tubes, these pointy picks can be stored safely without worry of poking yourself or others. And when you\'re done, you can use the tube again to store some more! Bring some of these home today to help you attain a cleaner mouth and enjoy a taste of spicy cinnamon every time you use them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-toothpicks-20ct.gif', '3693~cinnamon-toothpicks-20ct.gif', 'cinnamon-toothpicks-20ct'),
(3694, 'Hot Tamales', 29.99, '24', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Jumpstart your taste buds with the spicy flavor of Hot Tamales candy! This classic treat is another Just Born creation. They are similar to the famous Mike & Ike candies, with a capsule shape and smooth texture.Each piece is delightfully chewy and soft, so they are easy to bite and enjoy. Unlike Mike & Ikes, Hot Tamales feature an intense cinnamon flavor that will set your tongue on fire (in a good way!).Our bulk Hot Tamales are a popular choice for events, gatherings and casual snacking. Each box contains many individual bags that are convenient for sharing, giving and eating. Take a bag or two with you so you always have a quick treat to eat while on the go.Use them to fill up party favors for birthday parties and other celebrations. Hot Tamales also make a great addition to this year\'s Halloween candy bowl. Order today and make your mouth tingle with the amazing taste of sizzling Hot Tamales!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-tamales-24ct_1.gif', '3694~hot-tamales-24ct_1.gif', 'hot-tamales-packs'),
(3695, 'Sugar Free Cinnamon Bears', 36.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Sugar free gummies? Is it really even possible? It sure is, and these chewy, bright red gummi bears pack a powerful cinnamon punch. They are hot enough to turn up the heat, but definitely not so hot that you want to stop with only one. We\'re sorry, but you\'re on your own to try to muster up self-control. :)These Sugar Free Cinnamon Bears are kosher certified, sweetened with Maltitol syrup and made in the USA. They are also the perfect candy dish companion for Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, and black tie events.Most people just need to hear the words cinnamon and gummi for their heart to start racing a little faster. Of course, for many, consuming sugar-laden candy is out of the question, so that excitement quickly turns to a blend of disappointment and sadness, sprinkled with a hint of anger. If this sounds like you, prepare to be doing cartwheels over this bulk supply of Sugar Free Cinnamon Bears.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-cinnamon-bears-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', '3695~sugar-free-cinnamon-bears-sweets-bulk_1.jpg', 'sugar-free-cinnamon-bears-sweets'),
(3696, 'Cinnamon Squares', 18.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Spice up your day with the irresistible taste of cinnamon squares candy! This unique treat will make your taste buds tingle while satisfying your sweet tooth! Each piece features a handsome square shape formed out of a delicious jelly candy.The outside is smothered in a generous dusting of sugar granules. Each bite starts with a sugary texture followed by smooth, chewy gummy candy! Watch out because these enticing little red squares pack a sizzling bite! Each is packed with cinnamon flavor that warms your mouth with spiciness.Make any occasion a little more exciting by serving our cinnamon squares to guests. Pour into a candy dish and you have a quick and easy snack when surprise visitors arrive.The beautiful red color is also a great choice when making wedding favors. Whether you\'re looking for a tasty Valentine\'s Day candy or a new stocking stuffer at Christmas, our cinnamon squares are sure to please!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/i/cinnamon-squares-sweets.jpg', '3696~cinnamon-squares-sweets.jpg', 'cinnamon-squares-bulk'),
(3697, 'Sweets Hot Shots', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'When sweet snacks won\'t do, you need to try our Sweets Hot Shots! This is the ultimate candy for anyone who loves spicy flavor. Don\'t be fooled by their small size and cute round shape.These bite-sized confections are real firecrackers! Each includes a solid orb of bright red deliciousness. Pop one in your mouth and experience the sizzling effects of this intense cinnamon candy!Make sure you have enough to put your friends to the cinnamon test by ordering Hot Shots in bulk! You receive many individual pieces that are perfect for parties, picnics and other gatherings. Pour them into a bowl then tempt your friends with the promise of something cinnamon-y.Or use them to make fun party favors to give out after a big event! Sweets Hot Shots are also an eye-catching way to decorate cakes, cookies and other baked goods. No matter how you serve them, Hot Shots is one cinnamon candy that is sure to heat things up!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/w/sweets-hot-shots.jpg', '3697~sweets-hot-shots.jpg', 'sweets-hot-shots'),
(3698, 'Tic Tac Candy', 23.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Classic Tic Tac mints in their awesome share-enducing dispensers. Give it a shake, tip your head back and enjoy the immense flavor of Tic Tac Candy! This bulk supply will allow you to do that over and over again until you have candy whiplash.With classic flavors of mint and orange, you can decide which one you love most and bring home a big supply of Tic Tac Candy. Drop a few boxes into your purse to freshen up your breath on the go, stash a box or two in your desk to snack on during the day, even keep some in the pantry at home to enjoy when you need a flavorful pick-me-up. When you stock up on these tasty Tic Tac Candies you\'ll have a ton of deliciousness for weeks to come.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/i/tic-tac-candy-24ct_1.jpg', '3698~tic-tac-candy-24ct_1.jpg', 'tic-tacs-packs'),
(3699, 'Ball of Fire Gumballs', 49.99, '1080', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Fire in the hole! These Ball of Fire Gumballs pack the heat of an active volcano and are ready to blow the top off of the roof of your mouth. Still interested? Then we think you\'re strong enough to handle this severe blaze.Created with a hotter than heck cinnamon flavor, you\'ll have to suck on these balls of fire until the inferno gives way to a sweeter cinnamon, gumball center. If you can last that long through the heat, then you\'ll be able to reward yourself with another, because this supply comes with tons and tons of red hot gumballs for you to eat.Now get ready to light a fire that just can\'t be extinguished when you order these incredibly spicy Ball of Fire Gumballs today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/a/ball-of-fire-gumballs-1080-ct_2.jpg', '3699~ball-of-fire-gumballs-1080-ct_2.jpg', 'gumballs-ball-of-fire'),
(3700, 'Juju Cinnamon Bears', 13.99, '5', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Juju Cinnamon Bears - 5lb', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/juju_cinnamon_bears_-_5lb.jpg', '3700~juju_cinnamon_bears_-_5lb.jpg', 'juju-cinnamon-bears'),
(3701, 'Gimbals Jelly Beans Spicy Cinnamon', 59.99, '10', 'lb', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'If the bright red color didn\'t give to a hint then let us. These Gimbals Spicy Cinnamon Jelly Beans are hot, hot, hot! With a bold and spicy cinnamon flavor, get ready to set your mouth ablaze as soon as you crunch down on the hard candy shell of these spicy jelly beans.Whether you chew fast or slow, you\'ll feel the burn until you\'ve successfully made it past the melting point and into the delicious sweet cinnamon reprieve that finishes off this bean\'s brazen flavor. Get ready for Christmas with a bulk order of our Gimbals Spicy Cinnamon Jelly Beans and dress up your candy dishes. Just make sure you give your guests a heads up before they head straight into the inferno that these beans light in your mouth!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/gimbals-jelly-beans-spicy-cinnamon-bulk_1.jpg', '3701~gimbals-jelly-beans-spicy-cinnamon-bulk_1.jpg', 'spicy-cinnamon-jelly-beans-gimbals'),
(3702, 'Sugar Free Cinnamon Hard Candy', 34.99, '12', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Your taste buds will tingle when they experience the flavor of GoLightly sugar free cinnamon hard candy! It\'s not easy to find treats that are healthy but still full of the flavors you love.GoLightly has created some of the most irresistible confections that fit the bill perfectly. You get the amazing taste you love in a convenient candy that\'s also sugar free and gluten free! Make dieting easier by using GoLightly sugar free hard candy as your go-to snack when sweet cravings start. Don\'t struggle and feel deprived all day lone when you can satisfy your sweet tooth with these unique little morsels.Our bulk GoLightly candy is the easiest way to get larger quantities so you never have to go without your emergency sugar fix! When you feel satisfied, you are more likely to stick to your diet and achieve your health goals. Try our delicious cinnamon hard candy or any of our other GoLightly sugar free flavors!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/u/sugar-free-cinnamon-peg-bag.jpg', '3702~sugar-free-cinnamon-peg-bag.jpg', 'sugar-free-cinnamon-hard-candy-go-lightly'),
(3703, 'Jalapeno Lix Lollipops', 37.99, '36', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'Tempt your taste buds with the intense flavor of these sizzling jalapeno Lix lollipops by Hotlix! Hotlix is known for their novelty candies. From hard candy filled with scorpions and crickets to unusual flavors made with real peppers!Each is made with high quality ingredients and includes a distinctive look that is a great conversation starter at parties and gatherings. Our jalapeno lollipops in bulk is a great choice for events. Find out who has the toughest taste buds by offering these around when friends stop by.They also make unique party favors for any fun fiesta. Each piece includes a disposable stick with a jalapeno shaped top in dark green. Take a lick and experience actual jalapeno peppers in a lollipop! This is one of the most intense treats you can put in your mouth. Make sure you have a glass of milk nearby because you are going to need it!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jalapeno-lix-lollipops-36ct.gif', '3703~jalapeno-lix-lollipops-36ct.gif', 'jalapeno-lix-lollipops'),
(3704, 'Hot Dog Cinnamon Bubblegum', 17.99, '72', 'ct', 'cinnamon-red-hot', 'In the world of bubblegum cinnamon is a basic flavor, why not put it in a hot dog link and make it quirky and unique. Hot Dog Cinnamon Bubblegum did just that. Invented in the 1950s and made popular in the 196\'s, this retro candy will have nostalgic adults and young whipper snappers grinning from ear to ear. This gum packs a powerful flavor punch disguised in a small hot dog shaped package. Hot Dog Bubble gum is perfect for decorative additions to any edible holiday decor. For Businesses they are a great addition to that candy fundraiser in the break room, or lobby. Sell them for 5 cents apiece and watch your goals. Each pack comes with two hot dog links that double as two pieces of gum. Hot Dog Cinnamon Bubblegum comes in a retro style display box and contains 72 packs of links for 144 hot dogs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/hot-dog-cinnamon-bubblegum-72ct.gif', '3704~hot-dog-cinnamon-bubblegum-72ct.gif', 'hot-dog-cinnamon-bubblegum'),
(3705, 'White Wedding Mints', 21.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Here comes the bride! Make your special day all the more memorable with these delicate mints. With their delicious, smooth texture and refreshing taste, it\'ll be easy to say \'\'I do.\'\' Set them out at the reception as a beautiful centerpiece or use them in party favors. You can even pop one in your mouth before you walk down the aisle to make your first kiss as man and wife as sweet as the day you met. Their pristine, pearly coloring will match the white of any wedding and set your ceremony apart from any and all of the rest.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/y/dynamite-white-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', '3705~dynamite-white-mints-5lbs_1.jpg', 'white-wedding-mints-mighty'),
(3706, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Don\'t bite down on one of these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers! These hard candies are great for savoring a ton of sweetness for a long time.Buy a bulk bag of Jaw Busters hard candies for the little ghouls and goblins coming around the neighborhood on Halloween, or keep them around when you\'re craving something sweet for yourself. You can keep a bag of Jawbreakers in a wide assortment of colors and flavors all year long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', '3706~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-wrapped'),
(3707, 'M&M\'s Single Color', 56.99, '', '', 'coated', 'We\'re positive that you know this candy, but do you know what it stands for? M&Ms; Candy was named after Forest Mars and his business partner, Bruce Murrie in 1941. And we\'re sure glad these two got together to cook up such a delicious treat because these melty milk chocolate candies are one of our favorites.In a rainbow of colors from blue, to yellow, to red and many more, these tiny morsels will provide you wish a tasty and pretty snack! Stock up on some to cook into baked goods, add some to a pinata, make up goodie bags for friends and family, and more. Bring some bulk M&M\'s candies home today and see why this candy has stood the test of time.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/m/mms-colors-main-my-mms.jpg', '3707~mms-colors-main-my-mms.jpg', 'mms-individual-colors'),
(3708, 'Red Cherry Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Red cherry fruit sours candy is a great addition to any holiday spread. Let\'s face it; red goes with almost any occasion. It\'s the perfect color addition to Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, the Fourth of July, and it even works for a  bloody  element to Halloween. Red cherry fruit sours explode in your mouth with tartness and sweetness. These delicious candies are sure to be a hit with all your sour-loving friends at your next party.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-cherry-fruit-sours-candy-balls-75lb_2.jpg', '3708~red-cherry-fruit-sours-candy-balls-75lb_2.jpg', 'red-cherry-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(3709, 'Boston Baked Beans', 6.99, '24', 'ct', 'coated', 'These beans are more than meets the eye. That\'s because in every one of these Boston Baked Beans Candies awaits a whole peanut and hard candy shell. And coated in a rusty red, they\'re even pretty to look at too.Order some of this Boston Baked Beans Candy and you can stock the candy dishes in your home, add an unexpected treat to baked goods like cookies or even use some on top of ice cream sundaes. Crush some of these Boston Baked Beans Candies up and you\'ll even have yourself a delicious, confetti-like topping for cakes and iced treats. If you love peanuts and crunchy candy, then whip up some trail mix, get people together to indulge in a candy buffet or just order some of these Boston Baked Beans Candies to treat yourself!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/o/boston_baked_beans_-_24ct.jpg', '3709~boston_baked_beans_-_24ct.jpg', 'boston-baked-beans-mini-boxes'),
(3710, 'White M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'This little confection is the proud winner of the candy color popularity contest time after time. That\'s because these irresistible White M&Ms; match most occasions and have the rich, melty milk chocolatey taste that candy is famous for. Bring some to a wedding, add a few to a candy buffet bar to match any color scheme, or even use them in baking for a bright white look. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/white-mms_1.jpg', '3710~white-mms_1.jpg', 'white-mms'),
(3711, 'Green Watermelon Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'We think these candies are \'\'de-vine.\'\' A real knee-slapper we know, but in all seriousness, these Pink Watermelon Fruit Sours Candies taste like they\'re fresh off the vine. Covered in a beautiful, glossy pink shell and complete with a soft, fruity chew, these candies are cultivated by using some of the sweetest techniques in the candy biz. Use some for a light sweet at a backyard picnic, bring some to a gathering of friends, even use them for a lovely addition to an outdoor wedding. For watermelon and candy enthusiasts, alike, this bag will provide you with hours and hours of happy snacking.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/0/8/08017-_watermelon_sours.png', '3711~08017-_watermelon_sours.png', 'pink-watermelon-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(3712, 'Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 25.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Wooooweee! These tart purple candies deliver an unrelenting pucker with delicious, fruity flavor. If you like a sour shot to the mouth, try our Purple Grape Fruit Sours Candy. The sourest candy on the vine, these little pucker-packed candies will please every sour lover. Bring some to a purple themed party, add some to a lemonade for a sour grape flavor addition and pretty garnish, or keep them around the house when you\'re in the mood for a feisty snack. Their deep, purple coloring may look unsuspecting, but get ready for a dose of tartness that will thrill your taste buds!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '3712~purple-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'purple-grape-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(3713, 'Jelly Belly Jelly Beans', 78.99, '10', 'lb', 'coated', 'Oh, behold the possibilities! With 50 original flavors plus even more limited-edition beans, concoct combination after combination of inventive candy recipes with this bulk bag of Jelly Belly jelly beans. Maybe you have a hankering for chocolate covered banana, vanilla espresso or coconut orange. Whatever your signature recipe, you can be the chef with the pick of the littler of hundreds of beans brimming with unique flavor. The Jelly Belly company has been around since 1976 and has honed their talent in producing tantilizing flavors that have pleased customers for years. See why for yourself why they are an American favorite with this bulk bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/e/jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', '3713~jelly-belly-main-product.jpg', 'jelly-belly-jelly-beans'),
(3714, 'Purple M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Purple purists, unite! Our bulk, mono-hued M&Ms; are just the ticket to satisfy your purple palate. Your friends might wonder how you found the time to sift through bags and bags of candy in search of one color, but you\'ll just sit back, relax, and snack happily knowing it was as simple as purchasing them here. Since M&Ms; launched their line of customizable candies, chocolate lovers around the world have been able to spruce up any event or snacktime with their favorite colors. They make great personalized gifts and add the perfect touch of personality to any home\'s candy bowl.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple-mms_1.jpg', '3714~purple-mms_1.jpg', 'purple-mms'),
(3715, 'Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy Balls', 22.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Pucker up, buttercup! These Orange Tangerine Fruit Sours Candy have a mighty mix of sour and sweet to delight the mouths of many. Soft, chewy, tangy, and gorgeous, the bright mix of candy balls is a cheerful dose of sugar and citrus. Use them for an autumn inspired gift basket, on the Thanksgiving dessert table, or even as sour additions to a trick-or-treat stash. They can even make a summertime festival even more special by adding the beautiful color of the hot sun. There is no wrong way for your friends and family to enjoy these fruity, delicious and sour candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', '3715~orange-fruit-sours-small.jpg', 'orange-tangerine-fruit-sours-candy-balls'),
(3716, 'Fun Size M&Ms Milk Chocolate', 32.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Get the party started with these Fun Size Packs of M&Ms;! Great for Halloween trick-or-treating, birthday parties, or just to enjoy as a perfectly portioned snack, this bulk bag is ready to add some delicious flavor to your life and those you share them with.Get your bag today to add some extra deliciousness and magic into your every day snacking. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsize_m_ms.jpg', '3716~funsize_m_ms.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-milk-chocolate'),
(3717, 'Blue M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Mmmmmm. These amazing Blue M&Ms; will put you into a delirium of melty, milk chocolatey bliss for hours and hours. That\'s because this bulk bag is packed with over 45 pieces per pound! That\'s a lot of delicious candy to savor, so they\'re perfect to share with friends and family. Bring them to a baby shower for a boy, a Hanukah celebration, or even a Fourth of July backyard BBQ.Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-mms_1.jpg', '3717~blue-mms_1.jpg', 'blue-mms'),
(3718, 'Skittles Fun Size Bulk', 99.99, '22', 'lb', 'coated', 'A color and flavor for every taste bud. Pack these fun size Skittles into a pinata, add them to a stocking, or slip one into your kid\'s lunchbox for a delicious afternoon surprise. Whatever you choose, everyone will love to \'\'Taste the Rainbow.\'\' Skittles have been in the US since 1979 and have evolved into a quirky brand and a household name. Their original flavors of orange, lemon, lime, grape and strawberry got a revamp in 1989 with the introduction of tropical fruit flavors. Since then, 1 new Skittles lines have been created and amazed the mouths of people all over the world.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/k/skittles-fun-size.jpg', '3718~skittles-fun-size.jpg', 'skittles-fun-size-bulk'),
(3719, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 79.49, '25', 'lb', 'coated', 'Ouch! Yum! Ouch! Yum! Your mouth might be confused with the tough love these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers dish out, but we don\'t think you\'ll mind because of their delicious flavor. A classic candy with an extremely hard shell, these fruity treats aren\'t as mean as they look. They\'ll slowly melt away in your mouth for hours, treating you to a delicious fruity flavor in a variety of colors. Bring some to a birthday party for a long lasting treat, pack some into a candy machine for a retro look, or set some out on your coffee table for your strong-jawed friends to try. This may be one tough, candy, but we think you\'ll find it\'s nice side, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', '3719~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470_1.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-bulk-case'),
(3720, 'Red M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Behold, the color of love! These Red M&Ms; will ignite a fire in your heart and fill you with mushy, romantic thoughts. Stock yourself up for Valentine\'s Day to spoil your sweeties, add handfuls of these famous chocolate morsels to holiday baked goods, or even use these vibrant M&Ms; for a wedding to amplify the love between bride and groom. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-mms_1.jpg', '3720~red-mms_1.jpg', 'red-mms'),
(3721, 'Pink M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Did you know that you can buy M&Ms; in single-color bulk bags? Pink M&Ms; are the perfect addition to a baby shower when the mom-to-be is expecting a little girl. These delicious pink chocolates that won\'t melt in your hand are also perfect for birthdays, Easter, wedding showers, and any other occasion that calls for something sweet and pink. You could even put them together with some other delicious pink and red treats for a Valentine\'s Day surprise.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-mms_1.jpg', '3721~pink-mms_1.jpg', 'pink-mms'),
(3722, 'Peanut M&Ms 42oz Bag', 19.99, '', '', 'coated', 'Easy to crave and easy to eat, Peanut M&Ms; are a well-known classic candy for good reason! With their three layers of confection â€“ a colorful candy shell, a rich chocolate filling, and a lovable peanut heart â€“ Peanut M&Ms; provide hunger-satisfying nuts along with sweet-tooth-satisfying coatings. Piled in a dish, these candies quickly disappear, but while they remain their colorful appearance and perfect bite size give a thoughtful, cheery look to your candy bowl.The resealable bag in which these Peanut M&Ms; are packaged makes it easy to keep them on hand for family movie night snacking, or they\'re convenient to stash in a cool spot in the car if you anticipate needing a quick snack on the go. Fresh in their zippered bag, these M&Ms; candies make sure you\'re always ready to offer a sweet treat to unexpected guests, and adding a few to a lunch bag (or improving the morale at a long business meeting) has never been easier than with this bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/peanut-mms-42oz-bag_2.jpg', '3722~peanut-mms-42oz-bag_2.jpg', 'peanut-mms-bulk'),
(3723, 'Silver M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Fancy, schmancy. These Silver M&Ms; are exactly that with their illustrious silver sheen and delicious chocolatey crunch. Bring some of these beautiful silver M&Ms; to any event to add some instant drama and glamour. These classic candies make a great selection for wedding candy, look great around the holidays when paired with gold candies, and even can make a winter party even more magical. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/silver-mms_1.jpg', '3723~silver-mms_1.jpg', 'silver-mms'),
(3724, 'Dark Pink M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Pretty in pink. Girly and sweet. Sure are! Mars has taken their product to the next level with this sweet combination of M&Ms; pink candy shell and milky chocolatey center. They make the perfect addition to baby showers, bachelorette parties, and even breast cancer awareness events. Founded in the 1930s, M&Ms; have evolved through the years, getting their signature \'\'M\'\' in the 1950s, adding different flavors along the way, and in the past several years, adding a customizable option with a rainbow of colors. We\'re glad they have added these personalized pink variety and are sure you\'ll love them too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/a/dark-pink-mms_1.jpg', '3724~dark-pink-mms_1.jpg', 'dark-pink-mms'),
(3725, 'M&Ms Milk Chocolate 42oz Bag', 19.99, '', '', 'coated', 'If you love M&M;\'s then you will really love the fact that you are able to get your favorite milk chocolate candy in a bag that contains 42 ounces of candy and is able to be resealed. These candies are bite sized and are great for parties, flights, trips that include long drives, over night parties, game night, and even for a gift basket to tell someone that you hope they get well soon. You are able to get the great taste that you love and be able to reseal the bag to make sure that they stay fresh for as long as possible. If you have a sweet tooth, with a bag this large, you are sure to find that you will be able to meet that sweet tooth time and time again. This means no more trips to the store in the middle of the night but instead you can just reopen the bag.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/m/mms-milk-chocolate-42oz-bag_2.jpg', '3725~mms-milk-chocolate-42oz-bag_2.jpg', 'mms-milk-chocolate-42oz-bag'),
(3726, 'Orange M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'M&Ms; have been tempting young and old alike for decades. This world-renowned chocolate confection was originally created in the 1930s but really came into its own during World War II, when the design was practical for storing and eating chocolate. The brand has spread immensely since then, with the familiar black M logo added in 1950 and new fillings introduced in the years that followed. No matter how many times they innovate this timeless treat, everyone still look for the classic M&Ms; that made the candy so popular.Our bulk M&M; packages present solid-color quantities for events and more! Our vibrant orange M&Ms; are perfect for autumn parties, Halloween events, birthdays and any other occasion. Use them in party favors or serve in a glass dish to decorate tables and entice guests. We also carry other M&M; colors so you can combine two or more to create the perfect blend of hues for weddings, showers and any other important celebration!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/r/orange-mms_1.jpg', '3726~orange-mms_1.jpg', 'orange-mms'),
(3727, 'Sixlets 20 Ball Tubes', 11.99, '48', 'ct', 'coated', 'Sixlets 20 ball tubes are the most convenient way to enjoy your favorite chocolate candy! Every stick includes a clear wrapper that holds 20 round balls in a straight line. Take a bite out of green, yellow, orange, red or brown.No matter which hue you choose, every Sixlets candy contains a smooth chocolate center surrounded by a hard candy shell. Our bulk Sixlets box contains a generous number of full tubes so you have plenty to take or share.Individually wrapped candy is perfect for traveling and events. Tuck a few in your vehicle\'s glove box, your purse or carry on. You can also display them in glass vases or trays to serve at parties, school activities and other gatherings. Buying Sixlets in bulk is also a great way to ensure that you always have an easy, tasty snack on hand when chocolate cravings hit!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', '3727~sixlets-20-ball-tubes-48ct.gif', 'sixlets-20-ball-tubes'),
(3728, 'Black M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Black M&Ms; are not your typical chocolate candy. This dark and mysterious hue is perfect for a wide range of events. Use with orange or purple M&Ms; for Halloween celebrations or combine with any other color to serve in candy dishes at wedding receptions. Every piece includes the classic chocolate center and hard candy shell that makes M&Ms; such a popular treat. Unlike the candies you buy at the store, our bulk M&Ms; are available in different colors so you can find the perfect pieces to go with any event!There\'s something luxurious and formal about the sleek shine of ebony candy coating. Order a bag to add fine detail to your next event. Whether you serve them at the food table or include them as part of your party or wedding favors, everyone will admire the captivating texture and color that comes with every handful of our exquisite black M&Ms;!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/black-mms_1.jpg', '3728~black-mms_1.jpg', 'black-mms'),
(3729, 'Runts Candy', 94.99, '30', 'lb', 'coated', 'Runts candy made its first appearance in the 1980s. While its fruity lineup has changed since then, its popularity has not. Every kid can recognize the fun shapes and bright colors that make Runts so unique. Our extensive collection of bulk candy includes this childhood favorite so you can get your fill of sweet fruity goodness anytime you want! Serve at kid\'s parties, take as a non-perishable snack on camping trips or set some aside to hide away at home for moments when you need a sweet fix!Our Runts candy package include all the current flavors and shapes. You\'ll love biting down on a yellow banana or savoring a tart cherry piece. Each order also includes blue raspberry, watermelon and lime. Try the smooth, sweet taste of your favorite fruits followed by the tantalizing tanginess that makes Runts candies so delectable. You don\'t have to go to a vending machine to find your favorite treat because we have Runts in bulk and ready to ship right to you!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/u/runts30lbs.jpg', '3729~runts30lbs.jpg', 'runts-bulk'),
(3730, 'Hot Pink Sixlets', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'These glamorous Pink Sixlets chocolates are almost too pretty to eat! Almost... But eat them we shall with their pleasant crunch followed by a creamy milk chocolate center. Tinier than M&Ms; at about a third of the size, these little wonders can still satisfy every sweet tooth  big and small. Set them out in a bowl in your office, use them as a wedding candy buffet item, or add some extra girliness to a baby or bridal shower. Whatever you decide to do with these lovely, little gems, we are sure that you and your friends will love looking at them as much as eating them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3730~sixlets-pink-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-pink'),
(3731, 'Silver Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'These sophisticated chocolates are almost too pretty to eat! Almost... But eat them we shall with their pleasant crunch followed by a creamy milk chocolate center. Tinier than M&Ms; at about a third of the size, these little wonders can still satisfy every sweet tooth big and small. Set them out in a bowl in your office, use them as a wedding candy buffet item, or give them away as a glamorous gift. Whatever you decide to do with these lovely, little gems, we are sure that you and your friends will love looking at them as much as eating them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-silver-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3731~sixlets-silver-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-silver'),
(3732, 'Yellow M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'Yellow M&Ms; make the perfect spring or summer candy choice. They\'re the color of sunshine and springtime, and they taste just as sweet as feeling a cool breeze on your face in late April. These melt-in-your-mouth classics are perfect for an Easter outing, your candy dish at home or the office, or on a dessert buffet at your next party. They\'ll look especially gorgeous when placed in a pastel setting, pleasing both the eye and the mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/e/yellow-mms_1.jpg', '3732~yellow-mms_1.jpg', 'yellow-mms'),
(3733, 'White Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'White Sixlets are perfect for any occasion and would even look wonderful for a wedding event. These candies contain a white, sugary, crunch, outside coating with smooth chocolate on the inside that is sure to please. The great milk chocolate flavor that this candy offers is hard to beat.It makes a perfect choice for children as well as adults. These are completely round in their shape, like a small ball, but have a taste that is similar to that of M&M;\'s. This is a large bulk bag which means that you can ensure that there will be plenty of these to go around. The taste of these candies is sweet and enjoyable and sure to kick jump your taste buds into high gear. You can also be sure to find that your mouth will be smiling form the great taste after you take part in a few of these wonderful candies.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-white-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3733~sixlets-white-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-white'),
(3734, 'Royal Blue Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'If you are looking for Sixlets in a fun and exciting color then you may just find that royal blue Sixlets are what you have been looking for. These are fun colored on the outside and the inside is a delicious chocolate center that is sure to please anyone! The outside is a crunchy textured shell and once you make it to the inside you are sure to find the great texture of the sweet and creamy chocolate. This is sure to make your mouth water and please all of your taste buds. This bulk box is great for parties because there is sure to be enough to go around. You will also find that adults like this candy just as much as children do. Aside from a party you can use this great colored candy at a wedding or even at a baby shower for someone who has a little boy on the way!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-royal-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3734~sixlets-royal-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-royal-blue'),
(3735, 'Bulk M&Ms', 129.99, '25', 'lb', 'coated', 'M&Ms; are one of the most popular chocolate candies available today. While this confection is usually considered a tasty modern treat, it\'s actually enjoyed a long, rich history that dates back to the 1930s.During that time, the founder of the Mars candy company noticed that Spanish soldiers would eat chocolate pellets. These included tempered chocolate that was resistant to melting. He decided to take the idea to the next level and created a candy that used Hershey chocolate!Each round M&Ms; candy consists of a delicious chocolate center surrounded by a hard panned coating. Each piece comes in a handful of vibrant colors, including orange, red, yellow, green, dark brown and blue. Our bulk M&Ms; pack includes all the original hues in a large quantity that\'s perfect for events and celebrations.Use them to decorate cakes, cookies and more during the holidays or prepare for a special occasion by creating party or wedding favor with M&Ms;! Anytime is a great time to share the chocolaty taste of classic M&Ms; candies!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/m/mms-bulk-25-pounds.jpg', '3735~mms-bulk-25-pounds.jpg', 'mms-bulk-case');
INSERT INTO `candy` (`id`, `title`, `price`, `amount`, `units`, `category`, `description`, `original_image_url`, `local_image`, `page`) VALUES
(3736, 'Light Blue M&Ms Candy', 56.99, '5', 'lb', 'coated', 'If you are planning a baby shower for a boy then this would make a great option to have at the party. These M&M;\'s have a light blue color that looks great! They have the same great taste that everyone loves when it comes to M&M;\'s however and that is a nice milk chocolaty taste. These are must have for any event or occasion, as they would also go well with a birthday party for a boy. Since they are light blue you may even be able to consider using them a girl as well depending on the other colors that were used with them. Adults and children alike love the taste of these great candies and are sure to be pleased with them. There is just something about these candies that are able to tickle your taste buds in just the right way and that is what really makes them a favorite of many.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/light-blue-mms_1.jpg', '3736~light-blue-mms_1.jpg', 'light-blue-mms'),
(3737, 'Navy Blue Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'What better color to have for Sixlets than a navy blue. This is a great color and would be great for any patriotic or military event. You will even find that these would work great for many other special occasions, parties, and events as well. There is just something to be said about the fine taste that you get from these balls of milk chocolate. The texture is great too because of the candy coating. You are able to bite into the candy and have a bit of crunch that is then followed by the great silky milk chocolate that just melts away in your mouth. These can even be great to keep around the house in case you find that you begin to have a craving for something sweet, as these candies are sure to be able to handle the craving that you are having and much more as you enjoy their wonderful taste.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-navy-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3737~sixlets-navy-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-navy-blue'),
(3738, 'Fun Size M&Ms Peanut', 36.99, '5.75', 'lb', 'coated', 'Everyone one loves fun size M&Ms;, they are perfect for a quick sweet treat; just the right size so you don\'t over eat. Fun Size Peanut M&Ms; are one of the most popular candies Mars offers. They are perfect when just a few M&Ms; are needed for added edible decoration. They are the perfect amount for kids treat bags at parties, Trick-R-Treating at Halloween and in classrooms as prizes and incentives. Every teacher knows candy treats are good but, too much equals disaster. These smooth hard shelled candies give the perfect crunch followed by delicious chocolaty goodness and finished with a salty peanut in the center which all adds up to perfection. Fun Size Peanut M&Ms; work as stocking stuffers, in Easter baskets, and can be easily attached to a Valentine.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsizepeanut_1.jpg', '3738~funsizepeanut_1.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-peanut'),
(3739, 'Powder Blue Sixlets Candy', 22.99, '2', 'lb', 'coated', 'These powder blue Sixlets chocolates are the prettiest belles at the ball! Smaller than M&Ms;, Sixlets are the perfect dose of hard shell crunch and melty milk chocolate in a miniature form. Use some on top of a cake for a pop of powder blue pizazz, add them to a make your own sundae bar, bring them to a celebration of the birth of a baby boy, or even add them to a blue themed event like the Fourth of July! No matter what you decide to do with these lovely, little gems, we are sure that you and your friends will love looking at them as much as eating them.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/i/sixlets-powder-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', '3739~sixlets-powder-blue-bulk-10lb.jpg', 'sixlets-powder-blue'),
(3740, 'Fun Size M&Ms Milk Chocolate Case', 114.99, '20', 'lb', 'coated', 'These little candies are the life of the party! That\'s because these Fun Size M&Ms; are the perfect size to be enjoyed as a special snack any day of the week. These pint size packages make these candies ideal for a Halloween trick-or-treating selection, tucked into a piï¾ata, kept around the house to satisfy a small sweet tooth, or even to be put into gift baskets. Since 1941, M&Ms; button-sized shape, hard candy crunch, and milk chocolate meltiness have been pleasing palates near and far. See for yourself why these \'\'melt in your mouth, not in your hand\'\' classics have made their way into America\'s hearts and stomachs.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/u/funsize_m_ms_1.jpg', '3740~funsize_m_ms_1.jpg', 'fun-size-mms-milk-chocolate-case'),
