(3742, 'Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates Tub', 22.99, '240', 'ct', 'foil-wrapped', 'When you think of classy candy then immediately Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates jump to mind. These delicious treats have been sold in a delightful and recognizable green wrapping. When a person sees that wrapping they know that wherever they are, it is a place filled with class. It could be a restaurant that provides a free snack with the bill. It could be left on the pillow in a hotel. Even if it is in your own home the person who sees the shiny green wrapper will know that they are dealing with a person and a place that knows class. The chocolate treat is the reason for this as it provides a delicious chocolate treat with the blast of creamy goodness that shakes your taste buds and zaps them awake. There is just the right minty freshness to allow you to feel refreshed. There will always be enough class around with a tub of Andes Creme De Menthe Chocolates.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/n/andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub-240ct_1.jpg', '3742~andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub-240ct_1.jpg', 'andes-creme-de-menthe-chocolates-tub'),
(3743, 'Chocolate Cigars', 24.99, '24', 'ct', 'foil-wrapped', 'Back in the day, no trip to the delivery room was complete without a celebratory cigar. Nowadays, you can spread the joy of the birth of a new baby in a yummier and healthier way with these Chocolate Cigars. They are an innocent and delicious way to celebrate any exciting occasion, look official in their bright, gold wrappers, and come in traditional, little boxes that resemble the humidors of old. In every amazing box, you can enjoy rich, melty chocolate that\'s perfect for celebrating a growing family. Puff, savor, and celebrate with every delicious chocolate cigar in this bulk selection.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/gold_chocolate_cigars.jpg', '3743~gold_chocolate_cigars.jpg', 'chocolate-cigars'),
(3744, 'Red Milk Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'The mere sight of these will have you longing for Valentine\'s Day. Although these Red Milk Chocolate Hearts are the perfect candy or the year\'s most romantic day, you certainly don\'t have to wait until February to enjoy them.They are popular for weddings, engagement parties, bridal showers, and New Year\'s Eve parties, too. A lot of love goes into making these mouthwatering Red Chocolate Hearts. The delectable chocolate sauce is poured into molds and left to harden.Then, they are carefully wrapped with shiny red foil.Since they are all individually wrapped they\'re appropriate for any candy dish. You can even pour some in small jars, add a pretty ribbon, and hand them out to all your friends who don\'t have sweetheart to spend Valentine\'s Day with. Your mom, sister, aunt, and cousin will surely love them, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', '3744~red-milk-chocolate-hearts-5lb_2.jpg', 'red-milk-chocolate-hearts'),
