(3747, 'Lindt Chocolate Lindor Truffles', 49.99, '120', 'ct', 'foil-wrapped', 'Savor every rich bite of our Lindt chocolate Lindor truffles! Exquisitely smooth and irresistibly chocolaty, these delectable round candies are simply irresistible. Pamper your taste buds by biting into the classic chocolate shell to sample the creamy confection hidden deep inside. We carry the finest Lindt truffles flavors, including luxurious dark chocolate, sweet hazelnut, traditional milk chocolate, refreshing mint, delightful peanut butter, sensational raspberry and dark chocolate and scrumptious white chocolate. We make it easy to get all the Lindt chocolate truffles you need for any occasion. Our bulk candy packs are wonderful for serving at parties or as part of beautiful wedding favors. Treat your beloved guests to the heavenly taste that makes Lindor truffles so desirable! Every piece is individually packaged in a colorful wrapper with the elegant Lindt brand clearly displayed. Simply untwist the ends and you have a chocolate truffle treat that is unlike any other!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/lindor-truffles-main.jpg', '3747~lindor-truffles-main.jpg', 'lindt-chocolate-lindor-truffles'),
(3748, 'Milk Chocolate Long Stem Red Roses', 129.99, '36', 'ct', 'foil-wrapped', 'Designed to look like long stem roses, but filled with a flower made of incredible milk chocolate, these foil wrapped Milk Chocolate Long Stem Red Roses are the perfect mix of delicious and thoughtful.Feel the love during Valentine\'s Day season when you bring these chocolate roses home. Give one to a special someone, make a huge bouquet for someone who has your whole heart, even leave some on the desks of co-workers to make everyone feel loved. Milk Chocolate Long Stem Red Roses also make great get well basket additions and raffle items because of their unique nature and amazing chocolate taste.Be prepared for lots of hugs and kisses when you give these roses away to the ones you love!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/milkchocolatelongstem.jpg', '3748~milkchocolatelongstem.jpg', 'milk-chocolate-long-stem-red-roses'),
