(3759, 'Milk Chocolate Gold Coins Medium Size', 136.99, '10', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'This 5-pound supply of Milk Chocolate Gold Coins is perfect to hand out at nearly any event. Fill a treasure chest with them for a pirate-themed birthday party.Use them as a snack at your next poker party, include them in a gift bag, or hand them out at Halloween. These Milk Chocolate Gold Coins are about the size of a quarter, and the highly detailed gold foil makes them look like real currency. There are hundreds of coins in this bulk supply, which should be more than enough for any celebration.Although great for a party, you don\'t need to be planning a special event to order these Milk Chocolate Gold Coins. Stock your candy jar with them and you\'ll always have a quick bite size snack handy when you need to satisfy a little sugar craving. These medium size yummy chocolate coins are certified kosher, making them an ideal Hanukkah gift, too.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', '3759~milk-chocolate-gold-coins---medium-10lb_1.gif', 'milk-chocolate-gold-coins-medium'),
