(3764, 'Chocolate Flower Candies', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Chocolate flower candies are just as delicious as they are elegant. This unique confection features a gorgeous look that will dress up any candy dish or dessert table. Each piece is made of high quality milk chocolate that\'s shaped into a solid disc.Each round coin piece is covered in a layer of shimmering foil with a dazzling floral pattern. Our assortment features light pink and red flowers with stylish green leaves and pink, green, silver and purple background. Keep our chocolate flower candies on hand as an easy snack you can serve guests who happen by.They look fabulous at tea parties and brunches. Balance one on a saucer with a tea cup or place at table settings for a fancy dinner. These flower chocolates are also a beautiful choice for DIY wedding favors. Pour into tulle bags or a small gift box or use them to put the finishing touches on a summer or spring celebration!Approximately 55 pieces per pound', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/download_2_.jpeg', '3764~download_2_.jpeg', 'chocolate-flower-candies'),
(3765, 'Chocolate Crayon Boxes', 74.99, '24', 'ct', 'foil-wrapped', 'You won\'t have to worry about your little ones coloring on the walls with these Chocolate Crayon Boxes. That\'s because they\'ll be too busy unwrapping, indulging, and devouring them to even think about an impromptu artistic experience. If your little ones love art class and drawing, then surprise them with Chocolate Crayon Boxes. They make great additions to lunch boxes on the first day of school, can be given out to students if you\'re a doting teacher, or can be sold at a school function to raise money. Because of their adorable nature and deliciousness, these Chocolate Crayon Boxes can fill practically any candy need that you want them to.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-crayon-boxes-24ct_2.jpg', '3765~chocolate-crayon-boxes-24ct_2.jpg', 'chocolate-crayon-boxes'),
(3766, 'Fort Knox It\'s A Boy Coins', 13.99, '1', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Fort Knox Itâ€™s a Boy chocolate coins are a fun way to let friends and family know the gender of your new little one. Each piece consists of delicious milk chocolate candy in a disc shape. A baby blue foil wrapper covers the outside, keeping the candy fresh with a fun stork design. The flip side reads â€œItâ€™s a Boy!â€. Our Fort Knox chocolate coins are perfect for baby showers and gender reveals!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/fort_knox_its_a_boy_coins_-_1lb.jpeg', '3766~fort_knox_its_a_boy_coins_-_1lb.jpeg', 'fort-knox-its-a-boy-coins'),
(3767, 'White Foil Chocolate Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'If the key to someone\'s heart is through their stomach, then what happens when that edible is also heart-shaped and milk chocolate with gorgeous white foil? They\'re clear so much room in their heart for you that they will love you forever!With these White Foil Chocolate Hearts, get ready to make your heart pitter patter every time you take a bite. In melty white chocolate, they\'re the perfect treat to stock up on fro weddings or Valentine\'s Day. Or if you\'re planning on baking something sweet, use these chocolate hearts to decorate the top of a cake or to bring over to someone as a get well treat. Order some for yourself and let these White Chocolate Foil Hearts melt your heart today.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/white-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '3767~white-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'white-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(3768, 'Bronze Dark Chocolate Hearts', 59.99, '5', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Bronze dark chocolate hearts are a simple candy that\'s absolutely breathtaking to see! Each piece is designed to offer a versatile yet beautiful appearance that hides a delicious piece of dark chocolate.Just like our other chocolate hearts, this version is covered in a thin foil wrapper that\'s a shimmering bronze hue. The surface looks gorgeous in any lighting or setting! Simply unwrap the bronze foil and take a bite of rich, delectable dark chocolate!Each smooth heart candy is made of solid dark chocolate so you get more of the candy you love without an unnecessary fluff. Our bulk chocolate hearts pack gives you many pieces that are convenient for special occasions. Hearts are always a great choice for Valentine\'s Day and wedding favors.Our bronze dark chocolate hearts are especially versatile. Serve them to guests at Christmas, birthday parties or keep them at home as a quick and easy treat.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/r/bronze-dark-chocolate-hearts-5lbs.gif', '3768~bronze-dark-chocolate-hearts-5lbs.gif', 'bronze-dark-chocolate-hearts'),
(3769, 'Light Pink Foil Hearts Bulk', 99.99, '10', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Dazzle guests or loved one with the gorgeous shimmer of our light pink foil heart chocolates! This practical treat offers gourmet flavor in a beautiful package. Impress everyone with a stunning presentation and a decoration that can literally be eaten!Pour them into glass bowls or jars and set out on tables at a reception or birthday party or use them as elegant Easter basket candy. Each light pink foil heart includes a mouthful of solid gourmet chocolate. The shape includes a basic heart with curved sides and a pointed bottom.The back is flat while the front is three dimensional to provide a thicker profile and more chocolate in every piece. A thin layer of light pink foil covers the surface, adding a metallic shine to the finished product. Our bulk light pink chocolate hearts are just one of the many colors we offer! Use pink alone at girls birthday parties or baby showers or combine with our other foil covered heart colors.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/i/pink-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '3769~pink-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'pink-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(3770, 'Milk Chocolate Gold Gelt Coins Assorted Sizes', 139.99, '10', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'We have enough Milk Chocolate Gold Gelt Coins here to fill Fort Knox! You\'ll feel richer the moment you bring them home because of their brilliant, gold foil wrappers that are designed to look like coins and the tasty, melty chocolate that awaits within.Are you a poker player or fan of a casino night with friends now and again? Why not sweeten the potâ€”literallyâ€”by ordering some of these Milk Chocolate Gold Gelt Coins and adding them to the stakes. They also make great payment for chores done by your children, fun giveaways in pinatas or goodie bags or in a big pot on St. Patrick\'s Day to look like a pot of gold! Use your cent-ses and bring home some of these Milk Chocolate Gold Gelt Coins today!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/milk-chocolate-gold-coins---assorted-10lb_1.gif', '3770~milk-chocolate-gold-coins---assorted-10lb_1.gif', 'milk-chocolate-gold-coins-assorted'),
(3771, 'Pastel Blue Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'If Edgar Allen Poe had taken a bite of these amazing Pastel Blue Foil Hearts before writing The Tell Tale Heart, we\'re sure the outcome of that tale would have been much sweeter! That\'s because these little cardiovascular treats are pumping with so much chocolatey goodness that it will race through your veins and make you want to come back for more.Plus, with such a lovely blue foil wrapper, you\'ll fall in love with its exterior too. Bring some home for a Valentine\'s Day treat, birthday present candy stuffer, pinata candy, candy dish refills, or to put on top of baked goods and more!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/pastel-blue-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '3771~pastel-blue-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'pastel-blue-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(3772, 'Foil Covered Cherry Cordial', 84.99, '6', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Foil covered cherry cordials are the delectable treat that looks absolutely stunning! Whether you are planning a high class event or looking for a confection that will bring more elegance to your holiday gatherings, this is the easiest (and most delicious) choice!Each bite-sized morsel features a plump, round cherry in sweet liquid that\'s surrounded by fabulous chocolate. The combination of rich flavor and fruitiness is simply to die for!To add even more appeal to these handsome chocolates, each comes wrapped in a blanket of shimmering foil. Two distinct colors are available, including luxurious red and glimmering gold. No matter which you choose, each bite will offer a flavor experience your taste buds will remember!Our bulk cordial cherries are a must-have for winter events and much more! Use them to fill wedding favors or add them to a glass dish or jar to serve guests who happen by.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/foil-covered-cherry-cordial-6lbs_2.gif', '3772~foil-covered-cherry-cordial-6lbs_2.gif', 'foil-covered-cherry-cordial'),
(3773, 'Milk Chocolate Gold Coins Large', 128.99, '10', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Milk chocolate gold coins are sure to please guests at any event! This classic confection includes a basic coin shape. Each piece is made out of rich milk chocolate that forms a solid disc shape with smooth, straight sides and a wide top and bottom.A shimmering gold foil wrapper covers all sides, adding a luxurious touch that recreates the look of a real gold coin! Unlike real gold coins, these milk chocolate candies can satisfy even the most demanding sweet tooth. Our bulk milk chocolate coins are a great choice for events, parties and businesses.Use them as stocking stuffers or include them as treasure at a pirate party! Pour them into net bags or treat bags to give out as party favors. Chocolate coins are also a fun way to teach young children about currency and counting. Teachers can hand them out in the classroom while parents can keep them as a quick after school snack.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/i/milk-chocolate-gold-coins---large-10lb_1.gif', '3773~milk-chocolate-gold-coins---large-10lb_1.gif', 'milk-chocolate-gold-coins-large'),
(3774, 'Blue Foil Hearts Bulk', 109.99, '10', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Blue foil hearts are a simple chocolate candy with tons of potential. This delicious treat gets back to basics by providing a mouthful of gourmet chocolate. Instead of fillers and sugary fluff, you get right down to it with creamy, smooth chocolate!Every piece is molded to form a charming heart shape with rounded sides and a flat back. Even unwrapped, these chocolaty treats look beautiful with a smooth surface and recognizable shape. Anytime is a good time to serve up foil hearts candy! Each piece comes individually wrapped in shimmering blue foil to keep it fresh and enhance visual appeal.Simply peel away the thin foil and sink your teeth into this rich chocolate confection. Our blue heart candies are perfect for baby showers and wedding favors. Commemorate the arrival of a new little one or use them to sweeten someone\'s special birthday bash! We also carry other colors so you can create a custom chocolate heart mix for your event!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', '3774~blue-chocolate-foil-hearts-bulk_1.jpg', 'blue-chocolate-foil-hearts'),
(3775, 'Fort Knox Large Pennies', 13.99, '1', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Have you ever eaten a penny? Now you can with Fort Knoxâ€™s large penny chocolates! These candy coins look very realistic. Each piece includes a solid disc of delicious milk chocolate. The outside is covered by a copper foil wrapper with authentic U.S. penny detail. Peel back the foil and enjoy the sweet taste of Fort Knox candy. Our chocolate coins make learning about currency fun!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/o/fort_knox_large_pennies_-_1lb.jpg', '3775~fort_knox_large_pennies_-_1lb.jpg', 'fort-knox-large-pennies'),
(3776, 'Madelaine Milk Chocolate Basketballs', 55.99, '5', 'lb', 'foil-wrapped', 'Madelaineâ€™s milk chocolate basketballs will put more bounce in your candy dish. Each piece is made using high quality milk chocolate fashioned into a solid orb. The outside is smooth with a layer of orange foil on top. Black lines and text recreate the look of an actual basketball. Our bulk chocolate basketballs contains many delicious pieces that are convenient for team events, birthday parties, and much more!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/madelaine_milk_chocolate_basketballs_-_5lb.jpg', '3776~madelaine_milk_chocolate_basketballs_-_5lb.jpg', 'madelaine-milk-chocolate-basketballs'),
(3777, 'Gourmet Salt Water Taffy', 19.49, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'No one can resist the smooth texture and mouthwatering flavor of classic saltwater taffy! This nostalgic delight emerged from Atlantic City, NJ to become one of the most popular confections in the world. Often used in wedding favors or given as a special gift, saltwater taffy is sure to please any sweet tooth! Each individually wrapped piece includes rich molasses, sea salt and palm oil to produce that creamy taste experience that has everyone reaching for a second pieceâ€¦ or even a third and fourth!Saltwater taffy comes in a long list of delicious flavors, each featuring its own unique color. The many pastel hues, like yellow, pink and orange, harken back to this candy\'s seaside origins. You\'ll love sampling each distinct flavor, like caramel swirl or root beer float! Nothings better than a stroll along the boardwalk with watermelon or raspberry saltwater taffy. Explore our flavor list today and discover your new favorite beach snack!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/a/salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', '3777~salt-water-taffy-bulk-assorted-taffy-town-candystore-1024x1024-badge_1.jpg', 'salt-water-taffy-flavors'),
(3778, 'Key Lime Pie Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'When you pop a piece of key lime pie candy into your mouth, your taste buds will burst with citrus sweetness. It\'s like taking a trip to the beautiful, balmy Florida Keys without even leaving your home or office. These delicious green and white hard candies are perfect for any occasion, whether you want a refreshing tropical taste on a hot summer day or you want to remind yourself of the beach in the middle of winter.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/k/e/key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', '3778~key-lime-pie-hard-candy-medium-470x470_2.jpg', 'key-lime-pie-hard-candy'),
(3779, 'Spi C Mints Cinnamon Starlight Mints', 16.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'That hint of cinnamon flavor gives these mints a nice kick. Great for reception areas and front desks.  Big hit with customers and clients .. and bosses too. Many customers say these are similar to the ones they\'ve enjoyed at Pizza Hut. The red and white stripe makes them a perfect addition to a festive gingerbread house, in a candy dish around the holidays, or even tucked into your purse for a breath freshening treat whenever you need one. Get a bag of these today and make your candy wishes come true! Star light star bright, first star I see tonight. I wish I may, I wish I might, I wish I could try these minty star delights! You\'ll want to break out in rhyme every time you pop one of these Spi-C-Mints Cinnamon Starlights into your mouth.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/p/spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', '3779~spi-c-mints-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480_2.jpg', 'cinnamon-starlight-spi-c-mints'),
(3780, 'Jolly Ranchers Candy', 19.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Get ready for a dose of fruity happiness that can\'t be beat! This bulk bag of individually wrapped Jolly Ranchers have enough smile power to keep you grinning for days and days. Their inventive flavors and glossy, hard candy colors make these sweet treats one of the happiest in the world. In apple, blue raspberry, cherry, grape, and watermelon, you can bring some home to please every sweet tooth in your home. Jolly Ranchers have been around since 1897 and we\'re sure glad they\'re still here to give our mouths a rootin\' tootin\' good time. Grab yourself a bag today and make your mouths and hearts smile.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/o/jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', '3780~jolly-ranchers-alt2-470x470_1.jpg', 'jolly-rancher-bulk-candy'),
(3781, 'chocolate starlight mints thumbnail', 15.99, '', '', 'individually-wrapped', 'Chocolate starlight mints are a new and amazing take on a classic candy. Everyone loves the refreshing flavor of the traditional hard mint, now add chocolate.Starlight mints, which are also sometimes called pinwheel mints, feature a lovely white background with bold red stripes. Our chocolate starlight mints take that same elegant pattern and use it on a dark background with brilliant green stripes instead.Now you can enjoy that delicious minty taste with a touch of savory chocolate. Each round mint is crafted using solid hard candy. This allows them to provide the flavor candy lovers adore in a long lasting treat. Each mint is individually wrapped in clear plastic so you can admire their dark beauty before you open the first one up!Pour them into glass jars or candy dishes and serve to guests, use them in the office candy jar or make your gingerbread houses more unique with these tasty decorations!', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', '3781~chocolate-starlight-mints-candystore-480x480.jpg', 'chocolate-starlight-mints'),
(3782, 'Jaw Busters Jawbreakers', 17.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Don\'t bite down on one of these Jaw Busters Jawbreakers! These hard candies are great for savoring a ton of sweetness for a long time.Buy a bulk bag of Jaw Busters hard candies for the little ghouls and goblins coming around the neighborhood on Halloween, or keep them around when you\'re craving something sweet for yourself. You can keep a bag of Jawbreakers in a wide assortment of colors and flavors all year long.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/a/jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', '3782~jaw-busters-bulk-470x470.jpg', 'jaw-busters-jawbreakers-wrapped'),
(3783, 'Bulk Assorted Fruit Lollipops', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Lollipop, lollipop, oh lolli , lolli, lolli  Sorry, we\'re getting carried away with ourselves. It happens a lot here. It\'s just that we\'re so passionate about these scrumptious suckers that it makes us break out in song. They don\'t require a trip to the doctor and they come in bulk, so these pops are the perfect choice for any occasion. Stock up for your child\'s next party or put them in a jar on your desk for lucky coworkers to snack on. You\'ll quickly become a favorite in the office! With a light, sweet, fruity flavor, in a rainbow of colors, everyone can enjoy a mouthful of deliciousness.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/o/lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', '3783~lollipops-bulk-assorted-fruit-candystore-470x470.jpg', 'lollipops-bulk-fruit'),
(3784, 'Sour Fruit Balls Hard Candy', 15.99, '5', 'lb', 'individually-wrapped', 'Sour. Check. Colorful. Check. Fruity and delicious. Check, check! We\'ve got everything you need here for the makings of a great bulk candy selection.  Individually wrapped, these candies make tasty treats for parties, as filler candy, or just to have around the house for a qick fix of sweetness.With over 80 hard candies per pound, there\'s enough sweetness to treat all of your friends and family. Every time you snack from this bag, choose from yummy red, orange, yellow, green, and purple. Everyone who hears the crinkle of their wrappers will come running for more. And because of their perfect size, one after another can be enjoyed.', 'https://media.candystore.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/200x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/o/sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', '3784~sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy-alt3-470x470_1.jpg', 'sour-fruit-balls-hard-candy');
